name: Mutumutu
about:
Nejsme pojišťovna. Jsme technologický startup, který mění způsob pojištění života.

V Mutumutu měníme zastaralý model životního pojištění závislého na drahých a často nespolehlivých finančních poradcích. Oproti ostatním pojišťovnám se v Mutumutu vracíme k podstatě pojištění a zaměřujeme se na to, abyste byli zajištění hlavně vy. A i když jsme změnili pojištění života od základu, zachovali jsme to, proč se pojišťujete.

- Dorovnáme vám příjem peněz při dlouhodobé nemoci nebo úrazu.
- Nahradíme váš pravidelný příjem při invaliditě.
- Zajistíme vaše blízké v případě vaší smrti.

Mutumutu odměňuje klienty, kteří se zodpovědně starají o své zdraví, a vrací jim pravidelně až 30 % z pojistného. Sportujete, nekouříte, chodíte na preventivní prohlídky? Vrátíme vám spravedlivě část pojistného podle toho, jak se o sebe a svoje tělo staráte. Máte pak #mutumuturespekt 

____________________________________________________________________________________

EN
We're not an insurance company. We're a tech startup that changes the very principles of life insurance.

Our aim is to completely replace old life insurace models that are often reliant on financial advisors. Mutumutu returns to the basics, and focuses on you and your financial security. 

- Full income guarantee in case of illness and injuries.
- Full compensation of your income in case of disability.
- We'll take care of your relatives in case of death.

Mutumutu also rewards clients who maintain a healthy lifestyle by returning up to 30% of all installments. Excercise, do sports, don't smoke and attend regular  check-ups with your doctor, and we'll give you your money back. #mutumuturespekt

name: SUMM
about:
Our mission: Fostering inclusion by accelerating easy language adoption – making information universally accessible to everyone independent of cognitive abilities, education or linguistic proficiency.

Picture this: You probably look at stairs and recognize them as a convenient way to get to an elevated place. A physically impaired person, on the other hand, sees a huge barrier! And you probably read the news or company websites and get information out of them – but just as the stairs, their complexity can be a barrier – this time, a barrier to information.

For mentally handicapped, elderly or sick people, people with learning difficulties, or learners of a new language, a complex text can completely exclude them from information, because they simply can’t understand it. And with an ever increasing amount of information provided online, it is crucial to make it accessible to everyone. In Germany, over 10 million people rely on information being available in easy language – a style of language that follows specific patterns that make its structure and use of words easier to comprehend.

We are building the first AI-powered tool that automatically turns any text into easy language, fostering inclusion and breaking down information barriers at supersonic speed! We enable a variety of improvements:

- Translation agencies can increase their productivity by over 85% with our tool proposing a first translation they can build upon
- We support the public sector to comply with the barrier-free information technology (BITV) law by providing a tool to enable fast translation of new content
- We provide companies with an easy and convenient tool to communicate with customers in simple, understandable terms, e.g. for customer service, product descriptions, or terms of use

Die Corona-Pandemie hat den Wunsch nach mehr Vereinbarkeit von Beruf und Familie verstärkt. Wie ein Katalysator zeigte der Virus auf, wie sich die Arbeitswelt in Deutschland ändern muss, um weiterhin motivierte und produktive Mitarbeitende zu beschäftigen und damit einhergehend erfolgreiche Unternehmen zu führen. 

Die digitale Transformation schreitet voran, hybride Arbeitsmodelle sind in aller Munde. Home Office ist nur eines von vielen wichtigsten Benefits für Beschäftigte geworden. Familienfreundlichkeit ist ein Gut, das von immer mehr Mitarbeitenden gefordert wird. Bei der Wahl nach einem geeigneten Arbeitsplatz macht eine verankerte und gelebte Familienkultur den Unterschied zur Konkurrenz.
voiio bietet eine All-in-One-Lösung für zwei Probleme. Während die Plattform Mitarbeitenden hilft, Familie und Beruf in Einklang zu bringen, positioniert sich das jeweilige Unternehmen als besonders familienorientiert und steigert so den wirtschaftlichen Erfolg.

name: GENTWO
about: Your tailor-made issuance solution for financial products (Swiss ISIN)  Zurich-based innovative securitization specialist GENTWO has created a new generation of financial products. The innovative financial solutions provider enables institutional clients to securitize not only bankable, but also non-bankable assets with a Swiss ISIN.  Investing beyond borders, use the full potential markets can provide. Turn all your investment ideas into bankable/ conventional investment certificates.   Professional investors are now enabled to securitize bankable and (formerly) non-bankable assets (such as private equity, private debt, peer-to-peer lending, art, crypto assets, among others) on a balance sheet-neutral basis. New underlying assets can be securitized conventionally in so-called Swiss-compliant financial products with a Swiss ISIN code. It is a relatively new form of investment product that bridges the gap between the traditional and the new financial world.  Unique – modular – Swiss-compliant The focus on so-called off-balance-sheet investment products solves the problem of declining margins and growth barriers for many financial market players. It opens up new performance potential by creating access to a theoretically unlimited world of asset classes. Financial intermediaries, including banks, can even contribute to an overall better investment quality. They can use GENTWO's setup to not only realize own product, but also business innovations. When making others an innovator, GENTWO follows a modular and partner-oriented approach. GENTWO Digital is GENTWO’s subsidiary and a joint venture based in the Crypto Valley in Zug, Switzerland. It makes digital assets bankable and turns it into conventional securities.   Come visit GENTWO: www.g2fp.com and GENTWO Digital: www.g2d.io. Stay up to date! name: Supersheets
about:
To explore data effectively today, you need to be able to write SQL. Yet there are only millions of SQL developers versus billions of spreadsheet users doing data analysis every day! So despite all these incredible advances in data tooling, the humble front line knowledge worker is more disconnected from the data than ever before.

Supersheets is a search and spreadsheet tool that sits on top of your data warehouse. First, we connect to your data warehouse or any postgres database. We can then list out your tables and let you tag them with plain-english, e.g. “marketing” or “stripe” and view what’s in these table right in our explore view, unlike other data catalogs. You can then analyze data in our spreadsheet, with formulas and pivot tables compiling to SQL to run on the warehouse (coming soon). We also let you export to Google Sheets, letting users feed up-to-date data into their models. We know it’s not optimal but they’re doing it already, just manually!

But what about BI tools? They only work on pre-defined data and commercial teams aren’t comfortable using them. e.g. Hubspot internal survey says 10% of 3000 staff comfortable using BI.

But what about data teams? They feel the pinch too, they’re overworked (Ascend survey says 97% at or above capacity) and data requests are the least value-adding jobs they do.

No need to copy or move your data, Blossom prevents vendor lock-in.

Databloom is the federated AI, data access and analytics company that develops the federated and responsible AI engine "Blossom" to enable decentralized AI. It provides fast and interactive enterprise-ready distribution, consisting of additional tooling and configurations, enabling data scientists and analysts to run AI models and training against various decentralized data sources ranging in size from gigabytes to petabytes. name: IO-Dynamics
about:
⚡ Wir sind IO-Dynamics, ein Startup im Bereich der E-Mobilität und ansässig in Flensburg. Wir ermöglichen Unternehmen einen kostengünstigen, ökologischen und stressfreien Betrieb von E-Fahrzeugen, indem wir für sie die Herausforderungen beim Laden meistern. ⚡

UNSERE MISSION🌠
Wir wollen das E-Auto durch Vernetzung optimal in das Energiesystem eingliedern, um so den Übergang zur flächendeckenden E-Mobilität zu beschleunigen. Auf diese Weise wollen wir die E-Mobilität einfacher gestalten und einen entscheidenden Beitrag zur Mobilitäts- und Energiewende leisten.

UNSER PRODUKT 💥
Wir entwickeln und vertreiben IO-ELON, eine neuartige Software, die das Laden von E-Autos speziell in Unternehmensfuhrparks auf nachhaltige, verlässliche und effiziente Weise steuert und verwaltet. Durch Nutzung unterschiedlicher Datenquellen und abhängig von geplanten Fahrten, wird die optimale Energie zum richtigen Zeitpunkt für jedes Fahrzeug nachgeladen. Das Besondere dabei ist die Nutzung von Echtzeitdaten, welche mithilfe eines Telematik-Moduls erhoben werden.
 
UNSER ANSPRUCH 🌍
Nachhaltigkeit liegt uns sehr am Herzen. Durch die maximal schonende Behandlung der Akkus können wertvolle Ressourcen länger verwendet werden. IO-ELON streicht typische Bedenken wie Reichweite, Batteriegesundheit oder Ladestand und gestaltet den Betrieb der E-Autos transparent, verlässlich und kostengünstig.

name: IO-Dynamics
about:
⚡ Wir sind IO-Dynamics, ein Startup im Bereich der E-Mobilität und ansässig in Flensburg. Wir ermöglichen Unternehmen einen kostengünstigen, ökologischen und stressfreien Betrieb von E-Fahrzeugen, indem wir für sie die Herausforderungen beim Laden meistern. ⚡

UNSERE MISSION🌠
Wir wollen das E-Auto durch Vernetzung optimal in das Energiesystem eingliedern, um so den Übergang zur flächendeckenden E-Mobilität zu beschleunigen. Auf diese Weise wollen wir die E-Mobilität einfacher gestalten und einen entscheidenden Beitrag zur Mobilitäts- und Energiewende leisten.

UNSER PRODUKT 💥
Wir entwickeln und vertreiben IO-ELON, eine neuartige Software, die das Laden von E-Autos speziell in Unternehmensfuhrparks auf nachhaltige, verlässliche und effiziente Weise steuert und verwaltet. Durch Nutzung unterschiedlicher Datenquellen und abhängig von geplanten Fahrten, wird die optimale Energie zum richtigen Zeitpunkt für jedes Fahrzeug nachgeladen. Das Besondere dabei ist die Nutzung von Echtzeitdaten, welche mithilfe eines Telematik-Moduls erhoben werden.
 
UNSER ANSPRUCH 🌍
Nachhaltigkeit liegt uns sehr am Herzen. Durch die maximal schonende Behandlung der Akkus können wertvolle Ressourcen länger verwendet werden. IO-ELON streicht typische Bedenken wie Reichweite, Batteriegesundheit oder Ladestand und gestaltet den Betrieb der E-Autos transparent, verlässlich und kostengünstig.

about:

This ensures economic efficiency, but also scalability. KEYOU-inside technology can be used both ON THE ROAD and OFF THE Road. 
The further development of the classic combustion engine by KEYOU to use hydrogen as a sustainable fuel thus allows a quantum leap in propulsion development. The combination of high efficiency and power density achieves a completely new level. In the end, only harmless water vapor escapes as exhaust gas. The ideal solution for the commercial vehicle sector, with which engine and vehicle manufacturers can offer emission-free vehicles to their customers. The new "green" combustion engine with KEYOU-inside technology means zero emissions, efficiency and cost-efficiency at the same time - without any compromises in performance, payload or range. With KEYOU, "Sustainable Zero Emission" becomes reality.

name: Didimo (Techstars London 2016)
about:
Didimo is the world’s leading provider of fast, automated solutions for the generation of high-quality real-time digital human avatars. Our platform allows companies, software developers, collaboration platforms, and app builders to integrate a fast, robust, and reliable solution for generating user characters in their own software solutions.

We are your virtual human technology solution provider, with our RESTful API allowing our services to be fully integrated into a product or service.

Our proprietary and flexible pipeline can translate various image-based inputs of a user’s face, and using automated machine vision, topology generation, texturing, and rigging components, to output a real-time ready high fidelity avatar.  These are set up to be perfectly suited for real-time engines - and include a full facial animation system and text-to-speech animation capability.

Didimo is led by founder and CEO Verónica Orvalho, PhD, whose career at the cutting edge of research in computer graphics has uncovered many new ways to interact virtually, instilling trust and empathy in digital communication. Her inventions have been used by Universal Studios, Sony, Microsoft, and Amazon as well as in European and Portuguese funded research projects.

Didimo is on a mission to allow technology to feel more human - enabling the richness of human communication to enhance every virtual interaction.

name: IAMIP
about:
IamIP has digitalized one of the last few paper-based and manually handled industries, the complex intellectual property industry. This industry is plagued by complexity with over 2.7 M new patents filed every year (growing), and $20Bn+ is lost in double work in R&D in Europe alone. IamIP’s platform enables technology based companies to easily overview and evaluate their intellectual property portfolios, monitor competition and get valuable strategic insights – in time - for determining decision-making in innovation.

Trusted by the world’s most innovative companies, IamIP’s Intellectual Property platform provides a secure, web-based portal for centrally managing all published patents worldwide – from the published individual patents to setting up search alerts, sharing, commenting, monitoring, collaborating and more. With robust analytics, IP departments and business units can make informed strategic decisions about what, where and when to take important action; i.e. filing a patent application opposition, acquire a company or technology, or to develop a new technology with a thorough understanding of financial implications of such decisions, their potential risks and opportunities for maximizing value in intellectual property. 

By using innovative big data functionality IamIP has successfully developed ground-breaking visualization possibilities of patent data that will provide you with strategic actionable insights in one single click. The IamIP platform is the most user-friendly platform on the market, where you can share documents and tasks with colleagues, request feedback including automatic reminders, saved communication history and much more - all in one click.  Say goodbye to xls files and emails; with IamIP you and your colleagues will have everything in one place.

about:

Leading operators, infrastructure owners and network integrators including Bouygues Telecom, Sogetrel and Swisscom use Deepomatic to connect subscribers more reliably, lower the cost of compliance, improve quality of experience and drive long-term infrastructure ROI.

 
Through our products, we allow operational managers to create custom AI solutions and operate them at scale in as little as three months and without prior coding knowledge. 

In their restaurants, the Compass Group, a world leader in contract foodservice, has implemented a checkout system identifying and pricing each item on the meal tray, in real-time. This results in increased productivity, less waste, and enhanced guest experience in every restaurant.

Suez controls the quality of waste-sorting while Emovis now introduce free-flow technology to its motorway networks.

Als erste Progressive Web App bieten wir Handwerkern das beste Cloud Erlebnis am Markt.

Our damage appraisal relies on both human assessment and artificial intelligence - leveraging on a database of thousands of claims to ensure that our clients get the best price on their repairs.

Our prices are guaranteed - once we have done the assessment, if required, we will source a repairer from one of the thousands of independent professionals on our marketplace.

The majority of Axioma repairers will be able to carry out the work at your home location. Alternatively, they can arrange for your car to be collected and delivered back to you once the work is complete.

name: Contester
about:
We believe that website experience should be as engaging as watching Netflix. So we built Contester; Many-to-many video technology that enables personalized and scalable co-browsing and guided shopping solutions on any website. 

Ecommerce web shopping experience hasn't changed much over two decades when compared to how social platforms changed users' perceptions. 80% of users prefer personalized shopping experience and 64% prefer video shopping. Contester bridges the gap between social commerce and directory-based website experience. We built a browsable video technology that can be embedded on any eCommerce website, to enhance the shopping experience that drives sales.
Contester format enables personalized video shopping experiences that are impossible with available one-to-one and one-to-many live shopping. 

Contester is built to drive sales but eCommerce isn't only about short-term sales: 
- It improves customer experience to make more confident purchase decisions resulting in fewer returning items and less customer support. 
- It helps brands to reduce customer acquisition costs with cookieless personalization. 
- It helps marketing teams to get a higher return on content marketing and influencer partnerships. 
- And finally, the enhanced shopping experience improves brand loyalty and CLV in long term.


Start with a free forever plan

about:
“Excel is everywhere, and with Airrange it's for everyone.”

Airrange is a no-code platform for collaboration and productivity. Our mission: We want to give collaboration a new perspective. Airrange frees data from container applications and makes it flexibly available where and when it's needed. To prove it, we start with the most widely used business software Excel.

Here’s how working with Airrange will upgrade your Excel collaboration in Microsoft 365
• Share only what’s relevant – granular sharing of elements instead of spreadsheets
• Help others work intuitively with your spreadsheets and avoid errors
• Add interactive pivot, kanban, grid, check list, calendar and map views
• Mix live elements from multiple Excel sources to create stunning reports
• Work with Excel everywhere – it’s great on mobile
• Share any element by email, link, by app, or integrated in Teams & Co
• Always know what’s happening in your workbooks - KPI trends and change history on multi-workbook dashboards

Airrange has a unique technology setting that helps you to keep working with your existing Excel solution. 
• Realtime collaboration on the original Excel file (no redundancy, no sync, no conflicts)
• 100% Excel 365 compatibility
• App interfaces on-top of Excel (no-code, more productivity, less errors)
• No installation / no obstacles / share with a link
• Respects full user-rights and compliance from Microsoft 365 (easy for admins)
• Only solution that supports co-editing and story-telling
• All data remains inside the existing Excel/Office environment

Read more or try free on www.airrange.io 

Don’t forget to let us know what you think on www.airrange.io/start-trial

Boxmotions es el primer centro logístico de España especializado en la distribución, almacenamiento y manipulación de productos voluminosos con servicios de montaje y desmontaje incluidos.
Centralizamos los requerimientos logísticos como un solo punto de contacto, eliminando la necesidad de múltiples proveedores de almacenaje y transporte. 
Nos especializamos en transporte de voluminosos, como si de paquetería se tratara, mejorando la experiencia last-mile de tus usuarios finales.
Gestionamos tu stock con nuestro software de tecnología avanzada, para que puedas contar con información en tiempo real del estado de todos tus pedidos, facturación consolidada en un sólo punto y con una estructura transparente.
Boxmotions en tu partner logístico. Haz crecer tu negocio, nosotros nos encargamos del resto.

about: At KeenCorp, we know that you want to be a confident leader. In order to do that, you need better information to avoid surprises. We understand this dilemma of looking at what the currently available data is telling you versus going with your instinct. That’s why our customers use our AI platform based on 30 years of research.

name: WINGCOPTER
about:
Wingcopter’s core innovation is its unique tilt-rotor mechanism. 
It ensures a smooth and robust transition between hovering like a multicopter and efficient forward flying like an airplane. Engineered by our dedicated team in Germany, we have patented it in all major markets across the world.

The current version, the WINGCOPTER 178, is designed to carry up to 6 kilograms of additional payload, covers great distances of up to 120 kilometers and sets the benchmark for commercial VTOL drones, with a world-speed-record of 240 km/h.
The WINGCOPTER can be flown autonomously or in position control mode.

Delivering medical commodities to remote health facilities as well as parcels and food to private customers via WINGCOPTER – we create technologies to save and improve lives, as our vision is to create a better tomorrow for everyone by building the future of aviation.

name: Babelforce
about:
We started babelforce in 2013 because we’d seen how many broken processes existed in the contact center. Why should customers always struggle to get good service?

After looking around for a platform that could fix those processes – and simplify service – we realized that the product just didn’t exist.

So, we made it ourselves. babelforce’s goal is to make customer service easy – for customers, for agents and for you. Our No-Code platform makes it simple to create and evolve any customer service process, in a matter of days or even hours.

You don’t need coding skills to use babelforce; you can create your ideal customer solutions using intuitive visual tools. What’s more, those solutions will work across all your core systems because babelforce integrates with everything – literally.

Whether you’re focused on inbound, outbound, multichannel or self-service, you can create what you need with babelforce.

To do this, the team relies on intuitive operation and innovative technology that is already being used successfully in other industries. The result is a platform that enables flexible use and easy integration for the entire construction industry.

name: Virtual Office for Teams

Creating the next generation of a digital HQ for teams.

name: Butter Solutions
about:
Butter is re-engineering salary for hourly paid & gig workers by helping them make the most out of their salary. 
We enable them to access their salary as soon as they earn it, but then also give them the tools to reach their financial goals. 

We have a belief that creating a direct link between work and pay through real-time salary will fundamentally shift the way we think about work and our motivation for working.

We also believe thinking about money is hard, and that there are a lot of things we can do with behavioural design to make it easier. Thus we work in an extremely customer-centric way to create products that are helpful, fun to use but also change the way we think about work and pay.

Employers get a more motivated workforce, who are more likely to take shifts and can save their finance / HR teams a lot of time by ensuring their employees always understand which shifts they are getting paid for at which times.

We are a venture-backed company, backed by Founders who have built fantastic companies such as Pleo and Kontist.

name: Stashbee
about:
Space has never been at such a premium, and we live in an era where people have more belongings than ever before. Stashbee aims to reinvent the way we store stuff for the sharing economy generation.

Our easy-to-use platform connects individuals & businesses who have spare space (garages, spare rooms, parking spaces, warehouses) with those who need it (private and business storage, parking, warehousing). Think of it as Airbnb for storage.

For our Guests, we offer secure, vetted, local spaces at affordable prices. Meanwhile we empower our Hosts with an easy way to earn additional income.

Our world-class website automates the end-to-end booking process, seamlessly processes payments, and offers a powerful and easy-to-use dashboard for Guests and Hosts to interact and manage bookings. We make the process safe and secure by running ID checks. We also provide insurance, which is powered by Guardhog and underwritten by Hiscox and is specifically designed for peer-to-peer storage, to cover people's stored items.

name: Garentii
about:
Let’s face it! Paying a rental cash deposit is just not fun and is one of the most inefficient uses of capital. 

Garentii removes the frustration of cash deposit for tenants with a simple and super easy digital rent deposit insurance starting from as little as €3.00 per month, or the price of a latte! Landlords win too with Garentii’s deposit management software, which allows them to invite their tenants in a few clicks and manage all their rental deposits in one single place while getting industry-leading deposit protection. The app offers a seamless user experience and simplifies the rental process for both landlords and tenants. 

Our mission is to make renting easy, simple and accessible for everyone!

Learn more at www.garentii.com

about:
7Learnings helps retailers to upgrade to the leading pricing technology. Our solution uses advanced machine learning models to forecast demand for different price points with high accuracy. With our powerful self-learning algorithms, retailers can increase their profitability and revenues by up to 10%. We offer the most intuitive way to steer prices. Our prices simply maximize the business goals set by our clients. Our solution is easy to integrate and offers a high return on investment. 

Benefits for our customers
 • Up to 10% more profit & revenue

 • Easy to use web-based software interface

Chatwerk.

name: Klamo
about:
After three insightful MVP iterations, we developed our own marketplace system in less than six months. 
 
Our tech stack forms a scalable and bulletproof basis for our data platform - our next-gen analytics tool to identify promising designers for acquisition. 
We will collect more than 100m data points per year from users interacting with our marketplace and recognize trends with density-based spatial clustering. Our machine-learning algorithms are designed to benchmark key metrics, such as click-through-rates, and evaluate the performance of each designer - Autonomously and continuously. The proprietary recommender engine will react almost in real-time and boost the visibility of small designers on the marketplace. This is supported through a direct, API-based integration to online marketing tools.
 
We use state-of-the-art open source technologies & frameworks and agile development practices to ship and fail fast, facilitate collaboration and always stay on top of innovation.

name: Niikiis
about: niikiis is an HR tech company that helps employees do their job better.  With a plug&play intuitive employee experience platform, we enable digitalization and automation of HR processes, saving time and money, boosting engagement and performance at company and individual level.  We believe in memorable employee experiences that drive success:  - Centralize employee information and records in one place.  - Manage relevant employee documents and content in employee profiles. - Build powerful connections among your employees. - Keep your team in sync with organizational charts. - Set up onboarding paths for each one of your new hires, quickly, easy and effectively by automating the entire process so they turn into confident, knowledgeable and motivated employees.  - Easily manage your employees’ holidays, absences and working hours with niikiis' time tracking and abscence management tool. - Publish formative and informative content in our authoring tool. Micro-learning enables employees to quickly close a small knowledge or skill gap. - Accelerate employee performance and development in real time by accessing unbiased, timely and frequent multi-perspective feedback surveys. - Improve real time decision making by leveraging employee data and easily interpret it via our dashboards. - Automate employees' performance evaluations. about:
Bringoz, Demand Driven Logistics Platform
Elastic logistics | Customer Centric |  Last Mile |  On-Demand 

Bringoz is a technology platform for demand-driven logistics, streamlining the logistics processes in general and the last-mile in particular, we provide our customers with a robust infrastructure enabling them to compete in today's demand-driven landscape. We’ve built the Bringoz SaaS platform to answer the needs of a complex logistics operation, to build and scale a flexible infrastructure utilizing internal and external assets, designed to maximize efficiency and lower operating costs.

Bringoz is a holistic ecosystem, a modular SaaS technology platform for enterprise, providing end-to-end solutions to logistics-oriented businesses. The platform serves a wide variety of industries: e-commerce, retailers, food, CPG, FMCG, pharmaceuticals, automotive and freight, with the emphasis on last mile, and synchronizes between the various needs of the different parties involved (shippers, carriers, customers, stakeholders and drivers) to create a balanced, cost-effective and productive eco-system.
 
Bringoz provides real-time elastic capabilities, with strategic value and creates an optimal and superior delivery solution to streamline operations, maximize assets and lower operational costs, all while achieving maximum efficiency.

Interested to learn more? Leave your information at https://bringoz.com/demo

name: Connfair
about:
With a young and motivated team, the start-up Connfair is working on smart solutions for the digital management of fairs and conferences with the Connfair event platform.

Ticketing and admission management can be elegantly managed with our software solution since 2018. At the beginning of 2019, we also applied for a patent for a compatible hardware solution, the access gate. With this, efficiency and flexibility of admission control are greatly increased.

In the corona crisis we reacted quickly and developed solutions for automatic people counting and admission control. Our entry light as well as our counter app help event managers, administrations and supermarkets to survive the time of contact restrictions as successfully and healthy as possible.

Our long-term vision is to develop an algorithm based on artificial intelligence. This is supposed to analyze large amounts of data in order to automatically identify successful event management strategies and transfer them to other events - from the choice of the location to the sending of invitations to the successful approach to visitors on site. 

With the development of such an intelligent algorithm, the Connfair founders are ready to revolutionize the event industry, take on the competition with large tech companies and respond quickly and flexibly to challenges during and beyond the corona crisis.

Unique Branding

name: Aisot
about: Aisot GmbH ("AISignals and Operations in Trading") is developping algorithms for data analytics and predictive analytics.  Decision makers need signals from newly emerging types of raw data in order to take informed decisions. aisot provides reliable and transparent signals based on state- of-the-art research and technology. In times of skills shortages and high costs, aisot offers agility, efficiency and expertise to cut down on time and costs to go from raw data to trade and investment decisions.  Initially focusing on the crypto and traditional financial markets, we are convinced that there is a high potential for scaling our solutions to other areas showing a need for advanced (predictive) analytics.

name: Dynamic e flow
about:
dynamic E flow (DEF) is a Bavarian-based high-tech start-up company with strong electric engineering expertise founded in 2014. Based on extensive development work, a revolutionary wire and cooling method for coils has been developed which doubles the power of machines and is a broad enabler for machines in mobility and atomization. As a next step DEF is focusing on markets for the delivery of a maximum value, in order to transform the DEF technology into valuable products for satisfied costumer. DEF is focusing on electric motors for mobility and automation.

dynamic E flow GmbH provides new electric machine technology which reduces costs and increases power, meeting the industry's cost objectives. Our direct cooling technology capcooltech® doubles the power density of e-machine and massively reduces cost per kW of output. Capcooltech® system is composed of an electric motor with capcooltech®-wire-coils and a capcooltech® box, a coolant pump, heat exchanger and a control unit. 

Comprehensive IP strategy with 2 granted patents and 6 patent application. 

The initial market focus is on the most rapidly growing market segment (48V vehicle propulsion systems and commercial vehicle) where the innovation is "irresistible" - getting more power ar lower cost.
 
Preliminary (non-exclusive) negotiations with leading companies. 

>>> The project receives a funding from the EU Horizon 2020 Research & Innovation Programme under the grant agreement No. 804219.

>>> Winner of eMove360° Award 2018

>>> Member of BEM - Bundesverband eMobilität, Germany

>>> Winner of Handelsblatt Energy Award 2019

name: Aequitec
about: Aequitec is a register serving founders and investors. For registered shares it assists clients in recording ownership unambiguously via automated processing of all relevant corporate actions.

name: EASI Control
about:
Als dreiköpfiges Gründerteam beginnt die Geschichte von EASI Control im März 2020. Ausschlaggebend war die Ambition der Ideengeberin und heutigen Geschäftsführerin Monja Meier. Auf der vergeblichen Suche nach einer einfachen und dennoch umfassenden Möglichkeit für die beschwerlichen Wege des Arbeitsschutzes innerhalb der Bauindustrie, fasste sie den Entschluss, selbst eine Lösung zu schaffen. 

Seitdem arbeitet das gesamte Team an der Digitalisierung von Arbeitsschutzverwaltung. Tagtäglich suchen und finden wir bei EASI Control digitale Lösungen und bieten dadurch enorme Arbeitserleichterung in der Verwaltung und Umsetzung von Arbeitsschutzmaßnahmen. Unsere stationäre PC-Anwendung bietet in Kombination mit der mobilen App das digitale Gesamtpaket für den Arbeitsschutz im Baugewerbe. Mit unserer Software lassen sich nicht nur Geräte und Mitarbeiter verwalten, sondern auch Prüfungen und Gefährdungsbeurteilungen, sowie Unterweisungen und Beinahe-Unfälle. In formlosen Kurzunterweisungen, sogenannten Toolbox Meetings, können aktuelle Themen aufgefrischt und diskutiert werden. Die Last-Minute-Risikoabfrage erinnert daran, alle eventuellen Risiken an der Arbeitsstätte zu prüfen. Über unsere mobile App gelangt der Arbeitsschutz vor Ort auf die Baustelle, der Fokus der Beschäftigten wird zusätzlich geschärft und Unfällen wird vorgebeugt. 
EASI Control bewahrt vor dem Papierkrieg, macht automatisch auf Handlungsbedarf aufmerksam, sorgt für Sicherheit im Unternehmen und spart dabei Zeit und Geld -  das Ganze einfach in der Anwendung und gesatzeskonform in der Umsetzung.

name: ArgumenText
about: With summetix (formerly ArgumenText), customers are able to directly access decision-critical pieces of information. With our deep-learning-based solution (an international patent is already under application) arguments, containing highly relevant hints to product failures are directly filtered out of large customer feedback streams. With clustering approaches, the information is further aggregated, so that changes in the data streams are instantly visible to the user.

name: Déclique
about:
Podcast sur l'amélioration continue, le Declique du Lean : https://smartlink.ausha.co/le-declique-du-lean

Chez Declique, nous voulons vivre dans un monde où la production est locale, où ce qu’on achète ne vient pas de l’autre bout du monde.
OÙ LE MADE IN FRANCE EST ACCESSIBLE.

Pour cela, nous sommes convaincus qu’il faut aider les usines Françaises à réduire leurs coûts de fabrication, en investissant dans des outils/processus de production plus performants.

Nous sommes aussi convaincus que la performance passe avant tout par les opératrices(eurs) de l’usine. Ils sont au cœur de l’action, ils connaissent bien les problèmes puisqu’ils les subissent tous les jours.

Notre mission, c’est de vous aider à résoudre leurs problèmes, pour augmenter la performance de votre usine et rentre le made in France plus accessible.

name: Marta
about:
In an effort to address growing shortages in the elderly care markets, marta's self-service platform allows families and caregivers to find and connect with their optimal counterparts. Supported by a data-driven approach to matching, the platform brings more transparency and fairness to a market traditionally dominated by inefficient and expensive intermediaries.

We believe that everyone has the right to receive adequate care and to age in dignity. We also fight to empower caregivers and to ensure they can provide their invaluable services in fair working conditions and for adequate compensation.

We care deeply about providing the best possible experience to all involved parties.

name: WMT
about:
WMT targets the proteotoxic stress response / UPR to shut down cancer cell metabolism. This limits tumor autonomous growth and lowers intratumoral lactate to stimulate the immune system to re-attack the tumor.
Our TOBY program is a combination of targeted chemotherapy with an immunooncology approach, casted into a single small molecule.

name: SkipCash
about:
SkipCash is a mobile payment app that offers a convenient and enjoyable experience
throughout the payments journey for both consumers and merchants. The app enables
consumers to make digital payments using a proprietary QR code thereby reducing the need for
cash, physical cards, and Point-Of-Sale (POS) devices. SkipCash also allows consumers to link
their card securely to use it in all their transactions, monitor their spending via visual spending
reports, organize their payments receipts, enable virtual account for kids & family members, and
access to merchants’ vouchers & coupons.

name: SipInk
about: SIPINK is a world leading White Label VoIP soft switch and Hosted PBX platform that empowers phone solution providers to maximise their profits and provide services globally for ROI.   With global redundancy, infinite scalability and unbelievable call quality.  We ARE:  1. Cost Effective 2. Reliable 3.  Wholesale VoiP Aggregator 4. Customer Solution Oriented 5. Cloud-based Unified Communications as a Service (UCaaS)   As a Reseller based company; and client leads we get, are instantly passed on to the clients.

name: Spaceos
about: Dynamic and flexible workspaces are shaping the future of work. They require an operating system that connects all stakeholders, reduces costs, provides insights and offers smart management tools. SpaceOS provides transparency, cost efficiency and real-time information while focusing on the personal experience.   SpaceOS is the most beautiful and easy to use tenant experience and management software on the market. It turns workspaces into digital products tenants love by making daily activities faster and more efficient. Resource booking, payments, food ordering, facility support blend seamlessly into daily workflows and come with a great user experience.  SpaceOS offers a smart, simple and intuitive web and mobile app that helps communities grow. Operators get an easy tool to engage communities with news, events and push notifications in a non-invasive way. Finding a business partner, freelancer or friends is at members fingertips.   Operators usually struggle with making use of workspaces more effective and lowering operational costs. SpaceOS provides real-time desk and conference room booking that enables more flexible working environment. The use of space can be planned ahead by both tenants and operators.   SpaceOS is a holistic management system, which covers both management and user side. Smartphones are turned into ‘workplace remote controls’. Because of a modular structure spaceOS is ready to integrate with a variety of platforms to meet the specific requirements of any workspace infrastructure.

name: Applysia UG (haftungsbeschränkt)
about: Mit Applysia entfalten Sie das volle Potential Ihres Assessments. Durch unsere Software steigern Sie Transparenz und Objektivität und garantieren so einen validen, effizienten und fairen Assessment-Prozess auf jeder Ebene.

name: Yoona Technology
about: yoona.ai  an Artificial Intelligence-based B2B software solution, which shortens the value chain of the fashion industry to one click and furthermore the possibility to create individual designs which is  extended by using personal sports data. yoona.ai pursues the vision of holistic digitization and is committed to encourage conscious consumption and drive sustainability through the automation of the design process.

name: Prewarp
about: Bring data and Machine learning into your product decisions, improving price setting, enabling real time sell-through forecasts and optimising markdown investments.

name: WorkHeld
about: Workheld combines digital workflows with remote support via data glasses or video calls in one platform. With endless integration options to ERP, PLM and IoT, technicians, workers and engineers are ideally supported in the field and documentation is automated. Individual branding and customising make Workheld the one and only platform for our customers' manufacturing, assembly, service and maintenance processes.

name: KAZUAR
about:
KAZUAR is a one-of-a-kind intelligence grade security solution that protects organizations against the most advanced and sophisticated state-grade attacks. 

The KAZUAR solution provides a holistic “immune system” with redesigned secure hardware, software and cryptographic connectivity to enable secure convenient anywhere operations on the most sensitive business intellectual property.

name: FAUME
about:
NOTRE MISSION : Engager les marques et leurs clients dans la construction d'une économie circulaire.

Le marché de l'occasion augmente 24 fois plus vite que celui du commerce traditionnel et devrait atteindre 51 milliards de dollars en 2023. Sa croissance est la preuve d'un changement systémique de modèle avec déjà plus de 33 % de la génération des Millenials qui achète de la seconde main.

La plateforme technologique et logistique de Faume (www.faume.co) fournit une solution en marque blanche de A à Z pour les marques qui sont prêtes à reprendre ce marché aux plateformes concurrentes actuelles. Faume permet aux marques d'atteindre de nouveaux clients et d'approfondir les relations existantes, tout en développant des pratiques commerciales circulaires plus durables.

-------------

OUR MISSION : Engaging brands and their customers in the construction of a circular economy.

The second-hand market is growing 24 times faster than the traditional retail market and is expected to reach $51 billion by 2023. Its growth is proof of a systemic change with already more than 33% of the Millenials generation buying second-hand.

Faume's technology and logistics platform (www.faume.co) provides a white label solution from start to finish for brands that are ready to take over this market from current competing platforms. Faume enables brands to reach new customers and deepen existing relationships, while developing more sustainable circular business practices.

name: CrossEngage
about:
CrossEngage is a Customer Data and Prediction Platform that enables marketers and CRM managers to grow their customer base into valuable relationships. 

To stay in their customer's consideration set and increase CLV, brands need to focus on creating an exceptional experience for every single customer. We are convinced that the smart leveraging of customer data is the key to achieving this.

Therefore, we combine a real-time solution for customer data and cross-channel campaign management with advanced AI and AutoML methods. This allows all first-party customer data to be intelligently analyzed and used for engaging campaigns and unique customer journeys to maximize customer lifetime value (CLV). 360° views of every single customer, tailored, customer value-oriented predictive audiences, and their activation across all systems and channels enable optimal customer experiences and foster long-term customer relationships.

name: LemonOne
about:
Here at LemonOne, we believe that high-quality images have the power to disrupt the online market. Whether used in real estate, hotels, or food delivery services, appealing photos improve the viewer’s experience and increase online sales across all industries. 

Our mission is to create a platform that benefits both, companies and photographers. As one of the leading companies in the European photo industry, we take advantage of an extensive network of professionals and employ intelligent processes to effectively match companies and photographers. 

For the businesses, this means an incredibly convenient way of booking photo shoots. For the photographers, it’s a way of filling their time capacities with additional offers. This results in more time for the photographers to focus on their passion and it allows companies to work on their core business, booking the visual content on-demand.

The LemonOne team is a tightly-knit group of creative thinkers with a warm company culture. We work hard, have fun while doing it, we challenge each other and grow together. Our aim is to the world of photography to the next level - one photo shoot at a time.

Is your company looking to optimise their visual content? Are you a talented photographer in search for more job opportunities? Or perhaps you’re an enthusiastic person who lives and breathes photography, and you’d like to join the LemonOne squad. Get in touch at www.lemonone.com!

name: Synctive
about:
La plateforme Synctive permet une entrée facile, sûre et efficace dans les modèles économiques basés sur l'utilisation, tels que l'Equipment-as-a-Service et le Pay-per-Use.
Les fabricants d'équipements obtiennent un avantage concurrentiel en offrant à leurs clients une flexibilité maximale dans l'utilisation de leurs machines.  Cela permet d'augmenter sensiblement les marges et d'ouvrir de nouveaux marchés et groupes de clients. Le besoin d'une grande disponibilité et d'une grande flexibilité des machines est entièrement satisfait, de sorte que la satisfaction des clients augmente considérablement. 
Le passage d'un modèle d'entreprise centré sur le produit à un modèle centré sur le client conduit à une amélioration significative de la fidélité des clients et à des relations à long terme basées sur la confiance.
Synctive joue le rôle de facilitateur technologique, en assurant un accès sécurisé aux données d'utilisation des machines. En termes simples, Synctive transforme les données d'utilisation des machines en données de facturation validées.
Notre plateforme comprend toutes les fonctionnalités nécessaires à la gestion de l'Equipment-as-a-Service et du financement par paiement à l'usage. 

Les fonctionnalités principales sont : 
 ➝ Machine Connector
 ➝ Digital Machine File
 ➝ Fichier journal du service
 ➝ Gestion de la flotte
 ➝ Moteur de tarification
 ➝ Gestion des contrats
 ➝ Tableau de bord des ventes
 ➝ Tableau de bord de la comptabilité
 ➝ Générateur de preuves d'utilisation

Synctive - La plateforme de bout en bout pour les modèles économiques du futur.

name: cirplus
about:
cirplus is the global marketplace for recyclates and plastic waste feedstock. Our team and technical partners have extensive experience in the manufacturing & recycling of thermoplastics. We know from first hand what it takes to build digital platforms and bring them to scale. We are 100% independent and guard strict neutrality in our work. We are based in Germany, but our ambitions are truly global.

We are on a mission to make buying and selling recycled plastics easier and more efficient than ever before. We accomplish this goal with our next generation B2B-marketplace, connecting the plastic & recycling industries. Transparency, global reach, and standard-setting are just a few of the features that cirplus provides.

Our vision is to make plastics 100% circular. We are only satisfied the moment no more plastics enters the environment, keeping this valuable material in the loop. To this end, we serve as the digital catalyst of the circular economy. With our work, we will lover the transaction costs for recycled plastics and thus massively reduce the environmental footprint of plastics overall. Let’s make plastic waste history!

name: ing+
about: ing+ supports municipalities and their service providers in unleashing their data potential. Through automation and artificial intelligence, we simplify processes, minimize errors and enable better decisions for our customers.

name: neuroflash
about:
neuroflash’s AI powered marketing copy creation software helps marketing teams create highly effective short copy at scale – smarter, more intuitive and efficient.

neuroflash supports human creativity with AI-backed performance prediction, resulting in proven better performance and ultimately in more confident copywriters.

Since 2016, we have been on a mission to drive brand equity along the marketing value chain towards consistent operational execution by applying Big Data, optimized Natural Language Processing, and Neuromarketing science.

Today over 30 enterprise customers in more than 20 countries use neuroflash award-winning software, services and support to transform the way they communicate their brand values with the world. 

We make copywriters more confident: We encourage creativity by validating your copy impact with a predictive performance and brand-fit score before you actually publish the copy. Our generated copy delivers proven better performance and results in higher self-confidence of our users.

name: erste hausverwaltung
about:
Die Erste Hausverwaltung ist von Mietern und Eigentümern mit dem Ziel gegründet, Hausverwaltung aus Kundensicht neu, digital und modern zu gestalten. Wir setzen bei Verwaltung von Wohnungen und in der direkten Zusammenarbeit mit Ihnen als Kund:in oder Mieter:in auf einen persönlichen Service und digitale Arbeitsweisen. So ist Hilfe genau dann für Sie erreichbar, wenn Sie sie brauchen.

Im Gegensatz zu voll-digitalen Verwaltungen ist es aus unserer Erfahrung unerlässlich, dass unser Team nicht bloß zur Problemlösung, sondern auch zur Vorsorge regelmäßig bei Ihnen vor Ort ist.

Unsere Mitarbeiter:innen sind sich der Verantwortung bewusst, den Wert Ihrer Immobilie langfristig zu erhalten, gleichzeitig aber auch das Wohl der Bewohner:innen nicht zu vernachlässigen. 

Inzwischen betreut unser engagiertes Team von über 15 Mitarbeiter:innen mehr als  1.500 Miet- und Eigentumswohnungen in der Region Köln-Düsseldorf.

Unsere Dienstleistungen

Als Immobilienverwaltung für Wohnimmobilien sind wir auf die technische, wirtschaftliche und rechtliche Betreuung von Miet- und Eigentumswohnungen spezialisiert. Zusätzlich zur Aufnahme von Schäden oder Mängeln, übernehmen wir auch die Suche und Beauftragung von Hausmeister:innen, Gärtner:innen, Winterdiensten und vor allem Handwerker:innen und technischen Spezialist:innen. Auch mit Gewährleistungsfragen im Neubau sind wir vertraut.  
Im Einzelnen betreuen wir:

• WEGs (WEG-Verwaltung)
• Mietwohnungen/Häuser (Mietverwaltung)
• Sondereigentum (SE-Verwaltung)

Gemeinsam mit Ihnen als Eigentümer:in, planen wir Instandhaltungen und Modernisierungen, mit denen der Werterhalt Ihrer Immobilie längstmöglich erhalten oder gar gesteigert werden kann.

Neben der reinen Verwaltungstätigkeit unterstützen wir Sie auch bei dem Verkauf oder der Neuvermietung Ihrer Wohnungen. Durch die intensive und häufig langjährige Betreuung unserer Liegenschaften wissen wir aus erster Hand über die Vorzüge jedes einzelnen Objekts.

name: Cropt d.o.o.
about: Cropt is an innovative startup that develops data-driven solutions for high-tech agriculture. It was founded as a spin-off from BioSense Institute, the EU’s Centre of Excellence for application of IT in sustainable agriculture. The team has so far won many prestigious awards, such as the 1st prize at Syngenta Crop Challenge and the award at CGIAR Inspire Challenge, that secured Bill and Melinda Gates funding for developing scalable AgTech solutions for African agriculture. Cropt has received seed funding from the Serbian Innovation Fund for developing a smart system for optimising the sowing strategy, that has the potential to increase farmers’ profits for 30% while simultaneously reducing the risk for 10%. Through the Climate KIC project, Cropt will develop a solution for estimation of eco-footprint of different sowing strategies and mitigate the climate risk through optimal crop diversification.

name: Optimo
about:
ABOUT US:

We're a team of innovative minds on a mission to empower blue-collar workers 👷👷‍♀️ to their fullest potential🚀💎

We make life-long learning easy, attractive and accessible. 


ABOUT OPTIMO:

Optimo is a B2B SaaS EdTech Startup that helps manufacturing companies to upskill blue-collar workers for Industry 4.0. 

Optimo offers a web app that matches experienced workers with young workers to help them exchange skills and knowledge 🧠👷‍♀️👷‍♂️

Our vision is to close the skills gap and to help individuals to find their strengths.


Optimo GmbH

name: Alexis
about: Our mission is simple: Empower companies to make smarter decisions, better connect with their people, and ultimately create a better workplace. Made in Sweden, used by businesses all over Europe.

name: Habit Analytics
about: Our end-to-end insurance solutions help insurers increase direct distribution reach by matching their offers with high converting brands online.

name: Kertos
about:
Kertos is a young yet well-funded company with amazing partners on their side. We are the first holistic privacy platform in Europe, implementing automation and execution in a highly regulated environment focusing on the operational needs for all stakeholders involved. With our focus on product, integration, and automation we enable businesses to scale, to adopt and to maneuver in modern tech environments with only a fraction of the current workload. We drive consumer engagement and help companies to interact with their customers in sensitive matters.  

Together with you, we want to embrace data privacy.

name: Passionfroot
about:
Passionfroot's mission is to empower the independent businesses of tomorrow. 

The Passionfroot team envisions a future in which everyone can make a living by sharing their truest authentic self.

Today's creators share their unique passions online and build communities of like-minded people. These communities connect individuals who would have never otherwise met, and enable anyone to find a place where they feel like they belong.

By leveraging these communities the creators are also able to turn their passions into livelihoods. These livelihoods are the foundation for the next generation of businesses in the creator economy.

Passionfroot is here to pave the way for the rise of the creator economy which we believe will cause the largest shift of empowerment and wealth in this generation. It will uplift individuality over institutions, enable people to work on their own terms, and lead to a more equitable future.

name: Bliq
about: People and goods move inefficient today because actionable information is missing. At Bliq, we develop a powerful mobility information engine that boosts productivity of urban street mobility.  We leverage real-time data streams from more than 24M connected vehicles and Computer Vision on the Edge to build the world’s most advanced street-level sensor network.  Today, we provide street-level intelligence with two products: Bliq Park helps drivers find car parking 3x faster with predictions and real-time data on available car parking. Bliq Ride makes taxi and rideshare drivers earn 30% more with better positioning close to passengers.

name: Seadora
about: B2C and B2B fish-booking platform

name: StoryBox
about:
Wir sind StoryBox, ein Tech StartUp aus München. 

StoryBox ist eine innovative SaaS Lösung für Unternehmen, mit der MitarbeiterInnen schnell und einfach Videos erstellen und teilen – kollaborativ, markenkonform und rechtssicher. 

Unternehmen stehen heute vor der Herausforderung, ihre interne und externe Kommunikation aktuell, attraktiv und dynamisch zu gestalten. Gerade wenn es um die Aufmerksamkeit bei (potenziellen) MitarbeiterInnen und KundInnen geht, ist Video das überzeugendste und effektivste Medium. StoryBox sorgt für Aufmerksamkeit, Authentizität und langfristigem Informationstransfer.

name: Stimio
about: Stimio is a company specializing in providing IoT solutions for the rail and energy (IIoT) industry. Using connected sensors and a SaaS data processing platform, Stimio transforms preventive and curative maintenance into a predictive maintenance model that includes failure anticipation through an AI-based prediction engine.

name: Ecotrek
about:
Ecotrek is the world's first sustainable supply chain system.

We centralize various sustainability data within our platform to make supply chain impact measurable and improvable. Don't waste time searching and requesting relevant information - and leverage our automated processes. With AI, we uncover more at any given time.

Ecotrek enables procurement and supply chain teams that understand the business-critical importance of their sustainability work to actively achieve their goals through sustainable supplier selection and supplier development.

name: Via.Delivery
about:
Via.Delivery is the alternative delivery location company poised to transform the shipping and delivery markets by building the world’s largest alternative delivery location network. The company is helping the millions of online retailers that don’t have brick-and-mortar locations compete with Amazon and traditional retailers by giving them the technology they need to rapidly activate Buy Online, Pickup in Store (BOPIS) and giving their customers access to thousands of convenient commercial pickup locations with dramatically reduced shipping costs. 

Via.Delivery’s first-to-market next-gen digital logistics and cloud-based delivery platform makes it easy for e-commerce retailers to activate BOPIS, ship orders to thousands of commercial locations around the world, automatically alert shoppers of shipping and delivery status and incentivize those shoppers through promotions being offered by those commercial pickup locations. Via.Delivery’s API and other platform plug-in's (e.g. Shopify) also make it possible for e-commerce merchants to get up and running with BOPIS, almost instantly. 

Covid changed how consumers purchase and receive goods, seemingly overnight. With current volume projected at 2025 levels today, other alternatives like Buy Online, Pick Up in Store (BOPIS) is surging. At Via.Delivery, were excited and determined to support diverse online businesses (that don’t have brick-and-mortar locations), as well as consumers adapting to new ways of purchasing and receiving goods. 

Via.Delivery has more than 2,000 pure play e-commerce merchants on its technology platform and more than 66,000 alternative delivery locations around the world.

Via.Delivery is based in Menlo Park, CA with offices in Moscow, Russia. Follow Via.Delivery on Twitter, LinkedIn and Facebook.

name: Genus AI
about:
Genus AI Growth Platform enables brands to generate and predict best performing ad creatives, perfect audience targeting and control social media ads via a single dashboard.
 
D2C brands, eCommerce businesses, insurance and financial services providers that use Genus AI observe drastically reduced customer acquisition costs (CPA), improved return on ad spend (ROAS) and reduced customer attrition.

name: yoona.ai
about: yoona.ai  an Artificial Intelligence-based B2B software solution, which shortens the value chain of the fashion industry to one click and furthermore the possibility to create individual designs which is  extended by using personal sports data. yoona.ai pursues the vision of holistic digitization and is committed to encourage conscious consumption and drive sustainability through the automation of the design process.

name: Perkio
about:
Perkio brings the right wellbeing support to your entire workforce.

We know how important it is to keep your best people. Having to replace valued team members is costly - both financially & emotionally for the people left behind. Frontline workers have especially had it rough, with the high stress leading to even higher turnover.

We help you keep your people engaged and empowered by placing their wellbeing at the center of your organization.

We open a dialogue and intelligently listen to build trust & unlock deeper insights from your team.

We deliver the right wellbeing support anonymously based on people's current situation.

And we give you insights to drive the right change & build a company with happier people by showing them that you care, even on a tight budget.

name: Unlock
about: We’re on a mission to build a modern platform for remote team cohesion - all the stuff that makes work more than just work.  Whether it’s playing a game, random coffee chats, meditating together, or learning something from your work buddy, Unlock will be your cultural hub for creating a well-connected team.  And these moments can also be shared with others - be it your customers, partners, candidates or friends at other organisations.   Talk to us for early access to our beta!

name: moovin Immobilien
about:
moovin organisiert die Vermietung von Wohnungen für Immobilienunternehmen schneller, digitaler, transparenter - und deutschlandweit. Dabei stehen wir Entscheider:innen in der Immobilienwirtschaft als Partner zur Seite, der den gesamten Vermietungsprozess übernimmt und zu jeder Zeit lückenlos abbildet. Mit der Kombination unserer intelligenten Software und persönlichen Makler-Leistungen vor Ort, schaffen wir für Vermietende einen wirtschaftlichen Vorteil:  Denn, im Gegensatz zur gängigen Provision, kann durch unser hybrides Modell mit einer festen Pauschale von nur einer Nettokaltmiete vermietet werden. 
Wir optimieren und beschleunigen den Vermietungsprozess enorm, indem Arbeitsschritte automatisiert, und zielgruppenspezifische Vermarktungsstrategien vollends ausgeschöpft werden. Unser Team aus fast 100 Vermietungsexpert:innen und ortskundigen Wohnungsberater:innen in mehr als 80 Städten verfolgt die Vision, Immobilienunternehmen mit innovativen Lösungen fit für die Zukunft zu machen. Die vierstelligen Vermietungszahlen sprechen für sich, und für moovin, als einen der größten Dienstleister am Markt.


Mehr erfahren:
www.moovin.de
ante@moovin.de
040 - 22 61 630 - 73

name: SPARQ
about: Sparq OU is a Fintech company based in Estonia, Tallinn.  We combine together banking sector, fintech market and retail companies to bring a seamless experience for millennials and gen Z by providing free payments within EU, loyalty system and modern fintech solutions!

name: Open Social
about:
Open Social is an open source community building solution. 

We're a great match for your external, volunteer and ideation community. Our software is used by NGOs, governments and hundreds of smaller organizations to connect with their members, volunteers, employees, and customers.

Greenpeace Greenwire, an award-winning project with hundreds of thousands of volunteers worldwide, was the inspiration for Open Social. We are now a Drupal-based community solution with more than a thousand active installations.

name: Traide
about:
traide provides scalable technology to simplify the complexities of international commerce making it accessible to everyone. 

Our AI-based SaaS-solutions scales complianed customs processes in companies of all industries and sizes, while rapidly changing regulations, bans and restrictions make it almost impossible for companies to staying on top.

name: Digital Vault Services GmbH
about: Guarantee Vault is a place for the issuance and safekeeping of digital guarantees. It gives banks & sureties the possibility to centrally issue and store instruments such as Bank Guarantees, Surety Bonds and Standby Letters of Credit in an electronic (paperless) form. This combination of central issuance with digital guarantees is an innovation that delivers significant value to all market participants including applicants, guarantors and beneficiaries. Through the transparency it brings, Guarantee Vault adds an additional layer of efficiency right throughout the guarantee life-cycle. For our German LinkedIn page click here: https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/digitalvault-dach

name: Myterial GmbH
about: MYTERIAL is a construction tech start-up from Munich and the daily companion on the construction site. As a one-stop-shop app, MYTERIAL makes procurement on the construction site more efficient, transparent and reliable. With just one click, all materials, tools and machines can be ordered and the status of all construction sites can be managed. Thanks to MYTERIAL, all costs, budgets and orders are thus always in view. MYTERIAL therefore reduces desk work and creates more time for value-creating activities on the construction site.

name: urban ENERGY GmbH
about:
"Our vision is to empower utilities and property managers, to intelligently and efficiently manage their energy usage and emitted emissions to achieve tomorrow’s energy revolution today.”
--
„Unsere Vision ist die intelligente und ressourcenschonende Energieverteilung innerhalb von Quartieren, um Stadtwerken und Immobilienbetreibern die Energiewende durch Technologien von morgen bereits heute zu ermöglichen.“

name: Waylay.io
about:
Waylay is a leading enterprise IT-OT digital unification software company delivering low-code based orchestration, automation and analytics software solutions. 
Waylay has a passion for supporting citizen developer communities and ensuring it puts all valuable data to work for developers, data scientists and domain experts. 
Waylay makes the digital transformation painless and allows a seamless deployment from idea to working use case in just hours. 

Every Waylay automation solution is low-code or no-code enabled. Its unique and trusted software platform is designed to address the specific requirements of the customers of Waylay’s three business units.

Waylay IO brings an entirely new low-code business model to the developer community. It allows developers to build automation flows and use cases in no time. Its developer-friendly environment, backed by an engaged community creates the perfect setting to bring ideas to life, experiment with data and create insightful new applications and business models quicker than ever before. 

Waylay Enterprise provides a proven cloud-agnostic solution to OT-IT unification. Its Citizen developer approach endorses innovation velocity and puts the value of data in the hands of domain experts, data scientists, and corporate tiger teams to initiate new revenue streams and guarantee high ROI for IoT data, without going through lengthy software development cycles. Waylay commits to supporting enterprises by simplifying their complex digital transformation journey when OT-IT finally converge.

Waylay Digital Twin is a no-code Salesforce solution that connects IoT to Salesforce and boosts the visibility of data, health and performance metrics for connected assets. Salesforce users configure asset monitoring based on the business context, create new condition-based predictive maintenance use cases, optimize remote operations and leverage asset data for consumption-based business models. Waylay Digital Twin is available on Salesforce.

name: tridion benefits GmbH
about:
Bendesk ist eine digitale B2B-Lösung zur Verwaltung von Corporate & Employee Benefits. Über die Cloud können beide Seiten online oder mit dem Handy bzw. Tablet Ihre ausgewählten Module einsehen. Bendesk dokumentiert gleichzeitig alle historischen und aktuellen Daten so dass gesetzliche Vorgaben eingehalten werden.

Für das Unternehmen bietet bendesk die Möglichkeit interne Prozesse zu verschlanken, die Komplexität der einzelnen Module wie bAV verständlich abzubilden und zeitintensive Vorgänge zu vereinfachen. Gleichzeitig spart das Unternehmen Lohnnebenkosten und der Mitarbeiter effektiv Steuern per Mausklick.

Ungenutze Steuervorteile werden häufig nicht genutzt da das Wissen im Unternehmen nicht bekannt ist und die Umsetzung für viele zu kompliziert erscheint. Egal ob Gutscheine für Mitarbeiter, Essenszuschuß, pauschalbesteuerte Gutscheine oder betriebliche Altervorsorge (bAV) - bendesk ermöglicht mehr netto für den Arbeitnehmer.

Ein übersichtliches Cockpit ermöglicht den intuitiven Umgang und permanente Einsicht in alle relevanten Informationen. Sowohl für das HR-Team als auch jeden einzelnen Mitarbeiter optimiert bendesk den Zugang zu allen angebotenen Komponenten und zeigt mögliche Sparpotentiale transparent auf.

Optional unterstützt unser Team aus bAV-Experten bei der Integration und Umsetzung der betrieblichen Altersvorsorge im Unternehmen. Die Übernahme der internen Prozesse schenkt Zeit und spart Nerven. Von der Beratung, über den Abschluss bis hin zur nachträglichen Verwaltung - alles ist über bendesk möglich.

Ein Mehrwert für das gesamte Unternehmen als Mitarbeiterbindungstool und Arbeitgeberimage.

name: Remind.me
about:
Vergessen Sie Ihre Kündigungsfristen. Wir kümmern uns darum. remind me ist Ihr unabhängiger Erinnerungsservice für Kündigungsfristen aller Art. Mit uns halten Sie Ihre Kündigungstermine im Blick und optimieren Ihre langlaufenden Verträge wie z.B. Strom, Gas, Mobilfunk oder Internet.

remind.me ist seit 2017 am Markt und hat sich erfolgreich entwickelt. Mit einer soliden Finanzierung durch den High-Tech Gründer­fonds und weitere Angel Investoren haben wir bereits nachhaltige Kooperationen mit bekannten Partnern wie Burda Media, der Axel Springer Gruppe oder Viessmann aufbauen können. Neben dem Aufbau unseres eigenen Kundenstamms entwickeln wir für namhafte Kooperationspartner White Label- und Co-Branded-Solutions, um uns im Markt langfristig breit aufzustellen. 

Wir verstehen uns als innovativer Arbeitgeber, der seinen Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeitern viel Freiraum für die Umsetzung eigener Ideen gibt. In unserem Büro in Berlin-Mitte arbeitet unser erfahrenes und eingespieltes Gründerteam zusammen mit einem offenen, sympathischen und pragmatischen Team von Kolleginnen und Kollegen. Wir bieten u.a. Jobs in den Bereichen Produktmanagement, Entwicklung (Frontend-Javascript/React.js, Backend – Java/Spring Boot, Fullstack), Customer Care, Redaktion, Online Marketing. Alle aktuell offenen Stellen finden Sie unter https://www.remind.me/unternehmen/jobs.  Wir freuen uns auf Ihre Bewerbung per E-Mail an jobs@remind.me.

name: Oveo
about:
We help modern IT and finance teams gain company-wide visibility into software spend and utilization.

Our SaaS Management Platform give modern IT and finance teams the tools they need to discover, manage and optimise all SaaS spend and usage in one place. 

Unleashing the power of SaaS!

At some companies you can feel the momentum building. People are executing fast, enabled by modern software tools seamlessly integrated into a fully automated tech stack guided by processes that scale. Innovation thrives at companies like that and work quickly becomes addictive.

At others, it feels impossible to get things done. No one has an overview of all the software tools being used, the running costs and the data being exposed. People lose sight of the operational process and everyone starts pulling in different direction – or stop pulling at all.

We started Oveo because we believe employees should have easy access to all the SaaS tools they love and need, but with IT management simultaneously having peace of mind and seamless visibility into company-wide technology cost, utilisation and compliance risks. 

Today, our cloud-based SaaS Management platform help companies streamline their technology operations, boost productivity, employee engagement and enable any company in any industry to succeed as a SaaS-powered workplace. 

____

We are hiring! Check out our open job positions here: https://thehub.io/startups/oveoio-1

Our ambition is to bring together Artificial Intelligence, satellite, drone, and aerial data to provide industry users, public sectors, and NGO members with optimized geo-information in order to monitor and anticipate changes in their surroundings. 

At Picterra, we are convinced that without your expertise and situational awareness, Artificial Intelligence is nothing but an empty shell. 

This is why, we propose you to partner your field-specific knowledge with a unique interactive and scalable computer vision system, design to work in synergy with you. 

No programming or deep learning skills needed, simply train, deploy and customize your own AI to extract the geo-information you really care about.

name: ONIQ
about:

As an independent software vendor ONIQ offers Process Mining and Process Analytics Software for production and operations processes in various industries.

Our mission is to substantially improve OEE, time to market and delivery reliability of production through Process Mining and AI-based Analytics while reducing the production’s carbon footprint.
 
ONIQ offers the world's first production-specific Process Mining Software for real-time transparency over procurement, logistics and production processes, production progress, contiguous product quality, root causes for disruptions as well as product defects while enabling automated real-time reactions. 

ONIQ is home to a team of engineering, Process Mining and AI experts and we are actively engaged in the fight for carbon reduction. 

Partnerships with leading universities in manufacturing research contribute to our product development. ONIQ is an official Microsoft and SAP partner.

name: Packaly
about:
Packaly is the fastest last mile delivery platform that combines businesses and their customers with a on-demand delivery service. We create the opportunity for every single company in our cities of operations to deliver a package in 60 minutes or the same evening. We deliver today! We work together with supermarkets, book stores, sports retailers, local fashion outlets and much more to enable them to ship as an innovative transportation player.

"Making 60 minutes the norm" is the mission that Packaly is carrying around daily. When customers believe that they want to be in control of their delivery, they are not. We believe that deliveries can be empowered from smart, logistical in city thinking. We believe in a better world with less pollution, but a common goal for society. We want to disrupt the way we think about the last-mile and create a better way for people to distribute products around their city. Packaly is changing the future of delivery. We connect our dashboard services and e-commerce API together to empower stability, speed and result! We ship efficient, reliable, fast, eco-friendly and help stores to impress their customers. 

Packaly launched in 2019, taking on a big challenge together with some of our partners. We are operational in 35+ cities in multiple European countries with more than 1200+ delivery drivers.

name: Mistho
about:
mistho.io offers the first open payroll API for Europe, that enables consumers to easily access and share their salary and employment information with third parties such as banks, insurance companies, lenders and others at the click of a button. 

Our goal is to help businesses build the best consumer experiences in the fintech world that require income information. As a first step, we are now enabling businesses to easily integrate the Mistho app into their existing flow for income verification.

Remember the last time you searched for a flat to rent, wanted to lease a car or applied for a loan? At some point during your search you were asked to share your last three months of payslips. You probably had to upload them to a platform or send them via e-mail to your agent. In some cases, you might even have needed to ask your HR department to help you out. 

Mistho helps exactly here - by offering a digital, directly embedded income verification tool that asks the end consumer to do no more than log in to their payroll portal.

name: Voliro
about:
Voliro is developing advanced flying robots to perform Inspection and Maintenance tasks more safely, cost-effectively and faster than traditional methods. 

With its tiltable rotor system, Voliro expands the abilities of service drones from “fly and see” to “fly, see and touch”. The flying robot can be equipped with a variety of payloads, such as Non-Destructive Testing (NDT) sensors. The unique 360° drone design of the platform allows inspection of curved and sloped surfaces. No other flying inspection robot boasts these capabilities.

Voliro aims to provide innovative UAVs with unique capabilities. We promote the concept of omnidirectional aerial vehicles, where position and orientation of the flying platform are completely independent. This ability is crucial to achieve robust and reliable interaction with the environment.

name: Styla
about:
Styla provides a cutting edge headless storefront technology for small and medium sized businesses. Having focused on bringing innovative software solutions to the eCommerce space since 2012, Styla now provides the fastest frontend technology in the world, realized on top of headless shop-systems in a Jamstack architecture. Styla embraces API driven composable commerce principles so that it specializes on the fastest, simplest and most loved storefront for retailers and merchants of all sizes around the world. Styla’s vision is to bring benefits of heavy custom-built headless enterprise projects to small and medium sized businesses at a very affordable price.
As a booster for speed, SEO, usability and conversion, Styla installs a storefront and a PWA easily manageable via drag & drop, enhances a brand’s mobile commerce strategy and ensures a smooth shopping experience for all shoppers.

We are a team of manufacturing engineers, software developers and technology consultants who aim to accelerate digitalization of the manufacturing industry. Based on our many years of experience, we are developing software for data-driven quality evaluation in production. Currently we are funded via EXIST Transfer of Research, a funding program of the German government supporting outstanding research-oriented projects that involve expensive and high-risk resource development.
