name: Cauliflower
about:
Cauliflower uses AI to deliver deep and intuitive insights from text. No manual training required. Cross-industry proven.

1. Gain a deeper understanding
Out of the box, Cauliflower automatically identifies the most important topics, their associations, and the sentiment of your text data and visualises them in an interactive, intuitive dashboard.

2. Reduce mandatory setup work
Cauliflower uses a unique unsupervised approach to save you time and money. No extensive setup is required on your part, no industry or case specific training data necessary.

3. Evaluate first, customise later
Take advantage of the effortless setup and instead invest your time in making the analysis and visualisation work best for your business and your specific use case.

name: Kompany
about:
kompany is a RegTech platform for Global Business Verification & Business KYC (KYB). Operating a proprietary global live network that provides real-time access to official commercial and banking registers, we cover over 110 million company records in more than 200 jurisdictions. 

** More about us ** 

kompany provides dynamic access to primary source documents, delivering robust audit-proof data instantaneously. This makes us one of the few KYB providers who are fully able to satisfy the stricter due diligence requirements of the latest anti-money laundering legislation.

Our KYB solutions include:

KYC workspace – a web-based collaborative platform satisfying a range of KYB needs within a single application 

KYC API – a RESTful Enterprise API enabling easy integration of KYB information into existing ERP, CRM or other internal compliance systems 

UBO discovery® – a pioneering AI solution for transparent overviews of ultimate beneficiary and shareholder structures across companies and geographies

KYC onchain –  a traceable, immutable record of a business’s compliance records, leveraging blockchain technology

Headquartered in Vienna, Austria, kompany is a Clearing House of registers across the world. We serve business customers from 100+ countries, including international and regional banking groups, FinTechs, Big 4 accounting firms, law firms, banking as a service and compliance platforms, as well as multinational corporations.

name: Pacerin

Wir sehen eine klare Zukunft in den hybriden Arbeitsmodellen, sodass das Arbeiten von zu Hause in den meisten Flexoffice und „New Work“-Konzepten sich nachhaltig verankern wird. Dabei wird jedoch die Arbeitsumgebung der Mitarbeiter vergessen und 2/3 aller Nutzer arbeiten in einem nicht ergonomisch gesunden Set-Up zu Hause.

In unserer One-Stop-Lösung stehen die individuellen Anforderungen des Mitarbeiters, Gesundheit, Ergonomie und Produktivität im Vordergrund.

Wir sehen folgende Vorteile:
• Passende Ergänzung zum Flexoffice/Desksharing im Büro

Viele von uns benötigen tagtäglich Unterstützung in den verschiedensten Lebensbereichen. Dennoch fehlte es bisher an einem digitalen Angebot, welches diese zeit- und ortsunabhängig zur Verfügung stellt – und damit ebenso flexibel ist wie Du.

name: FINABRO
about:
FINABRO ist Ihr Berater für Sparen & Anlegen! 

Richtig Sparen und vernünftig Anlegen ist wichtig für viele Teile des Lebens. Sparen kann schwierig sein – Geld sinnvoll anzulegen ist nahezu unmöglich geworden. Das Sparbuch gibt null-Zinsen und die unterschiedlichen alternativen Anlageformen sind riskant, intransparent und teuer.

Durch unsere Technologie helfen wir Ihnen dabei, Geld zur Seite zu legen und es gut, kostengünstig und steueroptimal anzulegen. Und zwar einfach, transparent und individuell auf Ihre Wünsche angepasst. Dabei kombinieren wir bewährte traditionelle Elemente der Vermögensverwaltung mit verbesserten innovativen Methoden. 

Unser Service beinhaltet:
Hilfe beim Sparen: FINABRO hilft Ihnen bei der Festlegung Ihrer Sparziele und beim Erstellen Ihres individuellen Sparplans. Innovative Ansätze wie MorgenMehrSparen machen das Sparen leistbar und Ihre Ziele erreichbar. 
Erstklassige Vermögensverwaltung: ein Service wie bisher nur für vermögende "Private Banking" Kunden: Ihr Geld wird in einem individuellen Portfolio angelegt, kontinuierlich überwacht und FINABRO sorgt für regelmäßige Anpassungen. 
Aktives Risikomanagement: FINABRO managt das Risiko Ihres Portfolios, wenn sich die Märkte verschieben. Das Ziel ist, die optimale Rendite zu erwirtschaften und die Schwankungen zu minimieren.

Dabei suchen wir die steuermäßig günstigste Anlagestruktur für Sie aus – ein Wertpapierdepot oder eine fondsgebundene Lebensversicherung. Am Ende bleiben Ihnen dadurch bis zu 10-20% mehr übrig!

Einfach. Persönlich. 
Die neue Welt für Sparen & Anlegen


Impressum: www.finabro.at/impressum

name: Valutico
about:
Fintech start-up Valutico is a web-based company valuation platform providing the financial services industry and valuation experts with data-driven tools to perform accurate company valuations in a fraction of the time while solving the issue of complex tools, lack of data sources and time consuming reporting. With the world’s leading valuation methodologies to choose from, Valutico accelerates business valuation processes by 30-50%.

Valutico’s software solution currently comprises three different modules and a marketplace. The modules address specific valuation requirements for private/listed enterprises and provide access to industry and country specific valuation parameters. The marketplace brings together valuation experts and customers in need of valuation expertise.

With our product offering we especially address valuation experts in Advisory (e.g. Corporate Finance, M&A, Tax and Audit), Investment Management (e.g. Family Offices, Private Equity, Venture Capital), but also Corporates (e.g. Strategy, Financial Reporting, IR). 

By combining advanced technology with expert corporate finance know-how, we support our clients to overcome the high and expensive requirements of the valuation process, which demands technical/industry know-how, access to expensive financial databases and time. 

Our team of 40 employees is globally distributed and serves both national and international clients in over 25 countries including the US.

name: Bringoo
about:
Bringoo is a german tech-driven startup that brings local commerce online. 

Bringoo empowers merchants to grow their businesses by offering on-demand delivery in 45 minutes, data-driven insights, and better in-store efficiency. By building the last-mile delivery infrastructure for local cities in a highly efficient way while using an agile shopper/rider infrastructure, powered by e-mobility and our smart route algorithm, Bringoo is bringing communities closer, one doorstep at a time. 

Bringoo offers same-day delivery (in 45 minutes), a pick-up-service and timeslot-delivery, to bring fresh groceries and everyday essentials to busy people and families across Hamburg and Berlin. Bringoo has partnered with beloved national, regional and local retailers, including unique brand names, to deliver in all neighbourhoods of Hamburg, Cologne, Berlin and Pinneberg. In Q3 we aim to expand to at least 7-10 more cities.

The companies cutting-edge enterprise technology also powers the e-commerce platforms of some of the worlds biggest retail players, supporting their applications and delivery solutions; simultaneously, the platform offers cities an opportunity to counteract the disruption of inner cities as a result of the online boom triggered by COVID.

Si integra con i POS e i sistemi di cassa più utilizzati, grazie alla consolidata rete di partner commerciali.
Il sistema è gratuito per il profilo “acquirente”.

GetYourBill è un progetto di Ultroneo Srl, un’impresa nata da uno spin-off dell’Università di Udine e valorizzata da esperti del mondo del business.

name: NUMA Group (formerly COSI Group)
about:
In a world of stuffy, faceless hotels, we’re leading the industry into a new era. We’re replacing the unnecessary hassle with simplicity and delight. Mixing technology and taste together in the world’s greatest neighbourhoods, we create stays that are unashamedly original and unforgettably authentic. With the comforts of home and the quality of a boutique hotel, we make sure our guests have everything they need to live like a local, escape for a weekend, or unwind during a business trip. If they want to stay for longer, we’ve got that covered as well. We’ve designed our properties with our guests’ joy in mind, whether they stay for a night, a week, or a season. 

Numa does away with complicated check-ins, long queues, and unpredictable accommodations. Instead, we take the best parts of travel—the carefully designed spaces, the thrill of a new city, fluffy towels, a comfy bed—and blend them with state-of-the-art technology. For our guests, it’s a one-of-a-kind mix of ease and experience, a super-simple guest journey in Europe’s most exciting neighborhoods. 

Our world-class guest experience is just the tip of the iceberg. With our proprietary full-stack software suite, we’ve digitalised over 80% of our internal processes, from booking and room allocation to housekeeping, accounting, and more. This keeps us scalable and cost-efficient, and helps us to weather even the most volatile of market fluctuations. By using intelligent yield management, distribution and our in-house operating systems, we can significantly reduce our administrative workload operating costs. We’re always able to keep things agile and efficient, which frees us up to focus on what’s most important: the satisfaction of our visitors.

name: Wasteless
about:
Wasteless is the world’s first machine learning and real­time tracking solution for grocery stores to offer customers dynamic pricing based on product expiration date. We help retailers optimize markdowns, increasing their profitability substantially.

A winner of numerous accolades, including from Kairos, Seeds & Chips, Emerce Best European Start-up, AGFunder and Foodbytes by Rabobank NYC, we primarily aim to repair the broken food system by pre-empting food waste.

In fact, Wasteless more than halves waste in food retail, and increases the revenues through markdown optimization. Minimizing Food Waste is one of the most impactful measures against climate change, according to Drawdown.org. It can reduce carbon emissions by up to 70GTon over the next 30 years. Since supermarket waste is around 5% of total emissions, we're in the area that can have an effect of some 3GT reduced green house gas emissions ! 

For supermarkets, it's also a highly lucrative opportunity. BCG found that reducing food waste by supply chain optimization, and in particular dynamic pricing, is a global €100 Billion opportunity. Refed found that for US grocery retailers, food waste represents an $18.2 billion opportunity. On average, the value of wasted food in retail is equal to roughly double the profits from food sales.

Waste prevention solutions such as markdown optimization have the highest profit potential. Indeed, our patented algorithm turns waste into profits, and what would normally be garbage headed to the landfill, into the carts of happy shoppers, that Spend Less, Wasteless.

Let's get food waste out of our system. Join us in Refed, Friends of Champions123 or SamenTegenVoedselverspilling.

Unser Weg heißt SMASH® (Select – Match- Hire – Apply): Die „Bewerbung der Zukunft“ ist längst in der Gegenwart angekommen. Wir geben diesem überfälligen Wandel einen Namen, der die Wucht der Veränderung im HR-Umfeld auf den Punkt bringt: SMASH® – ein Begriff der die einzelnen Phasen des Recruitings, von der Suche bis zur Einstellung, neu definiert und von den verkrusteten Methoden der Vergangenheit befreit. 

Unsere Produkte: Unsere flexiblen SaaS-Lösungen lassen sich nahtlos in die bestehende Infrastruktur einbinden und erhöhen die digitale Recruiting-Performance. Wir konzipieren unsere Lösungen immer auf Basis der Anforderungen, die Kandidaten und Arbeitgeber an den Recruitingprozess stellen. 

Unser Ergebnis: Innovatives Recruiting dank optimaler Candidate Experience. Wir machen Recruiting-Strategien fit für die Gegenwart und optimieren sie für die Zukunft.

- Network planning, configuration, administration, documentation

name: Hokodo
about:
At Hokodo, we are modernising the way businesses buy from each other by making it easier and safer to sell to business customers! 

Our “Trade credit as a service” technology empowers B2B merchants to offer credit terms to their business customers instantly, even on their first purchase. In turn, customers benefit from additional payment terms through a frictionless checkout experience.

Over 30% of B2B trade takes place on credit terms, with trade credit representing the largest source of business financing in advanced economies. Yet current processes for offering trade credit are outdated and not fit for the digital age. Hokodo’s digital platform solves these issues by offering merchants a powerful set of solutions to manage trade credit and scale with confidence. Merchants that integrate with Hokodo see on average a 40% increase in revenues. 

Gone are the days of paper-based trading account applications, manual credit decisions and cumbersome sales journeys. Our easy-to-integrate digital platform streamlines the entire order-to-cash process, allowing merchants to make credit decisions in real-time, be protected against bad debt and get access to working capital finance options. We also protect merchants by insuring against the credit risk with Lloyd’s of London, and arrange the financing with our partners so our sellers can get paid upfront if they choose.

We’ve believed for a long time that the design and distribution of financial products has been broken, and we’ve been on a journey to fix it since. Our team cuts across geographical barriers and brings together financial services practitioners, engineers, data scientists and designers… all working together to create a better way of doing business!

Our team is ambitious, we work hard to make our goals a reality... and we still have fun! Want to join us on our journey? Drop us an email at jobs@hokodo.co

Hokodo’s solutions are backed by Lloyd’s of London via the Channel Syndicate, a unit of SCOR P&C.

name: Impak Finance
about:
Notre mission est d’aider le secteur financier à faire des choix plus durables grâce à des évaluations allant au-delà des critères ESG et comprenant à la fois les impacts négatifs et positifs de leurs actifs, cotés et non-cotés.

Agence leader de la notation d’impact basée sur une clientèle d’investisseurs, impak propose des données sociales et environnementales transparentes, comparables et mesurables, augmentées par l’intelligence humaine. Nous œuvrons pour que les gestionnaires de capitaux intègrent ces données dans leurs processus décisionnels afin de leur permettre de financer une économie véritablement capable de relever les défis sociaux et environnementaux actuels. Notre offre convient aux investisseurs institutionnels, aux services bancaires et d’investissement, aux gestionnaires d’actifs, de patrimoine et de capital-investissement, aux créateurs et gestionnaires de fonds indiciels cotés ainsi qu’aux services d’investissement responsable. 

Le Score impakMC et le bilan d’impact ont été développés par impak et sont issus de notre méthodologie basée sur les Objectifs de développement durable des Nations Unies et l’Impact Management Project. Au cœur de notre solution, ces deux éléments permettent une contextualisation de la donnée, une analyse suivant les principes de la double matérialité ainsi qu’une évaluation de son alignement aux nouvelles réglementations, grâce à nos modules personnalisés, tels que Taxonomie européenne, SFDR et Stratégie Climat.

Par exemple, nos bilans d’impact offrent à nos clients et partenaires de mieux gérer leurs risques internes et externes, et d’identifier les opportunités à impact positif, essentiels pour avoir une perspective à long terme sur les changements climatiques et l’impact alpha. 

Nous sommes la 2e génération d’agences de notation extra-financière, celle qui a appris des erreurs de la 1re génération de notation ESG pour réaliser un vrai changement de paradigme.

Visitez https://www.impakfinance.com/

Die CoIQ GmbH betreibt mit informunity.de eine führende Börsensimulation, an der seit 2010 mehr als 50.000 Nutzer teilgenommen haben. Aus deren Anlageentscheidungen wird das informunity Top Investor Portfolio gebildet. Mit einer jährliche Rendite von 18 Prozent im Zeitraum 2010 bis 2021 hätte dieses den globalen Aktienmarkt signifikant geschlagen. 

Der am 02.02.2022 gestartete „CoIQ Collective Intelligence Fund” (ISIN DE000A3C91C5) basiert im Wesentlichen auf diesem Portfolio. name: LIQUIDLOOP GmbH
about:
For cutting edge research in electrocatalysis.

Due to its outstanding time-resolution, pretreatment-free Product-to-Gas PoGASi interface, and modular design, LiquidLoop meets the challenging requirements for liquid and gas analysis for real-time monitoring of electro-catalytic reactions and processes.
The PoGASi allows the expansion and application of partial pressure mass spectrometers (MS), by granting a direct separation and consequent MS analysis of liquid and gas from any liquid carrier solution. A dedicated liquid inlet module is assembled on a pre-stage vacuum chamber before introducing to any MS system. 

The real-time analysis technology facilitates the access of MS analysis for fluids, which is otherwise nearly impossible. Our solution is ideal for laboratory analysis (electrochemistry) or process control in various industries. 


More info: info@liquidloop.eu

Our mission is to accelerate global finance flows into projects and innovations needed to attain UN Sustainable Development Goals.

A combination of a blockchain and smart contracts with the integration of AI and networks of smart sensors, drones, and satellite data enables us to solve main challenges of the growing (Est. $ 503 bln with CAGR 18% ) impact investment market - сostly & inefficient portfolio management, inaccurate impact measurement, mistrust between projects and investors, profitability and liquidity concerns. 

Evercity team has deep knowledge and expertise in development, legal, marketing, digital finance and impact finance markets. Our first experiments in impact measurement and decentralized green finance started in 2016 and resulted in some remarkable achievements such as the first green asset issuance in the blockchain. To develop our ecosystem we organize hackathons and partner with global cities,  international organizations, investors, governments and top research centers.

We believe that the Influx of new technologies and young talents will help humanity to fairly evaluate and distribute global resources between smart cities enabling us to create new socio-economic models for a sustainable future.

name: Excagol-medtech
about:
Excagol is developing an automated venipuncture device that will take on the most common invasive activity in healthcare centers: EVA, the electronic venipuncture apparatus.

A suitable vessel often has to be punctured. It seems simple at first glance. In facts, challenging vessels can be painful, dangerous and excruciating for the patient. It is often time-consuming and physically stressful for medical staff, and expensive for healthcare centers.

Medical personnel can perform punctures efficiently, safely and stress-free with EVA, the mobile computer-controlled system. Vascular structures are made visible by ultrasonic waves. An image processing algorithm recognizes vessels and recommends a suitable target. After the operator's confirmation, the needle is automatically steered and precisely puncture the target. 

Excagol's Vision is to become the healthcare industry's next-generation fast, efficient and safe solution for various puncture purposes for both patients with difficult-to-reach veins and nurses with different professional experience.

By this means, the operator can easily capture antibodies in any user-defined buffer, making acidic elution obsolete. Have a look at our website for further information and follow us on LinkedIn for fresh updates on our journey. There is a lot to come! Imprint: https://www.lumatix.bio/imprint-data-protection/ The start-up project Lumatix Biotech is funded by the Federal Ministry for Economic Affairs and Energy funding program “EXIST Transfer of Research” and is co-financed by the European Social Fund.

name: Agrimand
about:
Digitaler Agrarhandel – das ist es, was wir von agrimand erreichen wollen.

Was macht agrimand aber so besonders? Wir bieten Landwirten, Händlern und Verarbeitern den ersten unabhängigen, neutralen und digitalen Ausschreibungsservice - und alles ist so einfach wie Online-Banking.

Was hat uns zu dieser Idee bewogen? Als Branchenkenner war uns der Wandel des Agrarhandels schon lange bewusst. Hatten Landwirte früher nur ein bis zwei regionale Verhandlungspartner bei denen es oftmals nach dem Prinzip: „Beziehung baut vor Preis“ ging, hat sich dieses Bild mit den Jahren geändert. Mussten früher noch Angebote direkt händisch verglichen werden, ist die neue Generation auf den Höfen mit Portalen wie Check24, Amazon oder Ebay aufgewachsen. Transparente und vergleichbare Preise sind heute wichtiger denn je. Landwirte wollen unabhängig sein. Dennoch gibt es hier bislang kaum digitale Möglichkeiten, Preise zu vergleichen. Dabei ist die Landtechnik als Vorreiter schon lange vernetzt und digitalisiert. Smart Farming, Precision Farming – all das ist uns längst kein Fremdwort mehr. Der Landhandel hinkt hier deutlich hinterher. Hier schließen wir mit agrimand die Lücke und leisten einen wichtigen Beitrag hin zu einer vernetzten Landwirtschaft und zum digitalen Landhandel.

Unser Impressum: https://www.agrimand.com/impressum/
Unsere Datenschutzerklärung: https://www.agrimand.com/datenschutz/

name: Everwave
about:
The organisation everwave is a social enterprise that is dedicated to protect rivers and the ocean from plastic waste and to promote a more sustainable life-style, in order to protect aquatic environments as precious habitats, food resources and economic regions. 
 
For this purpose, everwave (former "Pacific Garbage Screening") is founded on two pillars: Technological innovation and ecological inspiration. 
 
Technological innovation focuses on a combination of active and passive cleanup technologies for rivers that prevent waste from entering the oceans. Due to their functional architecture, the stationary platform systems continuously take up and store waste drifting with the current. The flexible and AI-supported garbage collection boats are able to clean up waste hotspots in the larger environment - even in places that are difficult to access. The waste is then recycled by mechanical, thermochemical and biotechnological processes to new products.

Ecological Inspiration comprises raising public awareness for the global plastic crisis and promoting solutions through environmental education, interactive events and creative PR activities with international outreach. This includes high quality education material, a website and linked social media channels, interviews and media coverages in news portals and television as well as presentations, information stands and special events.

name: FinMarie
about:
FinMarie is the first online investment solution made by women for women in Europe. We combine personal financial advice with an online investment solution.

about: Digital innovators of all kinds - developers, product managers, entrepreneurs,... - need to create, deploy and integrate frictionless payment flows in their products, applications and systems.    Today, there are ever more payment networks and systems to choose from or to support, and payment infrastructure has never been so open and API-enabled as it is today.  However, the security and compliance burden has also increased, as has the complexity that comes with most power, choice and responsibility.  Weavr addresses these challenges in practical ways, simplifying how digital payments are purchased, delivered and consumed.   It does so by providing simple and configurable templates for defining payment behaviour, tools for integrating payment logic with their own systems, a means of finding and connecting with relevant payment providers, and facilities for deploying and running the actual payments.  With Weavr, building complex payment flows seems unreasonably simple.  There's no catch - Weavr is based on the results of an ambitious EU-Horizon 2020 funded research project that set to develop engineering solutions to the difficult problems of guaranteeing security and compliance while providing maximum openness and power to developers, and to simplify the creation of complex payment logic through model-driven engineering techniques.

name: Rectag
about:
RecTag is podcast discovery and beyond. We want to empower everyone to share their message, be heard and discover stories they love. As podcasters, we were quite frustrated with how hard it is to be heard and find an audience who cares - and we are not the only ones. We believe there are many talented storytellers out there who simply do not get the attention they deserve. It shouldn’t take a big media house or name behind your podcast, to get on top of the charts. At the same time, we want to give all listeners and podcast enthousiast the opportunity to discover stories and people based on the actual content and not just podcast title and description. Because books shouldn’t only be judged by their cover!

That is why we are building RecTag
Our AI enables content based discovery beyond simple chart lists. We use elements of social networking so you can connect to fans, that truly care about the hard work you put into your content. Furthermore, we want listeners to have a personal connection to their favorite podcasters.

Why we love Podcasting
Compared to its visual counterpart video, audio content carries a much greater emotional impact. Put differently, conveyed through a podcast, a story gets directly into the listeners’ ear and draws a picture in their heads. It taps into an audience’s active imagination and creates a much more intimate connection.
Famous comedian and host of the “WTF with Marc Maron” podcast Marc Maron put it this way:

“The medium of podcasting and the personal nature of it, the relationship you build with your listeners and the relationship they have with you- they could be sitting there chuckling and listening...There’s nothing like that.”

name: GOENOMICS GmbH
about: GOENOMICS provides genome annotations to help agriculture, biotech and academia to develop and better understand genomic traits for improved plants and fungi. Improving plants is important to secure worldwide food supply, by optimising for example heat resistance and resistance against nutrient and water scarcity, and agricultural pests. Better understanding fungal biology is important to treat agricultural diseases and to improve fungi for industrial drug production or waste management. The term genome annotation summarises all steps with which each of the nucleotides of a genome sequence is given an explanation. Genome annotations are done in two steps: In the first step, all regions are identified that might have functional importance for the organism. In the second step, each of the identified regions is assigned a putative function, which is derived by comparing the region against knowledge from many databases and literature. Genome annotations provide the base for all downstream experiments like breeding, genetics, genomics, and proteomics. By delivering high quality data, GOENOMICS enables customers to avoid needless, meaningless and unsuccessful experiments and therefore to save money. about:
Virtual i is created to let insurance industry see the risks. We bring a simple answer to a complex, unsolved current problem.

Our mission is to democratize high-quality and normally expensive services such as risk engineering and loss prevention and to allow business owners to access loss prevention advisory services, thus ensuring their business continuity in difficult times. 
We trust that small and medium enterprises are the basis of sustainable growth and want them to survive and prosper. We do not use big words, but do big things.

We enable the insurance industry to move from good faith-based underwriting to data-based dynamic decision making.
Our solutions are unique and affordable, tech-based, bringing your business immediate, visible results. 

We achieve cost savings for insurers, that will be able to work with any risk engineer anywhere in the world without the need to travel to the site of the project.

With our tools our clients manage to highlight more risks during the underwriting process and thus the probability of picking up a bad risk is reduced.

Loss ratio dropped by up to 12% after using our proprietary platform - Virtual Risk Space.

Clients who tested us could measure up to 40% workload efficiency improvement in their technical team (underwriters, risk engineers etc).
They managed to obtain up to 100% visibility and control over their portfolio.

To implement Virtual Risk Space™️ in your company, no change management and no change/ adaptation of IT systems is required. A simple training of your staff will do. Our tool is very smart and friendly.

Our service is available immediately. It takes about a week to have it working in your company.
See here details of Virtual Risk Space™️, that allows structured data collection and quick objective scientific risk assessment: https://virtualitechnologies.com/vrs

name: Parcelly
about:
Parcelly is the UK’s first and most advanced provider of carrier and retailer agnostic Pick-up and Drop-off (PUDO) technology. Enabling over 2,500+ collection points in the UK, GER, ESP and MENA to resolve industry problems associated with first- and last-mile delivery. Our core belief is that receiving, returning and sending parcels should be convenient, efficient, simple and above all sustainable - powering the new reality of retail.

Parcelly's innovative, multi-award winning approach helps reduce the number of driver destinations and delivery attempts, whilst driving air quality improvements and white van traffic reduction in congestion zones. From hyper-local to global, Parcelly is the omnichannel technology powering the future of parcel distribution. 

LOCAL SHOP OR BUSINESS
Customer convenience, additional footfall, increased cross-selling opportunities & a new revenue stream. No set-up costs or bulky equipment; compatible with any webshop or carrier worldwide. Parcel collection points are managed entirely via smartphone and can control the size & number of parcels to receive.

SELLING ONLINE
Improved online shopping experience with a last- and first-mile solution that fits busy lifestyles. Available on-demand with or without API integration at checkout. Guaranteed increase in first-time delivery rates. Cost savings through the reduction in customer service enquiries & compensation claims.

CARRIER OR SHIPPER
Access to a nationwide, carrier agnostic PUDO network. Seamless compatibility, smart delivery route & resource capacity optimisation. Fully customisable, on-demand click&collect technology with real-time tracking of delivery status & customer feedback.

CORPORATE OR LARGE ENTERPRISE
Avoid rising corporate mailroom costs and benefit from a sustainable click&collect and return service, reducing the number of non-business related parcel deliveries. 

✉️ partnerships@parcelly.com

name: Batalyse
about:
Batalyse develops software modules for effective test data evaluation and information management for electrochemical energy storage and fuel cells and addresses material developers, cell manufacturers, as well as R&D and QM departments.

Batalyse - Battery + Analysis
- Data Analysis evaluates your battery and fuel cell test data.
- Collect synchronizes your test and analysis data from networked measurement computers and stores it centrally.
- Mind is a laboratory information and management system. Link your test data with information on materials used, tools/equipment and processes and create your test item information.

By combining the Batalyse software modules, you document your data accurately and reliably for later AI use and automate your data analysis



With Batalyse you solve these problems:
- Different file structures and formats make it difficult to collect and to analyze data.
- Data is valuable, but only if it is accurately and extensively documented and securely stored centrally. In particular, efficient use of artificial intelligence (AI) requires good, documented data.
- Data evaluation is time-consuming and costs an engineer up to 40% of his working time.
- Key performance indicators of batteries and fuel cells are the basis for decision-making in order to differentiate from competitors. With competing solutions, sensitive, critical information is no longer stored in-house but with third parties.

Our customers:
- Material manufacturers who evaluate and benchmark their products
- Cell manufacturers evaluating and benchmarking cell samples in prototype lines
- Research and development: materials/cells/stacks/modules/packs, special analysis procedures

name: Nostos Genomics
about:
At Nostos Genomics, we partner with genetic testing labs to give more people with genetic diseases a fast and clear diagnosis.

Over 300 million people live with a rare genetic disease and for most, the journey from the first symptoms to a diagnosis takes more than 5 years. Even after that, diagnoses are often incorrect, and many people end up not being diagnosed at all.

Now, new technology is allowing millions to benefit from genetic testing for diagnosis, while at the same time targeted therapies for previously untreatable disorders are being developed.

But the last step in genetic testing – interpreting mutations – remains laborious and costly. It can take a genetic testing lab weeks to interpret data from a single patient. Because of limited understanding of the consequences of mutations, the test results are often inconclusive and leave 70% of people undergoing a genetic test without diagnosis.

Our CE-certified platform leverages a unique combination of machine learning and synthetic biology to characterize mutations at scale and automate the interpretation. By offering it to labs, we enable them to diagnose more people in a fraction of the time.

name: SteadyPay
about: SteadyPay's vision is to become the lifetime financial partner of gig-economy workers globally.  SteadyPay's app enables gig economy workers to enjoy regular income even when they work irregular hours (due to such factors as reduced shifts, fewer bookings, time of sick and holidays).   Using the SteadyPay mobile app, customers securely link to their bank via open banking. SteadyPay will then calculate a users average income and monitor for when their income drops below that average.   When this happens we provide a top-up, advancing money straight to the customer's bank to bring their income back up to their average.   No interest is charged on any top-ups; we are a subscription credit service.   By protecting income from volatility, we're enabling gig-economy workers to budget with confidence for everyday bills and essentials. Therefore reducing the need to use high-cost credit solutions that trigger debt spirals.  SteadyPay is authorised and regulated by the UK FCA.

sigo ist ein Start-up mit Sitz in Darmstadt, das E-Lastenräder im Sharing betreibt. Das Unternehmen ist mit seinen induktiven Ladestationen einer der ersten deutschlandweit agierenden Anbieter eines vollautomatischen E-Lastenrad-Systems. Für den Sharing-Betrieb wurden eigene, auf die Vermietung angepasste Lastenräder entwickelt: hochwertige Technik, robust, einfach zu bedienen. Die Räder werden an einer stationären Ladestation induktiv aufgeladen, sodass sie schnell verfügbar sind.  Die Ausleihe ist dank einer App nicht an Öffnungszeiten gebunden. 

sigo fährt ein B2B2C-Geschäftsmodell, das sich zum einen  an Endnutzer:innen richtet und zum anderen an Partner:innen wie Wohnungswirtschaft, Kommunen, Institutionen, den öffentlichen Nahverkehr, Energieversorger und Projektentwickler.

Durch das Sharing-Modell werden Quartiere für Mieterinnen und Mieter attraktiver, Parkplätze werden obsolet und letztendlich ist die Nutzung des sigo Lastenrades ein Beitrag zur Beruhigung der Städte und zum Klimaschutz. 

Das Unternehmen wurde im Mai 2017 von Tobias Lochen gegründet. Im Februar 2020 wurde in Kooperation mit der Nassauischen Heimstätte der erste Standort in Darmstadt eröffnet. Daraufhin startete das Roll-out weiterer Standorte z. B. in Bochum, Hannover, Solingen und Wiesbaden. Weitere Stationen sind in der Umsetzung. Geschäftsführer sind Tobias Lochen (CEO), Philipp Harter (CFO) und Edin Zekanovic (CMO).

name: Cold-sense
about:
We are a high-tech company making new and existing cold rooms more energy efficient, safer and environmentally friendly.

The challenge:
Heat exchangers in cold rooms operate below the freezing point of water and are prone to frost buildup - just like in a refrigerator or freezer. Frost formation leads to increased power consumption and reduced cooling capacity. Heat exchangers therefore need to be defrosted regularly. 

Our solution:
We develop customized and intelligent system solutions to prevent ice formation as well as to start the defrosting process automatically and adapting it to the complex logistical processes of the costumers. To do this, we equip cold rooms with our innovative ice sensor technology and provide monitoring and data analysis of the entire room.

The combination of our precise sensor technology with artificial intelligence allows an automated, safe and efficient control of the cold warehouse. Our solutions also reduce the footprint of one of the largest electricity consumers in the world: Process and space cooling.

About us:
We are a customer-focused, high-tech company with the mission to develop innovative, reliable, and robust system solutions to optimize technical equipment in cold and icing environments. Our long-term goal is to become the largest partner in Europe in the field of energetic efficiency of cold rooms. 

In the next 3 years, we are aiming to save at least 50,000 tones CO2 each year, helping companies of all sizes, from small fast food restaurants to larger facilities to be more sustainable.

about:
avegoo bietet Unternehmen die Möglichkeit ihre Mitarbeiter deutschlandweit flexibel und ortsunabhängig zu beschäftigen. Dabei profitieren sie von einem Netzwerk, welches ihnen Büroarbeitsplätze und Meetingräume zur Verfügung stellt.

Wie das funktioniert?

Die Plattform avegoo bietet ein übergreifendes Partnernetzwerk an unterschiedlichsten Arbeitsorten, welche flexibel, gebucht und nach einem Pay-per-Use Prinzip genutzt werden können. Die verfügbaren Arbeitsplätze befinden sich vorrangig in Coworking Spaces, Hotels & Cafés sowie in freien Büroflächen unserer Netzwerkpartner, als auch auf geeigneten Flächen im Grünen. Angestellte & Freelancer haben die Möglichkeit, Arbeitsplätze sowie Meetingräume und Zusatz-Features mit optimaler Ausstattung flexibel und nach ihren individuellen Bedürfnissen zu finden und zu buchen. 
Unsere Dienstleistung umfasst nicht nur die Vermittlung von freien Arbeitsplätzen und Meetingräumen, wir verschlanken auch Prozesse und übernehmen die Abrechnung auf Seiten der Kunden und Partner. 

Sie als Unternehmen können sich als Kunden auf der avegoo Plattform registrieren und Nutzerprofile sowie Budgets für ihre Mitarbeiter anlegen. Ihre Mitarbeiter loggen sich anschließend in unserer App ein. Über diese können sie Arbeitsplätze nach ihren persönlichen Bedürfnissen finden und buchen.
Am Ende des Monats erhalten Sie eine gebündelte Abrechnung über alle genutzten Tage/Stunden von avegoo gestellt.

name: Mentalis
about:
mentalis versorgt Menschen mit psychischen Erkrankungen nach erfolgter Behandlung im Krankenhaus mit einer nahtlosen, digitalen Nachsorge. Algorithmus-basierte Apps und Tele-Coachings stabilisieren die in der Klinik erarbeiteten Therapieerfolge und überführen Patient:innen bei Bedarf zielgerichtet in weiterführende Behandlungen der Regelversorgung. So können die hohe Rehospitalisierungsrate im Bereich der F-Diagnosen reduziert, komplexere Folgebehandlungen vermieden sowie individuelles Leid und Kosten für die Gesellschaft verringert werden. Die mentalis Nachsorge knüpft nahtlos an die Krankenhausbehandlung an, da sie technisch und prozessual in den Entlassprozess der Krankenhäuser integriert ist. Durch den Einschreibeprozess im Krankenhaus sowie einen intelligenten Algorithmus ist die Nachsorge maximal Patient:innen-orientiert, was zu hohen Adhärenz- und Completer-Raten führt. Die Wirksamkeit der mentalis Programme wurde in mehreren klinischen Studien nachgewiesen. 

mentalis provides seamless, digital aftercare following mental health treatment in a hospital. Algorithm-based apps and tele-coachings stabilize the therapeutic success achieved in the hospital and, if necessary, transfer patients to further treatment in routine care. We aim at reducing the high rehospitalization rates in the domain of mental disorders, more complex follow-up treatments, and individual suffering and costs for society. mentalis ties in seamlessly with hospital treatment, as it is integrated technically and procedurally into the hospital discharge process. Due to the integration in the hospital enrollment process as well as the intelligent algorithm, our aftercare is extremely patient-centered, resulting in high adherence and completer rates. The effectiveness of the mentalis programs has been proven in several clinical studies.

name: Kymera Labs
about:
Data owners, retailers, financial institutions, healthcare organizations: are you seeking a proven way to effectively mobilize and monetize your data without breaching GDPR / HIPAA and other privacy regulations?

Kymera Labs invites you to join the synthetic data revolution – newly generated data that scales the peaks that data anonymization failed to reach.

What is synthetic data? It’s entirely new data based on real data. While the real data is kept secure and used only for specific necessary purposes, the synthetic data can be utilized for every other possible use case. Crucially, synthetic data maintains the statistical quality and data features of the original information, while being free from privacy and sharing limitations. The possibilities are endless.

Founded in Israel, Kymera Labs is a privately-held company that was formed to answer a single challenging question: how can sensitive data be simultaneously secure and unlocked?

The solution is Kymera’s groundbreaking Synthetic Data Fabrication Software, which generates brand new data that mimics the real data in every way. This synthetic data can then be used in every case where previously only the real, sensitive data would do – such as training AI/ML models, improving data management processes, developing POCs, and more.

Our synthetic data has already gained approval from some of the world’s largest financial institutions. Contact us today to learn how your organization can start unlocking your data’s true potential.

name: LIDROTEC
about:
Material processing with ultrashort laser pulses is currently one of the most innovative production and manufacturing processes, and allows high-precision cutting, drilling and structuring of a wide variety of materials.

We aim to expand the application potential of ultrashort pulse laser processing through an innovation:

We efficiently use liquids in the laser processing zone, which greatly cools the workpiece and removes ablation products such as particles. As a result, the processing speed can be increased whilst maintaining high precision and achieving significantly cleaner surfaces.

Using our years of experience in the field of micromachining with ultrashort pulse lasers in liquids, we are currently working on building a robust industrial laser system. The implementation of this project is supported by the funding of the „EXIST-Forschungstransfer“ (BMWi).

name: Wirelane
about:
Wirelane ist ein zukunftsorientierter Full Service Provider und bewegt die Zukunft der Elektromobilität – Zuverlässige Hardware trifft smarte Software.
Die Firma ist aktuell in 5 Ländern (D, F, S, NL, CH) aktiv und hat Erfahrung mit großen Industriekunden (VW, Vattenfall, Bouygues u.a.) und ist in Europa einer der führenden Spezialanbieter für Hardware, Software und App-Lösungen im Bereich Elektromobilität. Wirelane bietet die Gesamtlösung als Software-as-a-Service („SaaS“) für B2C Endkunden und B2B Elektromobilitätsanbieter jeder Art. Drei Bereiche werden dabei optimal miteinander verbunden:  Hardware, Backoffice und Zugangsmedium (App & RFID Token).

Constantin Schwaab, der seit der ersten Stunde selbst überzeugter Elektromobilist ist, gründete gemeinsam mit einem motivierten Team im April 2016 die Firma Wirelane GmbH. Aktuell arbeiten an den 3 Standorten Saarbrücken, Berlin und München insgesamt 30 Mitarbeiter für eine saubere Zukunft.
Neben der Steuerung und Verwaltung von Ladesäulen entwickelte das Unternehmen eine neue High-Tech-Ladesäule für den privaten wie öffentlichen Bereich. Diese macht den Ladevorgang noch schneller und unkomplizierter als herkömmliche Ladesäulen. Die Wirelane-App erlaubt Zugriff auf 60.000 Ladepunkte in ganz Europa. Knapp 6.000 Ladepunkte nutzen bereits die Wirelane-Software für sämtliche nachgelagerten Abrechnungsvorgänge. Gemeinsam mit Wirecard wurde erstmals ein Zahlvorgang entwickelt, der es ermöglicht, den Ladevorgang per kontaktloser Kreditkartenzahlung (Tap Payment) zu steuern und abzuwickeln. Darüber hinaus konnte demonstriert werden, dass Blockchain basierte dezentrale Bezahlvorgänge über ein in unserer App integriertes Ethereum-Wallet möglich sind.

Email makes up 20% of a typical hotel's revenue, but especially in these times it is difficult to ensure timely and professional answers with limited staffing and colleagues with limited reservations experience.

HERA (Hotel Email Reservation Assistant) is a simple Outlook or Gmail Add-in which reads the incoming Emails and automatically looks up the availability and displays it directly in Outlook so that agent can customize the offer and send a perfect Email in seconds.

Quicker and more compelling responses lead to increased revenue, combined with time savings of up to 70%   The best part is that by using HERA you also make sure that Credit Cards are safely and secured collected with no extra effort.


Available at the Microsoft Apps Store https://appsource.microsoft.com/en-us/product/office/WA200000060?tab=Overview 
or Chrom Addon Store:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/hera-by-hotel-res-bot/pjgfeacpjmjaiohbdaiodnfgnblgegld

Hera@hotelresbot.com

name: MagnoTherm Solutions
about:
MAGNOTHERM® is an emerging university spin-off from Technische Universität Darmstadt with world leading expertise in permanent magnets and magnetic cooling.

Our technology, based on solid state materials and water, is capable of replacing standard gas compression cooling or heating solutions in compliance with current and future f-gase regulation standards.

Our developed cutting-edge energy conversion solutions allow cooling and heating with low pressure systems (approx. 0.5 bar) and is 40% more efficient than current systems. At the same time it complies with all current and future EU F-gas regulations, is explosion free and non-imflammable. It is efficiently scalable in all sizes (from 0.5 to 5 kW) for thermal energy conversion units in decentralized, mid-range powered applications.

With our 100% green technology, we are able to meet the world’s fast growing demand of clean and sustainable cooling and heating applications.

persomatch bietet aktuell den weltweit ersten und einzigen Customer Self Service, um Stellenanzeigen direkt bei Google zu schalten!

name: German Bionic
about:
Company

German Bionic Systems, headquartered in Augsburg, is the first European developer and manufacturer of exoskeletons for industrial use. Exoskeletons are human-machine systems that combine human intelligence and machine power, thereby enabling individuals to gain increased strength and endurance. German Bionic is one of the world's leading robotics companies focusing on humans in Industry 4.0

Product

The active-assistive exoskeleton German Bionic CRAY X was specially designed for people manually handling goods and tools, in collaboration with leading ergonomists. Working with its wearer, it reduces compression pressure in the lower back area when lifting heavy loads, thus preventing accidents at work and musculoskeletal injuries. The German Bionic CRAY X uses new micromechanical components and an ultralight ergonomic carrying system.
 
Linking robust hardware with the latest cloud and IoT technologies, the German Bionic IO platform is the gateway to highest performance solutions and true integration in enterprise systems – raising the bar for productivity and the health and safety of workers. The suite consists of four modules each designed to solve issues in specific areas. Together, German Bionic IO represents the leading IoT suite for the exoskeleton industry.

name: Dealcode
about:
At Dealcode, we finally make your B2B and SaaS sales teams data-driven. Leverage the value of AI predictive sales analytics to increase win-rates and revenue with our unique AI Guided Selling Software.

The only thing you need to do is to connect your CRM with Dealcode. And you will know who will be your next client.

AI Guided Selling Software enables sales teams driving better, faster and more secure to their destination. In plain text: Winning more deals faster. 

During a sales cycle a lot of engagement happens between buyer and seller. Which kind of sales activities are the right one might differ from seller to seller and buyer to buyer. Finding the best way for each situation might be hard, which often leads sales reps to listen to their gut feeling. But this may not always be the ideal path. What kind of clients match my sales profile? Do I focus on the right prospects? Where do I waste time? Do I show enough engagement in terms of progress in the sales process? Am I using the right communication tools? When is the right time to place the offer?

All these questions can be answered by a Guided Selling Software.

LIFT THE GOLD TREASURE IN YOUR CRM
Existing CRM data contain valuable information about patterns and behaviors of the individual winning formula for your sales team. Machine learning algorithms are capable of analysing these patterns. As a result, AI Guided Selling can act as a personal trainer on the edge of the field to give guidance and recommendations for each individual seller and sales process. This is where Dealcode's AI Guided Selling Software comes into play. Connected to any CRM system it provides tailored guidance and insight, paving the individual path to success. It identifies patterns and individual weaknesses in the sales process that one is not aware of and recommends immediate action to get deals won. Furthermore Dealcode provides sales leaders with actionable insights on how the team is currently engaging vs. the best way.

We provide systems to fully automate the coordination & orchestration of heterogeneous fleets with trucks, cars, buses, autonomous vehicles & delivery robots in open environments. We model Digital Business Twins of vehicles to let them make autonomous decisions and self-organize as a fleet.

Our vision is to enable the Machine Economy in logistics, what we call Swarm Logistics, where vehicles of competing companies orchestrate themselves fully autonomously with flexible time and location for trans-shipments. Vehicles are coordinating themselves like swarms and a server-less infrastructure based on Distributed Ledger Technology.

run by machines, based on blockchain and powered by AI.

Fleet Control - FULLY AUTOMATED DISPATCHING AND SCHEDULING

Carry out your daily dispatching, scheduling and planning of a whole fleet in a few minutes, fully automated by one mouse click and save up to 35% costs due to better planning.

You can integrate the Auto-Dispatcher easily into the existing Transport Management Systems (TMS) using the REST API interface.

Imprint: https://www.swarmlogistics.net/impressum.html

At vly, our mindset is health-first and our products are designed by nutritionists and then brought to life by food scientists. Our vision is to create the healthiest plant-protein food products consumers have ever consumed.

Within less than a year of trading, we already sold more than 1 million liter of milk alternative and scaled to >5.000 POS. We're beyond excited by this rapid development and are convinced that this is just the beginning.

Mit dem Drying Towel Max 2.0 Trockentuch gehören Wasserflecken auf Lack oder Folie der Vergangenheit an. Durch die spezielle Herstellungsart und Dichte ist es das wahrscheinlich weltweit saugstärkste und hochwertigste Auto-Trockentuch das du kaufen kannst.

Autopflege bedeutet für uns Begeisterung & Leidenschaft. Unser Anspruch ist, diese Begeisterung & Leidenschaft gegenüber Fahrzeugen und deren Reinigung & Pflege für die Menschen zu bewahren & zu steigern, die bereits Fahrzeug-Begeistert sind, sie für jene zu eröffnen, die sich nach ihr sehnen – und sie auch für kommende Generationen zu sichern.

name: MetisMotion
about:
We are a Munich based tech Start-up, founded in 2018. Our core competence covers ultra-dynamic and space/ weight saving linear force actuators. The MetisMotion technology platform combines decades of experience in actuator development for challenging automotive and industrial applications. We are further addressing diverse use-cases, spanning from aviation to robotics.
Compared to conventional linear actuators, our actuators are up to 80% smaller and lighter and respond up to 10x faster. In addition, they bring inherent sensing capabilities, which would not be readily available in electromagnetic, hydraulic or pneumatic solutions. This allows our solutions to drive the electrification of hydraulics for the Industry 4.0 revolution.

Our goal is to make at least 20 acquisitions over the next 12 months, then to further optimize and grow the assets post-acquisition.  Founded by two HBS graduates: one who built an e-commerce business to €700mn+ in revenue as co-founder, and the other a former Goldman Sachs SSG with extensive PE roll-up experience. Together, they raised over €100mn in seed financing led by Cherry Ventures, Felix Capital and Silicon Valley-based TriplePoint Capital with participation from Village Global.

Banger Games is developing the currency to unify all gaming currencies, establishing the new global gaming economy. We provide decentralized Play2Earn tools for gaming, a second layer solution on top of any game. Our new crypto gaming platform will bring the fun back into the Play2Earn model with the best traditional games, including CSGO, Call of Duty, DOTA 2, etc.… and all the new ones yet to come in an industry that is growing all the time.

The aim is to become the gamers’ and publishers’ go-to hub, where they will find a broad range of opportunities to compete, challenge, create, earn, trade, and enjoy a complete gaming experience.

Banger Games is the Netflix of gaming, an ecosystem in which gamers, content producers, developers, and publishers will find the best environment to successfully achieve their goals within the industry and benefit from all the advantages of finding the whole community unified in one place.

As a gamer, you can improve your skill level through participating in various activities such as fully automated SMART Tournaments (executed through SMART contracts), Battle Pass, in-game objectives, and P2P cloud gaming. In return, it will reward gamers with NFTs, Bombcoins, and a vast amount of other fabulous prizes offered by recognized brands and influencers.

As a publisher, you can help scale your studio utilizing the power of the Banger Games ecosystem - the new middle ground between the different shareholders within the industry. Benefit from new monetization tools, community access, anti-cheat client, grants, and investment opportunities.

The Banger Games team has experience across industries, including esports, blockchain, marketing, and entertainment. Our team members have worked ESL, EASports, Giants, Okex, Chainlink, Crypto Kitties, IBM, Booking.com, and many more top-tier projects.

KONVOI installiert Radarsensoren am LKW Auflieger und überwacht damit den Nahbereich jedes Fahrzeugs. Die Gefahrensituation um das Fahrzeug wird stetig analysiert und bei Erwartung eines Gefahrenfalls mit stufenweise stärkeren Präventionsmaßnahmen reagiert.

Wir entwickeln Hardware, Software und Services, um ein ganzheitliches security-as-a-service  Angebot abzubilden. Das Herzstück bilden unsere konfigurierten und modifizierten Radarsensoren im Zusammenspiel mit intelligenter Software.

Die ARCWARE 3D-Cloud Plattform ermöglicht VIRTUELLE 3D INTERAKTIONEN auf allen Kanälen für jedes Device.

name: Careloop
about:
We are a startup located in the heart of Berlin, Germany, on a social mission to solve the biggest challenge of the German health care system, the shortage of nurses. With Careloop we revolutionize the health care recruiting market as foreign nursing staff have the opportunity to find their dream job in Germany - without having to apply themselves.

As an online marketplace, Careloop connects qualified nurses from abroad with healthcare and nursing service companies in Germany. We turn the recruiting process upside down so that companies apply directly to candidates online who are only displayed if they are prescreened by us and actively looking for a new job.

Follow us and be a part of our journey!

name: Staiy
about:
Staiy is the first sustainable fashion marketplace merging aesthetics, sustainability and AI-technology in one place. Spotlighting international brands that craft their pieces in a responsible way, Staiy gives sustainable fashion a contemporary platform that reflects the modern consumers. Low environmental impact, ethical production and high personalization allow to discover mindful fashion without compromising on style.
Staiy’s overarching mission is to accelerate the transition towards sustainable fashion, restoring timeless values by implementing the latest tools. Innovative technologies, materials, concepts and production practices meet in a contemporary platform that reflects the modern consumer.
To define a new perception of sustainable fashion, Staiy roots around core concepts which can be found in its name: style, sustainability, AI. With leading sustainable brands including Komodo, Rotholz and Phyne, Staiy is focused on curating the finest selection of sustainable brands and styles available online. For Staiy’s founders, sustainability is not a trend. Rather it is the ethical foundation underpinning the lifestyle of the future, which they want to spread through their platform. Water, Air, Materials, Work Conditions and Commitment are the sustainability pillars upon which Staiy evaluates each of its selected brands, taking a step beyond standard evaluations to assess the broader picture. Artificial Intelligence signifies digital progress, and is implemented by Staiy to smoothen the approach to sustainable fashion. The personalization algorithm of Staiy uses the universal language of images, scanning product pictures and detecting their style, to then match items with the individual style of the consumer. 
The marketplace believes in the power of fashion as a means to make a statement. The platform stands to renew the importance of this dimension, connecting brands and clients through the rediscovery of sustainable craftsmanship, inspiring stories of innovati

name: Freshflow
about:
We’re supercharging the food supply chain and reducing global food waste. Freshflow is a new way to manage fresh products for grocery retailers. We do accurate order forecasting and replenishment that massively reduce food waste while still keeping shelves full. Doing that we reduce global carbon emissions, make fresh food cheaper and more available, and generate millions in profits for our clients.

We’re already working with the largest grocery retailer in Germany, as well as several online quick grocery retailers across Europe. We’ve secured funding from top investors and several highly relevant angel investors in the space. We’re also in close collaboration with professors at the DKFI, the German Research Center for Artificial Intelligence.

name: Liminalytics
about: Integrated analytics that assess climate & other sustainability impacts, both physical & transitional, across value chains, and translated into financial risks and opportunities. We aim to build the leading tool for banks to analyze climate and sustainability risks. To this end, we combine state-of-the-art models, the highest quality available data, and intuitive user interfaces. We are an agile start-up on a mission to create a positive impact. We are not a database looking for a client. Our starting point is the increasing urgency for banks (and other financial institutions and companies) to map and understand their sustainability risks. This drives the questions we ask and the methods we employ. We value scientific rigor and practicability. Combining both in our solutions sets us apart.

name: Live Rooster
about: Live Rooster is the Universal social Live streaming portal for event organizers and content creators to easily schedule shows or events with the ability to go live on specific dates. This simple, fun, and exciting platform promotes genuine connections brought through similar interests, thereby further empowering content creators to turn their interest into a Live Streaming Talkshow. What do we offer? -Access to a pool of upcoming events and Talkshows -Quick & easy overview -Access to video & audio opportunities -Effortless earning through our ticketing feature (Choose to have a free or paid event and select your ticket price) -Keep your audience up to date with future scheduled events and shows. name: Agrivero
about:
We founded Agrivero.ai in 2020, a deep tech remote-first company, with a mission to change global agricultural supply chains for the better.

We believe in a future where agricultural supply chains are fully traceable, fair, and efficient. Value and information have to be redistributed to allow producers to earn more and adapt to climate change, consumers know where their food comes from and trading companies finally digitalize their processes. This is the only way forward towards real sustainable food production and distribution. 

We develop solutions for quality control and traceability of agricultural products. The combination of technologies like Computer Vision, Hyperspectral Imaging, and AI enables us to scan the produce and analyze it non-intrusively, allowing our customers to analyze samples 3x faster with increased accuracy and reliability. This information is shared throughout the supply chain with producers and buyers to ensure full traceability and reduce information silos.

The first focus of Agrivero.ai is green coffee trading, which suffers from inefficient manual quality control and is eager to enforce traceability and fairtrade practices.

name: Crafting Future GmbH
about:
Einweg- und Verpackungsmüll ist eines der größten Probleme unserer Zeit. Eine Welt ohne Kunststoffe wird es aber nicht geben. Deshalb haben wir es uns zur Aufgabe gemacht, die Kunststoffindustrie zu hinterfragen. 

Bei der Materialauswahl, dem Produktdesign und der Produktentwicklung legen wir ein besonderes Augenmerk auf das Ende des Lebenszyklus eines Produkts. Dabei berücksichtigen wir die Rückgewinnung einer gleichwertigen Menge an Kunststoff im Vergleich zu der bei der Herstellung verwendeten Menge. 

Wir entwickeln unsere eigenen wiederverwendbaren Produkte für die Take-Away-Industrie und realisieren Projekte und Produkte gemeinsam mit Kund*innen auf der Grundlage individueller Anforderungen.

Insbesondere in Hinblick auf die kommende Mehrwegpflicht sind wir Partner für die Gastronomie, beraten und informieren über Mehrwegverpackungen und Mehrwegsysteme und bieten entsprechende Mehrwegprodukte an.

We're reinventing the way mental health care is perceived and delivered through a digital platform and in-person experience, integrating authenticity, empathy and a modern brand to reduce the stigma around mental health and build the most elevated end-to-end mental healthcare experience, that will bring high quality mental health support to everyone. Our team of innovators, psychologists, and technologists is on a mission to make caring for our mental health a priority.

name: LQID
about:
LQID is a lifestyle banking and digital commerce ecosystem. 
 
We operate two separate businesses: a digital bank, currently undergoing the authorisation process, and a mobile social marketplace. 
 
LQID has been established because the world is changing, and we see these changes driving a new way of working, a new way of operating in a digital economy, and a new way of managing money. 

We see an opportunity for a socially connected economy that is driven by individual consumers, entrepreneurs, and small businesses. 

We understand how the internet has transformed people’s lives, but we also strongly believe that there needs to be a better balance between technology and the human experience, especially when it is something as important as managing your money.
Our aim is to transform the consumer experience in a way that helps make life smoother for people and businesses, using technology to enhance experiences and provide opportunities for new businesses and communities to grow.

Alongside that, it also provides smart tools to maximize the efficiency of a restaurant’s autonomous home deliveries, while increasing the productivity and the coordination between production and logistics.

name: Salamantex
about:
SALAMANTEX is an Austrian FinTech company pioneering a new era of payment with digital assets. With smart, trusted and secure software solutions, SALAMANTEX enables merchants to accept cryptocurrencies, loyalty points and other digital or tokenized items as alternative forms of payment for both in-store payments and ecommerce.

Established in 2017, SALAMANTEX has since rolled out its solutions across Austria and is currently expanding throughout the entire Euro zone. This growth is fast-tracked through partnerships with major acquirers and point-of-sale device manufacturers for a seamless integration into merchants’ existing payment infrastructures.

The intuitive, platform-based applications from SALAMANTEX can be used online in webshops or in stores, supermarkets, restaurants, and hotels on a POS terminal or Android device.

name: Prospecter Ventures
about:
Value first. Everything else follows.

How valuable is a digital marketplace today? In tomorrow’s marketplace economy, value is created through relevance, reach, and scalability. And through the right message. To the right person. At the right time. Value is in our DNA.


Vision first. Technology second.

What changes the world? Technology? Or a potent vision that makes this technology what it is: a game changer? The latter turns technology into a powerful tool for creating sustainable growth.


Value first. Platform second.

What makes a platform successful in the long run? Relevance! Its importance for customers and vendors is the tangible added value for both sides of the value chain. Fused by an integrative technology and smart data, a multidimensional platform becomes the marketplace of the future.


People first. Technology second.

Which role do people play in modern enterprises? They develop, create, utilize, and scale ideas with the help of state-of-the-art technology – not the other way around. Innovation starts with people.

name: boltzplatz
about: boltzplatz - numerical plasma dynamics GmbH provides engineering & consulting services in the field of numerical modelling and simulation for companies in high-tech industries. With our unique expertise in rarefied gas & plasma dynamics, we extend your research & development department cost-efficiently. Our focuses are vacuum- & plasma-based technologies such as vacuum surface coating, semiconductor manufacturing and in-space propulsion. For this purpose, we offer complete simulation and development projects as well as technical support around the open-source code PICLas.

name: Byder
about:
Wir glauben, dass Menschen im Recruiting eine zentrale Rolle spielen müssen.

Technologie kann den Menschen bei der Rekrutierung von neuen Mitarbeitern nicht ersetzen, aber sie kann die Zusammenarbeit verbessern. Bei byder.io nutzen wir Technologie, um die richtigen Menschen zur richtigen Zeit zusammenzubringen.

In nahe zu einem Drittel der Stellenwechsel in Deutschland sind Personalvermittler oder Personalberater involviert. Unternehmen aller Größenordnungen suchen für ihre wichtigsten Positionen die Hilfe externer Dienstleister. Aber zum größten Teil findet die Suche und Zusammenarbeit in einem aufwendigen, offline Prozess statt.  Sowohl für die Unternehmen, die Hilfe suchen, als auch für die Personalvermittler, die sie unterstützen, stellt das oft eine große Herausforderung dar.

Mit byder.io verbinden wir Top-Arbeitgeber und spezialisierte Personalvermittler auf einer Plattform und machen die Zusammenarbeit besonders bei kritischen Stellenbesetzungen transparenter, schlanker und effizienter als je zuvor.

name: vitreo
about:
Our vision is to make your IBC supply chain processes more efficient, reliable and sustainable. To do this, we use the latest 'machine economy' technologies to make previously unused information available. 

Bring your IBC supply chain online with IoT sensors, receive visibility and work with real-time information.

name: niuli

name: raffle yourmarketplace UG
about: Nie wieder „Was ist letzter Preis“ Anfragen. Mit einem einzigen Bild und dem Wunschpreis können ungenutzte Dinge aus dem eigenen Haushalt zum Verkauf angeboten werden. Die Nutzer können mithilfe eines Matching-Prinzips durch die verschiedenen Kategorien stöbern. Mit einem einfachen Swipe nach links zeigt der Nutzer das ihm der Artikel nicht gefällt und der nächste Artikel aus der Kategorie wird angezeigt. Mit einem Swipe nach rechts bietet der Nutzer 0,50 € auf den Artikel. Nach Erreichen des Wunschpreises durch die Gebote, wird der Artikel unter allen Teilnehmer verlost. So erhält der Verkäufer immer seinen gewünschten Preis und der Käufer zahlt nur 0,50 €. Vom Fahrrad bis hin zu einem Auto und das alles für nur 0,50 €.

name: x-cardiac

100% interoperable: x-cardiac products integrate seamlessly into your hospital IT system.
Clinically validated: We develop algorithms that proved their superior performance in clinical studies.
Real-time prediction: x-cardiac detects complications right from the patient’s ICU admission allowing for rapid intervention.

Our DNA: Scientifically proven and clinically validated

Science is in our genes. Not only was x-cardiac co-founded by two of the leading scientists in the field of clinical application of AI. We also stay true to the promise of science, that is: 'Science is based on evidence'. Right from the start, we have maintained close professional and personal contacts to our clinical research partners like the German Heart Center Berlin (DHZB) and the Charité Berlin. Together we continue to improve the standard - precisely tailored to our customers' needs.

Intensive care units (ICU) are highly challenging environments that confront care teams with a demanding caseload and require rapid decision making, often in reactive behaviour.

This is where our first product x-c-bleeding comes in. It enables you to achieve proactive action to recognize postoperative bleeding before the devastating consequences manifest. 

x-c-bleeding is eligible for KHZG funding.

name: River Cleaning
about:
The amount of plastic waste poured into the seas is higher every year, and various studies indicate that most of this waste comes from rivers. 
The main problem to operate in river environments is the need to find a common and adaptable solution to very different situations, both in terms of width and depth of the watercourse and in terms of navigability.

The solution we have studied is a solution with a very low environmental impact, modular and able to adapt to each watercourse. In the study of this project, physical simulation tests were carried out using software and prototypes were made and tested to verify their functionality.

The RIVER CLEANING system, through the rotating movement of special floating devices anchored to the bottom and their particular transversal arrangement with respect to the course of the river, conveys all the floating waste in transit to a single point, where a collection system can then be positioned.

Watch the video on our website!

Transparent Sie sehen genau, wie viele passende Kandidaten es auf der Plattform gibt, welche Reichweite Ihre Stellenanzeige erzielt, und wie viele Kandidaten sich für Ihre Anzeige interessieren. Vorteile für Bewerber: Einfach Sie legen nur einmal Ihr Profil an und erhalten sofort Stellenangebote, die exakt zu Ihrem Profil passen. Our clients learn what PPAs are, which specific risks to be mitigated, and how PPAs are contracted. Green Energy Rating
Our standardized rating approach evaluates the willingness and capability of renewable energy projects, off-takers, and country-specific energy markets to enter into PPAs. Therefore, potential PPA counterparts are enabled to source and negotiate this contract in a fast and cost-efficient way.

Green Consulta Services
We support you in originating and contracting power purchase agreements by organizing and structuring PPA tenders or direct sourcing by using our excellent network to developers. IPPs, and off-takers. Additional services offered include site selection, permitting, land securing issues, technical design, contract negotiations, technical and financial due diligence. name: Dermagnostix
about:
At Dermagnostix, we envision the next level for molecular diagnostics in human skin to improve patients’ lives and clinical practice in dermatology.

Why Dermatology?
Dermatologic diseases are the 4th most common cause of all human illnesses.
Every individual experiences a skin disease at least once during their lifetime.
7 of the 15 best selling drugs are used in dermatology already today and many more promising treatments are in the pipeline.

Conventional Diagnostics 
... based on clinical view and histopathology are imprecise and impede the optimal use of the already available highly specific modern therapies in dermatology.

The Solution 
... is to offer modern diagnostics for modern therapies. With our first test – PsorEx – to differentiate between eczema and psoriasis on molecular level we achieved a milestone for molecular diagnostics in dermatology.

Dermagnostix offers a comprehensive technological platform for fast and objective molecular diagnostics in dermatology to reduce health care costs and improve patient treatment.

Dermagnostix provides molecular diagnostic solution for dermatology - economic, fast, easy and precise.

name: EVOCAL Health
about: What if we could early detect diseases and monitor health with nothing more than our voice?   We are on our mission to unlock the human voice as a prognostic and diagnostic marker for the early-detection of diseases and enable humanity to life a longer and healthier life.  EVOCAL Health is developing sophisticated Healthcare Intelligence Algorithms based on Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, that uses Vocal Biomarkers like voice-, breathing- and coughing noises to detect diseases.   Vocal Biomarkers have the potential to transform the way we detect and treat diseases through their accuracy, speed and cost-effectiveness. Unlike conventional testing methods, our vision is to use cost-effective everyday technologies like smartphones and enable a broad part of the population to detect and be diagnosed with Vocal Biomarkers on-scale, globally and wherever they are.  We are on a mission and if you wanna help us make our science become reality 1) Start now and donate your Vocal Biomarkers for labelling purposes for our "Open Research Project" at VOCALSforSCIENCE.com, 2) Spread the word about EVOCAL Health & VOCALSforSCIENCE.com, and 3) Get in touch with our Research Team via Mail (info@vocalsforscience.com)

name: EstateGuru
about:
In 2013 a group of real estate and fintech experts based in Tallinn, Estonia had a bright idea. What if they could break down the barriers which ensured that investing in secured property loans was a luxury only available to the wealthy and well-connected? And what if they could help entrepreneurs and visionaries in the property development business who struggle with the ‘one-size-fits all’ solutions offered by banks and major financial institutions at the same time? Thus EstateGuru was born.

Today, more than half a decade later, we have facilitated more than 2500 loans worth in excess of €380 million. Over 88 000 investors, from all walks of life and hailing from 109 countries, have earned average returns of 11.39% by backing property loans in Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Spain, Germany, Sweden and Finland with more markets to follow soon.

Due to the large and diversified investor base, with millions of EUR available to lend, our borrowers can get the money they need to realise their plans quickly, on their own terms, and investors can access pre-vetted and diversified, cross-border investment opportunities with a low barrier to entry and total transparency. Join us on our journey of building the bridges in property finance world.

Mit Tenera führen Bauunternehmen Ihre Hauptakteure in einem Netzwerk zusammen, harmonisieren Schnittstellen zwischen Tools und lassen Ihre Daten effizienter für sich arbeiten. Entscheidungen werden schneller datenbasiert getroffen. Die CCP baut auf die bestehende Infrastruktur auf und sichert maximale Flexibilität.
