name: Othermo
about:
Transparenz und Optimierung für Heizzentralen.

othermo ermöglicht die herstellerunabhängige Betriebsüberwachung und Analyse von Energiezentralen. Neben den Erzeugern sind wir in der Lage, eine große Bandbreite an weiteren Peripheriegeräten (z.B. Zähler, Pumpen oder Druckhaltungen) anzubinden. Dabei greifen wir auf die Bussysteme der angebundenen Komponenten zurück, um detaillierte Betriebsinformationen zu erhalten. 

Unsere webbasierte Plattform ermöglicht es Ihnen anschließend, die Anlage jederzeit umfassend im Blick zu haben und bei Störungen sofort informiert zu sein. Mit Hilfe der gesammelten Betriebsdaten versetzen wir Sie die Lage, Ihre Anlage aus der Ferne zu überwachen, Optimierungspotentiale zu identifizieren und die Effizienz des Gesamtsystems zu steigern. 

Mit einem selbst-lernenden Optimierungsalgorithmus und einer darauf basierenden Regelung optimieren wir den Betriebsablauf der Anlage. Statt der klassischen (auf aktuellen Messwerten basierenden) Regelungstechnik nutzen wir Vorhersagen über künftigen Verbrauch und Erzeugung, welche als Grundlage für die Optimierung dienen. Hierbei wird der wirtschaftlichste Betriebsablauf ("Fahrplan") identifiziert, welcher anschließend automatisiert umgesetzt wird.

name: Unconventional Capital
about: Entrepreneurial potential is global, but opportunity is not. Uncap aims to change that. We make seed funding accessible to every good entrepreneur. With our data-driven solution, we enable investing in Africa's bottom up growth. Through the use of analytics and behavioral science, we are able to conduct hands-off, semi-automated due diligence on thousands of entrepreneurs at a fraction of the usual costs. We invest following a standardized process using non-financial and financial metrics, giving every entrepreneur the same chance, no matter their location, gender or ability to produce polished pitch decks. Ultimately, this makes our solution scalable to thousands of entrepreneurs, thereby creating trust in a dynamic market. Working remotely is part of our DNA with people based in Munich, Nairobi, Berlin and San Francisco.

ARXUM® drives down costs in a highly competitive environment by helping companies to increase automation and data transfer and business logic robotization. 
- Transfer data between companies down to the machine level is controlled through smart contracts.
- Tracking of items in production and supply chain management is controlled through smart contracts, providing a single truth for all participants
- Tokenizing through smart contracts allows to count and control various items such as machine usage, budgets, user interactions or product counts.
Integrated blockchain cryptography ensures data security and immutable documentation and traceability.

name: Emax digital
about: Decode e-commerce: Langfristiger Erfolg im digitalen Handel durch Insights und Technologie!  We are emax digital a young start-up out of Munich. Online shopping is one of the most beautiful sideline activities in the world. However, Amazon & Co. are causing sleepless nights and headaches even for leading brands when dealing with the variety of self-service-tools and understanding the manifold data sets made available. Through strategic consulting and our smart SaaS platform we decode complex ecommerce patterns and offer relevant insights and actionable recommendations. We enable brands to optimize their appearances at the digital point of sale and boost sales.   Strategy & Planning: We analyse your business holistically and help you plan your individual e-commerce strategy for sustainable growth.  Retail Excellence: Optimize your retail health to increase organic traffic and visibility through strong selection, relevant content and excellent appearance on the digital shelf.  Marketing & Activation: Reach your marketing and sales objectives by leveraging Amazon‘s full marketing suite from Search (AMS) and Display (AAP) to custom executions (e.g. Prime Day).  Insights & Analytics: We use state-of-the-art tools and dashboards to decode the Amazon-blackbox and help you monitor, report and manage your Amazon business along meaningful KPIs.  The founders (Andreas Kleofas & Dominik Pietrowski): "As former Amazon executives we understand the complexity brands are facing in fast-paced digital environments. For 12+ years we worked closely with leading brands and manufacturers across the US and EU and developed successful e-commerce strategies for multiple verticals. We founded emax digital to help brands excel in e-commerce through smart tools, retail excellence and the right mix of marketing & activation."  Let us decode e-commerce together!

about:
VISION 
We need to stop wasting our planet’s resources. CO₂ emissions must be reduced. We are taking matters into our own hands by making clean mobility affordable for everyone. For you. For generations to come. 

THE SION
The Sion is the first series-produced car that can additionally charge its battery using solar power. A car that charges itself – a Solar Electric Vehicle (SEV).

The Sion is equipped with a 54 kWh battery, which corresponds to a total range of up to 305 km. Additional range is also provided by the solar panels, seamlessly integrated into the body of the car. These are able to harness the power of the sun and generate up to 245 km (average 112 km) per week of additional range at peak. Solar charging will be available whilst driving, to enable the most efficient use of daylight hours.

Our Mission:
With Sparrks Coaching we want to help employees and companies reach their full potential. 

How we put our mission into action:
We provide highly effective and personalized people development at all career stages. Our digital one-on-one Sparrks Coaching sessions are all facilitated exclusively by top executive coaches.

What distinguishes us from others:
Traditional coaching formats are time-consuming and expensive, which is why many employees reject them as an HR development tool. Yet it has been proven that coaching is the most effective approach to personal and professional development.

Our Sparrks Coaching format is cost- and time-efficient: individual goals are achieved in just two concise 45-minute coaching sessions. They take place in a digital format, making them convenient to fit into any schedule. Our coaching approach is based on the latest findings in learning research, which distinguishes it as highly innovative.

Our Coaches:

name: Numbat GmbH
about: Als Clean-Tech-StartUp aus Kempten liegt unser Fokus auf der Entwicklung, Produktion und Vermarktung unserer patentierten Klimaschutztechnologie für den Aufbau von Multi-Life Batteriezellen mit Schnellladefunktion. Der Numbat (Nachhaltiger umweltfreundlicher Multi-Lifecycle-Batteriespeicher) ermöglicht den Aufbau einer Schnellladeinfrastruktur mittels Multi-Life-Batteriespeicher flächendeckend, kostengünstig und ohne größere Eingriffe in die Stromnetzinfrastruktur. Seine durchdachten B2B Applikationen ermöglichen dem Betreiber eine optimale Stromnutzung – zur Eigenverbrauchsoptimierung oder zur Kostenreduzierung (Peak Shaving). Die Produktion legt den Fokus auf die Wiederverwertung von gebrauchten Batteriezellen, um ihnen weitere Lebenszyklen zu ermöglichen und Emissionen einzusparen. Der Pufferspeicher lädt sich aus erneuerbaren Energien, sodass der Elektroautomobilfahrer günstig, schnell und sauber laden kann. Ganz im Sinne unserer Vision: eine smarte Batterientechnologie und ein disruptives Geschäftsmodell zu vereinen, um eine Benchmark in der Ladeinfrastruktur zu setzen und einen nachhallenden und zukunftsträchtigen Beitrag in der Energiewende zu leisten. Bei Interesse oder Fragen senden wir Ihnen gerne ein Presse Kit: info@numbat.energy. -------------- As a clean-tech start-up from Kempten, our focus is on the development, production and marketing of our patented climate protection technology for the construction of multi-life battery cells with fast charging function. The Numbat (Sustainable Environmentally Friendly Multi-Lifecycle Battery Storage) enables the development of a fast-charging infrastructure using multi-life battery storage nationwide, cost-effectively and without major interventions in the power grid infrastructure. Its sophisticated B2B applications enable the operator to optimally use electricity – for self-consumption optimization.

about:

This is why we have developed the leading software to help financial institutions getting their clients' money back. RAQUEST is an easy yet reliable way for relief at source and reclaim of foreign withholding taxes. 

But how do we do it? That’s easy. We do what we do best: Speed up every step of the process using automation. As a subsidiary of Halvotec Information Services GmbH, RAQUEST has been built by experts in digitization and process automation. We thrive in an environment where innovation and knowledge meet. 

We believe that great things require dedication and the commitment to change the world. And the right bunch of people to get on board with you. Our team consists of experts and doers, visionaries and people out on a mission to change how it’s always been done. Our goal is to provide organizations and financial institutions with the skills and tools to get their clients' money back. name: Resolve
about: Resolve Biosciences is applying the power of Molecular Cartography™ to enable scientists to gain new insights based on the highest-resolution view of single-cell spatial biology. The platform features the company's proprietary, multiplexed, single-molecule detection technology, which offers full spatial context at subcellular resolution, all in a workflow that preserves the sample tissue. The platform offers unparalleled sensitivity and specificity that helps scientists detect individual transcripts and rare signals to interpret fundamental biology and rapidly advance the understanding of complex biological questions in critical fields such as oncology, neuroscience, and infectious disease. The technology has been under development since 2016 and is currently available through an oversubscribed early access program.

about:

With the SaaS solution from vchfy (pronounced „Vouchify"), online shops run their own dynamic couponing-, offer- and voucherpage that will easily reach the top ranking for search queries like „[online shop] coupon“. 

That way, potential customers, who already left the checkout process, will return and stay in the  funnel. Competitor's offers remain invisible and the user experience is fully in line with the online shop’s brand. This significantly reduces abandonments and doubles conversion rates for this channel.

In addition, smart features like basket-sensitive campaigns and gamification help online shops to optimize conversion rates, order value and margins.

name: SPITCH
about:

Wir sind ein Live-Fußballmanager, bei dem man an jedem Spieltag mit einer eigenen Mannschaft gegen andere teilnehmende Manager antritt. Mit einem Mix aus echten Fußballereignissen, seinem Fußballsachverstand und den richtigen statistischen Schlussfolgerungen, kann man schnell zu den besten Managern gehören und echtes Geld gewinnen.

Ein Team besteht aus elf individuell zusammengestellten Fußballspielern einer bestimmten Liga (z. B. Bundesliga) unter Berücksichtigung einer Budgetobergrenze (150 Mio. Euro). Dabei sammeln die einzelnen Manager Punkte, die auf der tatsächlichen (statistischen) Leistung der Fußballspieler in realen Wettbewerben basieren.

Unterschiedliche Teilnahmegebühren, Gewinnzonen und -summen unterscheiden jedes der vier Spielfelder. Während man bei der kostenlosen Variante bis zu 20 Euro gewinnen kann, erhält der Gewinner des 30 Euro Spielfeldes 4.000 Euro.

Alle lästigen Organisationsfragen rund um die Suche, Buchung und Fahrten zum Nachhilfelehrer entfallen. 
ubiMaster ist einzigartige Lernunterstützung per Flatrate: Schüler erhalten sooft Hilfe, wie sie es benötigen. 
Alle unsere Tutoren werden vorher geprüft und unterliegen einer laufenden Qualitätssicherung und Schulung. Der Unterricht findet über unsere sichere ubiMaster-App statt und ist immer personalisiert (1:1).

name: Sub Capitals
about:
We are Sub Capitals, a young and ambitious Fintech-Startup from Munich (Germany). We believe it is time to democratize artificial intelligence (AI) for private investors on the financial market. With the approach of direct AI trading, Sub Capitals takes over the entire portfolio management of private investors, who previously had difficulties to invest in the financial markets due to lack of time or expertise and only achieved low returns. Our approach can be compared to autonomous driving or in this case autonomous investing, where private investors can take their hands off the wheel or portfolio and leave both the placing of orders and the analysis processes to the AI. We call this Neo Investing, which creates more equality on the financial markets for all individuals through fair access to our AI.

Our beliefs:
The world is changing in so many different phases, most of them in pursuit of a better life together. We see too little of these changes in the global financial markets. It is time to demand more equality and a fairer approach to technological change. Our mission "democratize AI for private investors on the financial market". This is not just about access for all, but rather about fair prices and the possibility of using AI for a good cause. With our business we want to be part of the worldwide equal rights movement, which should also give everyone the same chances for financial equality. We are convinced that with the right will and a self-reinforcing and complementary network, this mission can be pursued, and we can approach global equality in small steps. Hence our motto: Enabling equality through Neo Investing.

name: cStream
about:
cStream is dedicated to an exciting and modern technical topic - the world of pumps.
We are developing a novel approach to fluid conveyance. With a piezo actuator, we generate a wave movement, whereby the fluid is pressed directly through a laterally sealed pump case.
The sStream PAM pump is clearly in this performance class
- More efficient
- Lighter
- More compact
-  More accurate dosing
than existing positive displacement pumps. Furthermore, the conveying direction can be reversed by electrical polarity reversal.

The entire cStream team is currently working on a prototype to produce a pilot series in 2021.

name: BIOBALANCE
about:
BioBalance is born from deep respect: for the wisdom of the human body, the advances of science and technology, and the profound healing power of nature.

Many of our products come from the land and the sea around us, or from certified organic producers around the world. As part of a balanced lifestyle, we use our products to keep ourselves and our families in optimal health: we insist that they be the safest and most effective natural solutions available.

We are committed to making natural health accessible by delivering certified quality and superior efficacy at an affordable price.

The Butler Family has thirty years’ experience in natural health and a strong understanding of the benefits of natural health products. From this deep knowledge base and New Zealand’s rich natural environment comes BioBalance: a range of high-quality and well-priced natural health products for local and international markets. BioBalance products are shipped daily around New Zealand and across the world, enhancing the wellbeing of people and animals in places as diverse as London, Shanghai, Tokyo, Sydney, Los Angeles and Seoul.

Located in the small South Island coastal community of Golden Bay, nestled between two of New Zealand’s celebrated National Parks (the Abel Tasman and the Kahurangi), BioBalance is at the heart of the spectacular environment from which many of its products are sourced.

All BioBalance products are GE-free and manufactured to strict New Zealand Food Safety Authority (NZFSA) and Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP) standards. We source organic products wherever possible, as certified by Asurequality Organic NZ. Pure and natural source materials combined with rigorous testing and manufacturing standards guarantee the quality, efficacy and safety of all BioBalance products. This commitment to high-quality natural health products has made BioBalance a popular and trusted name in natural health.

name: RIIICO
about: We enable intelligent and efficient processing of 3D point clouds in digital workflows. 3D scans are the foundation of every visual Digital Twin or BIM-Object but handling them is a huge pain. Objects in scans today have to be recognized and isolated by hand, costing the industry time and millions in labor costs. While automation is slowly entering the industry, most of it is based on heuristics or pseudo-AI which fail to be generally applicable. Our deep learning approach is changing that. Our solutions enable the automated recognition of objects in 3D scans, offering immense value for various industries from automotive to construction to manufacturing. Our highly intelligent data analysis precisely identifies and segments each object in the scan based on its 3D geometry and color. We make this knowledge available to the market as a technology and software provider in the form of value-adding tools and interfaces. Are you interested in a technical demonstration or would like to get in touch? Feel free to contact us at team[@]riiico.com

name: PANTOhealth
about: In future, the maintenance will not be done by the infrastructure owner. The maintenance of infrastructure will be done by companies which have better and bigger data from the infrastructure. These companies will use the collected data to find the trend of damages and predict the exact time and action of the maintenance operation. For this aim, they will use AI solution on the massive amount of data from infrastructure. They will reduce the maintenance cost (up to 80%) and improve lifetime (up to 20%) and uptime (up to 9%). These companies need high-quality data from infrastructure, which is the output of our products. The product is a package of the mainboard, camera and sensors which are designed to install on the pantograph. This product collects data (acceleration, displacement and video) from pantograph and catenary and sends to the server. In parallel, simulation software is used to process the collected data from the product. The processed data is useful to monitor the pantograph and catenary. In this project, the product will be rented to the train operators in the SAAS model (freemium and premium), and a massive amount of data will collect from all overhead lines and pantographs. The collected data will be subjected to big data analytics via Machine Learning algorithms.  Via the result of these analytics, we can estimate the trend of damages and predict the maintenance plan for pantograph and catenary. The leading service of this business is the monitoring reports and advisory maintenance plan for both pantograph and catenary.

name: _blaenk
about:
_blaenk entwickelt sich zum hybriden Omnichannel-Marktplatz für innovative Lifestyle Produkte. Sowohl stationär in Toplagen, als auch online wird den Konsumenten personalisiertes, erlebnisorientiertes Shopping geboten. Dabei liegt der Fokus auf hochwertigen Lifestyle-Produkten, die sich durch besondere Merkmale wie Innovationscharakter, Langlebigkeit oder Nachhaltigkeit von der Masse abheben. _blaenk bietet Produkte aus allen Consumer-Brand-Kategorien an: Von Fashion über Food bis hin zu Technologie. Die Produkte von Startups, Emerging Brands sowie etablierten Konzernen werden von _blaenk sorgfältig kuratiert. Die Vision hinter _blaenk ist es, den Lifestyle des Konsumenten individuell zu bereichern und das Wohlbefinden zu steigern. Dabei legt _blaenk hohen Wert auf das Produkterlebnis: Stationär wandelt sich der klassische “POS” zum Point of Experience, der dazu einlädt Marken zu entdecken und Produkte vor dem Kauf zu testen. Online können die Nutzer Content-getriebene Produktseiten des _blaenk Stores aufsuchen, in dem Informationen, Bilder, Videos und Preise abgebildet sind. Der Kunde hat die Möglichkeit, im digitalen Checkout-Prozess sowohl die Produktauswahl direkt stationär mitzunehmen, als sich auch nach Hause liefern zu lassen oder später abzuholen. _blaenk nutzt dabei umfangreiche Daten, um das Kundenerlebnis sukzessive zu personalisieren und die eigenen Retail-Prozesse zu optimieren. 
 
Marken können sich in dem _blaenk Omnichannel-Marktplatz via „Retail as a Service“ flexibel einbuchen. Dabei wird den Marken ein Baukastensystem aus stationärer Platzierung, Ladenbau und Personal, bis hin zu Marketingaktivitäten, Payment-Abwicklung und Fulfillment geboten. Ergänzend erhalten die Marken im Dashboard des _blaenk Business Managers ihre Kamera- und sensorbasierte Performance detailliert angezeigt (Views, Engagement, Umsatz, demographische Merkmale wie Geschlecht und Alter).

name: to be deleted
about: In space, the trend goes towards small and standardized satellites, so called CubeSats, allowing economic access to space. These satellites have an edge length of 10cm for a single 1U limiting greatly the missions that the satellite can fulfill. A way around this limitation is the use of deployable structures like appendices, antennas or sails which are unfolded once in orbit allowing new high-performance applications that are currently only possible with larger satellites. To tackle this problem, the Munich based new space company Deployables Cubed develops miniature actuators and CubeSat deployables, especially inflatables, with the goal to achieve Europe’s non-dependence on these miniature actuators and the cube satellite deployables they enable.

name: Verimi
about:
Verimi ist Lösungsanbieter für die Identitätsprüfung und sichere Authentifizierung von Kunden. Der Endkunde macht einen Ausweis-Check und hinterlegt seine digital erfassten Daten anschließend in seiner elektronischen Brieftasche, dem Verimi-Wallet. Damit kann er sich jederzeit, bequem und sicher bei Partnern einloggen, sich digital ausweisen, Verträge digital unterschreiben oder digital bezahlen. Partnerunternehmen integrieren Verimi mit wenigen Schritten und verbessern so das digitale Kundenerlebnis bei besonders hoher Prozesseffizienz. 

Für die Identitätsprüfung nutzt Verimi alle gängigen Methoden, z.B. eID-, Bank-, Foto-, Video- und Vor-Ort Ident. Verimi wendet besonders hohe Sicherheits- und Datenschutzstandards mit einer Verarbeitung der Daten in Europa an, unter Einbindung des sicheren lokalen Speichers des persönlichen Smartphones. Die Verimi-Plattform und die Zwei-Faktor-Authentifizierung (2FA) mittels App und PIN sind durch das Bundesamt für Sicherheit in der Informationstechnik (BSI) erfolgreich auf dem Vertrauensniveau substanziell geprüft. Als reguliertes Zahlungsinstitut ist Verimi nach dem Geldwäschegesetz (GwG) verpflichtet.

Die Verimi Gesellschafter sind: Allianz, Axel Springer, Bundesdruckerei, Core, Daimler, Deutsche Bahn, Deutsche Bank, Deutsche Telekom, Giesecke+Devrient, GMB - eine Investorengruppe namhafter Versicherer unter der Führung der GDV DL, Here Technologies, Lufthansa, Samsung und Volkswagen Financial Services.

name: Advanscreen
about:
Advanscreen is a full and complete solution with a user friendly interface that enables you to comply with "Know your Customer" Requirements for Businesses and Organizations that are subject to Anti Money Laundering and Terrorist Financing Regime. The system provides easy screening solution for Business Service Providers (accountants and lawyers), Money Service Providers, P2P, Diamond dealers and all other regulated entities to conduct background check and screening the names of their customers (or any third party) against leading sanction lists and sources of public information. 

Customer Due Diligence process in the global village of the 21th century 
/// Advanscreen

The Global war on Money Laundering & Terrorist Financing has introduced new Screening, monitoring and reporting duties to all Financial intermediaries such as: Banks, Money Services Businesses, Stock exchange brokers, Insurance companies, Diamond merchants, Business Professionals (Lawyers & Accountants) and more. Billions of Dollars in fines and criminal charges have been levied worldwide on Banks & Financial institutions for noncompliance with sanction law regulation.

/// The Problem:

Global Sanctions Information sources are various and unconsolidated. Each country or union publishes their own independent lists  - in different formats/accessibility levels - to be enforced only in their region and . 

/// AdvanScreen’s Solution:

•Innovative KYC concept: All the relevant information in one place to make a risk evaluated and informed business decision, avoiding potential fines and legal risks. Pay-Per-Screen pricing method makes competitors expensive annual subscription unnecessary.

•Simple and user-friendly interface; All searches are retained for audit 

•Reverse screening notifications: Live notifications of list changes allows peace of mind for end users without the need for continuous due diligence & screening.

•Social Intelligence feature: End users can add & share their own black lists.

Auch fremdsprachige Varianten erfordern nur wenige Klicks.

Ergänzt wird das Angebotsmanagement mit weiteren Software-Lösungen, wie z.B. AKIOMA.Rules! für die Festlegung von Freigabestufen, Verkäuferprovisionen und anderen Geschäftsregeln und AKIOMA.BPM! zur grafischen Steuerung von Geschäftsprozessen (Aufgabenzuweisung usw.). Mit AKIOMA.Connect! verschwinden isolierte Prozess- und Dateninseln: Die Integrationsplattform sorgt dafür, dass alle benötigten Informationen an jeder Stelle im Workflow vollständig und bedarfsgerecht zur Verfügung stehen.

AKIOMA arbeitet mit bewährten Partnern aus dem Entwicklungs- und Consultingumfeld zusammen. Eine besonders intensive Kooperation besteht mit Microsoft, dessen Office 365-Lösung sowie ERP (Dynamics Navision) eng integriert sind.

about: WIR SUCHEN VERSTÄRKUNG: check it out: https://transaction-network.jobs.personio.de/ Transaction-Network ist ein Enabler für den Maschinenbau und stellt die digitalen Möglichkeiten für ein Ökosystem aus Maschinenbauer und Produzenten der Nahrungs- und Genussmittelindustrie Die Digitalisierung der Industrie erfordert von den Maschinenherstellern ein deutliches Umdenken. Es benötigt digitalen Mehrwerte, Kundenzentrierung und Lösungen die eine wirkliche Differenzierung darstellen. Die zeitlichen und finanziellen Investitionen sind dabei sehr hoch und sehr oft fehlt die digitale Kompetenz im Unternehmen. Die horizontale Prozessintegration, also die Vernetzung durch die Maschinenbauer im Herstellungsprozesses des Endkunden, die Abbildung der Produktionslinie, komfortabler Zugang zu einer digitalen Maschinenakte und Betriebsdaten, Teileidentifikation und Bestellung, komfortable Prozessintegration zur Unterstützung beim Endkunden (Bediener, Projektleitung), Troubleshooting im Störungsfalle und letztlich Prädiktive Instandhaltung, sind Anforderungen die heute an den Maschinenhersteller gestellt werden. Transaction-Network unterstütz hier stellt das digitale Ökosystem für Maschinenbauer und Produzenten der Nahrungs- und Genussmittelindustrie. Eine Plattform für Asset-Management, Performance Data, Training & Know-How, Customer Service, Commerce und Maintenance-Management. Die Firma Transaction-Network GmbH & Co. KG liefert dabei mehr als nur Software. Wir bauen die Software und betreiben diese. Unter Betreiben verstehen wir vor allem die Datenaufbereitung und die erste Digitalisierungshilfe für unsere Maschinenbauer. Wir helfen beim Onboarding. Wir tun dies leistbar und wartungsfrei als SaaS-Lösung.

name: Becharged
about:
Wir betreiben eines der modernsten Backendsysteme für Ladeinfrastruktur und bieten Ihnen wirkliche Mehrwerte beim Betrieb Ihrer Ladeinfrastruktur. 

Neben den klassischen technischen Features für die Nutzeridentifizierung und Abrechnung haben wir ein integriertes, cloudbasiertes Lastmanagement umgesetzt, welches auf Wunsch auch die dynamische Steuerung zulässt.

Wir arbeiten technisch völlig unabhängig und sind somit in der Lage jede Ladeinfrastruktur, die mittels OCPP Standard kommunizieren kann innerhalb kürzester Zeit einzubinden.

Unser Highlight bildet die Wartungs-App für Ihr Servicepersonal. Hier wird auf Wunsch des Kunden der Installateur oder ein technischer Beauftragter über den Status der Ladeinfrastruktur informiert und kann im Falle einer Störung sofort eingreifen.

Neben dem klassischen Backendbetrieb bieten wir innerhalb Ihrer Projekte auch an, den kompletten Betrieb Ihrer Ladeinfrastruktur ganz oder teilweise zu übernehmen. Hierzu zählt der technische Betrieb, die Service Hotline, das Monitoring, das Nutzermanagement, die Abrechnung und die kontinuierliche Weiterentwicklung der besten Ideen und Vorschläge unserer Kunden. 

Stellen Sie sich einmal vor, dass Sie beispielsweise Ihr Quartier mit Ladesäulen ausstatten und Ihren Mietern das Laden mittels einer RFID Authentifizierung ermöglichen wollen. Auch öffentliches Laden soll möglich sein für Besucher. Nachdem wir gemeinsam die notwendigen Daten zum Betrieb definiert haben, ist es problemlos möglich, dass Ihre Mieter von uns direkt mit der notwendigen Ladekarte versorgt werden und die Abrechnungsprozesse automatisiert abgewickelt werden. Abgerechnet wird direkt nach dem Ladevorgang, ohne Risiko für Sie als Vermieter. Damit Sie nicht jeden Ladevorgang einzeln verbuchen müssen, erhalten Sie von uns am Monatsende die Gesamtabrechnung und Auszahlung der Umsätze.

Genau so könnte Ihr Szenario zukünftig auch aussehen. 

Wir freuen uns auf Ihren Kontakt und heißen Sie herzlich Willkommen bei becharged.

Corporates – such as automotive manufacturers – develop new digital business models as part of their digital transformation. Every business model requires the development of highly complex financial processes such as the management of digital payments, international invoicing or the management of subscriptions and contracts. Conventional accounting and billing systems were not made for today’s increasingly complex digital businesses.   But challenging the status quo is part of our company DNA, so in 2016 we decided to push the boundaries of what’s possible when it comes to monetizing digital products at speed.  With Nitrobox, companies are able to monetize new and digital business models more quickly and easily than with traditional software systems, by providing a software-as-a-service platform for the creation, automation and API control of their financial processes in an integrated system. name: Flowfox
about:
All-in-one import automation platform

Transforming Ocean Carrier’s import departments into profit centers and simplifying business for their importing customers.

Challenges addressed by Flowfox:

Manual import processes
Manual processes done by unencrypted emails are insecure, produce a high workload, lead to errors as well as result in unnecessary costs, a lot of waiting time and lack of transparency for the Importing Party and the Ocean Carrier.

Missing & late data
Unknown drop-off depots and dates lead to poor equipment control and unnecessary empty repositioning. Additionally, terminals often are not aware of the next mode of transport and the pick-up date before the container discharge, leading to unnecessary costs.

Unused sales opportunities
Currently, import processes are simply being performed. Services are not available within the current process, leading to missed revenue opportunities.

Import Automation with Flowfox:

Container Release
Container releases can be fully automated and is the base for all further automation, cost savings and revenue generation. Real time container release and real time status visibility will be enabled to the Importing Party and dead freights are avoided.

Container Reuse
Reuses can be requested from the Importing Party and automatically processed.

Drop-off Change
Drop-off changes can be requested from the Importing Party and automatically processed.

C/H Instructions
For carriers haulage shipments the detailed instructions like place of delivery or delivery times can be queried and submitted through Flowfox.

Dem, Det & Storage
Contracts and rates can be managed. Individual fees can be calculated, displayed to the customer, invoiced and collected.

Data Generation
Valuable data can be generated to make the supply chain more efficient. The drop-off depot and date can reduce empty repositioning for the Ocean Carrier. A timely known next mode of transport and gate-out date can reduce container moves at the terminal.

about:

Acodis has been pioneering document data extraction since its founding in 2016. As every business process starts, finishes, or involves documents, Acodis Intelligent Document Processing platform can classify, extract, and automate them within seconds - making data entry immensely easier and faster.

The document automation tool is diverse enough to meet all of your data requirements: whether you need a reliable PDF data extractor or an automated data entry program. Powered by machine learning, the AI data extraction process continuously evolves when you feed more data to it, meaning that it does all of the hard work for you. Furthermore, you are not even required to train the software yourself; Acodis will manage this process if it suits you.

Acodis can process your documents (e.g., an email, Excel spreadsheet, etc.) from any language and will seamlessly integrate with your systems. You can easily export your data from Acodis via API to feed and enhance your ERP, CRM, or RPA system of choice.

With Acodis, you can ultimately scale your entire document processes with a few clicks.

WÜRTH, REWE, B.Braun, Steigenberger, Kik.

BENEFIT
Konkret bedeutet dies, dass der Interessent eine Anzeige auf seinem Handy liest und innerhalb von 2 Minuten seine Bewerbung mit den wichtigsten Angaben eingesprochen hat.
Der individuelle Link wird im Vorfeld von dem Unternehmen mit Bezug auf eine konkrete Stelle oder ein Berufsbild erstellt. Der Link kann ohne großen Aufwand in alle Medien integriert werden (Posts, Homepage, Social Media oder Stellenanzeige) und ein Maximum an potenziellen Bewerbern erreichen. Offline kann der Link als QR-Code auf Anzeigen, Aufkleber, Flyer integriert und ohne große Kosten z.B. in den Filialen platziert werden.

DIVERSITY
Die Bewerbungen können auf allen verfügbaren und vom Arbeitgeber freigeschalteten Sprachen eingesprochen werden. Der Arbeitgeber erhält die strukturierten Ergebnisse in Textform sowohl auf Deutsch als auch in der Originalsprache.

name: MUSKthrust GbR
about: Take to the sky. Strive for greatness.  To Revolutionize Urban Mobility The history of urban mobility is strongly intertwined with the development of housing. For centuries we have succeeded in being able to support a growing number of passengers via an increasing number of transportation solutions, thus enabling us to increase the density of our cities, ultimately setting the foundation for our modern society. We strongly believe that we, to achieve the next step in this evolution, need to move into the third dimension. To achieve this goal we set out not just to create something capable of flight, but rather to create a product that is capable of bringing a premium experience to the consumer market.  To Revolutionize Personal Aerial Vehicles (PAV) It is our conviction that we can bring the freedom of personal air travel to the mass market. This goal was taken with the development of the first mass-produced car and has been pursued to this day in many ideas with varying degrees of success. However, none of these ideas have yet managed to achieve actual access to the mass market. For this reason, we are pursuing the goal of achieving not only further developments in our product but in every single step that comes before and after it.  To Revolutionize Industry The history of production is marked by several rapid upheavals that have fundamentally changed its face. Each of these upheavals has enabled humanity as a whole to advance into a new era of prosperity and freedom. It is now time for it to undergo fundamental change again. Our goal is to take 3D printing out of rapid prototyping and into mass production. This, in combination with a high degree of automation in production, enables us to achieve good cost efficiency in low production volumes. Also, our production can dynamically switch to new products and processes and incorporate modifications into existing products.  For more of our story, visit www.muskthrust.com

name: Degura
about:

In weniger als drei Jahren haben wir mehr als 100 vertrauensvolle Geschäftskundenbeziehungen mit Unternehmen aus ganz Deutschland und verschiedenen Branchen aufgebaut.

Die digitale Plug & Play-Lösung von Degura bietet ein einfaches und intuitives Betriebsrentenerlebnis. Wir nehmen den Personalabteilungen und Mitarbeitern die mühsamen, manuellen und intransparenten Prozesse ab, mit denen sie bei der Zusammenarbeit mit externen Rentenberatern, Versicherungsmaklern und -vertretern üblicherweise konfrontiert sind.

Wir ersparen unseren Firmenkunden wertvolle Zeit und Geld bei allen wichtigen Abläufen der betrieblichen Altersversorgung und bieten den Mitarbeitern einen einfachen und transparenten digitalen Versorgungsservice, dem sie vertrauen und auf den sie sich verlassen können.

name: GetHenry
about:
At GetHenry, we want to change last mile delivery and thereby shape the future of e-mobility – and reduce traffic-related CO2-emissions along the way. Our mission is to make sure that thousands of bike couriers have a smooth, fast, and save delivery experience every day. What we do is simple; we offer subscription-based full-mobility-service for leading delivery services. This includes providing our clients with e-bikes, weekly maintenance by our local service teams, and digital solutions for a user-friendly experience. We pride ourselves on working with leading players and industry disruptors like Gorillas, Flink, Getir, Wolt, Lieferando, Mjam and others.

We are a small team of dedicated professionals and hard workers with diverse educational and cultural backgrounds. We share an entrepreneurial mindset and are not afraid to think big. With the support of leading investors, we are expanding across Europe and assembling a team of motivated and talented people to help us move forward.

name: CrossBlock GmbH
about:

We reimagine investing in small caps with:  

- SideCaps Pool, our platform to automate block trades of small caps and, hence, increase liquidity and transparency in this market segment.

- SideCaps Insights, our content portal that aggregates all relevant information about small caps companies, enabling users to make better informed and faster investment decisions.

Through our innovative approach we enable:

- Trading at transparent midpoint pricing with low transaction fees attached.
- Low market impact through trading without pre-trade transparency.
- Execution on Xetra, adhering to the highest regulatory standards.
- Access to individualized, high-quality content & independent research for small cap investors as well as direct exchange with experts in the community.

We operate in a network of established partners and create added value for all constituents in the small cap space: institutional & private investors as well as financial service providers, information providers, and issuers.

There are so many buttons, dials, knobs, settings, and keyboard shortcuts to remember, that learning how it all works becomes in and of itself an exercise in patience and resolve. For content-focused video editing, you don’t need most of the features offered by most editing software, and the barrier to entry is very steep — you have to own a machine capable of running these programs and know-how all of the functions work. name: RightNow Group
about:
The RightNow Group from Düsseldorf is Europe's leading consumer factoring provider and one of the most successful German LegalTech startups. With its products, RightNow buys consumer claims from everyday life situations and pays a large part of their reimbursement within only 24 hours. The claims are checked using specially developed algorithms and enforced in court through highly automated processes. 

***

Die RightNow Group aus Düsseldorf ist Europas führender Consumer-Factoring-Anbieter und eines der
erfolgreichsten deutschen LegalTech-Startups. Mit ihren Produkten kauft RightNow Konsumenten Rechtsansprüche aus dem tagtäglichen Leben gegen große Konzerne ab und zahlt den Verbrauchern schnell, einfach und rechtssicher einen Großteil ihrer Erstattungsansprüche innerhalb von nur 24 Stunden aus. name: B.fab
about:
b.fab is specialized in the efficient conversion of CO2 and hydrogen (H2) from renewable energy into biotechnological value chains. CO2 and water are abundantly available and therefore it is our starting point to build a sustainable bioeconomy. 

We use formate as our central mediator to bind and store CO2 and H2 (made from water) in liquid form. Our bioprocesses start with the feedstock formate and we use Synthetic Biology to design specific pathways and to convert formate into value-added chemicals. 

Our platform is build on anaerobic and aerobic microbial production hosts to provide flexibility in the process design and adaptation to specific product requirements. We apply laboratory automation, high-throughput experimentation and advanced bioprocess development in an agile environment to develop new bioprocesses efficiently and in a minimal time frame. 

b.fab is dedicated to establish a Formate Bioeconomy in the coming years, and thus, providing an economical and sustainable new way to produce value-added chemicals for various industries.

name: BLVRD
about:
BLVRD is the online search engine for offline offers. We reach generation X,Y and Z and inspire them for local fashion shopping.

WHAT DRIVES US
As a young startup from the heart of Hannover, we have set ourselves the goal of not only preserving the local shopping experience and our city centres, but to make it a success story again. We are convinced that you have to see, feel and experience fashion in order to decide to buy, and digital experiences alone are not enough for this. Instead, it needs the best of both worlds: Online & Offline. That's why we use digital technologies to create real experiences, or as we call it: HYBRID RETAIL

DEVELOPED FOR DIGITAL TARGET GROUPS
With our app, consumers between the ages of 15-40 search for fashion items and then find out which local retailer carries the merchandise. The favourite pieces you are looking for can then be tried on at the dealer and bought directly.This saves long searches in the city, returns, parcel waste and runs faster than online orders. 

OPTIMIZED FOR LOCAL TRADE
From boutiques to chain stores, we help fashion retailers to reach new target groups and increase stationary sales.  Because with BLVRD we provide our trading partners with genuine unique selling points that online competitors cannot offer.  And all this free of charge until the end of 2020 with a very easy connection without additional software or interfaces.

name: Lylu GmbH
about:
Das Lylu Tablet vereinfacht älteren Menschen den Zugang ins Internet. Alles ist seniorenfreundlich zu bedienen. Ohne Ausnahme. 👵🧓
Unbegrenztes Internet. Unbegrenzter Support. Unbegrenzte Geräteversicherung. All das ist im Lylu Paket enthalten. 🙌

Mit dem Lylu Tablet können Großeltern mit ihren Kindern per Video telefonieren, Fotos von ihren Enkeln ansehen, Videos schauen, Wikipedia durchstöbern, online einkaufen oder ihrer Bank eine E-Mail schreiben – die Bedienung funktioniert immer nach dem gleichen intuitiven Muster. ❤️ 😊

Einmal erlernte Nutzungsweisen lassen sich auf zahlreiche andere Funktionen übertragen. Großflächige Bedienelemente ermöglichen es auch Menschen mit Sehbehinderung oder motorischen Einschränkungen durch das Netz zu navigieren. 

Lylu funktioniert Out-of-the-box: Wir sind Ihr Ansprechpartner während der gesamten Nutzungsdauer. Wir senden Ihnen das Tablet nicht nur fertig konfiguriert, im Abo ist jeglicher Service zum Tablet inkludiert. Sollte das Senioren Tablet beschädigt sein, erhalten Sie von uns ein neues Gerät, auch für Rückfragen sind wir Ihr Ansprechpartner: individuell, persönlich und schnell verfügbar. 👍

Im Abopreis ist unbegrenztes Datenvolumen ebenfalls inkludiert: So bricht die Verbindung niemals ab! 🥳

name: CloudRail
about: CloudRail is a fully managed solution to acquire data from industrial environments, preprocess it locally, and send it to any cloud — Plug&Play. CloudRail works for greenfield as well as brownfield applications. It uses industry standards like OPC-UA to connect modern equipment, while old machines are retrofitted with secondary sensors. A database of over 12.000 sensor definitions in combination with automated data transformation and device provisioning reduces the setup time for connecting a machine to the cloud from weeks to just hours. CloudRail takes away the hassles of sensor compatibility, communication protocols, data format, and connectivity to the cloud.

name: NUMA Group (formerly COSI Group)
about:
In a world of stuffy, faceless hotels, we’re leading the industry into a new era. We’re replacing the unnecessary hassle with simplicity and delight. Mixing technology and taste together in the world’s greatest neighbourhoods, we create stays that are unashamedly original and unforgettably authentic. With the comforts of home and the quality of a boutique hotel, we make sure our guests have everything they need to live like a local, escape for a weekend, or unwind during a business trip. If they want to stay for longer, we’ve got that covered as well. We’ve designed our properties with our guests’ joy in mind, whether they stay for a night, a week, or a season. 

Numa does away with complicated check-ins, long queues, and unpredictable accommodations. Instead, we take the best parts of travel—the carefully designed spaces, the thrill of a new city, fluffy towels, a comfy bed—and blend them with state-of-the-art technology. For our guests, it’s a one-of-a-kind mix of ease and experience, a super-simple guest journey in Europe’s most exciting neighborhoods. 

Our world-class guest experience is just the tip of the iceberg. With our proprietary full-stack software suite, we’ve digitalised over 80% of our internal processes, from booking and room allocation to housekeeping, accounting, and more. This keeps us scalable and cost-efficient, and helps us to weather even the most volatile of market fluctuations. By using intelligent yield management, distribution and our in-house operating systems, we can significantly reduce our administrative workload operating costs. We’re always able to keep things agile and efficient, which frees us up to focus on what’s most important: the satisfaction of our visitors.

name: SiaSearch
about:
Building robust, industrial AI like automated driving is extremely difficult. Everyone thinks about algorithms, but up to 75% of engineering time is spent on highly manual tasks, namely manually reviewing and selecting masses of data instead of building algorithms.

That is why we developed SiaSearch, a data management platform which automatically extracts frame-level, contextual metadata and utilizes it for fast data exploration, selection and evaluation. Automating these tasks with metadata can more than double engineering productivity and remove the bottleneck to building industrial AI.

In November 2021, SiaSearch was acquired by Scale AI. The SiaSearch team will join Scale's Nucleus business unit and the technology will be woven into the Nucleus product, enabling Scale AI to provide the full data engine for every AI team.

name: The CareVoice
about:
Driven by the purpose to make health insurance more human, we are a leading Asian health insurtech uniquely tackling 4 major health insurance pain points:
- Gap of customer engagement and health services
- Lack of differentiated insurance products, poorly customer centric
- Dependency on traditional sales channel, being unequipped to tap into the future of customer relationship
- Limited digital capabilities and integration challenges with ecosystem partners 

Through CareVoiceOS, the first healthcare operating system for insurers, we are expanding a “One Click” Connected Health Insurance Ecosystem. According to insurers’ maturity and technology investment, CareVoiceOS can be their turnkey solution, or become the new standard infrastructure to build their own customer engagement solutions. 

By partnering with us, insurers can enter the world of digital health insurance. They can effectively engage their customers with the latest health technologies and connected services, through an integrated customer journey experience that brings trust and health benefits. They can also design and launch tailored insurance products for specific populations, with relevant wellbeing & medical services and exclusive channels. 

Insurers can further benefit from our “sibling company” and strategic partner, StartupCare, a leading digital health insurance solution provider for employers and individuals, to drive further commercialization of these new health insurance products. 

Together this supports insurers unlock sales growth and optimizes the efficiency of their health insurance business. We operate in China Mainland & Hong Kong, and are expanding to Southeast Asia and Europe. 

After graduating from Ping An Accelerator, we closed a large Series A in  August 2019, and have accumulated nearly 15m USD funding. We are backed by top fintech, healthcare and software VCs as well as serial entrepreneurs, from China, Europe and the US.

name: Forte
about:
We do not currently have a way to finance high-quality education, especially vocational reskilling, at the scale required. 

Forte (which stands for Financing Of Return To Employment) is a new, better way to invest in human potential. It is a way to finance reskilling at no cost to either individuals or governments, and without needing philanthropy.

Here’s where the idea for the Forte approach comes from: The cost of reskilling is often far less than the increase in government taxation revenue caused by that training. Forte utilizes this empirical reality by enabling education to be paid for with that increase in expected future tax.

In practice, it works in three simple steps:

1. Via the Forte platform, investors can pay for the vocational training of individuals who would otherwise be paying no or negligible tax.

2. This training, by its nature, increases expected employment, incomes, and therefore government tax revenue.

3. Governments, as part of the contractual arrangement, pass back to investors an agreed portion of the tax revenue attributable to the training recipients, for a set period of time.

By way of example, suppose Lydia just lost her job and wants to be a programmer in the future. With the Forte approach, an investor could finance a six-month coding training course to 1000 people like Lydia, in return for 30% of the tax revenue attributable to them for 5 years.

This arrangement is mutually beneficial.

Individuals receive training at no cost. They just pay the usual tax rate. They’re effectively paying for their own training with their future tax.

Governments can help workers have lost their jobs, prepare the workforce for the jobs of the future, overcome skill gaps, and prevent long-term unemployment, without worsening the budget. And there are mathematical ways to guarantee they bear no risk and never lose out.

Investors can both do good and do well. They can invest in a way that genuinely helps those in need.

A true win-win.

Klassische Ausrüstung aus dem Functional Training wie TRX oder Kettlebells werden durch Klimmzug- und Dipstangen ergänzt. Neben dem Trainingsequipment finden Sportler in den Spinden auch eine Bluetooth-Musikbox zum kabellosen Abspielen der eigenen Musik sowie Hygienematerial zur anschließenden Reinigung des Equipments und eine Handy- Ladestation.
Ein Training mit dem ausgewählten Equipment, das bisher nur in Fitnessstudios, Sporthallen oder unter erschwerten Transportbedingungen durchzuführen war, ist mit SportBox künftig auch bequem unter freiem Himmel möglich.

name: reignite
about:
#reignite connects gamers across platforms. We are your social network for gaming. You'll help build a universal network that invites every player and every type of groupe - like clans, guilds, or just your after-work gaming group.

With reignite, the days of having to play with random teammates are a thing of the past. Our matching algorithm takes into account game statistics as well as personal characteristics and desired criteria to suggest the best possible teammates before you even join an online game. No matter which platform (PC, console or mobile) we are always there.

about:

A turnkey Holodeck VR attraction is designed for ease of operations, as it can be managed with low overhead (10 guests to 1 attendant) and it is simple to train new and non-technical staff on the system. Holodeck VR is the only LBE free-roam VR platform that is open to third-party content developers, which means that operators and guests will benefit from a variety of the newest, freshest content and experiences available. Holodeck VR is built to deliver the incredible throughput that will maximize operator revenue during peak hours and the high player density to allow for successful group and corporate events during slower times.

name: FreeD Printing GmbH
about:
The new and innovative model building process FreeD Printing enables modeling with freely formed modeling layers in model building for additive manufacturing processes (3D printing). For this purpose, the planning software automatically calculates the process paths comparable to conventional slicing programs, but taking into account the orientation of the process head by the robot that is possible with the system. With the development of appropriate modeling strategies, it is possible to model components with overhangs that can be manufactured without the support structures that would otherwise be required. In addition, material can be applied to existing, freely formed surfaces as well as the strand direction can be influenced, for example, to increase the strength of components.
The process offers the following key advantages, increasing the chances of using additive manufacturing processes in industrial production processes:
- Shortening of planning process and construction time
- Savings in manufacturing materials
- No post-processing to remove support structures
- Adding material to existing surfaces
- Influence of the strand direction during model assembly
- Flexible and large construction space according to the working range of the robot

•Vitomy ist alltagsnahe Die Coaching-App begleitet den Patienten 24 Stunden am Tag bei der Umsetzung einer gesunden Lebensweise, egal ob zuhause oder unterwegs. 
•Vitomy ist individuell: Jeder Patient bekommt seinen ganz spezifischen Gesundheitsplan. Fragebögen sorgen dafür, dass Gewohnheiten und Bedürfnisse im Detail beachtet werden können.
•Vitomy ist wissenschaftlich: Die App setzt auf medizinischen Werten auf. Alle Empfehlungen basieren auf aktuellen medizinischen Standards. Der Behandler kann über ein Cockpit jederzeit den Gesundheitszustand seines Patienten einsehen. 
•Vitomy ist nachhaltig: Die Coaching App unterstützt jeden Patienten bestmöglich bei der Umsetzung – durch eine schrittweise Anleitung, Erinnerungen, Motivation, vertiefendes Wissen sowie Tipps und Tricks, wie die Umsetzung leichter fällt.

Die wichtigsten Komponenten, die wir zur Sicherstellung höchster Qualitätsanforderungen ausschließlich intern bauen, sind die B2C-Plattform zur Quellensteuerrückerstattung, die auf einen 90-Milliarden-Dollar-Markt abzielt, die erste internationale API für Wertpapieraggregation, eine Wertpapierdatenbank und ein Dividendenscreener.

name: Syntho
about:
Syntho is a data technology organization with a strong expertise in privacy enhancing technologies (PET), headquartered in Amsterdam, Netherlands. It was founded in 2020 with the goal of solving the privacy dilemma and enable the open data economy, where data can be used and shared freely and privacy guaranteed. Syntho offers privacy-preserving synthetic data to unlock your data and take away legitimate privacy concerns.

We develop AI-based software that can be trained on any form of data. After training, our Syntho Engine is able to generate new, ‘synthetic’ data. This is the essence of what we do - we generate a completely new, artificial dataset that reproduces the statistical characteristics of the original dataset, while warranting that no records from the original dataset are present. In other words, the synthetic dataset has no privacy risk, while maximizing data utility. This allows you to easily use and share all of your data without privacy concerns and boost innovation.

We believe data can help solve the biggest challenges in business, science, and society - but why is it so difficult to shop for data online? We're on the mission to make it super easy for every company across the globe to buy and monetise data.

Looking for a new challenge? Join us: https://datara.de/careers

name: Dearemployee
about: DearEmployee ist eine Corporate Health Plattform, die Unternehmen unterstützt, gesunde und motivierende Arbeitsbedingungen für ihre Mitarbeiter:innen zu schaffen. Über die Plattform können Unternehmen mit Hilfe psychischer Gefährdungsbeurteilungen fortlaufend und wissenschaftlich Belastungen am Arbeitsplatz messen und maßgeschneiderte Lösungen für Ihre Teams finden. Dazu gehören u.a. Teamworkshops, digitale Gesundheitsangebote und Führungskräftetrainings. Durch die passgenauen Maßnahmen lassen sich einfach und effektiv Gesundheitskosten reduzieren sowie die Mitarbeiterperformance und Arbeitgeberattraktivität steigern. DearEmployee ist insbesondere in der D-A-CH-Region vertreten und hat über 200 Kunden, darunter sind zahlreiche große und mittelständische Unternehmen wie die AXA und DEKRA.

name: Top.Legal
about:
At top.legal we believe that a new era of contract process is dawning. After years of stagnation and frustration caused by inefficient contract workflows centered around paper and email trails, complicated legal language and constant friction between legal and sales the time is ripe for change.

We exist to create more valuable relationships. With our ai-powered contract software, we enable sales and legal to generate contracts 9-times faster and negotiate more valuable deals.

Our software allows sales managers and legal counsels to keep track of the contracting process at any time. We accompany your contracts from the first draft,  through internal and external negotiations, to electronic signature with subsequent analysis and evaluation. 

At top.legal we stand for innovation. With 50+ years of experience in professional services, we understand businesses from the inside. We have lived through the death valley of the contracting process several times over and have sworn to ourselves to make an end to this grueling experience. As a group of people that embrace technology, we found salvation in the application of web technologies and AI. We continue to live technology and strive for continuous development.

codary ist ein Berliner EdTech-Startup: Wir etablieren Programmieren als Nachmittagshobby für Kinder.

Unser Ziel ist es, möglichst vielen jungen Menschen die Programmier-Fähigkeiten beibringen zu können, die sie brauchen, um im 21. Jahrhundert erfolgreich zu sein. Die digitalen Präsenzkurse werden durch codary’s Lernplattform und Lern-App unterstützt.

name: streamboost GmbH
about: Wussten Sie schon, dass immer mehr Menschen, Livestreaming zu einem Teil ihres Lebens gemacht haben? 16.000.000.000 ist eine unglaublich große Anzahl an Stunden, die in 2020 auf der Live-Streaming Plattform Twitch weltweit genutzt wurden. Viele Unternehmen stellen sich nun die Frage: “Wie können wir genau diese Zielgruppen erreichen?“. Mit streamboost haben wir als erstes Unternehmen eine Plattform geschaffen, die genau das ermöglicht. streamboost eröffnet Ihrem Unternehmen schnell den Markt der Livestream Werbung. Durch unsere eigenentwickelte Software wird Ihr Content gezielt in die Live-Video tausender Influencer eingebunden und kann so nicht durch AdBlocker herausgefiltert werden. Ebenso können Sie verschiedene Livestreamer aktiv für Ihre Produkte werben lassen. Unser Fokus liegt darin, Ihre Werbebotschaft präzise der gewünschten Zielgruppen zu präsentieren, dabei werden Content und die Zuschauer jedes Streamers zielgenau mit der passenden Werbekampagne verbindet, um Ihre Werbewirkung zu maximieren. Mit streamboost können Sie aus einer Hand hunderte Streamer gleichzeitig bündeln, ohne jeden einzelnen zu analysieren und Verträge zu schließen. Ihre Werbebotschaften werden zu einem Teil tausender Livestreams und können authentisch und effektiv von den entsprechenden Zielgruppen gesehen werden. streamboost bietet Ihnen dabei ein umfassendes Analysetool, durch das Sie in Echtzeit jede Bewegung nachverfolgen und auswerten können.

name: Horizer
about:
Horizer elevates the cleaner mobility experience for cities and car owners alike. It also provides extrinsic motivation, namely government subsidies, incentives, and rewards for compliance with ever-changing regulations. 

Horizer engages in the design, development, manufacture, and sale of solar modules, energy generation and storage systems compatible with any vehicle. 
As the vehicle became increasingly convenience features enabled, almost 30% of energy burned goes into the powering these features. Horizer turns any vehicle into a solar-powered hybrid electric vehicle, powering vehicle`s auxiliary energy usage by solar module.

Internal combustion engine (ICE) cars are polluting cities, and are under increasing regulatory pressure regarding emissions. Automobiles make the biggest dent into the environment by polluting with particles, ammonia and carbon oxides, as well as thermally. 

98% of the vehicles on the road are ICE powered, and that is 1 billion of ICE vehicles.

Horizer turns any vehicle into a solar-powered vehicle, reducing fuel consumption, cost and CO2 emissions by 30%.

Horizer transforms 98% of the market into cleaner vehicles with Energy of Things. Flexible thin-film solar panel, batteries, installation, the app that tracks everything energy-related and handles certification for 90% lower price than any other solution.

Benefits of Horizer Mobile and Solar Energy Solution:
• Convert Sunlight into Energy
• Add on Solar Foil and battery on ANY Vehicle 
• 300 locations in Europe for certified installation in less than 1 hour
• The app tracks everything energy-related and handles certificates from consumption to sharing
• Use Free and Movable Clean Energy
• 100% of your electric needs covered
• The system pays out itself in 12 months
• After 6 months you earn on not paying for gas, charging, government taxes and getting benefits
• Reduces your fuel bill by 30% 
• For 90% lower price than any other solution

name: MedKitDoc
about:
By offering a remote medical care platform that combines video-doctor-calls with connected medical devices and real-time transfer of health data, MedKitDoc enables remote treatment of serious chronical medical conditions reducing unnecessary hospitalization of up to 50 percent. 
MedKitDoc enables treatment of 48/50 of the most common medical consultation reasons (video call alone only 24 out of 50) and we have the customers to prove it: MedKitDoc already works with multiple care providers to improve the life of chronically ill patients.

name: Everstox
about:
everstox is a Logistics as a Service platform enabling scalable and data-driven fulfillment across Europe through a network of qualified warehousing & fulfillment partners.

Being a VC backed, dynamic and ambitious team with first-class entrepreneurial and tech background, we aim to deliver tech-driven logistics solutions to complex operational problems. 

We are passionate about optimizing the flow of goods through Europe, solving inefficiencies in warehousing and fulfillment operations and reducing transport emissions along the supply chain. Ultimately we want to make first-class distribution accessible for independent retailers of any size to compete with established giants like Amazon. Simply the best delivery experience, for every customer.

name: Kiconn
about:
Für Systemgastronomie und Großküchen.
Gewerbeküchen stehen unter hohem Effizienzdruck: Die Anforderungen an die Wirtschaftlichkeit steigen stetig und der Kostendruck nimmt zu. Vorschriften zur Arbeitssicherheit und immer neue Hygieneauflagen fordern die Küchenleitung zusätzlich heraus. Der wachsende Fachkräftemangel macht die Situation nicht leichter.

Die Digitalisierung von Gewerbeküchen leistet einen wesentlichen Beitrag dazu, die Küchenprozesse sicherer zu gestalten, wiederkehrende Arbeiten zu vereinfachen, monotone Erfassung von Betriebs- und Hygienedaten zu automatisieren, sowie Verschwendung zu vermeiden.

Kiconn bietet individuelle Lösungen zur Lastspitzenoptimierung, vorbeugenden Wartung, Erfassung von Hygienedaten nach HACCP und Prozess-Überwachung an. Die Sammlung und Verarbeitung der Daten kann entweder vor Ort oder in der Cloud dargestellt werden.

Der Koch kann sich wieder auf das wichtigste konzentrieren – gutes Essen für seine Gäste zuzubereiten!

name: mycrocast
about: mycrocast is an open platform that combines audio and fan engagement. Clubs, leagues, associations and brands can emotionally engage fans, attract new fans and monetize this. The clubs can thus intensify the fans' bond to the club and offer their fans a free channel to present themselves with passion and heartfelt commitment. The fans can thus follow the game of their favourite club in a thrilling way as audio stream, no matter where they are. They can choose their most passionate commentator from a variety of streams. Mycrocast also allows other fans to broadcast the game of their favourite club audibly. With mycrocast you get a simple mobile solution. Thereby they can gain the respect of other fans and express their love for the club.

name: trivention GmbH
about:
Die psychische Gesundheit jedes Einzelnen muss und wird die größte Aufgabe jeder Gemeinschaft und Gesellschaft in den 2020er und 2030er Jahren werden. Wir gehen diese Herausforderung mit der Vision an, psychische Stabilität und Gesundheit für alle Menschen in unserer Gesellschaft erreichbar zu machen.

Die trivention GmbH entwickelt deshalb forschungsbasiert fokussierte digitale und analoge Angebote in den Bereichen Prävention, Intervention und Rehabilitation mit Fokus auf psychischer Gesundheit. Als Firma im Unternehmensverbund Neuropsychiatrisches Zentrum Hamburg  kann sie dabei auf die Erfahrung und die Expertise von einem der größten Anbieter ambulanter Versorgungsleistungen im Bereich Nerven und Psyche in Hamburg zurückgreifen.

Unser Ziel ist es, Privatpersonen und Unternehmensmitarbeitenden auf einfachem Weg Impulse und Strategien zur Verbesserung ihrer psychischen Gesundheit zu geben. Deshalb entwickeln wir eHealth-Produkte und umfassende Programme für das betriebliche Gesundheitsmanagement (z.B. unser Angebot für die Pflege coachforcare), die wirklich gebraucht werden und die helfen können, die Chancen der Digitalisierung sinnvoll zu nutzen und zu gestalten.

Vor dem Hintergrund von Versorgungslücken und langer Wartezeiten auf Facharzt- und Therapeutentermine wurde im Neuropsychiatrischen Zentrum bereits seit einigen Jahren an der Weiterentwicklung der Gesundheitsversorgung durch u.a. eHealth-Angebote gearbeitet. Im Jahr 2017 konnte der „Telemedizinpreis“ der Deutschen Gesellschaft für Telemedizin für die Online-Unterstützungsplattform psychOnline® gewonnen werden.

Bei unserer Arbeit stand und steht immer die fortlaufende interdisziplinäre Forschungsarbeit in den Bereichen Psychiatrie, Neurologie und Psychotherapie im Fokus. Diese garantiert die Qualität und Innovationskraft aller Leistungen und Angebote. In der Evaluation unserer Produkte arbeiten wir mit verschiedenen nationalen und internationalen Partnern, Universitäten und Krankenkassen zusammen.

name: WeShape.world
about:
WeShape’s mission is to make corporate social responsibility more tangible in order to establish a stronger emotional connection between corporations, their employees and customers. All while making a positive sustainable impact on the world.

We strongly believe that PURPOSE and IMPACT should go hand in hand with entrepreneurial thinking. This succeeds when SOCIAL COMMITMENT provides clear added value to the company.
 
WeShape provides a tool that allows the employees to use their companies donations to distribute to projects which are closest to the employees' hearts.

That is how we empower employees and companies to form a community committed to social change without having to ask themselves whether or not they can afford it.

Visit our website, to find out how you can Add Purpose to Your Brand.

name: ClUrb
about:
Accessible and affordable software solutions for urban challenges

The frameworks for sustainable development recently established by the United Nations - the Sustainable Development Goals/Agenda 2030 and the New Urban Agenda, aim at a sustainable, inclusive and resilient development of societies, grounded on the principle of "leaving no-one behind". 

Although remarkable progress has been achieved, there is still plenty of people being left behind. This is particularly true for the case of the least-resourced cities and communities. For them, most of the technology and tools currently available to support more sustainable development are completely out of reach.

ClUrb is a social enterprise aiming at closing this gap.

Our mission is to support cities and communities globally, in particular the least-resourced ones, to achieve a more inclusive, sustainable and resilient development .

Our value proposition is to simplify and digitalize complex frameworks to support cities and communities in implementing policies, plans and strategies in their most pressing issues in a rapid and collaborative manner.

name: Shapematchr
about:
Shapematchr is a fit intelligence platform that generates personal user shopping profiles and matches them to their perfect fit garments. 

We channel mass market products to their perfect fit customer and create the online shopping of the future.

name: Priceloop GmbH
about:
Priceloop helps e-commerce and retail companies to be more successful by using data-driven pricing decisions. Pricing is one of the most important business challenges for our customers. Imagine yourself in the shoes of a pricing manager who is responsible to set optimal prices for tens of thousands of products and keep them up to date when input factors change. The market standard of how companies set their prices today is manual pricing or rule-based automation, which both are not truly data-driven.
 
We at Priceloop are fascinated by the impact of artificial intelligence (AI) in commercial decision-making and we are convinced that in 5 years from now, all relevant retail and e-commerce companies will use AI-based pricing.

We are funded by leading VCs and closed a funding round that enables us to quickly deliver towards our vision.

name: nurii
about: nurii hilft Personen mit Lebensmittelunverträglichkeiten beschwerdefreier zu sein. Im digitalen Tagebuch werden Essgewohnheiten eingetragen. Der Algorithmus entdeckt Intoleranzen und liefert anschließend personalisierte Tipps. Zum Beispiel eine Liste mit Lebensmittel welche gemieden werden sollten, sowie eine Übersicht mit Nahrungsmitteln, welche gut verträglich sind. Ein Schwerpunkt liegt auf den Mikronährstoffen. Die App analysiert die eingetragenen Mahlzeiten und weist auf mögliche Defizite im Mikronährstoffhaushalt hin. Weitere hilfreiche Features sollen in den nächsten Monaten evaluiert und umgesetzt werden.

name: Vectra Global
about: Vectra Automation provides Robotic Process Automation (RPA) for 3D CAD Engineering Design. Our flagship Auto2D RPA platform completely automates the generation of Engineering Drawings for Mechanical Systems and Components. As a powerful add-on to leading 3D CAD software platforms, Auto2D RPA leverages scalable cloud-based processing to transform 3D models to 2D Engineering Drawings (or Annotated 3D models) in a matter of hours, not weeks. By automating the tedious, time-consuming, error-prone work of manual 2D attributing, Design Teams can dramatically reduce costs, free-up thousands of project hours for design flexibility, and eliminate the need for outsourcing and wasteful, redundant QC - and proprietary 3D content never leaves the designer workstation. Auto2D RPA can be configured to any OEM Design Standard for Automotive, Aerospace, Defense, and other Heavy Industry applications for Product and Manufacturing Engineering Design.

Dive into relaxing Virtual Reality: at work, at airports, in hospitals, in care homes, at home, before sleep. All is based on scientific research and a study for Magic Horizons by the Humboldt-Universität zu Berlin.  From real high-end Nature VR to CGI, from passive to interactive VR including gamification. One VR App fits for all.  We have traction in the area of Telekoms, Inflight VR, “well-beeing” for employees (HR departments), at dentists. Clean content for a global audience. VR for good!

SGS - Scalable Global Solutions - is the first DaaS "Department as a Solution" Provider. We blend EMEA and NEARSHORE resources to provide comprehensive business solutions that are highly cost-efficient.

We have invented "DaaS" [Department as a Solution] as the new disruptive solution for companies and their workforce. We bring them into the 21st century. Our "DaaS" allows our clients to increase productivity while reducing cost at the same time. - SGS is a High- Tech Software & Digital DaaS provider - Here for you, a market of 9+ Mio. Highly educated people.
We optimize with DaaS 8 core departments/functions of our clients. Our client can implement their tailormade teams in Sales, HR, Operations, Back Office, IT, Finance, Marketing and Customer Care.
Implementing for our clients under their lead and management, DaaS Teams across our client's vital corporate functions is our core competence and the added value we bring to the client. At the core of our DNA, SGS has earned a reputation to create high-impact solutions, helping our clients stay pertinent-relevant, more efficient & profitable.

about:
Founded as Cellulosic Technologies (now BIOWEG) in 2019 in Germany, we are a purpose-driven organization powered by conscious ChemDesign.

We match BioInnOvation to business problems. We explore and combine biotechnology, material science and molecular simulations learning to create and sell advanced sustainable and bio-based high-performance ingredients.

Our ingredients are 100% animal- and GMO-free, globally scalable, and sustainably produced without using any harsh chemicals.

We work with results-oriented, forward-thinking companies and consumer brands with global scale in the beauty, nutraceuticals, and food/beverage sectors who desire highly-differentiated, 100% animal-free and sustainable, science-based ingredient technologies

Wir wollen den Menschen Informationen und Transparenz rund um die 'Lebenslage Abschied'

name: Oceanis GmbH
about:
oceanis is an end-to-end shipping finance platform where ship owners and financiers are connected in a new digital way. 

It is our mission to provide every ship-owner easy access to diversified global financing sources and a transparent overview of best-possible terms. We equip owners with a modern solution to source required funding and built new relationships with global financing institutions. Through digitization and standardisation we create efficiencies, break complexities and bring down lead-time and associated costs.

name: Bareways
about: Bareways develops AI-driven software solutions to enable driving assistance functionalities outside of urban- or high way environments.

name: NautilusLog
about:
For centuries the manual data collection onboard has remained unchanged. With NautilusLog we have developed a smartphone application to digitize and simplify the documentation around the vessel.
NautilusLog is adapted to the needs of the maritime industry and helps you to combine the mandatory reports and tracking with innovative technology. 
The digital tools replace all the paperwork (e.g. from clipboards to logbooks) and increase efficiency. In the interest of the stakeholder, all relevant data can be collected and comprehensive reports are generated within seconds. The operating system connects all maritime stakeholders and creates business process between ship and shore.

name: RFA - Rocket Factory
about:
Rocket Factory Augsburg AG (RFA) was founded on the belief that opening fair and low-cost access to space will remove boundaries limiting human evolution. RFA is developing a launch service for small satellites to space in a unique set up to better understand and protect our Earth.
https://linktr.ee/rocketfactory

Rocket Factory Augsburg AG (RFA) is part of the OHB Group with headquarter in Augsburg. With our experienced core team, we are focusing on low cost launch technology within an automotive manufacturing environment. We are constantly growing and with a little more than 3 years into full operations we're at over 120 employees. If you are interested in joining the up and coming space program, then apply to us.

name: HOLY Energy
about: Most of your favorite soft drinks are tasty but unhealthy. At HOLY, we want to change that. By combining delicious taste, real functionality, and true sustainability, we aim to shake up the outdated beverage industry.

name: Theion
about: Zero emission crystal batteries.

name: Agentur Doppelpass
about:
Mit unseren Marken esport-manager.com und proclubs-efootball.com stehen wir für eFootball als Mannschaftssport, Fan-Engagement, leidenschaftliche Berichterstattung und Shows, Ausrichtung von Wettbewerben und Spielbetrieb und als helfende Hand beim Einstieg in den eFootball. Wir teilen die Begeisterung von Spielern, Teams und Fans und sind ein fairer und verlässlicher Partner.

Wir sind davon überzeugt, dass in Zukunft jeder Fußballverein eine digitale Verlängerung in Form mindestens einer eFootball-Mannschaft hat, bei der jeweils 11 Menschen ihre 11 digitalen Avatare steuern, sodass 11 vs 11 eine Möglichkeit ist, Mitglieder zu binden und zu gewinnen. Gleichzeitig kann diese Spielform in Klubs mit einer Fan-Basis eine hervorragende Möglichkeit zur Fan-Interaktion und -bindung werden.

about:

name: NODE Robotics
about:
NODE Robotics provides plug & play software solutions for automated guided vehicles, transforming them into autonomous mobile robots and reducing total cost of ownership for intralogistics by up to 65%.

NODE offers software solutions on two different levels: 

The robot-level advanced autonomous navigation system can be installed on new and existing vehicles granting basic autonomy without further hardware modifications. 

The cloud-level services for fleet coordination and cooperation add services and applications to orchestrate fleets, exploiting Machine Learning and collaborative robotics approaches.

We are an EXIST-funded robotics spin-off from Fraunhofer IPA in Stuttgart, Germany.
