name: Quantum Brilliance
about: Quantum Brilliance is building room temperature quantum computers, powered by diamond. Our vision is to provide ubiquitous quantum computing: from data centres to hospitals, from autonomous vehicles to remote facilities.  A single quantum processor can outperform a classical supercomputer. With our diamond technology, we avoid the cryogenics and complex infrastructure requirements of other quantum architectures, and can ultimately shrink our processor down to the size of a GPU accelerator card.

name: Relivery
about:
Serving Chefs ist ein Lieferservice, mit dem du ein echtes Restaurant-Erlebnis zu Hause genießen kannst, weniger Verpackungsmüll.

Der Markt für Essenslieferungen wächst rasant, und damit auch der Abfall. Jeden Tag werden allein in Deutschland über 9 Millionen Einweg-Lebensmittelverpackungen weggeworfen. Im Jahr 2030 wird die Verwendung von Einweg-Plastikverpackungen für die Lebensmittellieferung verboten sein und die derzeitigen Alternativen sind suboptimal (erzeugen immer noch Abfall, sind teuer und lassen sich nicht so gut transportieren oder isolieren).

Mit unseren innovativen und stilvollen Verpackungen liefert Serving Chefs ein echtes Restaurant-Erlebnis für zu Hause. Unser Rückgabesystem für die nächste Bestellung stellt sicher, dass der gesamte Prozess problemlos abläuft und macht die Zero-Waste-Lieferung extrem bequem.

COMING SOON!

Subscribe and get the latest updates
www.servingchefs.com

about: We support SMEs with an easy-to-use SaaS solution which helps them to analyze, optimize and communicate their sustainability. - We're hiring!

name: TINY Technologies
about:
TINY Technologies is an innovative biotech research and manufacturing organization for the supplement, cosmetics, cannabis and pharmaceutical industries.

We are developing drug delivery systems for improved bioavailability together with the institute of technical chemistry at the University of Hamburg.

Our main research areas are:
- Formulation of drug delivery systems
- Synergistic ingredient formulations
- Production scale-up
- Evidence of increased bioavailability from in vitro and human studies

TINY provides high bioavailable active ingredients to manufacturers and brands in bulk to enable them to introduce market leader products.
We also enable pharma companies to make better medicine.

On their side, companies benefit from an intelligent system allowing them to hire rare talents in tech quickly and hassle-free, that they need to be successful.

TieTalent launched in October 2018 and is already trusted by thousands of candidates and hundreds of companies in Switzerland and Germany, ranging from large corporations to some of the most promising European startups.

Join us on our journey as we expand internationally and benefit from a friendly, international and rewarding work environment.

name: Loopline Systems
about:
Based in the heart of Berlin, Europe’s most innovative tech hub, Loopline Systems has been an expert in HR and agile employee feedback since 2014.

name: Authorized.by
about: Our Mission: Everyone shopping online shall be able to identify an authorized brand partner and their genuine products before ordering it. We enable manufacturers actively to regain control over their brands in e-commerce and strengthen the positioning of authorized shops at the same time.  We, the founders... of authorized.by worked successfully in e-commerce for years and ran a number of companies in that sector in the last decade. During that time we gained experience in communicating with manufacturers, managing product data as well as controlling and scaling online shops. This means that we experienced the shared challenges of brands and manufacturers first hand and realized the need of a working authorization solution.  Our aim is... to support brand manufacturers in regaining control in e-commerce and thus increase their conversion.  Together... with experienced IT experts, marketing and sales professionals and supported by the expertise of renowned law firms specialized in European and international trademark, copyright and competition regulations we developed our software and are continuously expanding our services for brand manufacturers and shops . Our headquarters are located in the historical center of Munich which inspires us to combine traditional values of reliability and trustworthiness with the technical requirements of the digital age.

name: Greenlight Media Holdings
about:
ASMBLE - The Social Influencer Marketplace

ASMBLE is the staging ground for brands and agencies that want to create viral campaigns through thoughtful, instant, and scalable influencer recruitment, management and co-creation, enabling brands to aggregate, synchronize, and launch campaigns on demand. Campaigns deployed in 3 hours, not 6 months.

We are building the world’s largest collective of creative stars, coming together with brands, agencies, and other influencers to grow their careers through collaboration, education, and monetization of their outside followings on social channels like IG and TikTok.

name: Ocean
about: Ocean.io is a B2B data platform that leverages AI to help sales and marketing teams focus their time, money and effort on the right deals.

name: Qnami
about: At Qnami we develop fundamental new technology using quantum mechanics. The control and measurement of the state of a single electron enables us to measure what could never be measured before. We call this quantum sensing and we are enthusiastically developing this technique to improve people’s lives and the world.

name: Chefslist
about:
Wir sind ein Team mit der Mission die Zukunft einer der ältesten und größten Industrien überhaupt zu sichern - Lebensmittel.

Unser Ziel ist es, die gesamte Supply-Chain vom Lebensmittel-Großhändler bis hin zum Gastronomen und Café-Besitzer zu digitalisieren. Damit wollen wir die enorme Lebensmittelverschwendung verringern, die Marktteilnehmer operativ stärken und und sie mit Hilfe von Technologie profitabler machen.

Heute ist ChefsList ist eine Bestell-App die Lebensmittel-Großhändler mit all ihren Kunden verbindet - also Bars, Cafés, Restaurants etc. Ein einfaches Tool, das die Kommunikation optimiert, betriebliche Ineffizienzen beseitigt und den gesamten Bestellvorgang für alle Seiten vereinfacht.

name: Aiola
about:
aiOla’s mission is to bridge the gap between Human Intelligence and artificial intelligence while connecting the “AI promise” for the masses.
 
By making AI accessible to everyone, we empower sales professionals and frontline employees with real-time, user-friendly, HUMINT-Driven business insights and intelligence on-the-go.

name: VoerEir AB
about:
Voereir AB is a start-up founded mid 2015 and our focus is to help operators succeed with their NFV transformation. VoerEir AB has a list of customers including several Tier 1s, to both consulting engagements and the Touchstone product, launched in Q3 2016. 

Our team has many years of experience from OpenStack, NFV, Telecom application development and VNF onboarding. We continue to upgrade our knowledge base through industry cooperation, open source community engagement, cooperation with universities and, most important, assignments to evaluate and help to improve many different NFV infrastructures. 

Our focus is to continue to develop an industry leading offering consisting of test suites, processes and expertise that will help cloud transformation projects reduce cost, risk and time to successful implementation. 

VoerEir address a global market, with offices in Delhi and Stockholm

name: JANZZ.technology
about: JANZZ.technology is a Swiss company founded in 2008, run by investors and entrepreneurs from IT, HR, Education, Marketing, Business Development and Law, and staffed by passionate experienced professionals from these fields and a diversity of cultural backgrounds and languages.  Our Universe JANZZ.technology is a technology and consulting (start-up) company active in the field of semantic job and skills matching, and the use of complex occupation and skills data. We offer standard, white-label products and SaaS solutions for the modelling, analysis and use of big data on job portals, by public employment services (PES), and on companies’ job sites.  Products • JANZZon! The Ontology of Occupation Data. The world’s most comprehensive knowledge base in the area of occupations and skills. It is a unique semantic system of interrelated data: occupations, skills, competences, qualifications, etc. in more than 9 languages (40 in 2020). It maps over 80 standard taxonomies such as ISCO-08, O*Net, ROME v3, PCS 2003 and KldB.   • JANZZsme! The Smart Matching Engine. Interprets data’s meaning with context from JANZZon!. Semantic matching between big datasets on multiple levels. Understands what criteria to match and delivers comparable, accurate results.  • JANZZclassifier! The Classification Tool. It analyzes complex sets of occupation related data, such as job title, skills, function or industry, and annotates them with intelligent and standardized meta-data. Enhances data for further processes such as benchmarking, matching or statistical analyses.  • JANZZ.jobs: Platform and White Label Solution. A jobs and talent marketplace built from the latest semantic technology. It precisely matches people, businesses, jobs and projects based on multiple criteria like occupation, skills and experience. Can be a fully integrated application within a company’s private domain, for project building, workforce skills transparency and benchmarking, staff redeployment and outplacement.

name: Distributed
about:
Distributed allows companies to deliver digital outcomes faster, and to a higher standard than any comparable product through the use of an AI powered global workforce.

That's why we founded Distributed - www.distributed.co

name: Anapaya
about:
OUR VISION:
Anapaya builds a global B2B network based on a next generation internet protocol fit for the 21st century!

OUR MISSION:
We develop the technology that powers this next-generation B2B network and bring it to the market through our own global backbone and our partnering service providers (ISPs, IXPs, colo and datacenters operators, cloud service providers, managed services providers, combining:
- the security and reliability of private networks 
- with the universality and openness of today’s internet

Our technology helps businesses to meet the requirements for reliability, security, performance, and compliance caused by the exponential growth of an interconnected world.

WHAT MAKES US DISRUPTIVE:
A combination of a new and highly-secure internet protocol, SCION, developed over the past decade at the internationally well-ranked Swiss Institute of Technology (from whom we are a spin-off) to replace the current internet protocol from the 1980’s, with Anapaya’s proprietary network technology on top.

name: FrontM
about:
FrontM is a UK headquartered technology start-up with a team spread between London, SFO, and Bangalore. We connect & engage people when they're unconnected and digitally isolated - such as passengers on airplanes and seafarers on ships. 

We do that with our patented Edge AI software platform that offers developer SDK/APIs, pre-built applications using our developer APIs, and the ability to create new applications at pace. We offer front-end SuperApps and individual pre-built applications on a simple subscription model. 

The benefits to our aviation partners such as airlines are driving passenger reassurance, continuous engagement, and a 30% increase in ancillary revenue generation. This is vital for the industry to bounce back and return to profitability again.

Similarly, the benefits to our maritime partners such as shipping companies and fisheries are crew reassurance, operational efficiencies, and increased productivity. This is vital for seafarers left in limbo with Covid-19 and for sustaining their efforts to keep our essential supplies and commodities flowing around the world.

Talk to us here or email info@frontm.com to request further information.

name: CrowdDesk
about:
Wir schaffen für jedes Unternehmen einen einfachen und digitalen Kapitalzugang.

Die Aufnahme und die Vermittlung von Kapital gehört für Unternehmen zu den komplexesten und reguliertesten Prozessen, die es überhaupt gibt. Dafür hat portagon eine Software gebaut, die alle Entscheidungsprozesse einfach, digital und rechtssicher darstellt. So digitalisieren wir durch unsere Produkte und Leistungen das Geschäft der Kapitalaufnahme und -vermittlung für Unternehmen, Banken, Emissionshäuser und Finanzvermittler. 

Das geschieht mit unserer White-Label-Lösung. Das bedeutet, dass unsere Kunden in den Vordergrund treten. Von portagon ist lediglich ein Investment-Button zu sehen, der sich unkompliziert auf die bestehende Unternehmenswebsite integrieren lässt. Dahinter stellen wir die technische Infrastruktur zur Verfügung, die jedem Unternehmen einen kosteneffizienten und vollständig automatisierten Kapitalzugang ermöglicht.  

Jedes Unternehmen erhält so einen eigenständigen Kapitalzugang über einen Investment-Button auf der eigenen Website, über eine separate Website oder mithilfe einer eigenen Plattform. Sie sind unabhängig von Dritten in ihren Investitionsentscheidungen und ihrer Kapitalbeschaffung. Wir stellen unseren Kunden einen Modulbaukasten zur Verfügung, der die technologische Infrastruktur umfasst und es ermöglicht, die rechtliche Strukturierung, die Vertriebsstrategie und einen professionellen Anlegerservice vollständig digital abzuwickeln. 

Für Banken, Emissionshäuser und Finanzvermittler treiben wir außerdem die Digitalisierung ihrer Geschäftsmodelle voran und eröffnen neue Finanzierungswege für deren Firmen- und Privatkunden. 

Über 500 Projekte bei einem Projektvolumen von mehr als 800 Millionen Euro hat portagon bereits begleitet. Rund 300 Kunden nutzen unsere Software-Lösung.

name: Acapela
about: Your voice matters! Give a digital voice persona to your image. Acapela Group creates custom & personalized #digitalvoices adapted to your needs. #voicetech #neuralTTS #voice1st  Acapela Group is a European leader of voice solutions with 30 years of expertise and market feedback, strong partnerships, deep rooted R&D, an enthusiastic team and a strong appetite for innovation. Acapela’s recent innovation based Neural TTS is opening up new opportunities for the creation of personalized digital voices, adapted to the environment in which the voice is used.  We speech-empower Voice-First interfaces. about:
Convercycle is a Social Media Agency that strives towards providing #trulysocial solutions that is focused and tailored around the “people” that matter to you and your brand.

We strive on delivering solutions that complete the cycle of conversation through active listening, by creating compelling content, engaging the audience to foster interaction, further evangelizing them to be brand advocates, adopt feedback, help brands implement them and enhance the brand equity. With this CROP.ZONE  offers an alternative in farmers toolbox in a context of increased regulatory demands and societal expectations.  The innovative patented CROP.ZONE solution can replace significant part of today’s synthetic herbicide use, providing a competitive alternative for weed management hence contributing to yield optimization and farm profitability, while contributing to sustainability goals.  With its solutions, CROP.ZONE is positioning itself within the future of agriculture

name: Wellabe
about:
With wellabe you can maintain productivity, influence company culture & engage your employees in the new world of work.

We offer health check-ups at the workplace and personalised, digital prevention programmes. With our mobile labs, we provide employees with comprehensive insights into their current health status in less than 20 minutes. The real-time results are made available to the participants in the wellabe app and can be discussed with a doctor during a video consultation. The subsequent data-based recommendations are tailored to the specific needs of the participants and support them in achieving lasting lifestyle changes. This way, risk factors can be identified early on, and chronic diseases can be prevented.

name: FELS Group

about:

name: PPRoi Services
about:

Within the frame of long term cooperation PPROI Development provides our clients information and knowledge support for measurement and building up of their business ROI. Our company is provider and implementator of PPROI IS. 

Our philosophy and methodology reflects our belief, that

 Management basically means right decision making about optimization of products, processes and resources in their relationship.
 This decision making always has many alternatives and key role of management consists of their evaluation and selection of the best one.
 Main criterion for the decision making process has to be ROI, because only this criterion leads company to real aim – maximization of return on capital invested.
 Other partial criterions may lead to capital wastes.
 Universal implementation of this principle we call „Management by ROI“

name: ivicos GmbH
about:
Wer wir sind: wir sind ein Start-up aus Frankfurt am Main, das Lösungen für die virtuelle Zusammenarbeit in verteilten Arbeitsumgebung (Home Office / New Work) entwickelt.

Was wir tun: wir entwickeln Lösungen für die virtuelle Kommunikation, Interaktion und Kollaboration von Teams und Mitarbeitern in Unternehmen und Institutionen. Unsere SaaS Lösungen weisen ein hohes Maß an Sicherheit auf und erfüllen nachvollziehbar strengste DSGVO Richtlinien. 

Unsere Produkte: coded in Europe with Europe in our hearts. 

- iv:CAMPUS - you never work alone
- iv:SPACE - better results faster

Was uns antreibt: wir lieben es, mit smarter Technik zu zaubern, um unseren Nutzern magische Momente, Aha-Erlebnisse und intuitive Anwendbarkeit zu schaffen. Zufriedene und treue Anwender unserer Produkte sind unser Erfolgskriterium.

Was uns besonders macht: wir sind ein buntes Team aus erfahrenen Strategieberatern mit viel Industrie- und Teamerfahrung, jungen Talenten, innovativen Entwicklern und smarten Designern. Wir bringen alles mit, um gute Produkte zu bauen, die ein hohes Maß an Nutzen bei unseren Kunden stiften. Ein Teil des Teams hat sich noch nie persönlich getroffen, doch täglich arbeiten wir auf ivCAMPUS eng zusammen. 

Warum virtuelle Kollaboration wichtig ist: Die Zukunft der Arbeit ist hybrid, fließend und räumlich verteilt, funktionsübergreifend innerhalb von Organisationen und über Organisationsgrenzen hinweg. Unsere Produkte sind Bausteine für neue, hybride Arbeitsprozesse, die nicht nur nachhaltig und effizient sind, sondern sich auch am Menschen und seinen sozialen Interaktionsbedürfnissen orientieren. Ein funktionierendes „Hybrid Office“ und das Angebot flexibler Arbeit bindet Mitarbeiter ans Unternehmen und erweitert den erreichbaren „Talent-Pool“ erheblich. 

Unser Ziel: Unseren Kunden dabei zu helfen, die Transition zu „New Work“ erfolgreich zu meistern und ihren Mitarbeitern ein attraktives, vollkommen neues Arbeitserlebnis zu bieten.

name: Umeleon
about: Founded 2018, Umeleon develops the multicolor Extruder (MCE). The machine itself is an external add on for FMD desktop 3D-printers and colors a single monochrome plastic string (or filament) according to the user color needs. The coloring process takes place before the actual printing process. Furthermore, the MCE is compatible with every single 3D-printers. Another advantage is that the color information can be saved directly in existing software so that users can keep using their favorite software. Beneficial’s of this technology are specially engineers, designers, artist, the plastic industry but also end users will get a direct access their customized filaments in small batches.

name: Blocktac
about: BLOCKTAC is a leading European company commercializing authentication and anti-counterfeit solutions based on Blockchain technology. Our Blockchain certificates are sold to Fast-Moving Consumer Goods manufacturers (named “Digital Seals” in this case; currently mainly for Food & Beverages companies), idCards, professional and educational accreditations, artworks and medical records. We are also prepared to offer our service to other industries: perfume and cosmetics, fashion items and luxury accessories. In short, it can be applied to any product where it is handy to verify authenticity and traceability. Consumers, using their mobile phones, may scan the QR code to check it against the product's unique and uncopiable identifier. This allows them to authenticate the product using Blockchain or submit a complaint if it turns out to be false. We have reached four million certificates and seals across from clients in six countries: Spain, the UK, Poland, Colombia, Costa Rica, and Bolivia. We are launching the Blockchain of Things, aimed to develop disposable, autonomous devices that automatically grab data from the world and stores it in Blockchain. This innovation becomes the missing link between Blockchain, IoT and AI. Recently, we received the Seal of Excellence from the CE and a Neotec project from the CEDETI.

name: Occtoo
about: Occtoo is an Experience Data Platform built to fast forward the way companies create relevant customer experiences everywhere.  We help digital officers, marketers and developers to move into a new state where they spend less time integrating data and more time being creative with data. Our game changing technology is already used by companies such as Cartier, Intersport, Fjällräven and Filippa K.  With Occtoo you can easily unify all experience data (and yes we mean all data. Customer, product, transactional, behavioural, content etc) and make it accessible in real time in any frontend of choice. Match the right content with the right customer and create an API with a click to publish and collect data in real time in all kinds of devices, touchpoints and channels.    Occtoo is the missing piece in your unified experience stack, enabling speed in your ”idea-to-deployment” process and capability to offer a relevant customer experience in a millisecond everywhere. Forget about data locked in silos, time consuming and costly integration projects and slow experiences that kill conversion. Instead you get an increased ability to innovate and gain speed in providing customers with unique experiences that makes you stand out from the crowd.   Built for marketers. Loved by developers.

name: Greenforce
about:
We are GREENFORCE. We are a food tech startup based out of Munich, Germany. We develop and provide plant-based food products that are good for people and the environment. Our mission is to secure the protein supply for future generations because they can no longer be fed with animal proteins.

For 8 years we have worked on a raw material that revolutionizes vegan food. We developed an enzymatic process that will be able to convert almost any plant into high-quality, protein-rich food products. The decisive factors here are the rapid bioavailability of the proteins as well as the compatibility and taste.

All our products are 100% vegan. Quality is especially important to us. We therefore purchase the high-quality raw materials from trusted suppliers with full transparency of the value chain. Once all raw materials have arrived at our Bavarian site, production starts according to German food safety regulations. Our highest quality standards are constantly monitored.

name: SAM - DIMENSION
about:
SAM-DIMENSION is a young and innovative precision farming start-up. We develop intelligent computer vision techniques and combine them with data science to enable effective field surveys. SAM-DIMENSION offers a complete solution for full-area aerial surveys of fields from mapping to the application to prevent yield loss due to weeds in conventional, hybrid and organic farming.

SAM-DIMENSION helps forward-thinking farmers to reduce their crop protection costs while increasing their productivity. By using the SAM-DIMENSION maps, the amount of pesticides applied is reduced by up to 90%. In addition to the ecological benefits, the customer achieves a cost saving of 40 %.

SAM-DIMENSION started its product development in 2019 and is already working intensively with farmers and companies from Germany and the Czech Republic on the market launch of the drone weed detection at the cotyledon stage. The company is led by a founding team with extensive experience in agriculture and sensor-technology.

name: ActiTrexx
about:
ActiTrexx GmbH is a new biotech start up and was founded in 2020. Our vision is to offer a curative cellular therapy to prevent inflammatory reactions in conditions like GvHD, solid organ transplantation and autoimmune diseases.
Regulatory T cells (Treg) - natural guardian cells of the immune system - are the key players of our cell-based drug product. Isolated Treg are activated ex vivo via specific methods and administered to patients intravenously. Unlike other comparable approaches, activated Treg (ATreg) will not be expanded in vitro, protecting them against a possible loss of function. Thus, ATreg is a safe and efficient treatment option for transplanted patients preventing and providing substantial decrease of GvHD severity and related mortality as well. The founders of ActiTrexx GmbH combine many years of unique experience in basic research, biotechnology, clinical application and pharmaceutical development. The management team is supported and complemented by a strong network of collaborators, advisors and key opinion leaders as well as experienced managers. 
ActiTrexx GmbH is headquartered in Mainz, Germany.

name: Privé Technologies
about:
Founded in 2011, Privé Technologies is a leading Software as a Service (SaaS) provider, helping financial institutions to digitise their wealth management offerings using our modular platform.

The breadth of our suite of products – which spans from client acquisition and content marketing, to digital onboarding and CRM, to portfolio construction, portfolio management (PMS), portfolio monitoring and reporting, to account aggregation, and more – is unparalleled in the financial technology industry. 

Our lego block approach allows clients to choose and assemble unique journeys from our wide range of modules and digital solutions to suit their individual needs, empowering them with the tools necessary to achieve any digital goal, be it creating fully digital Advisor-led wealth management journeys to end-to-end robo-advisory solutions. This modularity and flexibility allows us to solve a wide variety of use cases across the wealth management landscape through our scalable, cloud based platform, and helps our clients to expedite their digitization efforts. It also allows us to service a range of different wealth segments from HNWI to mass retail. Our tools currently live with Private Banks, Retail Banks, Insurers, Asset Managers, Securities & Brokerage providers as well as Multi-family offices and External Asset Managers. 

Over the past 10 years, we are honored to have our efforts in the wealth management space recognized, not only by clients — Prive was ranked 26th fastest growing company across APAC by the Financial Times (2020) — but also through multiple industry awards across all of our product sets. We are proud to have been crowned Best IAM/MFO solution by Asian Private Banker (2017-2020), named Best Robo-Advisor methodology by a Kaplan & SMU report (2018), been part of the WealthTech 100 Cohort two years running (2020 & 2021) and to have won countless other industry awards for our solutions, be it directly or via our clients.

name: Visitor Analytics
about:
Visitor Analytics is a high-performing start-up that aims to offer an all-in-one solution for any website in regards to website statistics, UX & behavior (recordings, heatmaps, funnels, etc.), visitor interaction, and so much more. Founded in January 2016 in Munich and Cluj, our app has been installed more than 2.5M times by users from 190 countries.

Tracking and understanding website statistics, analytics and user behavior using most tools is very complex & time-consuming, especially for non-technical people. You have to install and use many tools in parallel, retrieve data from different repositories, and then compare them all. It’s easy to find yourself stuck in an overwhelming amount of graphs and charts. This is why we developed Visitor Analytics: all the tools you need, united into one app. A user-friendly structure, a straightforward presentation of complex data, and simplifying your work with  data synergy between modules!

We are 100% GDPR/CCPA compliant and collect all the data a website owner needs to know about their visitors in real-time: referrals, conversions, bounce rates, click paths, traffic structure, social media interactions, custom events, page visits, IPs, locations, browsers, devices or OS used, and much more. And get more value from the app by using our visitor behavior analysis tools: session recordings, conversion funnels, and heatmaps. Receive feedback from your website’s visitors with almost no effort using our amazing poll and survey features. Our app is built for entrepreneurs, marketers and companies focused on their site statistics, visitor behavior, and interacting with their website visitors. Stay tuned for more useful modules; we’ve always got a new feature right around the corner.

name: Autlay
about:
Wer wir sind?

Ein motiviertes Team auf dem Weg das Print Marketing zu revolutionieren!

AutLay ist ein disruptives Technologieunternehmen, das sich der Vision verschrieben hat, Design Prozesse mit Hilfe von Künstlicher Intelligenz effizienter zu gestalten. Wir bieten eine innovative KI-gesteuerte Software für die vollautomatische und maßgeschneiderte Layouterstellung von druckfertigen Werbemitteln an, wodurch manuelle Aufwände und damit verbundene Kosten erheblich minimiert werden. Die Resultate unserer Kundenprojekte zeigen außerdem, dass durch Autlay erstellte Printmailings  größere Warenkörbe, insbesondere durch Einsatz von Cross- und Upselling Artikeln, generiert werden und schließlich zu einer erhöhten Conversion Rate führen. Unser Team (17 Mitarbeiter) teilt ein agiles Mindset, die Begeisterung für Technologien und bringt vielfältige Expertisen aus den Bereichen Artificial Intelligence, Marketing Automation, Retail und Consulting zusammen.

Individuelle Mailings für jeden separaten Kunden? Wie funktioniert das?

AutLay hat aus der Forschung heraus eine smarte Technologie entwickelt, die ohne Templates individuelle und vollautomatische Layouts für druckfertige Werbemittel erstellt. Durch den Einsatz von Künstlicher Intelligenz können basierend auf über 50 Metriken aus den Bereichen Ästhetik, Typografie und Wirtschaftlichkeit Printmedien in Rekordzeit gelayoutet werden, wodurch Zeit- und Geldressourcen erheblichen eingespart werden können. name: baseclick
about:
At baseclick we believe that bioconjugation is not just a method to connect (bio)molecules, but a tool to develop valuable applications. Simple methods for efficient and robust nucleic acid labeling are at the core of the baseclick technology.
Our mission is to develop and provide the best nucleic acid labeling applications and reagents for the life science market.
History
In 2008 BASF venture capital and Prof. Thomas Carell from the LMU Munich started to turn this mission into reality and founded baseclick GmbH, with its site close to Munich. Back then, it was very hard, using standard labeling techniques such as dye-building blocks, NHS-chemistry or other techniques to efficiently modify nucleic acids with multiple modifications. This was due to a lack of efficiency and simplicity in labeling technology. So, a new strategy was needed: click chemistry! Since then scientists at baseclick and elsewhere are improving the technology and widening its scope by creating inventive applications. Our expertise in this field has led to collaborations with leading companies and laboratories in pharma, life science and academia. But what about pricing and quality? Even a great technology should be offered in good quality at reasonable prices. Therefore, we have developed a high-quality affordable product portfolio on click chemistry-based applications to support your research.

name: Fibraworks
about:
At Fibraworks, “Winding the future” is applied practice. With our innovative winding process, the so-called "Fibraforce Technology", the smart team around Lars Linnemann and Lukas Schulz is revolutionizing the future of lightweight design. Fibraworks produces with its winding process multi-layered, multi-directional semi-finished fiber products, like Organo-Coils or Tailored NCF, for cost-effective and sustainable lightweight solutions.

Flexible, material-independent and cost effective – our patented winding process permits, for the first time, the large-scale production of multi-directional semi-finished fiber products with a thermoplastic matrix, our so-called Organo-Coils, produced customer-specific and sustainably based on, e.g., natural-, glass- or carbon fibers. With our continuous and flexible production technology and minimization of downstream process steps we can attain outstanding cost efficiency that will accelerate the use of thermoplastic composites in lightweight construction in all industries.

We produce Organo-Coils based on UD-tapes that are wound and fixed into multidirectional layers. Our customers can select the arial weight and resulting fiber orientation within a wide range of options. We can generate fiber orientations between 30° and 70° that can be supplemented by 0° and 90° layers. The results are customer-specific bi-axial, tri-axial or quadraxial Organo-Coils. Due to their flexible fiber orientation, our Organo-Coils offer very high lightweight potential and superior cost efficiency. Our team consists of technology-savvy and innovation-driven experts from the fields of composites, special purpose machinery manufacturing, aeronautical engineering, and business administration. Our innovative winding process with its ultra-high-volume output rates facilitates the production of energy- and resource-efficient, recyclable products for sustainable and large-scale lightweight solutions.

So - let’s wind the future together!

What started as an idea of two educators turned into a transformative movement for an educational change. By combining different concepts of learning with modern Mixed Reality technologies, Heartucate was born. In interdisciplinary teams of education, media and technology we create a new mixed media format, that will change our way of learning and opens up spaces for a collaborative, positive approach towards learning. 

We create Learning Adventures with Augmented Reality, in which children become world and time travellers in their class room. By solving tasks as a team, they learn contents of the curriculum as well as working together in order to achieve a shared goal.

Heartucate won the Samsung 5G for Society Challenge and is thereby supported by national and international partners such as Samsung, the Technische Universität Dresden and the 5G Lab Germany. 

Our goal is to bring Heartucate everywhere and thereby foster collaborative learning patterns regardless of existing infrastructures or cultural differences. We believe in the magic of shared experiences, shared values and shared common goals.

So let’s do this - let’s #heartucate!

name: Grandperspective GmbH
about:
With the scanfeld™ system Grandperspective provides the world's first early warning solution for hazardous gases that covers complete industrial sites. Based on our optical sensor units that identify a multitude of chemicals from the distance, we visualize and locate hazardous gas clouds and warn in real time against gas leaks and fugitive emissions. 

Grandperspective is a young company rich in experience. Our know-how in the development and application of remote sensing systems has been developed over years of working with plant operators and first responders all over the world. scanfeld™ bundles this knowledge into an innovative solution for the remote monitoring of plants of any size.

The scanfeld™ early warning solution combines a novel detection system with an intelligent software package to form world’s first remote monitoring solution that is completely automated. Hundreds of different chemicals are identified from kilometers distance by passive FTIR spectroscopy. Large areas such as production sites, storage or transportation areas are monitored with just a handful of sensor units. Gas leaks are quickly detected and the distribution of hazardous gas clouds is monitored and visualized in real-time.

The fully automated early warning solution is designed for the control room of the plant. It delivers an intuitive visualization of gas clouds and a mapping of hazard zones. It provides additional safety barriers and helps to mitigate the effects of gas release events.

Our solution:
Use our veripass app to digitally secure and manage your personal credentials.

Whether certificates or qualifications: With our veripass app, all your paper-based credentials are digitally available in one place at any time.

By digitizing paper-based credentials the effort required for credential management and credential audit (compliance) reduces by up to 40% - 90%.

Damit der gute Herr Kornmann bald nicht mehr das völlig verstaubte und unpräzise Gebärmuttermodell und die viel zu großen Holzpenisse heranschleppen muss und alle peinlich berührt an die Decke starren. Damit es heißt: “Jetzt ladet ihr mal bis zur nächsten Stunde die App KNOWBODY herunter.” 

Damit Sexualkunde enttabuisiert wird und Informationen modern aufbereitet und für alle verfügbar sind. Damit wir alle verstehen, dass man auch während der Menstruation schwanger werden kann oder dass auch durch Oralverkehr Geschlechtskrankheiten übertragen werden. Damit wir alle wissen, dass Schamlippen unterschiedlich groß sein können und sie auch gar nicht Schamlippen heißen müssten. Denn da ist nichts, wofür man sich schämen muss. 

Damit man auch anonym Fragen stellen kann und nicht gleich vor der ganzen Klasse. Und natürlich auch, damit Schulunterricht im 21. Jahrhundert vielleicht irgendwann eine Spur digitaler wird.

Bis die App mithilfe unserer vielen, vielen Partnerinnen und Unterstützer fertiggestellt ist, freuen wir uns über Ratschläge, Mithilfe und vor allem über Lehrer:innen, die bereit wären sich interviewen zu lassen. Damit wir die aktuellen Herausforderungen der Sexualpädagogik verstehen.

name: Beezer
about:
Beezer is your all-in-one platform to create, distribute, and manage your own mobile app. Spread awareness, engage customers, and improve conversion with a Beezer-built Progressive Web App. 

Our platform allows Marketing Managers, Events' Organisers, Business Owners, and more to quickly and easily create their own Progressive Web App - without any coding or technical skills - by simply uploading their content.

Business is increasingly online, and “online” is increasingly mobile - businesses know this. But capitalizing on it can be hard. The web is no longer fit for purpose on mobile, which is why users spend 90% of their phone time in apps. But apps aren't much better: they cost a fortune to develop, and once that's done, they go into the app store...where, unless they're owned by Facebook or Google, they're unlikely to be downloaded or used.

At Beezer, we decided that there had to be a third way. And that's why we created a platform that puts the power back into the hands of small businesses. It's easy to use, it's affordable, and it empowers anyone to not only build, but also distribute, manage, engage with, and analyse their own PWA.

What are PWAs? Progressive Web Apps marry the best of the web – namely, discoverability, easy distribution without gatekeepers, and download-free access – together with the security, offline functionality, slick UX/UI, and tools of engagement normally seen in native apps. 

With a Beezer-built PWA, you get your own powerful mobile-first online presence - on your own terms.

Beezer: build something brilliant.

name: Cervest
about:
The rapid pace of climate change demands new approaches to adaptation. We need new instruments and insights to protect our most valued assets, decarbonize at scale, and build an equitable and resilient future for our planet. We need Climate Intelligence. 
Climate Intelligence is mass intelligence for managing climate decisions  — intelligence that enables us to be more prescient, decisive, and collaborative about asset-level adaptation than ever before. It transforms how we build, manage, and adapt our most valuable assets, including power plants, factories, hospitals, transport networks, forests, and homes.

We’re a Certified B Corporation with a vision to build a climate intelligent world — one where everyone is able to use Climate Intelligence to adapt with climate change. 
By making Climate Intelligence open, democratised and transparent we will power a global Climate Intelligent Network™ that drives a chain reaction of climate intelligent decisions to protect the world’s critical assets, including our greatest asset — the planet. 
Built on the core principles of irrefutable and evolving science, quantification for every asset, and open access for all, our AI-powered Climate Intelligence platform makes on-demand Climate Intelligence available to every business, government, NGO, and individual.
 
Using our flagship EarthScanTM product, anyone can discover how current and future climate events such as flooding, droughts, and extreme temperatures will impact their assets. 

EarthScan helps our customers confidently de-risk decisions, meet financial disclosure needs and improve the resilience of the assets they own, manage or rely on. Learn more at cervest.earth.

With uugot.it language learning becomes not just super easy but so much fun.

Besides language learning uugot.it is a helpful tool for migrants and refugees to arrive in the society of their host country. Why is that so? TV is a mirror of the society, uugot.it enables that local channels will become understandable, people who use uugot.it will understand: What moves the society of their host country as well as what are the people laughing about, which traditions and values they have or which fears and challenges they're facing. uugot.it makes the content easier to understand and therefore we enable an entrance to the society with a low threshold.  

By doing that uugot.it slips into the role of a bridge builder and opens the host society for those who come to live with us.

name: ViTeach
about:
ViTeach is a virtual, highly interactive online teacher. 

ViTeach deliberately rethinks current, oftentimes antique teaching methods and develops state of the art teaching content and study materials to cater to a variety of skill levels and select the most effective modes of delivery (different people have different preferences as to how they learn) at the right point and right time. Content selection, sequencing, and difficulties are based on individual user assessment (leverages machine learning models to continuously self-optimize).

ViTeach encourages regular user feedback and is maximizing user engagement through various reward approaches (gamification, i.e. gathering points and badges)

ViTeach has a strong social focus as it has been established time and time again that the percentage of students having access to tutoring rapidly declines with a lower income of the parents. Reserving licenses for students from weaker socio-economic backgrounds will help to offset this inequality.

ViTeach is dedicated to helping achieve UN Sustainability Goal #4 while also building a sustainable business.

name: Circunomics
about: Circunomics is building the World's largest virtual battery recycling and second life network. Today, we manage 1.5 GWh of spent batteries and 5,000 tons of recycling capacity. We are tackling one of the largest and most profitable problems of the Circular Economy: "How to enable efficient data, material trading and recycling processes in the Circular Battery Economy?" By 2030, 11 million tonnes lithium-ion batteries will have to be recycled. The lack of standards in processes, certification, track & trace technology results in high process and transaction costs, the loss of valuable raw materials, and prevents the development of recycling and second life scenarios worth over USD 8 billion annually. Circunomics aims to (1) reduce friction, build trust between market participants and increase market transparency to achieve a positive cost-benefit ratio for the private sector; (2) achieve significant waste reduction of precious battery resources, creating a profitable battery aftermarket, and to reduce the dependency of foreign lithium and cobalt supply; and (3) enable significant product, service model and process innovations for the Circular Economy.

The proprietary technology includes both a novel approach to metallization and novel particle-free ink formulations. This combination offers a multi-level improvement to the production of printed metal electrodes with regards to costs, material economy, energy expenditure, waste generation, and environmental friendliness.

OrelTech’s product portfolio includes particle-free inks based on silver, gold and platinum that can be printed with a variety of deposition methods like inkjet printing, aerospray, dip coating or slot die. Read more about our products at https://oreltech.com/products

Our patented surface coating technology can be utilized across a range of industries, including printed electronics, medical devices, sensors, fuel cells, (electro)plating, decoration, aerospace/automotive, as well as many emerging markets.

Die Farmerscent GmbH ist 2020 in Osnabrück gegründet worden. Als Start-Up suchen wir neue Lösungen für eine nachhaltige Landwirtschaft. Schwerpunkt unserer Arbeit ist die Entwicklung des AeroDiffs, einen von uns konstruierten Diffusor. Mit unserem System können Tierhalter auf verschiedene Situation in ihrem Stall reagieren. Hierfür entwickeln wir fortlaufend Liquids, die der AeroDiff in den Ställen vernebelt. Dabei setzen wir zu 100% auf natürliche Stoffe ein und testen die Produkte direkt in den Ställen. Eben dort, wo sie wirken sollen. 


Our goal: Sustainable solutions for animal husbandry

The Farmerscent GmbH was founded in Osnabrück in 2020. As a start-up we are looking for new solutions for a sustainable agriculture. The main focus of our work is the development of the AeroDiff, a diffuser designed by us. With our system, animal owners can react to different situations in their stables. For this purpose, we are continuously developing liquids that the AeroDiff atomizes in the stables. We use 100% natural materials and test the products directly in the stables. Exactly there, where they are supposed to work.

about:

￼
Unsere Expertise im B2B-Bereich entstammt der langjährigen Erfahrung in der Entwicklung von cloud-basierten ERP-Systemen und branchenübergreifenden SaaS Software-Tools. Es ist dem täglichen Umgang mit den Geschäftsprozessen unserer Kunden zu verdanken, dass wir ein klares Bild davon besitzen, worauf es bei der Digitalisierung wirklich ankommt.

￼
Für uns stellt die Dienst- und Schichtplanung einen Kernaspekt mittelständischer Unternehmen dar, bei dem noch wesentliches Verbesserungspotential vorhanden ist. Unser Ziel ist es daher, Unternehmen, die noch auf Basis einer händischen bzw. Excel-basierten Arbeitsweise ihre Dienstplanung vornehmen, eine kostengünstige digitale Alternative an die Hand zu geben, die sich mühelos in den betrieblichen Alltag integrieren lässt. Wir möchten Mittelständlern und Startups außerdem dabei helfen, von teuren – und meist auch unnötig komplizierten – Softwareangeboten abzusehen und stattdessen auf kostengünstige und moderne Cloud-Anwendungen wie Aplano umzusteigen.
Unsere Vision ist, dass sich Kunden mit Hilfe unserer Software wieder auf das wesentliche im Betrieb konzentrieren können – ohne sich mit den lästigen bürokratischen Aspekten des Arbeitsalltags herumschlagen zu müssen. Apano ist eines unserer Produkte, mit dem unsere Kunden schon heute dieses Ziel verwirklichen.

Die baukobox funktioniert plattformunabhängig und ist über die gängigen Browser sowie auf mobilen Endgeräten abrufbar.

Sie wurde aus der Lehre am Fachbereich Architektur der TU Kaiserslautern mit Unterstützung des Deutschen Forschungszentrums für Künstliche Intelligenz entwickelt.

Im Rahmen der Architekturlehre an Hochschulen und Universitäten in Deutschland, Österreich und der Schweiz lässt sich baukobox zudem als ideales Recherchetool für Studierende und Lehrende einsetzen.

Our platform enables frictionless supply chain collaboration within all involved parties. We offer you the solution of nearly all your logistics pain points: no more surprises at the ramp, no more downtime on the yard, no costly and faulty paper processes, no more countless mailings and calls, no more stressed employees.

On the other hand, the major challenges of today's work and life require the organization of thousands of datapoints, whether one is working on extensive research for a master's or doctoral thesis, or on complex business models or consulting projects.  Infinity Maps was developed with knowledge workers in mind, who are pushed to the limits of existing productivity and mapping tools when representing and navigating vast content and complex relationships, and are looking for a unique solution to combine detail and overview. name: PARKLAB Technologie
about:
PARKLAB gehört zu den intelligenten Systemen der Smart-City Plattform und spezialisiert sich dabei insbesondere auf die Smart-Parking-Systeme.

Demzufolge befasst sich PARKLAB mit der Digitalisierung und Vernetzung von öffentlichen beziehungsweise privaten Parkflächen mithilfe der selbst entwickelten Parkplatzsensoren.
Die von den Sensoren gewonnenen Daten werden in Echtzeit an den Nutzer durch die neuzeitliche LoRaWAN Technologie weitergeleitet. Diese können den Fahrer beispielsweise durch die App auf dem Smartphone zum Zielort navigieren und die Parkgebühren mit dem Smartphone zahlen.

Neben Autofahrern bietet PARKLAB auch smarte Lösungen für Unternehmen, sowie Kommunen an, die mithilfe eines Dashboards Kunden bzw. Bürger bei der Parkplatzsuche begleiten können und dabei die Parkplatzsituation aktualisieren.

Mit seinem System trägt PARKLAB auch zum Klimaschutz bei. Mit der Smart Parking Lösung von PARKLAB wird der CO₂-Ausstoß, der bei Parkplatzsuche im Verkehr entsteht, reduziert. Zusätzlich bieten wir mehr Mobilität für Pendler sowie Reisende.

Durch die erfassten Daten wird in der Zukunft autonomes Parken besser mit der zunehmenden Digitalisierung und Automatisierung der Fahrzeuge, die vermehrt auf intelligente Systeme zurückgreifen, verknüpft.

Mit einem großen und vielfältigen Produktangebot kommt PARKLAB allen Bedürfnissen seiner Kunden nach. Neben Parkplatzsensoren bestehen noch weitere Sensortechniken und Softwareprogramme, die eigens von PARKLAB hergestellt wird und entwickelt wurde. Für weitere Fragen können Sie uns gerne kontaktieren.


Überblick der Eigenschaften:
>Verbeugt Co2-Ausstoß 
>Geschützt gegen Umwelteinflüsse 
>Unterschiedliche Sensortechnologien zur Erfassung 
>Längere Lebenszykluskosten als vergleichbare Produkte 
>Kurze Installationsdauer 
>Wartungsarm 
>Echtzeitdaten 
>Selbstkalibrierend 
>Diebstahlschutz 
>Mobiles Bezahlsystem 
>Routenoptimierung

name: Blackshark.ai
about:
Blackshark.ai provides powerful insights into the world by extracting information from satellite imagery fully automatically. A scalable artificial intelligence builds the core of the blackshark platform, detecting features with incredible precision and speed. A novel machine learning approach was developed to train a neural network for new features rapidly, enabling blackshark to serve various use cases in many different industries.

Input sources supported: 

- satellite imagery
- 2D photographs (aerial, street level, ...) 
- point clouds (photogrammetry or lidar)
- HD map data
- OSM
- & more

Examples for feature detection:

- buildings (footprint, height, type, roof, orientation, facade)
- vegetation
- streets
- land classification
- flood detection
- & more

Blackshark.ai can also fully automatically and semantically reconstruct detected features in 3D, using a patented technology for efficiently storing  and streaming petabytes of data.

Blackshark.ai is a team of 100+ data scientists, geospatial engineers, 3D rendering programmers and developers, based in San Francisco, US, and Graz, Austria, Europe's computer vision hub.

We are on a mission to answer questions such as:

- Can my drone land in this backyard?
- How many solar panels are installed in India?
- How many tents does a certain refugee camp have?
- How many cars are parked in a specific parking lot?

What would you like to know?

Fachkraft1 is intended to become the recognized service-as-a-software solution for German companies in all industries with bottlenecked professions, starting with in the healthcare sector, and professionals in third countries, creating a win-win-win situation:

name: Treasurize.de
about:
Treasurize ist der Marktplatz für e-Learning und digitale Weiterbildung.

Die Weiterbildung und Entwicklung der Mitarbeiter nehmen eine immer größere Rolle im Unternehmen ein. Aktuelle und passende Bildungsangebote zu finden, kann zu einer echten Herausforderung werden. Daher haben wir alle namhaften Anbieter getestet und ausgewählt.

Darüber hinaus gibt es oftmals keine einheitlichen Qualitätsstandards, wenn es um die Themen e-Learning und digitale Weiterbildung geht. An diesem Punkt setzt Treasurize an und bietet geprüftes Fachwissen und Anbieter. Höchste Qualitätsstandards und ein reibungsloser Prozess werden garantiert.

Hinzu kommt ein sehr großes Portfolio. Mehr als 16.000 e-Learning-Kurse, 400 Online Weiterbildungen, 200 Online Studiengänge und 130 digitale Zertifizierungen.

-- e-Learning --
Über 16.000 e-Learning-Kurse in 11 Kategorien von IT bis Sprachen stehen zur Verfügung. Technologie-Konzerne wie Microsoft, amazon oder IBM, die bekanntesten deutschsprachigen Anbieter wie Lecturio, Campus Lab oder Lingoda sowie die größten internationalen Anbieter wie LinkedIn Learning, Udemy, edX oder Coursera bieten ihre e-Learning-Kurse auf Treasurize an.

-- Digitale Weiterbildung --
Über 400 digitale Weiterbildungen stehen in 10 Kategorien stehen zur Verfügung. Zusammen mit über 60 Universitäten und Hochschulen bietet Treasurize anerkannte Weiterbildungen wie Hochschulzertifikate, IHK-Zertifikate und staatliche Abschlüsse.

-- Online Studium --
Über 200 Online Studiengänge stehen in 10 Fachbereichen zur Auswahl. Zusammen mit 29 Universitäten und Hochschulen bietet Treasurize Studiengänge im Online Studium mit anerkannten akademischen Abschlüssen.

-- Digitale Zertifizierungen --
Über 130 digitale Zerifitizierungen in den Bereichen Change Management, IT, Marketing und Projektmanagement sind auf Treasurize verfügbar.

name: Kaholo
about:
Kaholo lets any engineer easily and quickly build even the most advanced automation workflows without spaghetti scripts or specialized knowledge.

Kaholo’s solution allows software organizations to increase usage of automation throughout the full software development life cycle and as a result, shorten development time, improve code quality and increase infrastructure resilience.

Companies such as CheckPoint software and Align Technology use Kaholo to improve their software development process. Software developers use Kaholo’s platform for software builds and setup cloud environments. Testers use Kaholo for QA orchestration. DevOps use Kaholo for CI/CD processes and automatic remediation and security teams use Kaholo for data enrichment.

name: Alternative Derivatives Exchange
about: We intend to operate the leading electronic global futures marketplace for trading a broad array of alternative products with special focus on Digital Assets. Currently, we are the only marketplace planning to offer an electronic venue for trading of a range of deliverable Digital Assets products as futures. Through our electronic trading venue, our marketplace brings together buyers and sellers of derivative contracts on Digital Assets and several other alternative products. Our electronic platform increases the accessibility and transparency of the Digital Asset markets and enhances trust, speed and quality of trade execution. Additional, products in the product pipeline include Freight, Weather and Hashing futures. Freight and Weather will be launched in partnership with entities that act as brokers in these markets or large participants e.g. shipping companies.  The open architecture of our business model — meaning our ability to offer centralized access to trading in futures on a decentralised cleared basis through multiple interfaces — allows our participants to optimize their trading operations and strategies. We intend to conduct our futures business directly, and our Clearing business through Third Party Regulated Clearing Houses or, should it become necessary, through a wholly owned subsidiary, ADE Clear Chain.  At launch ADE will be the largest Digital Assets futures exchange outside of North America (by default). We will also offer a variety of market data services for futures, which we intend to spin off into a market data subsidiary. ADE owns its entire technology stack which is currently offered via SaaS agreements to form an additional revenue stream for the business. At ADE we will offer market participants price transparency, a full market depth view, liquid markets and transactional integrity all at a fixed low cost.  ADEs technology is ready and deployed. We are presently doing a late seed round in anticipation of a q4 2020 UAT deployment.

name: Exaloan
about:
Exaloan is a Frankfurt-based fintech that specializes in developing machine learning tools for predictive analytics in digital loans. We provide institutional investors with cutting-edge technology and help them connect to the digital lending market on a global scale. Through our integrated Loansweeper software they can run a dynamic investment process in individual digital loans with the same standard across lending platforms.

“High-quality analytics and a visionary mind to revolutionize investments in digital loans”

Our team combines extensive know-how and experience in the areas of quantitative portfolio management, capital markets, machine learning, and software development. We aim to shape the future of digital loan investing. Respecting our craft, our team, and our partners we dedicate ourselves to excellence.

name: Gorillas
about:
GROCERIES DELIVERED IN 10 MINUTES AT RETAIL PRICES

We are Gorillas. We’re on a mission to change the way that you do groceries. We believe that in a world where we have the technology to go to the moon, grocery shopping has to be radically faster and far more convenient. With an emphasis on high-quality, locally sourced products, our offering includes a wide selection of fresh fruits, dairy, vegan products & cooled drinks, plus unique selections from our local community partners.

Born out of a love for cycling and a desire to bring about change, Gorillas is redefining an entire industry from the ground up. Until recently, groceries delivered to your door in 10 minutes was a concept that was almost unimaginable. Today, our rider crew makes magic happen on the daily.

At our core, we are bold and authentic people with unrivaled team spirit and a mindset to always be riding. Now live in nine countries (with more on the way), we are one of Europe’s fastest-growing startups. True to our need for speed, in March 2021 we became Germany’s fastest ever unicorn company with a $1bn valuation and €305m total funding raised. And we’re just getting started.

name: icho systems gmbh
about:
Die ichó systems gmbh entwickelt interaktive Systeme für Menschen mit kognitiven Erkrankungen.

Das erste Produkt ist ichó, ein interaktiver Therapieball für Menschen mit Demenz. 
Durch modernste Sensortechnologie erkennt ichó alle äußeren Einflüsse. Je nach Anwendung kann ichó mit farbigem Leuchten, Vibration, Klang oder Musik reagieren. Die Reaktionen sind frei und individuell auf die Bedürfnisse des Nutzers anpassbar.
Hierdurch erreicht ichó eine höhere Aktivierung und Förderung, durch gezieltere Ansprache.

name: PaxlifeInnovations
about:
PaxLife Innovations GmbH specializes in content delivery software solutions for transport operators, systems integrators or manufacturers to maximize the benefit of installed WiFi systems for media streaming onboard. Partnering with media providers, PaxLife enables virtually unlimited onboard WiFi bandwidth for passengers' delight, providing a as-at-home digital experience during the journey while preserving most of the vehicles´ existing cellular bandwidth for other uses. 

PaxLife´s SaaS and IaaS portfolio includes:  
- Live streaming capability, for video and audio  
- A hybrid Content Delivery Network in vehicle for media streaming apps and other digital services to be hosted onboard 
- A bouquet of up to 32 DAB+ interruption-free radio channels, 
- Ultra high-speed, burst-mode rail-to-ground data exchange 

Affordable, simple plug-in, fully managed and modular proposition. PaxLife Innovations covers everything from management of media players/services providers, technical integration and delivery to vehicles, ongoing monitoring, support and maintenance. Supplied as part of your own WiFi product, or contracted separately as an add-on. It works for rail and for buses.

Based in Potsdam, Germany, PaxLife originally started out by connecting aircraft passengers to the digital world. To answer the challenge of bringing onboard content and passenger services in a modern fashion, PaxLife developed a disruptive digital architecture that is at the heart of its solutions. PaxLife´s railSTACK is a powerful cloudedge hosting platform for operators to support, deploy and securely manage any applications that run on rail or buses, enabling the easy setup of new adding value services onboard any fleet at any time. 

This is PaxLife´s contribution to support public transport as tomorrow´s mobility of choice. Get in touch! sales@paxllife.aero

name: Tuten

El mundo cambió, las personas lo hicieron y las expectativas de servicio de los clientes cada día son más urgentes. En Tutenlabs nos convertirnos en un socio estratégico de los principales actores del mercado para transformar digitalmente tu negocio y cumplir las expectativas de servicio de tus clientes. Creemos en un mundo donde los clientes reciban experiencias de servicio memorables, ajustadas a sus necesidades, costumbres y valores. 

Somos una empresa joven, con presencia en Chile, México y Colombia, que lleva más de 5 años en el mercado y que ha logrado ir duplicándose anualmente. Ya somos más de 90 colaboradores enfocados en el desarrollo de soluciones tecnológicas para digitalizar el negocio y la experiencia de servicio de grandes empresas. Hemos levantado más de USD 5 millones en capital de los inversionistas más relevantes de Latino América, nuestras soluciones están siendo utilizadas por más de 5 mil usuarios, y estimamos duplicarlos para el 2021. Algunos de nuestros clientes son Sodimac, Engie, SURA y CAM.

The motivation. People. Transformation. Innovation.

name: Greenforce
about:
We are GREENFORCE. We are a food tech startup based out of Munich, Germany. We develop and provide plant-based food products that are good for people and the environment. Our mission is to secure the protein supply for future generations because they can no longer be fed with animal proteins.

For 8 years we have worked on a raw material that revolutionizes vegan food. We developed an enzymatic process that will be able to convert almost any plant into high-quality, protein-rich food products. The decisive factors here are the rapid bioavailability of the proteins as well as the compatibility and taste.

All our products are 100% vegan. Quality is especially important to us. We therefore purchase the high-quality raw materials from trusted suppliers with full transparency of the value chain. Once all raw materials have arrived at our Bavarian site, production starts according to German food safety regulations. Our highest quality standards are constantly monitored.

name: Cannamedical Pharma
about:
Cannamedical® Pharma GmbH has a pharmaceutical wholesale licence in accordance with 52a of the Medicines Act (AMG) and a permit to handle narcotics in accordance with § 3 of the Act on Narcotics (BtMG).

As the only independent German cannabis wholesaler we cooperate with several selected international producers. Our independence guarantees a qualitatively and quantitatively unique range of medical cannabis on the German market. In addition to our independence we were also one of the first companies that received the license to import cannabis to Europe.

As the laws in Germany only changed in March 2017, making medical cannabis legal, we were one of the very first to deal with the authorities and have since obtained 7 different licenses, allowing us to import from any GMP production in the world.

Thus we are one of the pioneers in the European cannabis industry and have become specialists in GMP processing and authority auditing. With our strong team, we are committed to act responsibly and ethically at all times. We fulfill our social responsibility and tasks with passion and dedication. Our clear focus lies on ensuring the adequate supply of medical care for patients, providing information within a professional framework and satisfying our customers.

Etvas (a conjunction between "et" (lat: and) and "VAS" (en: value-added services) is a company based in Hamburg, which helps businesses bring added value to their customers.

Value-add services complement other products and services to make them more attractive, i.e. Cyber-Monitoring for Cyber-Insurances, Buyback Guarantees for electronic devices or airport lounge access as part of a premium credit card. In our platform, we connect all providers of value-add services with businesses that want to provide more value to their customers for better loyalty and higher income.

Configuring value-added services should be that easy. Etvas brings all the relevant providers into ONE marketplace so that our business partners only have to find their ideal service and offer it to their customers with ease. Save time and effort sourcing, contracting & integrating service providers, cutting back costs and decreasing service integration time from 1.5 years to 1 month.



FOR VAS PROVIDERS: Integrate once and let clients reach you.
Etvas gives access to all of our business partners with one platform integration. As a service partner, companies are granted full access to a marketplace with endless ways of improving revenue via an all-inclusive sales channel with minimal effort.

name: Brain-cloud
about:
Great ideas that you never had time to implement? Projects or campaigns where you can only achieve something together? brAIn-cloud is an AI-based B2B tool for idea management. Based on artificially intelligent textual analysis we bring people with similar ideas together. Projects and ideas, for which there was not enough time or which could not be realized alone, should be developed and realized in a suitable team. We network employees in order to use synergies optimally.

Every idea - whether for research or process optimization - affects several topics in different proportions. These "topics" are word clusters with similar meanings, which are captured in a mathematical framework by machine learning. brAIn-cloud works like an AI dating agency for ideas. Every single idea, no matter from which source and by whom, has the chance to get attention and finally generate added value.

about:
LIVA power management systems GmbH, Frankfurt, is a specialist for artificial intelligence (AI) based power management solutions. The P7 software ecosystem simulates and operates various energy storage assets like lithium-ion and Vanadium Redox Flow batteries as well as Gas-To-Power facilities with artificial intelligence routines and self-learning algorithms. Besides maximizing the efficiency, safety and lifetime of the batteries, the software enables the economic integration of sector coupling strategies with renewable energies and green hydrogen. LIVA is part of the AMG Group.

About AMG N.V.
AMG is a global critical materials company at the forefront of CO2 reduction trends. AMG produces highly engineered specialty metals and mineral products and provides related vacuum furnace systems and services to the transportation, infrastructure, energy, and specialty metals & chemicals end markets.

AMG Clean Energy Materials combines our recycling and mining operations producing materials for infrastructure and energy storage solutions while reducing the CO2 footprint of both suppliers and customers. Clean Energy Materials spans the vanadium, lithium, and tantalum value chains. AMG Critical Materials Technologies combines our leading vacuum furnace technology line with high-purity materials serving global leaders in the aerospace sector. AMG Critical Minerals consists of our mineral processing operations in antimony, graphite, and silicon metal.

With approximately 3,000 employees, AMG operates globally with production facilities in Germany, the United Kingdom, France, the United States, China, Mexico, Brazil, India, Sri Lanka, and Mozambique, and has sales and customer service offices in Russia and Japan (www.amg–nv.com).

The world needs new nutrition solutions! We are aware of our responsibility and know what it means to rely on natural resources. That's why we don't just make meals, which are quickly prepared, but create awareness for a wholesome, plant-based nutrition.

about:

This new generation of microprocessors will enable Europe to set out its technological sovereignty on the strategic markets for high performance computing, artificial intelligence and connected mobility.

SiPearl is developing and will market its solutions through close collaboration with its 26 partners from the EPI - scientific community, supercomputing centres and leading names from the IT, electronics and automotive industries - which are its stakeholders and future clients. It is supported by the European Union.

SiPearl is also a member of the Mont-Blanc 2020 consortium to equip Europe with a dedicated modular and energy-efficient high performance computing microprocessor, and is a member of the PlayFrance.Digital collective for Europe to lead the field for digital technology.

Virtuelle und hybride Events in Form von Konferenzen, Messen und Vorlesungen haben sich etabliert und fügen den traditionellen Events eine neue Kategorie hinzu.

Gemeinsam mit Streavent entwickeln Sie eine passende Plattform nach ihrem Wunsch, egal ob Konferenz, Vortrag, Podiumsdiskussion, Webinar, Workshop oder Messe! about:
Wir von der tensorscope GmbH sind ein interdisziplinäres Team von neugierigen Köpfen mit Sitz in Göttingen. 
Wir entwickeln innovative machine-learning basierte Analysetechnologien für die Bereiche Biologie und Medizin.
Unsere Vision ist es, neue Perspektiven in KI-basierter Bildanalyse zu schaffen und Ihnen das Leben leichter zu machen. Und da Sie am besten wissen, wie Ihre Arbeit funktioniert, passt sich unser Service ganz einfach an Ihren gewohnten Ablauf im Labor an.

So bestimmt unsere Software zur vollautomatischen Analyse von Spermiogrammen anhand intelligenter Algorithmen die mikroskopischer Kennzahlen des männlichen Ejakulats. Die Parameter : Konzentration, Motilität und bald auch Morphologie werden präzise  und schnell nach WHO-Standard berechnet.

name: Laserhub
about:
Laserhub ist ein B2B-Start-up aus Stuttgart, das eine herstellerübergreifende Beschaffungsplattform für industrielle Metallteile entwickelt hat. Die Gründer Adrian Raidt, Christoph Rößner und Jonas Schweizer haben dabei vor allem ein Ziel vor Augen: Sie wollen die Digitalisierung der Industrie vorantreiben. 

Deshalb vereint Laserhub, alle Schritte von der automatischen Angebotserstellung bis hin zur Auftragserteilung, Umsetzung, Logistik und Abrechnung von Metallteilen in einem schlanken, digitalen Prozess. Durch die Verquickung aus schnellen, verlässlichen Lieferzeiten, marktgerechten Preisen und guter Qualität sparen sich Anwender Zeit und Kosten. Über die Laserhub-Plattform decken sie Bedarfe aus den Bereichen Laserschneiden, Biegen, Rohrlaserschneiden und CNC-Drehen, um etwa Ihre Bleche nach Maß zu beschaffen. Der smarte Algorithmus verknüpft für jeden Auftrag die individuellen Spezifikationen der Kunden mit den Ressourcen der Produzenten aus dem Laserhub-Netzwerk. 

Neben den Bearbeitungsverfahren für Biegeteile, Drehteile, Rohrlaserteile oder Kantteile, bietet Laserhub auch weitere Möglichkeiten wie beispielsweise Entgraten, Verzinken und viele mehr an. Einkäufer:innen konfigurieren und kalkulieren auf unserer Beschaffungsplattform ihre Metallteile, Biegeteile, Drehteile, Kantteile und Laserteile genau nach Ihrem Bedarf ab Losgröße eins.

Zu den Laserhub-Kunden gehören mehr als 5.000 Unternehmen mit einem Schwerpunkt in der Industrie und dem metallverarbeitenden Gewerbe. Darunter sind vor allem mittelständische Maschinenbauunternehmen, Betriebe aus dem Bereich Metallbau und sogar etablierte DAX30-Konzerne. Laserhub beliefert Kunden aus Deutschland, Österreich und Frankreich.

Laserhub ist die verlässlichste Lösung zur Beschaffung von Metallteilen für Industrie und Handwerk. Der simple, digitale Prozess erhöht die Effizienz im industriellen Einkauf enorm.

name: MonitorFish

By enabling fishfarms with machine learning, the system is able to support fish farmers to run their operations smooth and stable through data driven decisions integrated in their daily work routine.

Our bespoke AI-powered solution is designed to tackle the individual challenges of each farm which allows fish farmers to manage their business as efficiently as possible, increasing profitability and reducing their environmental footprint.

The goal is to manage and simplify fish farmers day-to-day operations to make aquaculture more predictable, more sustainable and even more fun.

name: Compounder.eu
about:
Den passenden Studiengang auf der richtigen Hochschule schnell finden und sich ganz einfach und direkt dafür bewerben, ohne auf hunderten von Webseiten nach Informationen suchen zu müssen – das muss doch heutzutage möglich sein!

Diesen Gedanken hatten wir bereits im Jahr 2017, kurze Zeit nachdem wir als ehemalige Studienbewerber selbst Ewigkeiten gebraucht haben, bis wir uns für einen Studienplatz entschieden und uns anschließend an der Hochschule eingeschrieben haben. Es dauert einfach viel zu lange, bis man endlich herausgefunden hat, welche Dokumente wann, wo und auf welchem Weg rechtzeitig eingereicht werden müssen. Vor allem, wenn man sich nicht nur für einen Studiengang oder eine Hochschule, sondern für mehrere bewirbt. Nach Abschicken der Bewerbung fehlen dann teilweise noch einige Dokumente und müssen per Mail nachgereicht werden, was den gesamten Bewerbungs- und Einschreibeprozess noch langsamer macht. Nach einigen Gesprächen mit Freunden, die das gleiche Problem hatten, war eins klar: dieses Problem müssen wir lösen. So wurde Compounder® ins Leben gerufen.

Einige Zeit und Recherchearbeit später wurde deutlich, dass nicht nur auf Seite der Studieninteressenten, sondern auch auf Seite der Hochschulen etwas verändert werden muss, um den gesamten Prozess effizienter gestalten zu können. Gesagt, getan – In Zusammenarbeit mit Hochschulen haben wir eine Lösung erarbeitet, die es ermöglicht, jede einzelne in- und ausländische Bewerbung automatisch auf Vollständigkeit und Zulässigkeit für ein Studium in Deutschland zu prüfen.

So wollen wir mit Compounder® nicht nur jungen Studieninteressenten ermöglichen, sich auf moderne und einfache Art und Weise Studieninformationen zu beschaffen und sich auf direktem Wege für ihren Wunschstudienplatz zu bewerben, sondern Hochschulen auch Zeit und Arbeit im Bewerbermanagement abnehmen – und das alles auf nur einer Plattform.

name: Emporium Collection
about:
Emporium Collection provides a bespoke service that offers an extensive collection of some of the most exquisite and exclusive suites & experiences around the world. Our inventory of posh properties has been curated to cater to our 21st-century haut monde travellers that are only interested in the finer things in life.

Why Us

We pride ourselves in the being the Go-to Luxury Hotel Provider
with a reliable system and an exclusive membership. We handpick properties that conform to our highest standards to give our members an experience par excellence. Knowing out discerning members, there are certain aspects that hold immense importance, such as the architecture, location, spa facilities, unique concepts, corporate ethics, culinary offerings and the most imperative of all, the commitment of the team to achieve excellence..

Who we are

Whether it is hotels, experiences, shopping, restaurant bookings or flight bookings, our diverse network makes the impossible possible! name: Smartr365
about:
Technology platform Smartr365 unites financial advisers and state-of the-art technology to empower better financial decisions and planning for clients. 
 
Smartr365 gives clients access to all of their financial data – mortgages/insurance/pensions/investments – in one place. The data is Cloud based, with bank grade security.  Data can be updated in real-time, notifying all relevant parties simultaneously.
 
Clients can be paired-up with their existing financial adviser, and have access to the same financial data.  Using ‘smart’ data, clients can see the value of their home, mortgage balance and home equity at the touch of a button, along with the relevant mortgage products for their specific circumstances.  They will get the advice they need on their finances 24/7, either from the platform's robo-advice offering, or from their trusted face-to-face adviser.
 
The platform's HomeTrack/CallCredit/Mogo/E-Conveyancer integrations are powerful features, as is the auto-email and remortgage feature and the fact that Smartr365 will be offering robo-advice on an open-platform basis. Two of the big four banks are onboard, with formal announcements to follow shortly. 
 
Smartr365 has been built on Microsoft's Azure PaaS framework.  It is designed to integrate seamlessly with all aspects of the 365 solution, including auto-syncing of actions to Outlook, client documentation storage and retrieval via SharePoint. 
 
If clients or advisers want to proceed with new financial products/offerings, this is delivered at the touch of a button, with no downtime nor expensive, aborted transactions.
 
Smartr365 is the technology behind Capricorn Financial.  It has been instrumental in propelling the consultancy as one of the industry’s major players in the UK, with more than £1billion of lending in 2016 and £1.4bn forecast for 2017 and will shortly be rolled out to other major brokerages/networks in the UK.
