To do so, we develop a system which enables users to ride their bikes and get benefits for each KM. The collected RydeUp-coins can be used to purchase products from our partner-stores. As we connect users and enterprises who understand the importance of a sustainable lifestyle, we want to create a platform which draws more attention to ecological products and supports green mobility.

name: Sympatient
about:
Sympatient revolutionizes the traditional health care market by developing cutting edge virtual reality applications. 
We combine scientific rigor with agile and fast-paced product development to induce innovations into the global health care market.

name: TableSnappr
about: TableSnappr is a unique food tech startup that allows customers to order food & drinks from multiple traders at street food markets. No boring apps to download, no data to share and NO MORE QUEUES. Simply snap & order. The platform has been road-tested in Germany and the UK over two years with a proven uplift in basket size, re-ordering & repeat visit. Just snap & order...

name: Terranigma Solutions
about:
As a spin-off from the Institute for Computational Geoscience and Reservoir Engineering at the renominated RWTH Aachen University, we strive to share our technological expertise and bring our scientific insights in the area of geological modeling to real-world applications. 

Our story began with the creation of GemPy, which has now become the most popular open-source software for 3D geological modeling. Today, our excellent team of geoscientists, software developers, and marketers works in close collaboration with academic and industrial partners to transform our specialized knowledge into tangible benefits and economic value. 

Our main areas of expertise are:
 - 3D implicit geological modeling
 - Immersive visualization
 - Real-time model updating and interaction
 - Uncertainty analysis
 - Probabilistic machine learning

If you want to know more about us and our technologies in development, please contact us at info@terranigma-solutions.com.

name: Vivenu
about:
We started with a bold vision - To finally transform the global ticketing industry for good. Hundreds of thousands of sellers around the globe rely on ticketing solutions that haven’t kept up with their needs and expectations. Platforms from the 90s that still feel like we are in the 90s made the jobs of ticket managers worldwide constant miseries. 

So welcome to ticketing for the digital first era. Our API-first ticketing solution breaks limitations and unlocks huge potentials. Manage, market & analyze ticket sales effortlessly with our powerful unified platform.

Do you want to be part of Germany's next big B2B SaaS company? We’re looking for driven people to help us in enabling effortless ticketing without limitations. We are not just another company and we are not looking for people who seek just another job. Ready for personal growth? Join us.

name: Volytica diagnostics
about: We address battery and e-vehicle manufacturers' design, monitoring and warranty management challenges by leveraging data collected from devices in the field. Our mission is to bring transparency to the degradation of the single most expensive e-vehicle component: the battery.  (Banner Photo by RawFilm on Unsplash)

Kundenmagazine, Whitepaper, Broschüren und andere Publikationen sehen dank der vorkonfigurierten, responsiven Design-Templates immer hochwertig aus. Zusätzlich profitieren Unternehmen von digitalen Möglichkeiten wie Suchmaschinenoptimierung, Data Analytics oder Call-to-Action-Buttons.

name: Abaut
about:
Construction and mining sites directly to decision maker`s screen – 24/7
abaut allows construction and mining companies to manage sites in real time from remote, track progress and processes, reduce risks and increase productivity through better decision making.

name: Zeitpulver
about:
++Rethinking functional food++
Wir entwickeln vollwertige und nachhaltige Mahlzeiten aus geretteten Lebensmitteln, die alle essenziellen Nährstoffe enthalten und schnell und einfach zubereitet werden können.

Was macht Zeitpulver besonders, wo liegen unsere Stärken und Vorteile?
1) Zeitpulver basiert auf echte, pflanzliche Lebensmittel wie Obst, Gemüse, Nüsse, Hülsenfrüchte und Vollkorngetreide
2) es enthält alle essenziellen Nährstoffe (inklusive der kritischen Nährstoffe wie Vitamin B12, D und Selen) und erfüllt die Zufuhrempfehlungen an Obst, Gemüse und Getreide von unterschiedlichen Ernährungsinstituten
3) es ist vegan, glutenfrei, ohne Zuckerzusatz und ohne Konservierungsstoffe
4) Zeitpulver ist nachhaltig: wir achten auf Regionalität, kurze Wege entlang unserer Wertschöpfungskette und es ist in plastikfreien, zu 100% heimkompostierbaren Verpackungen erhältlich
5) Zeitpulver ist lange haltbar, kompakt dank Pulverform und flexibel in der Zubereitung.

name: Magnes AG
about: Magnes is a spinoff from the Institute of Robotics and Intelligent Systems of ETH Zurich. Magnes has developed a disruptive real-life-monitoring solution to analyze walk patterns of patients with neurological disorders. It is the only solution giving direct haptic feedback to patients. Using smart sensors embedded in sneaker-like shoes we collect data while the patient is walking or doing daily activities. Our AI processes the data to generates automatic reports and provide the patient with direct feedback on their gait or warn/prevent situations like falling. Our technology can change the way clinical trials are performed today and improve efficacy by enabling data driven therapy through tailored medication dosage.

name: Agrando
about:
Agrando is a rapidly growing AgTech company from Munich and the reliable partner of the successful agriculture. The combination of Germany's only independent online trading platform, exclusive market analyzes and professional agricultural advice makes farmers, traders and manufacturers sustainably successful.  

Our courageous team leads our agriculture into the future: Agrando gathers brave specialists and experienced practitioners from all areas of modern agricultural management and digitization. Farmers work hand in hand with programmers, analysts, marketing and sales professionals - all of them are passionate about securing the traditional profession of our farmers and making them internationally competitive.

name: LAQA GmbH
about:
Wer einen stressigen Tag hat, vergisst schnell mal ausreichend zu trinken. Doch bereits ein geringfügiger Flüssigkeitsmangel kann Auswirkungen auf unseren Körper haben. Wasser ist Bestandteil und Voraussetzung allen Lebens. 
So kann unser Blut nur fließen, weil es zu über 90 Prozent aus Wasser besteht. Wasser ist wesentlicher Bestandteil unserer Zellen, ohne Flüssigkeit würden unsere Nieren nicht richtig arbeiten, unsere Muskeln nicht funktionieren und unser Gehirn könnte nicht die erforderliche Leistung erbringen. Auch ist Wasser ein wesentlicher Bestandteil sämtlicher Stoffwechselprozesse im Körper.
Mit zunehmendem Alter reduziert sich der Körperwasseranteil, das natürliche Durstempfinden schwindet. Zusätzlich wird das Handeln älterer Personen zunehmend von Vergesslichkeit und Nachlässigkeit geprägt. Die Gefahr einer gesundheits- oder gar lebensbedrohenden Dehydration steigt exponentiell an.
In deutschen Krankenhäusern wurden im Jahr 2017 über 125.000 Fälle von Volumenmangel als Hauptdiagnose festgestellt, 5.371 dieser Patienten verstarben noch im Krankenhaus. In weiteren 925.000 Fällen wurde Volumenmangel als Nebendiagnose festgestellt. Über 90 Prozent der betroffenen Personen waren 65 Jahre oder älter.
Mit unseren Produkten und Dienstleistungen wollen wir uns diesen Themen stellen. Wenn Sie mehr erfahren wollen besuchen Sie einfach unsere Webseite oder nehmen Sie Kontakt mit uns auf. Wir freuen uns auf Sie!

LAQA - drinking made smart

name: Grafter
about:
Grafter is an easy-to-use network, where employers and workers can meet and engage for flexible, short-term and temporary work. 

With over 50,000 registered workers on Grafter, employers can quickly find the local temporary staff and workers they need. Complete a postcode search, browse available workers and discuss the job using ‘chat’ to hire the right person.

If you are looking for flexible work, it just takes a few minutes to sign-up. Add your skills, qualifications, experience and references. Then quickly apply for work with one click. Grafter will also send you alerts, when work comes up in your area.

name: Mara Seaweed
about:
Mara means the ‘the sea’ in Gaelic; it's at the heart of what we do.

We aim to “Nourish Body and Soul” by
•Harnessing goodness from the sea 
•Creating nutritious and delicious seaweed products
•Supporting coastal communities

Mara Seaweed is leading expertise in the seaweed industry, from sourcing and processing, to nutrition and taste. All of Mara's award winning products 
• Contribute to essential everyday nutrition; rich in iodine, high in fibre, full of essential minerals 
• Provide a healthy salt alternative
• Offer natural flavour enhancement through umami

Mara was founded in 2011 and is majority owned by Fiona Houston. 

Mara’s wild seaweeds are sustainably hand-harvested under license from the Crown Estate in Fife, on the East Coast of Scotland. Mara is also committed to working with other local harvesters around the coastlines of Scotland and Ireland.

Mara established the UK’s first SALSA-accredited sea-to-shelf production facility for retail seaweed products in Edinburgh. Their locally sourced seaweeds sell as a range of flakes and powders throughout the UK, including nationwide in Ocado, Tesco and across Europe and America. 

Awards
• Winner, Healthy Choice for Furikake, Scotland Food and Drink Excellence Awards, 2017
• Winner, Great Taste Award, 2016 (including 3* & Golden Fork nomination); 2015, 14, 13, 12, 11
• Winner, Best Accompaniment for Shony flakes, Scotland Food & Drink Excellence Award, 2016
• Winner, Best Artisan Product for Dulse flakes, World Food & Beverage Innovation Awards, 2016
• Finalist, Best Producer, BBC Food and Farming Awards, 2015
• Winner, The Crown Estate Scottish Marine Aquaculture Award for Innovation, 2015

name: Solublue
about:
SoluBlue is a material technology company operating in the food packaging space. 

SoluBlue provides B2B solutions for the future of food and packaging industries: we are developing hyper-biodegradable packaging that extends the shelf-life of food, using renewable resources. Our technologies are highly scalable, sustainable and commercialisable, with the potential to eradicate plastic and food waste from our food system. 

SoluBlue won the global NextGen Cup Challenge in 2019. This year we are Nominated for the Postcode Green Lotteries Challenge – one of the largest competitions in the field of sustainable entrepreneurship. We have also been selected for the European Institute for Technology (EIT) Food Seedbed and the Innovation prize. SoluBlue is also supported by the University of Cambridge Institute for Sustainability Leadership (CISL).

about: At Meinkart, we aim to ease grocery shopping from your local retailer with a fast delivery. Our platform allow users to save time & make money.

name: Smart Mile
about: Smartmile is an international venture building a shared and sustainable online delivery platform into Cities in Europe and beyond.   Smartmile make urban online delivery smarter: more efficient, more convenient and more sustainable.  Smartmile - enables consumers to receive all their online purchases from any webstore worldwide at the location and time they prefer - reduces traffic and carbon emission in the city - enables couriers to deliver more efficiently in cities - provides retailers and shopping centers with a convenient click & collect solution - includes and connects to the latest technologies, like PackRobot self-service parcel stations  Smartmile is currently looking for investors who recognize the need for better and more sustainable urban online delivery and disruption of the traditional logistics model.

name: WEMOVO
about:
At wemovo, we are building the backbone for frictionless door-to-door mobility.
 
We are revolutionizing the industry by helping mobility operators to transform into Mobility-as-a-Service ecosystem with complementary mobility products. A true inter-/multimodal experience is delivered through our journey planner, real-time booking engine, and a wide range of operators in our inventory – buses, trains, ferries and in near future public transport and (micro) mobility-on-demand.
 
By radically automating processes and designing a superior user experience we enable seamless integration between clients as efficient and easy as never before in the multi-trillion mobility industry.
 
Our rapid growth since our market entry in summer 2015 has enabled us to operate cash-flow positive. In addition, our dedicated team of professionals, based in our Berlin and sunny Catania offices, has helped the company overcome innumerable challenges.

Our numerous clients trust in the solutions of wemovo by appreciating the valuable inventory of 200+ mobility suppliers and a wide variety of distribution channels in more than 30 countries.

name: Hybrid Lidar Systems
about:
Wir haben ein neues Verfahren erfunden um mit Licht eine Distanz zu messen. Mit diesem patentierten Hybrid Verfahren entwickelt wir unsere solid state Flash Lidarsensoren LiSSA 3D Lidar für die Industrie und die Automobilindustrie. 

We have invented a new method to measure distance with light. With this patented hybrid method we develop our solid state flash lidar sensors LiSSA 3D Lidar for the industry and the automotive industry.

name: cloudplan GmbH
about: Secure and intelligent private cloud solution backed by leading German seed investors. The cloudplan solution adds well known cloud storage and collaboration features to the company network as well as Workflows ans eSigning in a secure envoirment. Private Cloud Storage, Workflows, eSigning, Collaboration and connected features cover the whole lifecycle of your files in hybrid, cloud or on-premise environments. Lean deployment specifications and simplified IT tasks meet SME requirements.

name: Elma Care
about:

Gracias a nuestra tecnología y equipo médico y personal sanitario propio, ofrecemos al usuario diversas funcionalidades digitales; atención primaria, derivación médica, recetas online, planes de salud personalizados y herramientas de prevención, entre otros. Por supuesto, sin olvidar una amplia cobertura médica con mas de 37.000 especialistas y centros hospitalarios. 

Elma, un reset a los seguros de salud.

name: AVA
about: Our mission is to enable individuals, organisations and societies to make the best-informed security decisions. We aggregate, standardise and contextualise internal and external data to provide decision makers with actionable insights. Covering all relevant risk-related information including crime, acts of terrorism, natural and industrial disasters, epidemics and many more, our solutions allow everyone to manage their past, present and future security. AVA is the operating system for a safer world, creating the foundation for anyone to build world-changing solutions in risk management.

name: Nyris
about: nyris is a visual search platform that gives people a more natural way to find what they are looking for. With nyris, companies of all industries realize financial value while improving how people find, discover and get things done. Up and running in minutes, only nyris’ technology is designed and engineered to handle any search challenge.

name: Active Giving
about: Active Giving is a global movement supporting an active lifestyle that contributes to make the world a better place. Our Active Giving mobile sport app enables individuals to contribute to social and environmental projects with their sport activities.

name: Cabin Experience
about:
We select extraordinary locations across Europe to host small cabins. Our cabins are designed to be part of the landscape. They are built with local materials and are free of chemicals.

In order to make the most of your experience, we offer you the possibility to become a co-owner. As a co-owner, you choose when you want to come and you get an attractive return by renting the cabin to other travellers. Local hosts provide you there with everything you need, and receive for their effort a part of the revenue.

With our platform we will interact with co-owners and allow travellers to customize their cabin experience.

By joining the community, you also give something back to nature. For each new co-owner we will plant a tree in the forest. This way we sow a seed towards restoring local ecosystems.

name: circuly GmbH
about: We build software, that enables companies to rent out their products instead of just selling them. In this way, we create further sales potential for our customers and at the same time bring sustainability to e-commerce.   With our subscription management software for physical products, we support young companies in optimizing and scaling existing rental models and help established companies to build new, circular business models as a second mainstay.    Our software is a white label solution that creates a customer-centric rental experience along the entire value chain of the rental model. Starting with the conclusion of a rental agreement, the set-up of recurring payments, the self-service by the end consumer up to the administration and tracking of all products as well as the integration of logistics service providers and financing partners in the backend.   We make circular business models easy and your existing online shop smart for rentals.

name: Digital Workforce Nordic Oy
about:
Digital Workforce is the leading and fastest growing company specializing purely in Intelligent Automation services on an industrial scale. We automate the routines of computer based knowledge work and free up human employees' time for more productive and valuable tasks. The deployment of digital workers requires no changes to the existing information systems. Digital Workforce was founded in the summer of 2015 and it currently employs over 240 IA specialists in the US, UK, Finland, Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Poland.

Digital Workforce offers a range of services and tools to support organizations in their robotics journey. Our services include Robot as a Service from the private cloud or Azure environment and Robotics Consulting. Our services make it possible to achieve tangible results from Intelligent Automation rapidly.

A Digital Worker automates existing rule- and role-based manual user tasks and processes. The operation cost is 1/10 of traditional IT projects, both in terms of time and money. Digital Workforce is your opportunity to be 10 times more efficient.

name: HeyCharge

We offer a no-hassle, fast retrofit of low-cost electric vehicle chargers to your residential multi-unit property (e.g. a parking garage below an apartment building). We offer ZERO UPFRONT COST for installation. Contact us to learn more.

#forpeoplewholovetomakelove #nevernot #dowwhatyouwant

name: Nota, inc.
about:
Founded in 2015, Nota is a compressed AI solutions and software optimization platform business with a focus on the B2B and B2G markets. Our mission is to accelerate and maximize the everyday use of AI in the global market. Our main platform solution, NetsPresso, resolves Cloud and server-based AI solutions related issues, such as limited network, excessive cost, and privacy breach. NetsPresso is an automatic model compression platform which downsizes computer vision models to a size small enough to be deployed independently on smaller edge and low specification devices. Optimization of target models being key, the platform combines a variety of compression methods which enables it to downsize AI models without causing performance degradation. 

Nota’s AI technology empowers intelligent transportation systems, facial recognition, and security and surveillance. The company’s solutions include Driver Monitoring System, Driver Authentication, and Smart Access Control System. Nota‘s current projects cover a wide range of industries including construction, mobility, security, smart home, and healthcare. Nota’s partnership with top-tier global market leaders including Nvidia, Intel, and ARM has helped accelerate its entry into the global market

name: Phoenix Reality
about:
We are Phoenix Reality, a Hamburg based Mixed Reality (MR) Startup. We believe that MR will become “The Next Big Thing” for revolutionary digital marketing- and entertainment concepts.

It is our mission to close the gap between MR hardware suppliers and location-based offers for the consumer market, which is why we are developing a modular MR display area - The SymArea, that can be used for various use cases:
• Location Based Entertainment 
• Showrooms & Point of Sale
• Expo presentations

We are also working on “Project Paranoid”, Europe’s first scalable Location-based Mixed-Reality Multiplayer Live-Adventure, developed with Unity for Magic Leap. 
Ready to play Summer 2021.

name: Riitail
about: The in-store retail landscape is changing drastically: Existing companies meet the fierce competition of attracting customers by striving for continuous experiences throughout all channels - these include representing showrooms, exciting event concepts and new, engaging ways of experience driven retail. Riitail enables retailers for the first time, to leverage the same marketing tools and methods that could previously only be used in E-Commerce and other online channels. Marketing analytics and A/B-Testing for in-store retail. We supply AI-supported camera devices and cloud-services to identify customer interactions in retail. We link these events with marketing measures and campaigns in real-time. Steering marketing optimization based on defined targets and actual impact. Riitail technology is based on edge-computing and hardware-anonymization - Riitail delivers these insights while not only respecting data-privacy laws, but the highly valuable privacy of every in-store customer. We are Riitail! Impressum/ Imprint: https://www.riitail.com/imprint/

name: SageFund
about: Sagefund is a sustainable wealth management platform. Investing is of critical importance for everyone to grow and protect their wealth throughout their lives. Because of this, Sagefund has set out to ensure that investing is safe, easy and accessible. They work with industry experts to ensure that all investments are stable in performance and sustainable, complying with UN global compact goals. They are set to launch later this year, sign up on their website to get on the waiting list.

name: Cleanbrace
about:
Cleanbrace entstand durch die Verknüpfung von zwei alltäglichen Bedürfnissen, die vermutlich jeder kennt:  Der Wunsch, sich egal wann und wo die Hände zu desinfizieren und dies auf eine möglichst einfache Art und Weise. 

Das Cleanbrace Armband zur mobilen Handdesinfektion ist Ihr täglicher Begleiter in Sachen Handhygiene. Ob beim Pendeln, auf Geschäftsreisen oder bei der Arbeit mit Kollegen und Kunden - Cleanbrace versorgt Ihre Mitarbeiter bequem und verlässlich mit Desinfektionsmittel zur lokalen Handflächendesinfektion.

In Berufen mit Kunden-, Personen- oder Bargeldkontakt ist die Infektionsgefahr durch Krankheitserreger besonders hoch. Um diese Berufsgruppen zu schützen bieten wir Unternehmen eine kostenlose Beratung hinsichtlich Ihrer Hygiene-Infrastruktur. Durch die Integration von Hygienestandards in den Arbeitsalltag ermöglichen Sie Ihren Mitarbeitern und Kunden einen einfachen Schutz vor Schmierinfektionen.

Wie funktioniert Cleanbrace?

Das Band funktioniert nach dem selben Prinzip wie ein Desinfektionsmittelspender. Durch das Betätigen des Tanks mit dem Daumen wird eine perfekt dosierte Menge an Desinfektionsmittel/-gel auf die Handfläche gesprüht. Das Desinfektionsmittel/-gel wird danach einfach auf den Handflächen verteilt.

Das Band kann für 5-6 Anwendungen genutzt werden und das Beste: Es ist mit unserem mitgelieferten Refiller innerhalb von ein paar Sekunden ganz einfach wieder aufgefüllt werden. So bleiben nicht nur die Hände sauber, sondern auch unsere Umwelt!

name: VCoach GmbH
about: We empower your employees to communicate better - with immediate impact, “on the job” & at scale!  Lack of effective communication is a major constraint for organizational performance. Current training solutions fail to deliver substantial impact. vCOACH solves this problem sustainably, conveniently & at scale.  Our previous participants improved their skill level on average by >20% in less than 3 weeks (~5 Min per day, anywhere/anytime).  What we do? Our mission is to develop scalable, yet impact-focused soft skill coaching solutions. We aim to enable as many people as possible to unleash their full potential. Both, professionally as well as in their private lives. To do so, we combine latest scientific research with cutting-edge machine learning technology. Our solutions comprise objective soft skill assessment, individual feedback and success tracking. But only constant practice ensures sustainable improvements. That’s why our trainings are built “mobile first” & are based on microlearning sessions. You can train anytime & anywhere – whenever it fits your needs and schedule.  Who we are? We are a diverse team of highly ambitious young professionals with backgrounds in consulting, operations, IT/tech and psychology. We are constantly looking for driven, open-minded and down-to-earth people that share our vision. Our offices are located in the heart of Munich, Germany.

name: Writeaguide
about:
Seit Jahren hören wir Tag für Tag von Angestellten, Experten und Führungskräften aus den verschiedensten Branchen, wie kompliziert Wissensmanagement in kleinen und großen Unternehmen praktiziert wird. Umständlich über E-Mails, Word-Dokumente und in den Tiefen der Server-Verzeichnisse wird nach dem entsprechenden Wissen gesucht. Langsam und unübersichtlich.

Wir sind der Meinung, dass Wissensmanagement auch smart und unkompliziert sein kann. Deswegen haben wir writeaguide entwickelt. Eine Cloud-Anwendung in der alle Team-Rollen effizient und einfach Wissensmanagement betreiben können. Egal welche Größe das Unternehmen oder die Einrichtung hat. Neben dem intuitiven Erstellen und Vernetzen von Wissen in Guides, legen wir mit writeaguide auch einen großen Wert auf die datengesteuerte Wissensanalyse. Der Schlüssel dazu sind unsere komplexen Statistiken und Auswertungen. Sofort sind die Spezialisten zu einem Thema erkennbar, die Auswertungen zeigen, welche Teammitglieder schon die neue Schulung abgeschlossen haben oder wie der Wissenstransfer-Score für einen bestimmten Guide ist. So gestalten wir sämtliche Wissensprozesse schneller und übersichtlicher und geben den Verantwortlichen wieder mehr Zeit für die wesentlichen Dinge.

Folge uns
Twitter: https://twitter.com/writeaguide
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/writeaguide
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/writeaguide/

Through our proprietary technology, we will be making MRI accessible to every patient globally. Join us in the journey to becoming the imaging standard of care in a myriad of previously inaccessible medical domains.

name: Dynamic42
about:
Dynamic42 GmbH is company highly specialized in the controlled, standardized and scalable production and development of human Organ-on-Chip technology.

Our biochip-based microphysiological platform can be used to screen new pharmaceutical compounds, chemicals and nutritional supplements as well as it is possible to set up specific disease models to test new therapy options. Our well characterized organ models show typical cell type-specific morphology, marker expression, certain physiologic functions and are highly scalable in cell type complexity. Here, Dynamic42 is specialized in integrating components of the immune system like tissue-resident macrophages or circulating immune cells into organ-on-chip technology.
Dynamic42 Organ-on-Chip technology contributes to obtain scientific data closer related to human physiology and can be used in a variety of scientific and pharmaceutic research fields.

name: Headmade Materials
about:

As the inventor of the Cold Metal Fusion (Metal SLS) technology, we are the first to enable our customers to cost-effectively manufacture 3D printed metal parts in series of more than 100,000 parts. 

With our roots in material science, we distribute our self-developed, in-house produced standard feedstocks or adapt individual alloys according to customer requirements. 

In terms of application, we offer knowledgeable support from the first idea to the additive-compatible design to the process-reliable production of part series. Implementation at customer site is supported through our practical expertise and collaborations with industry experts.  

With our technology and smart materials, we actively contribute to the future of metal 3D printing by opening new possibilities and making it more accessible to ultimately increase its general acceptance in the industry.

name: N8n
about:
Free, open and self-hostable workflow automation tool.

n8n is the leading low-code automation tool, enabling you to connect anything to everything. With n8n, for the first time, people can move beyond simple integrations to build multi-step workflows that combine both 3rd party APIs and your own internal tools to create easy-to-use automations. Thanks to its fair-code distribution model, n8n will always have visible source code, be available to self-host, and allow you to add your own custom functions, logic, and apps. n8n is supported by a fast-growing and passionate community of thousands of people building a powerful and extendable workflow automation tool. 

n8n is privately held, with funding from Sequoia, Felicis Ventures, Firstminute Capital, Harpoon Ventures, and others. Individual investors include Eventbrite's Kevin Hartz and Supercell's IIkka Paananen. n8n was founded in 2019 and is headquartered in Berlin.

We eliminate the intimidating, unrealistic, and superficial online dating environment, encouraging users to be their perfectly imperfect selves.

All SFL users SHINE, posting an attractive picture and listing their positive traits, but we also explore their SHADE, an imperfect picture and imperfect traits. The SHINE/SHADE approach creates a fun, easy-going environment, where users are comfortable and relaxed. Ultimately, better connections are made, and long-lasting relationships are formed.

At SettleForLove, you may not be perfect, but you’re perfect for someone :)

name: Dynamaze
about:
DynAmaze – Quality Time for everyone!

Was ist DynAmaze? 
Auf unserer B2B2C Freizeitplattform vermitteln wir ungenutzte Restplätze von Freizeitanbietern zu dynamischen Preisen. Unsere dynamische Preissetzung basiert auf einem von uns entwickeltem Algorithmus, welcher unter Einrechnung von Nachfrage, Verfügbarkeit, Erfahrungswerte bestehender Anbieter und weiteren Faktoren den optimalen Preis für jeden Anbieter individuell identifiziert. 

Wofür steht DynAmaze? 
Das „Dyn“ in DynAmaze steht für das Dynamisieren der Preisstruktur und Anbieter, während das „Amaze“ für das Begeistern der Endkunden für aufregende Erlebnisse steht. 


Welche Vorteile bringt DynAmaze mit sich? 
Auf der B2C Seite bieten wir den klaren Vorteil, Nutzern spontan die Möglichkeit zu geben, zu reduzierten Preisen spannende und vielseitige Freizeitangebote wahrnehmen zu können & sich zu neuen Aktivitäten inspirieren zu lassen. 

Auf der Anbieterseite umfassen unsere Vorteile die Steigerung der Ticketverkäufe in Randzeiten, Auslastungsoptimierung, eine erhöhte Sichtbarkeit des Anbieters & das Targeting relevanter Zielgruppen, sowie Neukundengewinnung. 


Wer ist DynAmaze? 
DynAmaze – das sind wir, Pétur, Jasper und Timo, drei junge und dynamische Gründer aus Köln. 2019 haben wir unsere Idee, Freizeitanbieter dynamischer zu gestalten (Dyn) und jedem die Chance zu geben sich für großartige Freizeitaktivitäten zu begeistern (Amaze), in die Tat umgesetzt.

name: Oh Honey

Denn von jeder Flasche fließen 10 Cent in Schutzprojekte für Wild- und Honigbienen. In unserem Bio-Eistee verbinden wir Geschmack und Nachhaltigkeit und verwenden deshalb 100% natürliche Zutaten und regionalen Bio-Honig. Gemeinsam tragen wir zum nationalen Bienenschutz bei und begeistern mit unserem Produkt und unserem motivierten Team bereits zahlreiche Kunden im Raum Köln und Kiel.

name: Yaliyomo GmbH
about:
Founded in Cologne, Germany by a duo of International entrepreneurs with over 50+ years of experience in global content and data management, Yaliyomo and our industry-leading Content Management Platform (CMP) Y™ answers the growing demand from consumers in a changing world, for full transparency and better traceability. Consumers are keen to know everything about the product they are purchasing and brand owners/retailers are interested to keep their products identity and integrity.

Yaliyomo’s platform helps brands to enable consumers to identify their products, trace it from the origin and validates the all attributes for building trust. Retailers working with the content that they securely receive and syndicate via Yaliyomo’s platform can keep all stakeholders accountable and transparent on the content by securely and storing it in the cloud and by leveraging the state of the art blockchain technology – an industry first for a CMP.

By storing information in a way where content is 100% secure, untenable and fully traceable. Y™ helps brand owners and retailers market and sell their products and drives business growth by not only collecting, enriching and storing product content in a highly intuitive and centralised way, but also by demonstrating traceability and authenticity of a product to customers.

Whether a consumer is purchasing a luxury handbag, ethically sourced coffee or life-saving medicine, Yaliyomo and Y™ gives them confidence and authentic content that what they are buying is the real thing, every time.

name: Brickblock
about:
Brickblock is the creator of ScalingFunds.com. The SaaS solution enables fund managers and GPs to raise capital from LPs more efficiently and scale from local to global distribution. Moreover, it allows a more efficient fund administration and helps to reduce costs by up to 70%.

Brickblock reduces the time for clearing and settlement of trades on a secondary market from weeks to minutes. A fast and global secondary market for fund shares raises the attractiveness of all alternative investment funds.

While the initial marketing focuses on Real Estate funds, the technology is agnostic to the investment class and can process Infrastructure, Private Equity, Private Debt and Hedge Funds.

Brickblock is trusted partner of Sanne Group and JTC Group totalling over €350bn assets under service and was one of the first to get a Security Information Sheet approved by BaFin, the financial regulatory authority for Germany.

name: VYTAL
about: In Germany the consumption of take-away, convenience and delivery food & drinks is responsible for about 281 kilotons of single-use packaging waste for immediate consumption and is growing at double digit rates. Most of the time, To-Go food containers, snack boxes or coffee cups have a very short life-span of only 30 minutes after which they are tossed into trash (or litter parks, beaches & the ocean). This is not only a giant waste of economic resources as each single use costs between 15 and up to 0,60€ for a stable bowl/box with a lid. It is a horrendous waste of environmental resources (wood, water, crude oil, metals & energy) that are used to produce this packaging. Therefore, a single use packaging not weighing more than 30 grams can easily come with an ecological backpack of more than 8 kilograms when taking into account all the resources used in production (material intensities taken from Wuppertal Institute for Climate, Environment and Energy). Looking at GHG emissions, the picture is similarly bleak: Using CO2 emission factors and the detailed material mix of the single-use packaging waste analyzed by NABU (German Nature and Biodiversity Conservation Union), the 281 thousand tons waste from To-Go consumption generated around 556 thousand tons of CO2 or the equivalent of 195k passenger cars per year (assuming an average distance travelled of 15,000km). With the expected rise of take-away, convenience and delivery food, the related emissions are expected to increase at double digit rates as waste volume is expected to increase and as we saw a shift to plastics relative to cardboard or other materials. While there is a growing awareness of the problem, especially in Germany, there is no scalable solution yet and the commonly used alternative of nature-based & ‘biodegradable’ materials like bagasse or PLA also require many resources for production & transport, and have to be incinerated or go to landfill after use as there is currently no way to compost them.

Der aktuelle Out-of-Home Markt ist sehr konzentriert und wenig digitalisiert. Zum einen sind Flexibilität und die Möglichkeit den Kunden direkt anzusprechen nur selten gegeben und zum anderen bedarf es oft großer Werbebudgets, um überhaupt OOH Werbung schalten zu können.    

Das wollen wir ändern! Mittels unserer digitalen Outdoor Displays werden filialspezifische Angebote und Werbung nationaler, regionaler sowie lokaler Marken an den*die Verbraucher*in übermittelt — statisch, animiert oder als Bewegtbild. Gemeinsam mit unseren Standortpartner*innen schaffen wir flexible digitale Kommunikationslösungen, um unseren Zielgruppen relevante und aktuelle Informationen zu bieten. 

Das treibt uns an 
Wir haben uns zu folgenden Grundsätzen verschrieben:  

- Unsere Kund*innen und Partner*innen stehen im Mittelpunkt 
- Wir wollen den OOH-Markt durch Digitalisierung revolutionieren 
- Wir arbeiten mit modernster Technologie und nehmen uns vor, neue Maßstäbe zu setzen 
- Wir hinterfragen uns immer wieder selbst und schätzen ehrliches Feedback, um jeden Tag noch besser zu werden 
- Wir erreichen unsere Ziele im Team und entscheiden verantwortungsbewusst 
- Wir leben die Demokratie und dulden keine Diskriminierung 
- Wir sind kreativ, mutig und gehen an Grenzen, um für unsere Kund*innen und Partner*innen die bestmögliche Lösung zu erzielen 

Wenn Du Teil unseres Teams werden willst, informiere Dich hier über aktuelle Stellenausschreibungen: https://digooh.com/karriere

Birgit Severing
Human Resources Manager

Die Idee für den Online-Shop entstand aus einem persönlichen Bedarf. Als passionierte JägerInnen lieben wir es, so oft wie möglich mit der Natur verbunden zu sein. Für ein erfolgreiches Jagderlebnis respektive gelungenes Outdoorabenteuer braucht es hochwertige Outdoor- und Jagdbekleidung, die je nach Einsatzzweck verschiedenen Witterungsbedingungen gewachsen sein muss. Doch viele werden das Problem dabei kennen: Um die gewünschte Ausrüstung zu erwerben, bedarf es oft stundenlanger Recherche im Internet oder den umständlichen Weg über den stationären Handel. Das wollten wir ändern! Bei Waidlife wird genau das angeboten, was vielen Jagdanhängern und Naturbegeisterten bis jetzt fehlte: Hier findest Du hochwertige Premium Outdoor-Bekleidung – sorgfältig ausgesucht und übersichtlich an einem Ort gebündelt.

Unsere Auswahl richtet sich an diejenigen, die es lieben, sich in der Natur aufzuhalten, und für die die beste Qualität gerade gut genug ist. Hochwertige Materialien sowie präzise Verarbeitung sind zwei Standards, auf die wir besonderen Wert legen. Egal ob für einen spontanen Waldspaziergang, eine ausgiebige Wanderung oder für die Jagd: Im Waidlife Online-Shop wird jede(r) Naturbegeisterte fündig. Unsere Premiummarken wie Filson, Norrona oder Blaser setzen bewusst auf bewährte Naturstoffe wie Bio-Baumwolle und Naturdaunen und kombinieren diese mit Kunstfasern und Hybridstoffen (z. Das von den damaligen Projektleitern Martin Šoltés und Sascha Koberstaedt entwickelte E-Fahrzeug soll nicht nur bei einer Idee bleiben. Die Industrialisierung des Forschungsprojekt ist nun das Herzensprojekt einer mittlerweile großen Mannschaft, die mit viel Engagement und Motivation die Verwirklichung der Mission vorantreibt. 
Gefertigt wird das aCar im Werk in Bayerbach bei Ergoldsbach.

Besonders geeignet ist das geräuschlose und emissionsfreie aCar für den natürlichen Lebensraum. Durch den Allradantrieb wird es zum multifunktionalen Geländegänger. Aber auch indoor ist das aCar durch die Größe (1,5 m breit und 1,99 m hoch) das ideale Nutzfahrzeug für Ihre logistischen Belange.  

Mit der zusätzlichen Ladefähigkeit von 1.000 kg Zuladung oder 1.000 kg Anhängelast (gebremst) ist das aCar Nutzfahrzeug im Alltag nicht mehr wegzudenken. 

Das aCar dient auch als Stromquelle. Die externe Steckdose ermöglicht den Betrieb jeglicher elektrischer Geräte (230 V) mit bis zu 3 kW Dauerleistung.

name: BitNinja
about:
BitNinja is the first integrated server defense network in the world. It works like a botnet, but for good purposes to protect the servers worldwide. As an integrated solution, it combines the most powerful defense mechanism and this way it can provide a broad level of protection. Each protected server can detect and defend against a wide range of server attacks. The servers share attack information with each other and this collective knowledge of the defense network makes BitNinja a very efficient and unique solution.
BitNinja can be installed on any Linux servers and it provides immediate protection against 99% of server attacks. Server owners have a dashboard to monitor all the servers they subscribed with. BitNinja users can protect their server like a pro sysadmin without the need of supervising the service.

name: FibreCoat
about:
All areas of our lives from our clothing to communication satellites are based on materials. The higher the volume in these markets, the higher the price pressure. 
As a result, the best technical solutions cannot be used in mass markets. FibreCoat is changing that. By producing composite fibres at high speeds, we achieve exceptional properties at low cost.

Aluminium-coated basalt filaments already available on the market achieve the properties of full metal fibres at one-tenth of the price. This cost advantage makes highly technical applications inexpensive and entirely new products feasible for the first time.

These aluminium coated fibres are also an affordable solution for shielding against EM-radiation (5G, Wifi,...). In a world where everything is becoming more and more connected EM-shielding will become a part of our daily lives.

We are convinced that continuous progress in material sciences will sustainably improve our environment, our society, and our lives. Therefore, in our pursuit of innovation, we realize sustainable, accessible, and affordable materials for our planet and beyond.

Auf diese Weise kommt es zu einem interaktiven Erlebnis, das mittels realitätsgetreuem Austausch Praxiserfahrungen bereitstellt. Ein Expertenstatus kommt nur über Übung zustande. Theoretisches Wissen ist eine tolle Grundlage für Erfolg in der Praxis, kann jedoch ohne entsprechendes Training nicht bestehen. Vor allem im Bereich Vertrieb gibt es Nuancen, die Sie alleine durch Theorie niemals erwerben können. Übung kann jedoch ein dröges Unterfangen sein. Peter Pitch bietet hier eine besondere Alternative. Die Gesprächssimulationen basieren auf spielerischen Elementen und ermöglichen eine unbeschwerte Annäherung an die reale Vertriebskommunikation. Peter Pitch hilft Ihnen und Ihrem Team dabei, Informationen, Kenntnisse und Fähigkeiten von der Theorie in die Praxis zu übersetzen.

Die Trainings tragen zum psychischen Wohlbefinden bei, fördern die Konzentration und schaffen Raum, um die sich ständig verändernden Rahmenbedingungen kreativ zu nutzen. name: 4Stop
about:
4Stop, based in Germany, is a global KYC, compliance and anti-fraud risk management company. With the founders of 4Stop collectively bringing 60+ years experience within the risk management industry they have developed their proprietary anti-fraud technology with real-time intelligence and data aggregation to be the best-in-class, all-in-one solution to future-proof businesses ongoing KYC, regulatory and fraud prevention requirements.

GLOBAL KYC DATA SOURCES 
Access to 400+ KYC global data sources with the ability to activate them in real-time and perform real-time cascading verification logic, all via a single API integration. 

INSTANT GLOBAL COMPLIANCE
We make you PSD2 compliant while keeping you current on compliance for regulatory authorities, such as; FCA, Bafin, Fincen and Fintrac. With the ability to activate and deploy any required KYC in real-time, you'll instantly be compliant and stay compliant, regardless of regulatory changes; bringing confidence to enter any market.

WORLD-CLASS FRAUD PREVENTION TOOLS
Our proprietary anti-fraud technology supports enterprise-level volumes and provides in-depth customer profiling, association logic and time-frame intelligence. Our rules engine wis built with 800+ pre-determined rule sets, an immediate free-form rules creator,  custom rule weighing, real-time rule deployment and more with automated customized system actions to a variety of parameters.

ADVANCED MONITORING
With real-time auto-refreshed intelligence and monitoring you can  Improve reaction times, review merchants, sub-merchants and customers transactions instantly and stop fraud in seconds. 


OUR TEAM IS DEDICATED TO WORKING WITH YOU IN DETERMINING THE BEST PLATFORM INTEGRATION AND PROCESSES TO PROVIDE YOUR BUSINESS OPTIMAL RESULT.

Contact us to schedule a demo and to work with our team to answer any questions you might have about functionality, integration or pricing based on your business region and needs.

name: qubeto
about: We are an innovative start-up from Münster with the vision to revolutionize the analysis of substances and other factors for their compatibility for humans and the environment. Our primary focus lays on the analysis of chemical substances, such as pesticides, for the chemical and agricultural industry. With our patented product platform we set new standards in sensitivity, data analysis and cost efficiency (of at least 15%). Our digital and automated platform is based on the analysis of behavioural changes in small model organisms, such as insect larvae, and uses state-of-the-art computer vision and machine learning algorithms in combination with AI-powered Big Data Analysis. The results lead to a significant acceleration of development cycles and early classification of compounds and, consequently, higher predictability for our customers. Our platform is modular, versatile and can be customized to meet the needs of our customers. We are a fast growing company and are constantly looking for new employees, collaboration partners and investors for our mission to make the world more sustainable and safer. Have we piqued your interest? Then get in touch with us at info@qubeto.de

We are experts in Internet of Things, Artificial Intelligence and Data.

Our intrinsic engine:
WE‘RE HERE TO IMPROVE GLOBAL ENERGY USAGE.
To achieve this, we’re bringing top performance IoT technology together with decades of experience in the energy sector. The climate change is without a doubt the biggest challenge of our time. Smart, connected technology plays an active role in climate protection.

SCHWARM MEANS MANY.
We are founders of the IoT open source based platform OPENVOLERY ™. It is organized in a foundation to protect the community and ensure its freedom.

Value Propositions:
OUR IOT PLATFORM CONNECTS ALL KIND OF SENSORS AND DEVICES, WITHOUT ANY LIMIT.
Our secure SCHWARM IoT Platform processes limitless quantities of live data from different sources and allows to connect all kind of sensors and devices. Safe. Fast. Affordable. Without any vendor lock-in. That’s the way we connect individual households, power sources, companies and energy systems together for better energy transition.

Using energy better:
OUR IOT ECO SYSTEM IS DESIGNED FOR ALL MARKET ROLES.
Millions of decentralized power plants must be integrated in a complex energy system. Renewably generated energy is volatile and therefore more difficult to predict. Client and prosumer behavior increases the complexity of production and product landscapes.This market environment is a major challenge for all market participants regardless of their respective market role (manufacturer, energy producer, TSO, DSO, trading, sales, consumer). Our ecosystem focuses on solving all these issues and on the integration of all process on the way to a new energy world.

WELCOME.

about: Wheels is a last-mile, shared electric mobility platform changing the current landscape in dockless mobility. With innovative products focused on sleek design and safety, Wheels provides a low-cost, fun, and comfortable way to get around cities through the connection of a smartphone. Wheels is headquartered in West Hollywood, California, with plans to expand quickly across the world. Wheels was founded by brothers Joshua Viner and Jonathan Viner. Prior to Wheels Joshua and Jonathan founded the popular dog walking app Wag with the mission of creating the safest and most trusted platform to get your dog walked. They scaled to over 100 cities, raising almost $400 million in funding for Wag. Wheels also added former Bird, Uber and Lyft executives to it’s management team. name: Sharpist
about:

All of Sharpist’s coaches are certified by highly reputable organizations, have extensive management and executive experience, and 10+ years of coaching practice. Upholding our inclusion and diversity principles, our global community of coaches possess a variety of personal and professional backgrounds, and offer coaching sessions in over 30 languages.

The secret of our success (98% positive user reviews) lies not only in the quality of our coaching but also in the matching process itself - based on the learner’s focus areas, a team of psychologists, with input from our algorithm, pairs your learners with the optimal coach for them.

Furthermore, Sharpist has the industry’s largest learning library and tailor-made content for personalized learning. We work with top content partners such as MIT Sloan, Business Insider, brand eins, and getAbstract to ensure the availability of content in multiple formats.

Global leading brands that trust Sharpist include LVHM, Porsche, Swisscom, STRABAG and Miro.

name: Aidhere
about:
Die aidhere GmbH ist ein Digital Health Unternehmen, das 2019 von Dr. Nora Mehl, Dr. Tobias Lorenz und Henrik Emmert in Hamburg gegründet wurde. Wir entwickeln und vertreiben digitale Gesundheitsanwendungen (z.B. Apps) für verschiedene Indikationen. Die entwickelten Therapien beruhen auf verhaltenspsychologischen und neurowissenschaftlichen Erkenntnissen sowie aktuellen Ansätzen aus der KI-Forschung. Die erste digitale Gesundheitsanwendung ist zanadio (Launch Oktober 2020), welche sich an Menschen mit Adipositas richtet.

zanadio ist angelehnt an die Leitlinien klassischer Adipositas-Behandlung und setzt diese App-basiert um. Der Fokus liegt dabei auf der Veränderung des gesundheitsrelevanten Verhaltens von Patientinnen und Patienten in den Bereichen Ernährung, Bewegung und Verhalten. Dadurch kann eine dauerhafte Gewichtsreduktion und vor allem -stabilisierung erreicht und das Wohlbefinden der Betroffenen gesteigert werden.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

aidhere GmbH is a Hamburg-based digital health company founded by Dr. Nora Mehl, Dr. Tobias Lorenz and Henrik Emmert in 2019. We develop digital health applications for a variety of indications. Our holistic therapies are based on behavioral psychological and neuroscientific research as well as the latest findings of artificial intelligence. In October 2020 we launched our first digital health application zanadio which has been developed specifically for people who have been diagnosed with obesity.

zanadio is based on traditional obesity treatment guidelines that have been implemented into the App. The focus lies on changing the health-related behavior of patients in the areas of nutrition, exercise and behavior. This enables a long-term weight reduction and weight stabilization which leads to an increased well-being of those affected.

name: Frequenz Energy-as-a-Service
about:
Frequenz' autonomous mind platform aims to revolutionize the way renewable energy production and procurement is managed and executed. As a central power exchanges member, we autonomize the renewable production value chain to increase our partners' revenue and profitability through designing and developing sophisticated AI, IoT and battery storage technologies. 

Simultaneously, we help our demand side partners reduce electricity costs by autonomizing the electricity procurement process. This includes the fully autonomous optimization and operation of all on-site electricity consuming and producing micro-grid components and devices upon real-time market pricing actions and AI predictions. 

These predictions use micro-level energy consumption data received through smart meters, IoT sensors, satellite data, weather forecasts, agent-based modeling and behavioral analysis to forecast future market developments in real-time. Through all those means we are aiming to support the transition to 100% renewable energy and a fully electrified global society.

Tangany is a custody provider for companies to tokenize assets into digital assets. The service will handle the storage of private keys in the cloud as well as blockchain access via a stable node infrastructure. 

Our clients are saving a lot of development time and costs as they can use a full and ready solution instead of developing an individual one. In addition, the blockchain usability for clients and users is increased enormously - no more hassle with private keys management.

- Made in EU
- Full GDPR compliant
- All data are stored within EU data centers
- State-of-the-art cloud HSM private key storage
- The world's easiest API to integrate blockchain
- Fair and transparent volume-based monthly fee model

name: Rfrnz
about:
rfrnz leistet einen Beitrag zur intelligenten Digitalisierung und unterstützt Unternehmen und Kanzleien dabei, ihre Verträge automatisiert zu prüfen. Die Contract Intelligence Platform von rfrnz automatisiert die Analyse von Verträgen mit Hilfe von Künstlicher Intelligenz. Dafür verwenden wir modernste Technologie: State-of-the-art Algorithmen aus dem Machine Learning und Natural Language Processing. 

Durch den Einsatz der Legal Tech Lösung von rfrnz sollen Juristen*innen von Routineaufgaben befreit werden und bessere Ergebnisse bei ihren Tätigkeiten erzielen. 

Die Contract Intelligence Platform erkennt relevante Informationen in Verträgen und Dokumenten wie Themen, Klauseln oder Einzeldaten und extrahiert diese. Unübliche oder fehlende Klauseln werden identifiziert. Die Ergebnisse können mit eigenem Standard bzw. zwei korrespondierende Verträge können automatisiert auf Übereinstimmung abgeglichen werden. 

Besonders geeignet ist das System bei der häufigen Prüfung von einzelnen (Standard-) Verträgen (bspw. NDA, AGB, AVV) und bei der Verarbeitung großer Datenmengen (bspw. bei der Legal Due Diligence in M&A-Transaktionen, Compliance). 

Die flexible Lösung von rfrnz ist in der Lage, schnell neue Vertragsarten und Sprachen zu lernen. Seitens der Kunden ist kein aufwändiges Training oder Labeling notwendig, unsere Anwendung ist sofort einsetzbar. Unsere Vertragsspezialisten trainieren die Plattform mit Beispielsklauseln und das System lernt dadurch, Klauseln und Inhalte wiederzuerkennen. 

Die Lösung funktioniert als eigenständige Webanwendung oder als Integration mit anderen Systemen, z.B. Software für Vertragsmanagement und CRM oder virtuelle Datenräume. Sie kann leicht in bestehende Workflows integriert werden.

Die rfrnz GmbH ist ein deutsches Legal Tech Unternehmen. Die Nähe zu unseren Kunden und die Kenntnis des deutschen Rechtssystems befähigt uns, Kanzleien und Rechtsabteilungen dabei zu unterstützen, das Beste aus Arbeit und Zeit herauszuholen.

name: Helios Aircargo Network
about:
Every month there are 2 million passenger flights worldwide by 700 small and medium Airlines, whose cargo holds are largely empty. This is roughly equivalent to the total current air cargo volume of  €100B per year.
We aim to empower industry experts by creating an operating system that puts the right information at their fingertips at the right time, and connects them with  partners on the other side of the transaction. 
Helios will interconnect the routes of small and medium Airlines to create a New Air Cargo Network that helps them compete with larger Airlines. This means more competition in the industry and win-win for every player in the ecosystem.
Analogous to Amadeus for passenger traffic, we are developing a Global Distribution System for air cargo. This will double Global Air Cargo capacities, increase the revenue potential of small Airlines for cargo twentyfold, and significantly reduce the need for polluting freighters which will reduce CO2 emissions.

name: High Bridge Management Academy
about:
I'm Flavio, Founder at High Bridge.

I've always been astonished at the professional skills gap of young people joining their first companies.

Universities innovate slowly – that is the harsh reality.  They lack the incentives to adapt to rapid market changes.

On the other hand, companies often underinvest in training their new recruits - and rather choose to not assign them roles of responsibility.

The result? A lose-lose situation, where the talent and motivation of recruits get wasted as they are given little or no real responsibilities at work for a long time.

Our answer to this problem is High Bridge Management Academy – a school for young talent to bridge the professional skills gap.

We envision a world where junior employees arrive at the workplace ready to take ownership of truly impactful projects right away, as they will already possess the necessary skill set and attitude for that.

High performance also leads to much greater career satisfaction and work-life balance.

Thus, it becomes a win-win situation for everyone.

High Bridge Management Academy is a next-generation consulting bootcamp, combining elite workshops, focused exercises, and professional coaching to prepare you to get top job offers & thrive as a consultant.

It's designed and delivered by a team of 40+ ex-McKinsey, Bain, and BCG consultants with over 100+ years of combined consulting experience, to bring elite interview and consulting skills to young talent.

Our pedagogical DNA is to directly provide: 
-Market professionals over professors 
-Work skills over academic skills 
-Class interaction over one-directional lecturing.

Find out more about our upcoming bootcamps on our website.

WELCOME TO HIGH BRIDGE MANAGEMENT ACADEMY!

https://highbridgeacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/full-program-2021-1.pdf

name: SciMo - Elektrische Hochleistungsantriebe GmbH
about:
‘SciMo – Science for Motion’ was founded by a group of Ph.D. students from the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology to offer electric motors with a power density far beyond the state of art. Furthermore, SciMo will offer services around electric motors like the electromagnetic design, mechanical calculations, CAD constructions and as well the manufacturing of prototype motors. The unique performance characteristics of our motors are reached via our key technologies of:

- Copper fill factors above 70% using distributed windings
- Innovative cooling concepts, such as indirect cooling of the copper windings
- no expensive materials used

The SciMo High Performace Electric Motors are being built and used since the year 2013. A peak power density of more than 20 kW/kg and a continuous power density of 10 kW/kg have been reached. Our technology is suitable for all applications with highest demands for power density and efficiency.

> No installation. > No hassle. > Pure Me-Time. 
High-quality safe materials. Dust- & water-resistant. 
Patented and Design-protected.

To this end, we not only develop robotic hardware such as arms and hands but also the intelligent software behind it. Our ultimate goal is to make robots more intelligent, enabling humans to work even closer with their robotic assistants and to deploy robots in even more application scenarios. We go beyond cyber security to build cyber resilience that works in tune with your business, preventing downtime and loss of revenue, protecting reputation and enabling you to stay focused on achieving business outcomes.

We consult on resilient cyber security that improves your ability to detect, withstand and respond to security attacks.

We provide three practice areas offering cyber security advisory, managed security services and advanced technologies. 

We enable businesses to define, deliver and maintain a robust, pragmatic and compliant cyber security programme through flexible security solutions and expert advice on emerging technologies that help you to get ahead of attacker innovations.

Our rigorous processes, experience and expertise are delivered with complete transparency to customers. We bring 15 years’ of cyber experience at the highest level and we aim to build trusted relationships with customers that embed cyber security into the fabric of your business processes, enabling you to operate securely and with confidence.

ISO27001 Accredited

name: Foodly
about:
We are a young and growing startup that strives to radically simplify grocery shopping and turn it into a truly convenient and personal experience.

In the Foodly app you find delicious recipes and can order all ingredients with just 1 click! It is totally flexible: you decide how many dishes you want, you can leave ingredients out and order only the ones you really need. On top of that you put all the things you run out of, like beverages, washing powder or toothpaste. Local supermarkets will do the delivery and bring everything conveniently to your doorstep. The smart thing about Foodly is that the recipe recommendations do not only fit your food preferences, but also the ingredients in your cart and the groceries you might already have at home. name: OneFiber Interconnect Germany GmbH
about:
Die OneFiber Interconnect Germany GmbH plant in Deutschland den Aufbau, Betrieb und Vertrieb eines flächendeckenden, homogenen und hochleistungsfähigen Glasfaser-Zubringernetzes: das Gleisfasernetz. Der Aufbau des Netzes erfolgt entlang des deutschen Schienennetzes unter Verwendung innovativer Verlegverfahren in nur rund fünf Jahren. Mit einer Netzlänge von mehr als 27.500 km und mehr als 5.500 Zugangspunkten an fast allen Bahnhöfen und Haltestellen Deutschlands wird die flächendeckende Voraussetzung für die Digitalisierung von städtischen als auch ländlichen Regionen geschaffen. Auf dem Gleisfasernetz werden ausschließlich Gigabit-Leistungen in Form von Dark Fiber, gemanagte Wellenlänge und Gigabit-Ethernet an Unternehmen, Carrier und Administration im Open-Access-Modell angeboten. Bei der Auswahl der einzelnen Netzkomponenten werden dabei die höchsten Ansprüche an Qualität und Technologie gestellt, woraus sich einzigartige Eigenschaften hinsichtlich Cyber-Sicherheit, Redundanz, Latenz, Verfügbarkeit und Reaktionszeiten ergeben.
_____________

Our vision is to promote transparent global supply chains that foster better working conditions and more sustainable manufacturing practices across all industries.

name: Flashhub
about:
We know from our own experience how frustrating it can be to constantly manage bottlenecks and seeing great plans that don’t make it into reality.
Back in 2018, we saw everything crash and burn as one of our biggest projects was failing. As a result of this failure, we learned how to transform and scale our business.

First, we’ve transformed our own 2 local businesses with over 43 local employees into a digital workforce with virtual teams of over 150 global freelancers. Based on that experience we’ve built Flash Hub as a platform to scale systematically with virtual teams in the most flexible and reliable way.

One thing became very clear after all these trials and tribulations; 
Work can be different, work can be free and without limits, and work can be done by people who like their job, who can be independent and self-determined, and work can be done by people who see their job as something positive in their lives.

What we recently introduced in our offer that can help you transform and grow is 
- The Flash Hub Academy: a starter pack with 15 videos on how to build your own highly efficient remote team of global freelancers; 
- The Virtual Team Challenge: two-week group coaching featuring Manuel Pistner himself, where you will learn to build your own digital leadership system; and finally, 
- Personal support, where together with you, we analyze your individual business goals and create the blueprint of your virtual teams that can scale reliably with global freelancers. 

Grow your business beyond local borders. 

With Flash Hub, you get everything you need to grow your business with virtual teams and global freelancers and scale work beyond your imagination and local staff shortages.

management.

Cyber Insurance - the cyber risk quantification capabilities allow insurance companies to automate and mange the entire cyber insurance process, from risk assessment, to underwriting, to policy renewal. This includes portfolio analysis and advanced financial impact calculations.

Consulting firms - by using ACRO, consulting firms can save up to 60% of the time and effort spent on manual processes in cyber risk assessment projects. The platform allows consulting firm to increase client stickiness, perform multiple projects simultaneously and provide actionable insights tailored to their customers.

3rd Party Cyber Risk - large organizations can use the platform to automate and manage 3rd party cyber risk assessments to multitudes of vendors. By validating defense capabilities with internal technical sources, the system provides the organization with a true analysis of the inherent risk their vendor poses, and not just based on external, zero-touch, hygiene check.

name: Enapter
about:
Enapter is a rapidly-growing energy technology company based in Pisa, Italy with offices in Germany, Thailand, and Russia. We develop and produce Anion Exchange Membrane (AEM) electrolysers for green hydrogen production from water and renewable electricity, enabling low-cost green hydrogen production at any scale. Our patented and proven AEM technology is the foundation for mass-produced electrolyser products, not projects. We project they will make the cheapest hydrogen with scaled production, competing with fossil fuels purely on price.

Hydrogen is essential for the rapid decarbonisation of sectors that are reliant on liquid and gaseous fuel. Enapter’s mission is to make green hydrogen affordable and accessible to all. 

Our compact hydrogen generators can be deployed rapidly thanks to their modular, plug & play design and our Energy Management System Toolkit for simple software integration and remote control. Used by customers in 40 countries for energy storage, mobility, heat, industry, power-to-fuel and more, our electrolysers put affordable, highly-efficient green hydrogen generation in your hands. 

Enapter is preparing for mass fabrication with increased production capacity at our Italian facilities, as well as the expected completion and soft launch of our Enapter Campus automated mass-production site and R&D facilities in Saerbeck, Germany by 2023.The Campus is a blueprint that will pave the way for further AEM Electrolyser mass-production sites around the world: a decentralised network of factories that would bring the world gigawatts of green hydrogen production capacity and unlock the green hydrogen futures that are within our grasp.

We cut down onboarding time, costs & eliminate room for human error by looking at the process from end to end. Starting with an enhanced client experience, and the internal onboarding management  enabling client Due Diligence, Screening and compliance. Our Modules and Tools are integrated with AI, ML & automation for document understanding, facial recognition, task tracking and verification of information.

We make the on-boarding process easier to understand and follow-through by the customer and by the company representative. 
Through our technology the process can be broken down into bite-sized steps, each with the exact instructions and tools needed for completion.
 This is achieved seamlessly by importing existing enterprise content and digital tools through an easy wizard based configuration dashboard.

•        General on-boarding

about:

In Canada, the Company's wholly-owned Canadian subsidiary, Pure Sunfarms, is one of the single largest cannabis operations in the world, the lowest-cost greenhouse producer and one of Canada's best-selling brands. The Company also owns 70% of Québec-based, ROSE LifeScience, a leading third-party cannabis products commercialization expert in the Province of Québec,

In the US, wholly-owned Balanced Health Botanicals is one of the leading CBD brands and e-commerce platforms in the country.  Subject to compliance with all applicable US federal and state laws and stock exchange rules, Village Farms plans to enter the US high-THC cannabis market via multiple strategies, leveraging one of the largest greenhouse operations in the country (more than 5.5 million square feet in West Texas), as well as the operational and product expertise gained through Pure Sunfarms' cannabis success in Canada.

Internationally, Village Farms is targeting selected, nascent, legal cannabis and CBD opportunities with significant medium- and long-term potential, with an initial focus on the Asia-Pacific region and Europe.

name: YUKKA Lab
about: YUKKA Lab provides fact-based actionable insights to the financial markets. YUKKA's self-developed algorithms are leading edge, containing natural language processing (NLP), machine and deep learning. Our solutions enable users from fields of asset management, market research, financial advisory, risk management and sales lead to handle the rapidly increasing amount of various financial data in real-time.  What the YUKKA News & Trend Lab is about: Markets can often be anticipated by analyzing news. YUKKA Lab's financial market sentiment is a real-time leading indicator. Our sentiment-technology anticipates trend reversals in advance, and thus, the news sentiments function as an early warning system. Our YUKKA News Lab is based on pro-feeds of the largest news agencies (such as awp, dpa-AFX), partnerships with publishers worldwide and others providers. Users get insights about market-moving thematic contexts and learn about a market's pain points and its success factors within a few seconds. This information is contextually visualized in fully reactive data graphs. YUKKA News & Trend Lab presents an easy to grasp an overview of sentiments in single markets, various regions, and indices, as well as industries and sectors. In unseren "Puks" erzählen wir wunderschöne Geschichten mit liebevollen Illustrationen – ein ganz klassisches Leseerlebnis also. Hier können Eltern ihren Kindern vorlesen und gemeinsam mit ihnen in eine neue Welt entdecken

Gleichzeitig nutzen wir vielfältige interaktive Funktionen, die das Lesen für Kinder spannender und intensiver machen. Wir machen die Informationen in unseren Sachbüchern für Kinder erlebbar und verständlich, z.B. durch Gesangsaufnahmen zum jeweiligen Vogel oder ein kurzer Clip mit einem Löwen. Theorie wird so gleich Praxis. In unseren Geschichten lassen wir, z.B. durch eine Entscheidungsfunktion, das Kind entscheiden, wie die Geschichte weitergehen soll oder binden Geräusche mit ein. So werden Kinder ganz Teil der Geschichte. 

Hier gibt es unendlich viele Möglichkeiten, Lesen zu einem ganzheitlichen Erlebnis für Kinder zu machen. Dieses Erlebnis können sie dabei ganz selbst steuern. Jede interaktive Funktion wird vom Kind aufgerufen, das Kind wird nicht „berieselt“, sondern kann entdecken wie viel und worauf es Lust hat. 

So können Eltern einen gemeinsamen interaktiven Lesespaß mit ihren Kindern erleben,

name: Movaco
about:
The MOVACO app helps colleagues, friends or families to quickly organize and communicate their daily carpools. 

We target organizations (companies, schools, institutions) and combine their members and mobility needs on our platform. We empower organisations in urban and rural areas to help them move their members. We developed a matching algorithm that allows passengers to easily find and join daily rides. 
Therefore we provide smart ride-suggestions for other rides and passengers on the same direction and area. The target is to keep tracking the demands (passengers) and suggest those to potential drivers. Additionally we provide a route-related fare sharing proposal. 

Besides building a strong and safe community for carpooling, the app automatically saves parking spaces as side-effect. Our app can also be expanded by a smart parking system management (parking sensors + in-app-management). The advantage: free parking spaces are automatically allocated for carpools. 
In this way, a large number of required parking spaces can be reduced in a very short time.
Overall, this also reduces the volume of traffic and promotes sustainability.

Hierfür müssen technische Lösungen, die die einzelnen Potenziale im Abwasser ausschöpfen, entwickelt und wirtschaftlich sinnvoll ausgelegt werden. Seit Januar 2020 setzt die revincus GmbH als patentgetriebenes Start-Up in diesem Bereich an und entwickelt neuartige Lösungen - primär zur dezentralen Energierückgewinnung aus häuslichem Abwasser.

This saves companies money and time, while their legal department staff can focus on strategic work. Sentryc's software of the same name provides market transparency, monitoring and brand protection. 


The Sentryc software is based on machine learning algorithms that combine keywords, images and product descriptions for each search and learn continuously. In this way, over 62,000 suspicious offers have been successfully removed from leading B2B and B2C platforms to date (March 2021).


As a fast-growing B2B SaaS company, we not only have an exciting product, but also a great team for which we are looking for support. #StartUpYourWay #TechCompany #BrandProtection #Software #FemaleLeadership

name: Spanflug Technologies GmbH
about: Spanflug Technologies GmbH is an online manufacturer of CNC turning and milling parts that offers its customers a fully automated procurement process. To calculate a price in the online shop the user uploads a CAD model (STEP file) of the component to be manufactured, selects the desired material, the quantity (1 - 1000) and the delivery date. In addition, the customer can upload a PDF of the technical drawing to automatically read out information on individual manufacturing tolerances, fits, threads and surfaces. This allows functional components with high technical requirements to be considered. By applying an algorithm, the platform calculates a quotation price in a few seconds. Based on this price customers can order the components directly online.  With Spanflug, the effort to request and wait for price quotes from multiple suppliers is eliminated. The ordering process is often shortened from several days to a few minutes. If required, components will be delivered within 10 business days . The goal of the company, which was founded in January 2018, is to make the often time-consuming and resource-intensive bidding process for CNC turned and milled parts as quick and easy as possible for both customers and suppliers, and to advance the digitization of the manufacturing industry in the area of CNC turning and milling. The additional procurement costs for turned and milled parts can thus be reduced significantly. The production of the CNC components takes place exclusively with qualified suppliers in Germany. Spanflug is a spin-off from the Institute for Machine Tools and Industrial Management (iwb) of the Technical University of Munich (TUM) and participated in the incubator program Xpreneurs of the UnternehmerTUM Entrepreneurship Network.  Imprint: https://spanflug.de/impressum/

about:

Umfragen zeigen, dass ein Drittel der erwachsenen Bevölkerung an Schlafproblemen leidet und 10% die diagnostischen Kriterien für eine klinische Schlafstörung (Insomnie) erfüllen. Schätzungen zur Folge befinden sich nur ein Bruchteil der Betroffenen in professioneller Behandlung. Wir haben uns zum Ziel gesetzt, diese Versorgungslücke zu schließen. Mit somnio haben wir ein digitales Schlaftraining entwickelt, das als erste App auf Rezept im Bereich der Schlafmedizin zugelassen wurde und von Ärzt:innen und Psychotherapeut:innen verordnet werden kann.
Mehr Informationen finden Sie unter www.mementor.de und www.somn.io.

MOBI's mission is to explore Blockchain and related technologies, promote standards, and accelerate adoption for the benefit of the industry, consumers, and communities.  MOBI was created to help the mobility industry apply secure, peer-to-peer Blockchain technologies to improving peopleâs lives by making mobility more efficient and affordable, to reduce congestion and pollution, and to improve safety. name: Discovergy
about:
Als Innovationstreiber der Energiebranche ist Discovergy von dem Ziel getrieben, die Weichen der künftigen, klimaneutralen Energiewelt zu stellen. Wie kann man Energieverbrauch für Haushalte und Unternehmen transparenter und verständlicher machen? Wie können Millionen von Energieerzeugern auf stabile und sichere Weise in das Stromnetz integriert werden? Und wie lässt sich etwa die Mobilität elektrifizieren und die Energieversorgung dezentral und klimafreundlich gestalten? 

Die Antworten auf diese und viele anderen Fragen unserer täglichen Arbeit, finden wir in den Daten unserer intelligenten Stromzähler. Denn diese sind unsere Kernkompetenz: Kommunizierende Messtechnik, die ihre Messwerte in Echtzeit überträgt, damit mit den gewonnenen Daten weitere Lösungen zum Gelingen der Energiewende entwickelt werden können. Mehr als 75.000 solcher Smart Meter hat Discovergy bereits als wettbewerblicher Messstellenbetreiber installiert, und das ist nur der Anfang auf dem Weg einer smarten, effizienten Energiewelt.

Bei Discovergy geht es deshalb nicht nur um Zähler, sondern um die Vielfalt an Möglichkeiten, die unsere Smart Meter entfalten: Smarte Zähler ermöglichen die Visualisierung von Stromflüssen via Web-Portal und App, sind die Grundlage für ressourcenschonende Lösungen wie Mieterstrom oder dynamische Ökostromtarife und werden künftig die einfache Steuerung von Ladeboxen, Stromspeichern oder Erzeugungsanlagen erlauben, so dass das gesamte Stromsystem auf die Schwankungen der Sonnen und Wind als Energieträger sich anpassen und reagieren kann.

name: Grino Water Solutions
