Grino provides a battery-free solar-based desalination system. Powering the system with solar energy keeps it independent from all power grids and stays renewable. Removing of batteries makes Grino one of the most economic desalination systems in the world. The innovative process created by Grino allows the desalination unit to work dynamically. In contrast to current technologies, Grino adopts completely automatically to the sunlight. The power management minimizes the energy losses and maximizes the water production, even in cloudy and rainy weather conditions.  You want to profit from clean Grino Water, have questions or feedback? We are happy to hear from you at hello@grinowater.com! • Save time: the manager can be freed up from onboarding and training.

• Save money: more productivity, fewer mistakes, empowered employees and freed up time results in significantly reduced costs.
• Ignite your business: there is space to think and have better ideas for growth.
About the how-to content:
• Ownership: it is all yours and you only share it with the users you want to.
• Immediately updated: if you want to create a new standard operating procedure or change one of the existent ones, you can do it directly in your private dashboard and it is automatically, and immediately, updated for all users.
• Multi-language: we support most languages and if you need one we don't yet have, just ask us!
• Support materials: images, videos and GIFs can be uploaded directly.
• Voice-guided interface: we take care of making it immediately interactive and hands-free for your employees to use straight away.

Our users report that the team is much happier. Everyone is more focused because they don't have to worry about the how-to, they can totally rely on how.fm supporting them.
And for those with a lot of fluctuation, it is great for newbies as well! They ask a lot of questions to the app - that before they never dared to ask more senior employees or managers - so they get up to speed much faster.

name: Yolife
about:
Yolife is an app that helps people live longer in good health and avoid age-related diseases. Our vision is to add 15 healthy years to 1 billion people. We believe that the active and social pursuit of healthy longevity is the greatest potential to be unlocked in our society.

We have the opportunity to radically reduce our risk of age-related diseases like cardiovascular diseases, diabetes, cancer, and Alzheimer’s as well as to free ourselves from reoccurring illnesses and a general impairment of our capacities.

So much can be changed for the better through lifestyle changes. What is needed are right instructions, good experience design, and a social environment. This is what Yolife aims to provide for a large number of people of all ages.

It is not just a business for us, it is what we live ourselves and what improved our own lives so much that we cannot but make this our mission.

And the near future is even more promising. Breakthrough rejuvenation therapies and drug discoveries are on the rise to directly target aging as a disease and extend our overall healthy lifespan. Therefore, we will make Yolife a gateway to those exciting measures for as many people as possible.

We think that re-designing our habits and mindset for longevity and leveraging the achievements of science and technology for this purpose is the most important next step in human evolution. Being part of it makes our lives meaningful. That’s why we’ll never give up.

name: Zveetz
about:
Wir alle kennen das große Problem: Wir lieben und “brauchen” unsere Süßigkeiten, aber die negativen Auswirkungen von Zucker sind weltweit enorm - Stichwort Diabetes, Adipositas und Karies.

Damit wollten wir uns nicht zufrieden geben - deshalb haben wir ein Fruchtgummi entwickelt, das 100% zuckerfrei ist. Aber das ist nicht alles! Zveetz enthalten bis zu 80% weniger Kalorien als herkömmliche Fruchtgummis,  bis zu 70% weniger Kalorien als andere zuckerfreie Fruchtgummis und sind frei von abführenden Nebenwirkungen.

Wir verzichten zwar auf Zucker, aber nicht auf den Geschmack. 

Während der Produktentwicklung haben uns viele Leute erzählt, dass unser Produkt unmöglich ist, aber wir haben nicht aufgegeben und es möglich gemacht!

Zveetz sind...
...laktosefrei
...glutenfrei
...aus 100% natürlichen Zutaten
...ohne Gentechnik

Sie sind für jeden geeignet, der auf seinen Zuckerkonsum und seine Ernährung achten möchte sowie für Diabetiker, Sportler & Fitnessfans, Kinder und Allergiker. 

Seid dabei, wenn wir die Welt von Zucker befreien!

about:
Unsere Flaschengärten sind durch ihre Form und den Naturkork nicht nur besonders dekorativ, sie bestechen auch durch ihre extrem leichte Pflege.

Neben – drei bis Viermal gießen im Jahr – benötigen sie relativ wenig Licht. Der Flaschengarten ist ein sich selbst erhaltendes Biotop und daher besonders Pflegeleicht.

Sie müssen die Pflanzen nicht umtopfen, sich keine Sorge bezüglich der Vertrocknung machen und der Deckel sollte immer auf dem kleinen Garten bleiben.

Wir bieten eine große Auswahl an Flaschengärten in unserem Showroom in Berlin an. Hier finden Sie kleine Biotope mit ausgewählten tropischen Pflanzen, perfekt abgestimmt, um ein autarkes System zu errichten.

Die kleinen Gärten erhellen nicht nur jedes Raumdesign, sie erfüllen ihren Zweck auch gänzlich als Zimmerdekorationen im Büro, auf Ihrem Tresen, in Ihrem Hotel oder als besonderes Geschenk für jeden Anlass.

about:
Die Spacific GmbH ist ein deutsches Start-up Unternehmen, das sich auf skalierbare AR/MR-Lösungen für die Industrie spezialisiert hat. Das 2019 gegründete Unternehmen fokussiert sich auf die digitale Transformation von Engineering- und Produktionsprozessen. Die Gründer und das Team von Spacific bringen mehr als 15 Jahre Praxiserfahrung in diesen Bereichen mit.

Mit Spacific Measurement hat das Start-up eine Lösung im industriellen Maßstab entwickelt. Sie kombiniert eine validierte Messmethodik auf Basis von Microsoft HoloLens mit einer cloudbasierten Plattform, die die erstellten CAD-Modelle intelligent und in Echtzeit für die weitere Datenverarbeitung verfügbar macht. 

Die Engine ermöglicht präzise 3D-Modelle, die direkt in industriellen Engineering- und Produktionsprozessen eingesetzt werden können. Ein Standardanwendungsfall für MeasuresSpaces ist die Generierung von As-Built-Dokumentationen, sei es als Startpunkt für neue Engineering-Projekte oder als Teil von Abnahme- und Inbetriebnahmeverfahren für Industrieanlagen, Schiffe oder Baustellen.

name: True Flood Risk
about:
True Flood Risk is mission driven company pioneering the next generation of geolocation intelligence for flood risk. 

Our patented flagship solution (US Patent No 11,120,557) calculates the structural height, often called first floor height (FFH) or lowest floor elevation (LFE), for over 250M residential and commercial properties globally. Our AI-driven climate analytics platform provides floodplain managers, insurers, property owners, renters, real estate professionals and mortgage lenders key insights on understanding property-specific flood risk.

Our Value Proposition: Property-level data, specifically, first floor elevation & presence of a basement, coupled with flood zone, are the leading indicators of flood risk. Current & prospective homeowners use data to understand a home’s flood risk; Mortgage & insurance pros use property-level data for underwriting, expedite online quotes, claims dept identify part of portfolio at risk before incoming weather events, notify customers to relocate high value assets (customer engagement). Marketing departments can use data to target specific properties. Local gov’t can understand areas of community most at risk due to flooding.

Description of Product(s): Property-level data: Roof pitch, structure type, # of floors, presence of a basement, structural height (intl)/first floor elevation, FFE (US), flood risk score, resilience score, flash flooding simulations, real estate values at risk, cost-benefit analysis on mitigation strategies, neighborhood comparison, data available as a single address API query, batch processing for desktop or mobile users; Enterprise dashboard: visualizes proprietary data with trusted 3rd party data from USGS, FEMA, NOAA; Market reports: market overview on FFE data by state, county or zip code.

Staffbook is a new concept which gives you all the benefits of an agency without the hassle of dealing with recruitment consultants!
We are a fully automated recruitment website and have successfully combined online networking with recruitment, which means you can search for new employees using our unique matching tool.  Your criteria can be as narrow or broad as required and will present you with our top five matches.  You will be presented with their photograph, CV, job specific test results and details of their previous experience.  You will be able to contact the candidate directly through the site, giving you full control of the process.
This service is free to use however, if a placement is made Staffbook charge a one off fee of £395.  Fees are completely contingent on success, so you can browse the database, select candidates and interview without any obligation.  Staffbook works on the principal no win no fee!

name: Topas Therapeutics
about: Topas Therapeutics GmbH is a private Hamburg, Germany-based biotechnology company focused on developing products to address areas of major unmet need, including autoimmune diseases, allergies and anti-drug antibodies. The Topas Particle Conjugates technology platform induces antigen-specific immune tolerance by harnessing the liver’s natural immunology capabilities. The Company has several proprietary programs; lead product candidate TPM203 has recently entered clinical testing for pemphigus vulgaris, an orphan disease. Other programs are in anti-drug antibodies, celiac disease, Type 1 diabetes, as well as a multiple sclerosis program that is available for partnering.  Topas has a research and option agreement with Eli Lilly and Company focused on antigen-specific tolerance induction, and a multi-year agreement with Boehringer Ingelheim to collaborate in the field of anti-drug antibodies. Topas’ investors include: Epidarex Capital, Gimv, EMBL Ventures, Evotec and Boehringer Ingelheim Venture Fund.

about:
Twinsity is the state-of-the-art digital twin software solution for your massive reality capture projects.

We offer an all-in-one high-performance and intuitive technology solution for creating stunning high-res visualizations of your 3D models.
Discover your high-quality digital twins immersively and in real time, create amazing showcases for presentations and use the new technology to perform virtual inspections.
With our powerful software solution, inspections can be carried out in a faster, secure and more accurate way - to enrich the work of engineers, contractors and inspectors.  

Twinsity helps businesses drive expanding and promoting their digitalization work, to enable a new, safer and more collaborative way of working.

Stunning 3D experiences and a variety of effective features provide the application of Twinsity in a wide range of industries - including inspections, cultural heritage, restorations, planning or simulation.

Discover the advantages of the digital world for your work with Twinsity!


For further information, please visit twinsity.com.

Imprint: https://twinsity.com/en/imprint/

name: VISUS Industry IT
about:
Mit unseren Softwarelösungen DIMATE PACS und DIMATE CCM digitalisieren wir die ZfP-Prüfprozesse in der Materialprüfung, Inspektion und Wartung.

DIMATE PACS:
Die industrielle Plattform zur Organisation und Analyse von Testdaten.
> Revisionssichere Archivierung von Prüfbildern, Reporten und Dokumenten
> Digitale Auswertung von Prüfbildern, z.B. RT-, UT-, VT-Bilder und Signale
> Übermittlung der Prüfaufträge an die Prüfgeräte und/oder an die ZfP-Dienstleister

DIMATE CCM:

> Zertifikate
> Verträge

name: BOOST THYROID by VLM Health
about:
BOOST Thyroid is an app helping people with hypothyroidism and Hashimoto’s.

Hashimoto's is the most common autoimmune condition. Affecting over 200 million people, it causes an underactive thyroid and other health complications.

We support patients and doctors by providing expansive tracking options and informational health content. Our goal is to reduce symptoms and enable preventive health management for all underactive thyroid patients.

We’re the first iOS app to address hypothyroidism and Hashimoto’s in collaboration with healthcare professionals and researchers.

With machine learning and empathic scientific information, we offer personalized options to improve and maintain health.

BOOST Thyroid is a startup supported by VCs, Sanofi, IBB, the EU Horizon 2020 programme PERMIDES and INNOLABS, the German Ministry of Education Research (BMBF), the Vodafone institute F-LANE accelerator, and the Fast Track Malmö accelerator.

The app was developed in 2016 in collaboration with the University of Oxford, Stanford University, Charité Berlin, and the University of Utah.

about:
remberg is a Munich-based start-up that provides industrial companies with a SaaS solution to help them become digital champions in customer & field service and preparing them for the age of IoT. 

https://remberg.de

name: Envelio
about:
envelio is a startup from Cologne, Germany developing software for the digital transformation of energy grids. 

Distribution grid operators’ existing IT systems and processes are not ready for the challenge of integrating millions of new renewable generators into the grid. envelio has developed the Intelligent Grid Platform (IGP) to support distribution system operators in their future challenges and the mass integration of renewable energies and EV charging points into the grid. The IGP is a modular digital and flexible assistance system with three main application areas: 

1.) Data quality: Create validated digital grid models with machine learning algorithms

2.)Grid planning: Automate and accelerate processes and workflows of grid planners

3.) Grid operation: Analyze the grid state and avoid congestions in real-time

The IGP is already implemented at various European distribution grid operators including i.a. Iberdrola S.E., one of the biggest utilities in Europe and Westnetz GmbH, the biggest German distribution grid operator.

The IGP is already being used at various European distribution grid operators including i.a. Iberdrola S.E., one of the biggest utilities in Europe and Westnetz GmbH, the biggest German distribution grid operator.

name: Kraftling
about:
WIR SIND KRAFTLING

Mit dem Ziel Menschen zu einem aktiven und gesunden Leben zu inspirieren, bringen wir innovative und funktionale Produkte in die Welt. Frische Snacks und Drinks ready-to-consume für eine bewusstere Ernährung. 

Bekannt geworden mit dem schärfsten Ingwer Shot am Markt, wollen wir nun ganz Deutschland mit unseren frischen und gesunden Produkten erobern. 2018 angefangen in einer WG-Küche, kann man unsere Produkte mittlerweile deutschlandweit verkosten.

about: myResilience nutzt die Kombination modernster Sicherheitstechnologien mit der Weltklasse-Servicekapazität von Encode und globalen Sicherheitsexperten, um kostengünstige Managed Detection and Response Services anzubieten.

name: ProTunes
about: proTunes is a global transaction platform and marketplace that seamlessly connects music rights holders, music buyers, media distributors, and performance rights organizations. proTunes offers business solutions, powered by data and technology, that eliminate the pain points of B2B music transaction workflows through search and discovery, compliance, license management, payment, and royalty collection.

name: SPREAD
about:
We are driven by the hardest challenges engineers are facing when creating and maintaining the most complex and amazing products in this world.

We spend a lot of time together with those engineers to understand their challenges and derive paths towards more efficient and sustainable product creation.

Based on that, we created SPREAD, with the aim to create tangible value for engineers throughout the product lifecycle and the virtue to enable more sustainable products.

From Engineers - for Engineers!

name: Wonde
about:
An innovative data management solution for the Education sector, Wonde extracts data (i.e. student, teacher and parent records) from within a school, stores it in the cloud and then provides third party applications access.

Third party applications need to access school data to both set-up and keep their software up-to-date. Rather than individually integrating with every school, Wonde provides an efficient method of data integration which requires only one integration. This saves companies time, money and valuable resources; allowing them to grow faster and focus on their core product.

When it comes to schools, Wonde ensures they are able to manage access to their data, giving them greater visibility and control over what information is accessed by third parties. This ensures they’re compliant with their data protection obligations. Schools also now only need to maintain one external connection to their school data, rather than a connection to each software application they use.

name: RIDE Capital
about: RIDE is building the digital privat bank of the 21st century. We strive to democratize wealth planning by combining low infrastructure costs, low taxes, and high returns. Herefore, we provide services that make administration and legal cheap, and strive towards offering alternative investments on our own platform. (With us, investors safe taxes on their investments whilst keeping costs low and calculable.)

name: Ably Medical
about: Ably Medical is an up-and-coming global medical technology company committed to creating products that improve quality of life for both patients and providers. Through a combination of machine learning and Scandinavian design, Ably Medical aims to deliver products that are functional, user-friendly, and truly innovative.

name: Augmania
about:
Augmania is a storytelling tool that enables marketers to build interactive AR campaigns and eventually memorable experiences to share with their audience.

Augmania combines multiple AR triggers: 
 - Face detection
 - Location based
 - Image recognition
 - QR codes

Sharing content has never been easier thanks to Augmania Viewer that allows you to share experiences created easily on mobile apps,  social network and even embed it on websites.

Augmania understands how data-driven can marketers be, and that's why it offers its users the opportunity to track and measure their campaigns ROI and their consumers' behavior through Augmania Analytics.

name: Better Basics Laborbedarf
about:
Wir bei Better Basics Laborbedarf entwickeln, fertigen und vertreiben smarte Grundausstattung für Labore.

Unsere innovativen Produkte basieren auf der 3D-Drucktechnologie und lassen sich durch ihre Modularität schnell und einfach an die jeweiligen Bedürfnisse des Anwenders anpassen. Unsere Grundausstattung für Labore schafft Ordnung und organisiert Arbeitsplätze, verbessert die Arbeitssicherheit und steigert die Effizienz der Anwender.

Als Ausgründung aus dem Leibniz-Institut für Polymerforschung in Dresden stehen wir für innovative Laborgrundausstattung – Made in Germany. Wir bieten Lösungen für die unterschiedlichsten Arbeiten in Laboren. Unsere Produkte finden u.a. in der Chemie, Biologie, Biochemie, Pharmazie und Medizin Anwendung.

name: IO-Dynamics
about:
⚡ Wir sind IO-Dynamics, ein Startup im Bereich der E-Mobilität und ansässig in Flensburg. Wir ermöglichen Unternehmen einen kostengünstigen, ökologischen und stressfreien Betrieb von E-Fahrzeugen, indem wir für sie die Herausforderungen beim Laden meistern. ⚡

UNSERE MISSION🌠
Wir wollen das E-Auto durch Vernetzung optimal in das Energiesystem eingliedern, um so den Übergang zur flächendeckenden E-Mobilität zu beschleunigen. Auf diese Weise wollen wir die E-Mobilität einfacher gestalten und einen entscheidenden Beitrag zur Mobilitäts- und Energiewende leisten.

UNSER PRODUKT 💥
Wir entwickeln und vertreiben IO-ELON, eine neuartige Software, die das Laden von E-Autos speziell in Unternehmensfuhrparks auf nachhaltige, verlässliche und effiziente Weise steuert und verwaltet. Durch Nutzung unterschiedlicher Datenquellen und abhängig von geplanten Fahrten, wird die optimale Energie zum richtigen Zeitpunkt für jedes Fahrzeug nachgeladen. Das Besondere dabei ist die Nutzung von Echtzeitdaten, welche mithilfe eines Telematik-Moduls erhoben werden.
 
UNSER ANSPRUCH 🌍
Nachhaltigkeit liegt uns sehr am Herzen. Durch die maximal schonende Behandlung der Akkus können wertvolle Ressourcen länger verwendet werden. IO-ELON streicht typische Bedenken wie Reichweite, Batteriegesundheit oder Ladestand und gestaltet den Betrieb der E-Autos transparent, verlässlich und kostengünstig.

name: SALESmanago
about:
SALESmanago is the only no-code, AI driven CDXP (all in One Customer Data Platform & Customer Experience Platform) used by 2500+ midmarket and large Enterprises in 50 countries including Starbucks, Vodafone, Lacoste, New Balance, Victoria’s Secret and many other global brands. Financial Times ranks SALESmanago as the fastest growing marketing automation platform in Europe.

SALESmanago is harnessing the full power of first- and zero-party data, combining advanced analytics and AI Hyperpersonalization to deliver highly configurable personalised experiences, across a comprehensive range of natively built and integrated marketing execution channels.

The company is based in Kraków, Poland and employs 300 highly experienced consultants, data scientists and engineers. SALESmanago works internationally via an extensive network of over 1000 reselling partners.

Get started with SALESmanago with 2 month free Proof of Concept. Register at www.salesmanago.com

name: STOKR
about:
STOKR is the EU’s pioneering digital investment marketplace for alternative assets, where smart investors connect with and fund innovative businesses.

STOKR is the all-in-one solution for young and growing ventures looking to raise capital in the EU. Operating out of Luxembourg, STOKR provides founders with the full suite of technical deployment, investment structuring, and compliance support for the issuance of EU-compliant security token offerings (STOs).

Through carefully selected high-profile offerings, STOKR fosters a risk-reduced environment, liberates investment opportunities from traditional venture capital, and directly connects visionary ventures to a network of professional and retail investors . STOKR allows investors to participate in the future success of a diverse range of ventures through profit- or revenue-sharing rights, without middlemen such as custodians or brokers.  

We believe in better living through innovation. It’s the reason we get out of bed in the morning.

Our vision is to create the leading marketplace where everyone is empowered to invest in alternative assets.

#FuellingInnovation

about: We build AI-based systems by combining a passion for simple economic solutions, software engineering expertise and excellence in machine learning algorithms.

name: Noveltea
about:
NOVELTEA was started in Newcastle upon Tyne in 2017 by our ‘Two Germans in British Tweed’, Vincent and Lukas, with a simple mission: to pioneer a new category, Alcoholic Teas, based on the world’s fascination for tea.

Blending the highest quality loose leaf teas (cold-brewed to extract a fuller, more rounded flavour) with a range of expertly crafted spirits, our ‘Tales’ build on Britain’s history of culinary innovation to deliver a ‘Tea with Spirit’.

Since then we’ve grown rapidly in the UK, launched internationally (China and Germany). We have super exciting plans to recruit (alcoholic) tea lovers faster and wider.

name: Kenkou
about:
Kenkou is a pioneer company in cardiovascular measurement through the smartphone.
With its main product, a software development kit (SDK), we provide the fastest and the most accurate point in time measurement on major vital signs, including heart rate variability (HRV) and heart rate (HR), through PPG technology. Once integrated inside an application, it’s available for all app users and provides real-time data of their body state. It’s a CE marked medical device with ECG quality and no wearables are needed. 

Kenkou makes vital signs measurement accessible for Everyone.

name: Planck Re
about: Planck is the leading commercial insurance data platform, built to enable insurers to instantly and accurately underwrite any business. Planck's technology platform aggregates and mines massive datasets, using the latest advances in artificial intelligence to automatically generate and deliver key insights customized to the commercial underwriting process. The end result is a frictionless underwriting process with greater insurer visibility into risk factors, leading to improved new business conversion and retention rates and lower loss ratios. Planck’s platform brings automation and intelligence to the underwriting process – empowering commercial insurers to focus on underwriting that truly requires human expertise.

name: Roamler
about:
Founded in 2011, Roamler provides businesses with B2B crowd-based solutions, answering the call of companies for efficiency with widespread, on-demand professionals and individuals. These 'Roamlers' are recruited, trained, and organized according to their skills, experience, and location, and then matched to 'tasks'.

Roamler is the European leader in crowd-supported field-marketing activities, performing tasks for the biggest FMCG manufacturers, consumer brands, PCGs, and retail chains.

Since 2016, Roamler is also active in crowd-supported technical solutions such as installations, service and repairs, executed by network of certified professionals spread across the Netherlands, the UK and Germany.

In 2018, Roamler launched the first-ever venture to increase flexibility and efficiency in the home care and healthcare industries, by leveraging the power of a large network of professional caregivers active across the Netherlands.

name: Kapilendo
about:
Die Invesdor Group ist eine europäische Investmentplattform. Sie bietet umfassende Investment Services für Privatanleger und digitale Finanzierungslösungen auf Eigen- und Fremdkapitalbasis für Unternehmen. Die Platzierungen erfolgen öffentlich oder als Private Placement. Sie ist in den Kernmärkten Deutschland, Österreich und Finnland aktiv. 
Die Invesdor Group ist 2021 aus dem Zusammenschluss der drei Plattformen Kapilendo (seit 2015), Finnest (seit 2015) und Invesdor (seit 2012) entstanden.

name: augustusai
about:
Augustus offers clients a suite of solutions that enable them to quickly and cost-effectively integrate AI into their systems without needing to build complex infrastructure, hire dedicated technical teams, or sacrifice security. 

We are a transatlantic company. Our headquarters are in New York City, and we have dedicated offices in Menlo Park, Munich, and Paris to serve both the American and European markets.

name: AI Superior

We focus on bringing value to the business by enabling AI.
AI Superior provides end-to-end product and solution design based on big data, machine learning, and artificial intelligence. Our experienced team guided by PhD Data Scientists will build a solution that fulfils your requirements and allows flexibility for future evolution.

We are customer-oriented and business-driven:

    # We use a pragmatic approaches to solve business problems

    # Consider AI-hype that is generally damaging industry (according to Gartner

       of the project.

Awards:
Clutch Top Artificial Intelligence Companies in 2021

3rd place in the International Trade Council Go Global Award 2021 in Artificial  Intelligence.

We are a member of the German AI Association.

name: Alife Foods
about:
We are Alife - a consumer-first, product-oriented, cell-based meat brand. We believe cultured meat will be the successor to traditionally farmed meat. 

Our mission is simple: We will offer a slaughter-free option for the consumer’s favorite meat products. From meat balls to burger patties - we want people to have their favorite food without a moral compromise. 

We cover the second part of the supply chain and see our role as a middleman between producers of cultured meat, industry organisations, food retail and consumers.

Axiado’s products protect sensitive data from the attack vulnerabilities found in current processors and ensure security for every system.

name: Blockchain Acedemy UG
about:
Beratung:
Streben Sie einen Strukturwandel an und wollen im Bereich Digitalisierung zu den führenden Unternehmen gehören? Dann sind Sie bei uns richtig - Wir unterstützen und beraten Sie gezielt zu der Thematik Blockchain und dessen Implementierungsmöglichkeiten in Ihrem Unternehmen. Seien Sie der Konkurrenz einen Schritt voraus und sichern Sie sich so einen Wettbewerbsvorteil.

Softwareentwicklung:
Viele Unternehmen suchen nach der richtigen Blockchain-Anwendung um effizienter, innovativer und fortschrittlicher zu werden. Wir bieten Ihnen die Möglichkeit Software-Lösungen zu entwickeln, die einzigartig und vollständig an Ihre Bedürfnisse angepasst sind. Mit unseren Experten und internationalen Netzwerk an Partnerunternehmen bieten wir ein vollumfängliches Paket vom ersten Tag der Beratung, bis zur vollständigen Entwicklung, Implementierung und Instandhaltung der maßgeschneiderten Blockchain-Infrastruktur an.

Wissenschaftliche Prüfung und Zertifizierung:
Experten und Entwickler für verschiedene Bereiche der Blockchain-Technologie gehören zu den gefragtesten Fachkräften auf dem deutschen Arbeitsmarkt, sind bisher jedoch kaum verfügbar. Unabhängig davon ob Sie erst in die Welt der Blockchain-Technologie eintauchen wollen, oder ob Sie bereits über ein fortschrittliches Wissen verfügen, bietet Ihnen die Blockchain Akademie umfangreiche Weiterbildungsmöglichkeiten. Absolvieren Sie anhand wissenschaftlicher Standards entwickelte Prüfungen, um hochwertige Zertifizierungen zum Nachweis Ihrer Fähigkeiten zu erlangen.

We are driven by our motivation for a digital public transport and fully dedicated to the bus and railway industry. Get in touch!

name: Bettercard
about:
Bettercard ist das auf Visa Business Cards spezialisierte Fintech. Wir haben die traditionelle Firmenkreditkarte neu gedacht und smart gemacht: Die Funktionen sind so flexibel, dass sie sich an die individuellen Bedürfnisse anpassen – egal ob Startup, Mittelständler, großer Betrieb oder Selbstständige. Mit dem inkludierten Bonusprogramm werden zudem Punkte gesammelt, ganz automatisch und ausnahmslos für jede Transaktion. 

Verwaltungs- und Buchhaltungsprozesse vereinfachen, Kosten senken, Transaktionen sicherer, transparenter und lohnender machen – die Idee von Bettercard ist, alles in einer Firmenkarte zu vereinen.
Heute hat jeder eine eigene Visa Firmenkarte: der Chef, die Mitarbeiter und auch jede Kostenstelle, mit individuellen Rechten und Budgets. Ab 0€ und ohne neues Bankkonto.

Wir sind Bettercard. Von Unternehmern für Unternehmer. Von Gründern für Gründer.

name: BIOMES
about:
Are you interested in strengthening your immune system and improving your digestion? You want to know why you feel tired, sleep badly or don't lose weight?

We at BIOMES aim to help you. 

Everyone seems to be talking about the microbiome these days. Not without reason, since now we know that we are only as well off as   our billions of bacteria inhabitants. With the help of our scientific self-testing kits, you can get to know your microbiome better. This will help you find out which adjustments you can make to better understand your health and feel perfectly fit and balanced.

As a fast-growing biotech startup, we analyse and interpret the human microbiome in unprecedented detail. In doing so, we examine the DNA of the bacteria that live in and on the human body. It turns out that our bacterial composition is as individual as a fingerprint.

Our scientists are experts in genomics – the next big thing in biotechnology. We combine state-of-the-art, high-throughput DNA sequencing with machine learning algorithms and the power of community to find significant patterns between DNA and microbiome profiles as well as lifestyle and health phenotypes. 

For our first BIOMES product INTEST.pro., a DNA-based gut microbiome analysis, send a tiny stool sample to our lab in Wildau, Germany. We extract the DNA, analyse it, and derive 100% evidence-based recommendations so you can take action and naturally restore the balance of your gut microbiome. INTEST.pro is available in the BIOMES online shop (www.biomes.world) or in selected pharmacies.

name: DropFriends
about:
Wir machen Jeden zum lieferdienstunabhängigen und bezahlten Paketshop - per Smartphone App.

Keine Warteschlangen vor DHL, Hermes, DPD, GLS und UPS Paketshops mehr. Nie wieder vor verschlossener Tür stehen, weil die Öffnungszeiten der Geschäfte überschritten sind. Keine überfüllten, kaputten oder schmutzigen Packstationen, die an irrelevanten Standorten platziert sind. 

Mithilfe der DropFriends-App (erhältlich im Google Play Store und App Store), unseren Online-Software-Produkten (SaaS) und unserer technischen Schnittstelle (Public API) entscheiden z.B. Besteller beim Shopping, wohin Pakete geliefert werden, wenn sie nicht zu Hause sind. Während des Einkaufs und nicht erst danach. Natürlich zustellerunabhängig und an relevante Standorte in der Nachbarschaft oder auf dem Heimweg. Kurze Wege sind King!

Wir entwickeln Online-Software, die es dem Einzelhandel und den Online-Händlern erlaubt Service- und Logistikkosten einzusparen, Retouren zu vermeiden, vorort unabhängig von gesetzlich vorgeschriebenen Öffnungszeiten zu sein und sichtbarer für Zielgruppen zu werden.

Endlich wird die Zustellung von Verkäufen für Verbraucher unkompliziert. Und das nur indem wir den Fokus vom Zustellmanagement von Kurieren, Boten und Lieferanten zum Empfangsmanagement setzen. Das spart für Shops Aufwand, Kosten und zwei Drittel CO2 pro Paketsendung. Da freut sich sogar die Umwelt. 

DropFriends bietet dies zu einer Zeit, in der mindestens 3,1 Mrd. Pakete in Deutschland verschickt, verarbeitet und zugestellt werden müssen. Alleine für das Jahr 2023 wird ein starker Anstieg auf 4,4 Mrd. Pakete prognostiziert: Das entspricht 25%.

name: eco.income engineering GmbH
about:
We are addressing the biggest and most urgent challenge of our time: Climate Change. We aim to help millions to easily track, better understand and finally reduce the personal consumption-based Climate Footprint. 

⚛️ For this we have developed the eco.income Climate Footprint Index, a world leading index solution to calculate the entire climate impact of our lives and consumption based on categorized spending transactions, for 40+ countries. We use the most sophisticated methods such as Environmentally extended Multi regional Input Output Analysis (EE-MRIOA) und Databases such as EXIOBASE.
➡️  Any Retail Bank or any other organization operating with payment transactions (and with a transaction categorization system in place) can offer science-driven and insightful Climate Footprint analytics to their customers with our solution. 
➡️ How? Simply license and download our data and do the calculations within your own system. Or integrate with our API. Based on our Index we provide the science-driven GHG intensities for any given categorization system (in kg CO2e/currency unit) with high-impact habit modifiers in relevant categories. In addition we provide curated content for climate action, i.e. generic climate insights and concrete tips with its reduction potential.
➡️  All that at easily affordable prices.

Sounds interesting? Get in touch! We'll be happy to answer your questions.

The market for contact lense solution is constantly growing and it´s volume is currenty USD 3 Mrd. Looking ahead, LENXBOX can easily be equipped with digital functionality, leveraging the potential of smart lenses - a market that is predicted to be > USD 10 Mrd in 2025.

name: Maon
about:
Decisions in energy markets are all about the future. But, the future is driven by a mix of uncontrolled factors such as climate change, public policy and innovative technologies. To make optimal decisions, complex outcomes need to be forecasted with speed and accuracy.

Forecasts represent a necessity for trader’s positions or investor’s evaluations of plants, consumers and sector couplings. Same applies to transmission grid operation and planning as well as topics of public interest like market design analysis or security of supply assessments.

As a result, we developed in 2018 the world’s first browser-based high spatial resolution electricity market model. The integrated simulation environment enables fast and cost-efficient in-depth market analysis without schooling and without any installation of hardware or software.

The unique platform supports users by parallel mobile workflows and instant visualizations. Ready-to-start input data with close-to-reality results enable immediate usage. Results like unit commitments and electricity prices can be analyzed rapidly via graphs and maps in the browser.

In high-stakes energy markets this gives a remarkable advantage. It predicts the future so it is possible to choose the right action in the right moment. Maon enables to make the most accurate and curtain decision possible within minutes knowing what to do and what not to do.

Before you commit to your next big decision: How confident are you that it is optimized to consider every factor and that you know all the possible future outcomes that could benefit you? Leading European transmission system operators and business consultants trust Maon to provide exceptional decision insights. We can do the same for you.

𝗨𝗻𝘀𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝗠𝗶𝘀𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻
Unser Ziel ist es, jedem Menschen die zahlreichen präventiven und therapeutischen Effekte des Fastens zugänglich & nutzbar zu machen.
Das Bedürfnis nach gesunder & nachhaltiger Ernährung sowie Lebensweise ist so groß wie nie, dabei sterben heutzutage mehr Menschen an den Folgen falscher Ernährung als Mangelernährung!

Heilfasten ist eine evidenzbasierte Prävention & Therapie für zahlreiche grassierende Leiden unserer Zeit: Diabetes, Bluthochdruck und Adipositas – die häufigsten Todesursachen falscher Ernährung!

Trotz eindeutiger Datenlage werden die vielseitigen und nachhaltigen Effekte des Fastens leider kaum genutzt. Für Patienten und Ärzte ist Heilfasten meist zu teuer & aufwendig – das wollen wir ändern!

𝗘𝗻𝘁𝗱𝗲𝗰𝗸𝗲 𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗛𝗲𝗶𝗹𝗳𝗮𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗻𝗯𝗼𝘅

𝗘𝗻𝘁𝗱𝗲𝗰𝗸𝗲 𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗳𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝗔𝗽𝗽

ODIN automatically measures particles, cells, droplets, algae, bacteria and droplets in microfluidic systems. Its smart algorithms provide more than 30 parameters of the object like size, circumference, aspect ratio or brightness and shows them in a user-friendly interface. ODIN can be easily set to differentiate objects and to control for example a sorting gate at high speeds and ultra-low latency. The application spectrum of our platform technology ranges from life sciences and medical research to environmental technology and materials science. Typical applications are cell analysis and differentiation, microfluidic system control and sorting, particle tracking and manufacturing process control.

Das Kassensystem soll dem Unternehmer die Sicherheit geben, die er braucht, um zukünftig auch gegen den Online-Wettbewerb bestehen zu können und sein Unternehmen besser zu kennen.

Die mobile Bedienoberfläche erlaubt eine wesentlich flexiblere Handhabung als ein klassisches System und ist so intuitiv konzipiert, dass sich jeder Mitarbeiter direkt zurechtfindet und kassieren kann. 

Mit seinem Kooperationspartner Seithe & Partner kann das Unternehmen auf über 25 Jahre Erfahrung im Bereich Softwareentwicklung für den Einzelhandel zurückgreifen. Entsprechend ist Sicherheit und Sorgfalt bei Tillhub oberstes Gebot. 

Das Kundenportfolio von Tillhub reicht vom kleinen Floristen, der die Einfachheit und Intuitivität der Bedienoberfläche schätzt, über den Bäcker, bei dem es oft schnell gehen muss, bis hin zum großen Filialisten, der zentral all seine Geschäfte managen möchte. 

Neben neuen Features plant Tillhub sich als elementarer Knotenpunkt im Handel zu festigen und immer mehr Einzelhändler, Dienstleister und Gastronomen dabei unterstützen, tolle Produkte zu verkaufen.

Die Vibrosonic GmbH ist ein Pionier der Medizintechnik, der sich darauf fokussiert, hörgeschädigten Menschen mehr Klangqualität zu bieten: Unsere Kerntechnologie, die Hörkontaktlinse®, ist der weltweit erste Hörgerätelautsprecher, der mittels Mikrosystemtechnik hergestellt und direkt auf dem Trommelfell platziert wird. Dadurch erfolgt die Klangübertragung durch direkte mechanische Stimulation des Gehörs. 
Ergebnisse zeigen, dass sehr tiefe und besonders hohe Töne abgedeckt werden können. Tiefe Töne sind beim Genuss von Musik entscheidend, weil der Klang dadurch satter wird. Hohe Töne zu hören, ist insbesondere für das Sprachverstehen wichtig. Unser Ziel ist, mit unserer Technologie das weltweit erste unsichtbare Hörgerät mit diesen besonderen Klangeigenschaften zu entwickeln.
Die Vibrosonic GmbH wurde 2016 in Mannheim, Deutschland, aus einer Forschungskooperation heraus gegründet.

It leverages state-of-the-art generative deep neural networks with in-built privacy mechanism to retain the valuable information while rendering the re-identification of any individual impossible. This way it provides as-good-as-real, yet fully anonymous data, that can be freely processed, analyzed and shared further.

Hos LegalHero stiller vi en platform til rådighed, hvor private såvel som virksomheder kan oprette sager og modtage kyndig juridisk rådgivning online. Rådgivningen leveres af LegalHeros jurister, der udgøres af nøje udvalgte juridiske eksperter, der er blandt de dygtigste indenfor deres områder.

Når du har oprettet en sag, vil du modtage tilbud fra én eller flere jurister. Tilbuddene vil indeholde en præcis beskrivelse af pris og dato for færdiggørelse. Alle tilbud er faste, så du slipper for ubehagelige overraskelser. Du vælger selv det bedste tilbud og rådgivningen kan gå i gang. 

LegalHeros rådgivningsplatform er udformet til at håndtere hele den juridiske sagsbehandling på den nemmest mulige måde. Det indebærer bl.a. muligheden for udveksling og sikker opbevaring af dokumenter samt chat-kommunikation.

Hos LegalHero kan du ligeledes tegnet et abonnent, der sikrer din virksomhed adgang til relevante juridiske dokumenter, gratis juridisk hotline og tilbud på større enkeltopgaver. Abonnementerne er tilpasset din virksomhed, så du aldrig får hverken mere eller mindre end hvad du har brug for. 

Hos LegalHero går vi højt op i sikkerhed og tryghed. Al data er krypteret og vores rådgivere er forsikrede gennem vores rådgiveransvarsforsikring. Du kan derfor trygt vælge LegalHero som din betroede rådgiver. 

Hos LegalHero er timeprisen kr. 1.796,- ekskl. moms.

FireBug, born in the UK in 2011 is the brainchild of South African fire specialist and entrepreneur Nicolas Link. It is and has always been Nick’s vision to create a company that provides the fire industry with high quality, efficient, cutting edge technology and products.



Pushing the boundaries of accepted practices and traditional products, FireBug, under Nick’s guidance, are committed to the research and development of unique technologies for the fire fighting industry. Through a dedicated development program the company specialises in harnessing the power and simplicity of the previously prohibited natural element ‘water’ in the extinguishing of all fires, including class B and class F fires.


Working in partnership with a number of British Fire Bridges and leading fire suppression experts, all products are tried and tested to the maximum, being designed, created and recreated until they are perfected. Specialist fire fighting equipment manufacturers.


Along with new and unique fire systems FireBug also support their customers with a comprehensive range of traditional product and technologies.


The FireBug team are dedicated and focused, committed to making the FireBug experience positive and enjoyable.  The team works with an elite number of customers to distribute their technologies through the United Kingdom, the Middle East, Europe and The Africas’.

We can guide you through your global mobility challenges, from relocating new hires to visa changes, postings and transfers between offices. We are a startup led by three female founders, we like to do things differently and we are always looking for people bringing new ideas and ways of thinking into the team. Get in touch if you are interested in joining us!

name: Claider
about:
Claider è la prima piattaforma Insurtech che permette una gestione digitale dei sinistri completa, dalla denuncia alla chiusura.

La piattaforma in cloud, fornisce servizi saas, digitalizza e ottimizza le attività degli assicurati e di tutti i gestori professionali ai sinistri: agenti, broker, addetti sinistri delle Compagnie, periti, amministratori condominiali, gestori flotte.

Per i professionisti l'adozione comporta un risparmio di costi del 97% e il taglio del 90% del tempo impiegato nella normale attività di gestione.

Le principali interfacce della piattaforma sono l'app mobile, dedicata all'assicurato e la web app, rivolta all'operatore professionale.

L'app mobile è tap & claim, clicca e denuncia. Consente all'utente di elaborare una denuncia in pochi clic, quando si verifica un incidente, guidandolo attraverso ogni fase: dall'identificazione dello scenario pertinente allo scatto delle foto più utili, anche dei documenti e dei dati necessari, fino all'invio in automatico della denuncia completa all'intermediario.

L'app mobile può essere utilizzata per qualsiasi sinistro, con qualsiasi polizza di qualunque Compagnia.

La web app è personalizzata per ogni categoria di professionisti. Consente la gestione digitale dei dati ricevuti e offre la possibilità di connettersi e collaborare su un ricco set di dati.

Claider espone API per lo scambio di dati.

La app è personalizzabile con il proprio logo ed è conforme al GDPR.

Smart data e l’Intelligenza Artificiale saranno presto disponibili, grazie alla gestione digitale delle denunce in tempo reale.

name: Ekkono Solutions
about:
Ekkono means *cognition*, and that’s what we add to the world of connected things (IoT). We make them smart through self-learning, anomaly detection, predictions of future faults, and by identifying what makes them work at an optimum and be more intuitive.

The unique component, based on seven years of machine-learning research at the University of Borås, is a small embedded Advanced Analytics software engine that we license (OEM) to software and hardware developers. Ekkono’s tiny footprint enables it to run on the actual device, i.e. do Edge Analytics. This applies even to small micro controller platforms at par with RaspberryPi/Arduino, and smartphones (iPhone, Android).

The result is personalized intelligence for ever individual unit, instant response, less data traffic, lower network load, and consistent functionality, even when losing connectivity to the Internet. This translates into money as you proactively avoid unscheduled maintenance (Predictive Maintenance), and by optimizing each asset’s performance. You upgrade your things from being connected to becoming smart. Ekkono’s solution increases data integrity by sending pre-processed instead of raw data, which is hard to interpret for a third party. It also makes your products more pleasant as they become more intuitive. By doing this on the actual device, you make better use of computing capacity; And by adding Ekkono’s crowdsourcing capabilities to cross-reference between multiple units, you make use of the intelligence of many.

name: Cargometer
about:
CARGOMETER - Frachtvermessung „on-the-fly“

CARGOMETER Dimension in Motion ist eine innovative und kostengünstige Lösung zur 3D-Frachtvermessung, die Ladegut direkt am fahrenden Gabelstapler „on-the-fly“ vermessen kann. Gegenüber der derzeit üblichen stationären Vermessung bietet CARGOMETER klare Vorteile für Spediteure und Frachtunternehmen:

- Maße, Volumen und Gewicht der Ladung werden erfasst und sind unmittelbar im TMS verfügbar. Bild, Video und ein vollständiger PDF-Report können außerdem im System Monitor über Internet abgerufen werden.

- Der Arbeitsfluss bleibt ohne Stopps erhalten. Eine Umstellung des terminalinternen Prozesses ist nicht notwendig – egal ob am Ladetor oder Portal vermessen wird.

- Die Nutzung der Hallenfläche wird optimiert, denn Platzbedarf für Anfahrtswege und Messstationen fallen weg.

- Umfassende Digitalisierung aller Maße als Grundlage für Industrie 4.0.


CARGOMETER wächst mit Ihnen

Das System „CARGOMETER Dimension in Motion“ basiert auf kostengünstiger Hardware - einem Sensorsystem direkt an Ladetoren oder Portalen - sowie einer durchdachten Software, die die Messergebnisse unmittelbar in das Kundensystem einspeist. CARGOMETER bietet zudem zahlreiche Zusatzmodule, die jederzeit zu- oder abgeschaltet werden können. Und wir arbeiten ständig an der Enwicklung weiterer Module, um auch in Zukunft Ihre Bedürfnisse abzudecken.

Ein Vermessungssystem – viele Möglichkeiten

Abgestimmt auf die Gegebenheiten beim Kunden bietet CARGOMETER individuell flexible Lösungen - egal ob Sie Frachten bei einzelnen Toren vermessen wollen oder Verladung über Portale betreiben oder beides kombinieren wollen.

Die Zukunft

Mit Verfügbarkeit der Volumeninformation kann außerdem erstmalig die Auslastung der europaweiten Stückgutnetzwerke auf Grundlage von realen Daten optimiert werden. Dies wird zu signifikanten Kosteneinsparungen und zu einer deutlichen Verringerung der Umweltbelastung führen.

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVhVl-gLwI6m16XhrpHIUpw

name: MatchX
about:
MatchX manufacturers superior LPWAN Hardware and Software, delivering comprehensive IoT Cloud and Reporting Solutions across diverse domains. 

At MatchX, the focus is to deliver a robust End-to-End IoT network solution that facilitates data transmission over ranges of up to 35 km using LPWAN (Low Power, Wide Area Network) technology. The package solution comprising hardware, software and cloud reporting offers a revolutionary breakthrough to the world's data needs, an end-to-end network solution that ensures increased data efficiency, increased data range, whilst reducing energy consumption and significantly reducing costs.

The MatchX system is plug and play and is equipped with the Listen-Before-Talk technology which enables data transmission only at the most opportune times in order to prevent data loss and network overcapacity. 

The MatchX gateway is the vehicle that supports this End-to-End encrypted data transmission and delivers it to the MatchX cloud in a consumable format. MatchX sensors support a battery life of 10 years and can operate in extreme temperatures. 

MatchX is disrupting the world of smart city planning with use-cases ranging from smart waste management to street lighting optimisation and air quality data collection. MatchX also finds applications in agriculture and logistics for location tracking, connecting devices and security. 

Join us in the IoT revolution as we seek to build a connected world through our commercially sustainable and scalable solutions. Visit www.matchx.io for more information!

about:

name: Kriptown
about:
📈 La Néo-Bourse des startups et des PME ! 

➡️Kriptown apporte une solution innovante, simple, rapide et à faible coût aux start-up qui souhaitent lever des fonds, tout en touchant une base d’investisseurs large et diversifiée. Elle permet aussi à toute personne physique ou morale issue de l'Union Européenne d’investir en euros de façon liquide. 

Grâce à l’utilisation de sa blockchain privée, Kriptown démocratise l’accès aux levées de fonds en fournissant pour chaque levée un whitepaper standardisé sur l'entreprise (inspiré du prospectus AMF) validé par trois tiers de confiance. Une fois la levée finalisée, les investisseurs peuvent acheter ou revendre leurs tokens sur la plateforme de Kriptown, ces tokens étant liés à la valeur des parts de l’entreprise qui a levé des fonds.

Kriptown est ainsi une nouvelle forme d’investissement que l’on a nommé ITO ▶️pour Initial Token Offering. Cet ITO s’inspire des IPO (entrées en Bourse), et entend conserver les avantages des ICO tout en se prémunissant contre leurs nombreux désavantages (majorité d'arnaques, risque de blanchiment d'argent, etc), en apportant ainsi liquidité, fiabilité, transparence et éthique dans la pratique.

Unterstützung bei der Absatzfinanzierung

Cycling is more than just a means of transportation

Cycling is great for your mind and your body. Taking your bike also improves local air quality and reduces carbon emissions. “I’m a big fan. Don’t know how you do it but the mapping and planning is great, and best of all gets us off busy roads. Our way experience has been great. Keep up the good work!”

about:
Clue is the #1 doctor-recommended period & cycle tracking app available on iOS, Android, and Apple Watch. Across the globe, more than 10 million active users rely on Clue to help understand their bodies better and keep their data safe and private.

Clue’s mission is for women and people with cycles to make good choices for themselves, and live full lives not in spite of their biology, but in tune with it. Clue was founded in 2012 by a Danish female entrepreneur, Ida Tin, who is convinced that technology will profoundly change the future of family planning.

The app calculates and predicts users’ periods and PMS based on users’ data and calculates fertility windows based on global averages, which can be made more accurate by users’ entering ovulation test data. Their newest offering, Clue Plus, aims to make Clue accessible to as many people as possible around the world at only one euro (or the local currency equivalent) per month. Clue Plus offers enhanced Analysis and personalized predictions for cycle-related symptoms with Forecast.

Clue launched helloclue.com in February 2018 to help close the knowledge gap about the menstrual cycle—with information that’s accessible, serious, scientific, and empathetic.

Numerous major media have greatly praised Clue, including TechCrunch (“Clue is the most underrated app ever”), BuzzFeed, Wired (“Hottest Startups 2015”), Cosmopolitan (“We love Clue”) and The Huffington Post (“Awesome”). 
The Berlin-based startup has the backing of prestigious investors such Union Square Ventures; Mosaic Ventures; Groupe Arnault, the controlling shareholder of LVMH Moët Hennessy - Louis Vuitton; Brigitte Mohn of Bertelsmann; and entrepreneurs from Spotify, SoundCloud and Dropbox.

Products include Vaultoro Trading; the world’s first gold-hedging solution, the Glass Books Transparency Protocol and Bar9, a gold savings account. 

To date, more than two tons of gold (with a current value of 95 million dollars) have been traded on Vaultoro, whose head offices are located in the UK. The start-up currently has more than 31,000 customers from over 95 countries.

Founded by Philip Scigala and Joshua Scigala, Vaultoro’s management team includes Laurin Bylica (former Financial Analyst at Block.one), Ana Valdes (London School of Economics).

Vaultoro is backed by Techstars, Finlab AG, and more recently by the Dash DAO, who invested in the development of the market’s first Dash to physical gold pair.

name: Risk42
about: Risk42 offered a sophisticated risk management platform for E-Commerce, Financial Services and Banks. Use cases include risk assessment of payment transactions and risk based evaluation of account openings and credit applications. The Risk42 business was sold to @Unzer in April 2020.

name: Budge
about:
Philanthropy is at an inflection point, with Generation Y finding traditional means of giving to be tedious, boring, dated and time consuming.  It's time for real change!

Budge provides a mobile app that enables people to create challenges with friends and raise money for causes at the same time. We also offer a unique and compelling marketing platform that allows corporations to hold CSR campaigns for and sponsor non-profit organizations.

More information on Budge can be found at: http://www.fundable.com/budge

Budge is fun. 
Challenges can be anything from eating as many sushi rolls as possible in a minute, doing a silly dance on the street or participating in a fun run.

Budge targets Gen Y. 
Generation Y is the most educated, tech-profcient, and soon-to-be largest American generation ever.

Budge is social. 
Fully integrated into Facebook, so that challenges can be shared, charities get exposure and the viral nature of social media takes over.

Budge is Gamified. 
For every donation made, users receive points and badges as a reward. Badges can be redeemed for discounts or prizes with participating sponsors.

Budge is disruptive. 
We overcome the traditional roadblocks to philanthropy by inspiring people to use their regular daily activities and interactions as a means to donate to causes they feel passionate about.

name: Morpher
about:
Morpher is a trading platform on the Ethereum blockchain that fixes trading and investing. Morpher empowers its users to trade unlimited assets with zero fees and infinite liquidity. 

Morpher’s fractional trading capabilities makes the financial markets accessible. Trade stocks in pre-market, weekends, holidays, and everything in between.

Only with Morpher can you short Tesla with just $1 on a lazy Sunday afternoon.

name: Andersen EV
about:
We are UK producers of smart charge points for electric vehicles. Scandinavian-inspired, we blend product design and 75 years of class-leading technical expertise. 

Our signature features include a great solution that hides the cable and plug from sight. All our intelligent electric car charging points allow you to monitor your vehicle charging progress and track your energy usage.

Our clients enjoy using the online configurator to design their own charge point. With a multitude of colours and finish combinations, you can be sure to find one that suits your home and style. Andersen EV charge points are worth driving home to. 

Get started on your design today!

name: REMMEDVR
about:
RemmedVR, telemedyczna usługa terapii widzenia z użyciem wirtualnej rzeczywistości.
Problem niedowidzenia oraz zeza dotyczy nawet do 5% dzieci na świecie. Zbyt późno wykryte lub nieleczone skutkują w poważnych problemach z nauką, koordynacją ruchową, braku chęci do kontaktów towarzyskich, co może prowadzić do zaniżonej samooceny, niepełnosprawności i depresji w dorosłym życiu. Misją RemmedVR jest wyrównywanie szans rozwoju dzieci z wadami wzroku na całym świecie.

name: Zwopr UG
about:
Wir bringen hilfsbereite Menschen und ihre individuellen Fähigkeiten zusammen, um damit den Einzelnen und somit die gesamte Gesellschaft zu stärken.

WIE GEHT DAS?
Mit Zwopr haben wir eine intuitive App entwickelt, die Nachbarn und Kolleg:innen nutzen, um sich gegenseitig beim Meistern von Alltagsaufgaben zu helfen. Wer Hilfe erhält, kann Danke sagen mit dem Pflanzen von Bäumen.

Wer bei Zwopr aktiv wird, kann sowohl Helfer für die Community sein als auch Klimaschützer durch das Pflanzen von Bäumen. Anstelle der Bezahlung, bedankt man sich durch Klimaschutz. Dazu haben wir das Zwopr Aufforstungs- und Klimaschutzprogramm ins Leben gerufen. Jeder virtuell gekaufte Baum wird somit auch im echten Leben gepflanzt.

WAS SIND ZWOPR FIRMEN-CHANNELS?
Mit einem eigenen Firmen-Channel in der Zwopr App können sich Kolleg:innen gegenseitig bei Alltagsaufgaben unterstützen. Außerdem können sich Mitarbeitende im Channel zu einem Drink nach der Arbeit oder gemeinsamen sportlichen Aktivitäten verabreden.

name: Ozon.io
about:
OZON is a high-tech startup that uses all its expertise to solve a global problem: the insecurity of SMEs facing cyber risks. SMBs are very vulnerable targets to cyber attacks from a technical and financial point of view.
* OZON is a unique all-in-one Internet cybersecurity solution designed for SMBs around the world.
* OZON's cloud platform delivers cyber prevention and cyber protection services in minutes to fight all Internet cyber threats, hackers and fraudsters.
* OZON's solution combined high-grade cybersecurity technologies, automated processes and human expertise for SMB immediate, transparent and continuous protection.

name: Myego
about: myEGO  ist  eine  digitale,  blockchain-basierte  Plattform  für  Selbstbestimmtes  Identitätsmanagement  (SSI), d.h.  der  Nutzer  kann  den  Besitz  seiner  personenbezogenen  Daten  kontrollieren  und  bestimmen,  an  wen und welche Informationen mit Dritten geteilt werden sollen. Die einzelnen Datenpunkte einer Person – seine Identität  (z.B.  Personalausweis,  Führerschein,  Bankinformationen,  etc.)  werden  durch  die  myEGO  Plattform verifiziert,  validiert  oder  durch  Dritte  attestiert.  Unser  Verständnis  basiert  auf  der  Idee  offener, sicherer und nutzerzentrierter Ökosysteme – myEGO  revolutioniert  so die  Kundenbeziehung  zwischen Kunden   und   Unternehmen   durch   einen   innovativen   und   nachhaltigen   Onboarding-Ansatz.   Die Mehrfachverwendung  der  (verifizierten)  Benutzerdatenbestände  können  über  Ökosysteme  und  Dienste hinweg  verknüpft  und  so  Datensilos  eliminiert  werden.

name: Inzmo
about: Berlin-headquartered insurtech INZMO aims to simplify the insurance process with its full-stack platform combining all steps from purchasing a policy to filing a claim in a user-friendly, digital-first manner. The startup focuses on B2B2C solutions across multiple verticals from consumer electronics and bike insurance to rental deposit insurance. It is backed by respected early stage VC firm Change Ventures and Swiss insurance leader, Helvetia. In 2017, INZMO was recognised as the best Fintech startup in Europe by the European Commission. The company also received the prestigious Insurance Shaper of the Year 2019 award at EXECinsurtech and has been listed as one of the Top100 Global Insurtech companies.

name: Surfly
about:
Surfly is a high-growth interaction middleware player that can share, secure, and transform web experiences. We’re on a mission to create (and be) the next wave of online interactions, currently powering online in-person experiences for 200,000+ users worldwide.

Our solution enables anyone to add a collaborative layer to any web application without having to modify or change the original application. Leading organizations use Surfly to accelerate remote deal-closing, collaborate better with seamless functionality, and engage with their own customers in a more efficient and meaningful way. 

Backed by powerful technology and API-first approach, Surfly’s industry-leading Co-browsing product recreates an in-person experience as part of a digital customer journey, and helps companies thrive in the era of digital transformation and remote service distribution. With Surfly, you can innovate online interactions in real-time, however you want, without creating cumbersome integrations or continually adding complex and costly technology.

A Surfly Session is equipped with co-browsing, video & voice chat, secure e-signing, responsive document annotation and completion, file sharing, and more. Our customers can use the technology on its own, integrate with their own tool stack, or even build on top of it to gain a competitive advantage, innovate faster, and elevate their customers’ experiences.

Surfly is built to meet the highest security standards and regulations— it’s compliant by design. The entire Surfly Session has been developed to act as infrastructure, with information only passing through but never stored. And when no data is stored, no data can be lost. This enables us to be ISO 27001, HIPAA, PCI DSS, AICPA SOC, and GDPR compliant.

We are hiring: https://jobs.surfly.com

name: ETFmatic
about:
ETFmatic provides you with an easy way to manage your investment goals. We use index based investment strategies and Exchange Traded Funds (ETFs) to construct and manage unique investment portfolios tailored to your personal preferences and circumstances.

We are an European Automated Investment Service licensed by the Financial Conduct Authority. With our App and the Investment Engine behind it you can easily build a unique portfolio instead of being stuffed into high-fee cookie-cutter portfolios dressed up as a personalised service. ETFmatic is lead by a team of experienced entrepreneurs that believe we all deserve a simple and cost effective way to put our savings to work. Our Advisory Board includes Private Banking and Fund Management Executives from the Financial Industry and Professors from the most prestigious Business Schools.

At ETFmatic we believe risk amounts to more than the expected fluctuations of a portfolio. The likelihood of you accessing part of your savings early or how you will react to a scary market movement is at least as important as the criteria employed to analyse the stock market’s performance.

The current version of our investment platform deploys 125 base portfolio strategies which are then time-adjusted reducing volatility and adapting the asset allocation to what makes you comfortable, essentially infinite portfolios that enable us to deliver the best investment solution for you. Beyond the adjustment if anything in your lifestyle or attitude to risk changes, by using dynamic targets and, in goals with target date, volatility reduction, the target weight for each asset evolves over time.

Investing in stocks & bonds puts capital at risk. ETFmatic Ltd is a Discretionary Investment Manager authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (No. 657261) and office at Google Campus, 4-5 Bonhill Street, EC2A 4BX, London, United Kingdom. Robo Advisor does not imply we provide advice.

name: trbo
about: Munich-based trbo GmbH is one of the leading technology providers for dynamic on-site personalization, optimization and testing. Founded in 2013, the company's data-driven onsite personalization platform provides an all-in-one solution to create, dynamically play out and measure personalized experiences for each individual visitor - onsite, in real time and fully automated. The self-learning algorithm analyzes user behavior on the basis of more than 50 visitor characteristics. This data then enables a targeted delivery of various layers in the design of the online presence, which demonstrably optimize the shopping experience for website visitors. Among trbo's customers are Ströer, Telefónica, limango, Galeria Kaufhof, FTI Touristik, mydays, Triumph and Thomas Cook AG. trbo GmbH is run by Felix Schirl.

name: Qivos
about:
Qivos is a marketing technology agency that creates loyalty through customer data intelligence and machine learning, delivering measurable results to our clients. 

By collecting data in-store and online, Qivos builds unified customer profiles. We manage to leverage customer data and offer personalized experiences to consumers with advanced marketing technology solutions powered by machine learning. Through Qivos Cloud, we help our clients reach, connect, and delight their customers faster and more accurately. As a result, we drive customer lifetime value and contribute significantly to brands' profitability.

Qivos Cloud is a (SaaS) Customer Data and Loyalty Platform that enables marketers to identify shoppers in the real world, analyze their behavior, and connect with them in real-time like the way they do in the digital world.

Our headquarters are based in Athens, Greece, and we serve clients from various industries in 8 countries.

name: Wowworks
about:
Wowworks is a highly innovative, web and mobile-based facility service provider operating in Europe now. 

Wowworks is not a yet another software-based FM-solution. Unlike anyone else in the market, we extend our service all the way through to the actual job completion.

The service is provided by using the crowdsourcing online platform software designed by Wowworks for facility managers, employees of facility management departments, technicians, and real estate managers working in medium to large enterprises. It’s a reliable solution that enables the real estate occupiers including retail chains, supermarkets, banking, insurance, real estate owners etc.  who has to repair and maintain to do it fast and cost effective without any fix costs. 
The platform  combines simplicity in using and power to help users accomplish facility operations with maximum efficiency. 

Wowworks is a robust facility management solution that delivers valuable benefits to midsized and large B2B businesses. 

Overview of Wowworks’ Benefits for the customer: 

- Place your order for repair and forget about it - we take over all the job until it is done
- Cost and time-consuming complex processes that are automated 
- Qualified, by customer assessed craftsmen 
- Pay only for the real job done - no fix costs, no month fee 
- One contract  - nationwide coverage. We are your contract partner with full responsibility. 
               
Combination of app, web portal and API integration enables a variety of communication and control options, makes things move fast and save on all stages. 
- Online platform is simple to use 
- Interface to the customer's ERP system possible                
- Mobile app for craftsmen 
- Portal solutions
- Analytics and reporting
- AP invoicing

More than  47000 craftsmen.   
85000 tasks a year.     
Even localities with

name: XOM Materials
about:
XOM Materials ist eine Online-Plattform für den Handel mit Werkstoffen wie Stahl, Metall und Kunststoff. Sie umfasst Beschaffungs- und Verkaufslösungen, mit denen Käufer und Verkäufer, die sich zukunftssicher aufstellen wollen, sofort starten können. XOM ermöglicht Kunden eine einfache Digitalisierung, ohne in eigene Lösungen investieren zu müssen. Gegründet 2017 in Berlin, unterhält XOM Büros in Berlin, Duisburg und Atlanta. Das Unternehmen beschäftigt über 60 Mitarbeiter.  

XOM Materials is the go-to online platform for buying and selling materials such as steel, metals, and plastics. It provides ready-made procurement and sales solutions, eliminating the cost of digitization for buyers and sellers aiming to future-proof their business. XOM enables users to go digital painlessly, without investing in developing an in-house platform. Founded in Berlin in 2017, XOM operates from offices in Berlin, Duisburg and Atlanta and employs more than 60 people.

name: EverReal
about:
EverReal ist die erste und einzige Immobiliensoftware für Prozessoptimierung bei Mieterwechsel und Verkauf.

Im Vermietungsprozess automatisiert EverReal bereits alle Workflows von A bis Z. Die Mietinteressenten verwalten die Besichtigungstermine und die Unterlagenabgabe selbst im Portal. Dadurch schaffen professionelle Immobilienunternehmen mit vorhandenen Personal- und Zeitressourcen mehr Vermietungen und haben Zeit und Energie, ihren Auftraggebern und Mietern die qualitativ beste Dienstleistung zu gewährleisten.

Heute verfügt EverReal über einen Kundenstamm, der mehr als 500.000 Wohneinheiten in den Bereichen Wohnen, Gewerbe, Bestand oder Neubau in der DACH Region verwaltet.

name: Insert Coin
about:
Insert Coin provides world-renowned expertise and a leading gamification platform that helps companies achieve sustainable digital growth by improving key metrics such as engagement, retention, and churn.

With customers such as Storytel, Forza Football, and Raiffeisen Bank, we engage more than 10 million users globally. Insert Coin’s platform is resource-effective, quick to implement, and easy to manage for our clients. The power of AI combined with our science department guarantees scientifically proven and sustainable gamification.

For more information visit www.insertcoin.se

We offer a German made & hosted DAST scanner that integrates well in agile software development. Our scanner outperforms competitors for javascript applications & Rest APIs.

Our customers save up to 40% of their manual pentesting budget and never release untested software.
