about:
We help world-class developers to find full-time remote jobs 🏆. For companies, it is free to come and browse pre-vetted, remote developers. The future of work is remote, come and be part of it.

🚀 Backed by APX Ventures

name: IVE.ONE
about:
iVE.ONE is an infrastructure that enables banks, corporates, asset managers  and investment companies access to a modernised financial market with compliant digital securities and cryptocurrencies. iVE.ONE’s trusted Regulatory Engine enables compliant digital asset transactions in the primary and secondary market. The infrastructure is used by banks and by partnering with exchanges, securities brokerages, crypto custodian, iVE.ONE is coming closer to their vision of a new financial market - Better Digital Assets for Everyone. 

iVE.ONE is backed by block.one in collaboration with C3 Management GmbH, tokentus Investment AG, High-Tech Gründerfonds, CVVC AG and a business angel.

name: Trustless.ai
about:
Between Zurich, Rome and Washington DC, we are building an ultra-secure 2mm-thin personal computer - carried in a leather wallet and later embedded in the back of your next smartphone - that will bring unimagined freedom, control, and peace of mind to the private digital lives of millions of persons that are most targeted for profit or political motives, and their close associates.

We achieve such levels of security by uniquely ensuring extreme levels of “ethically-aligned” security review in relation to complexity - for all techs and processes critically involved in the life-cycle, including for legitimate lawful access - as verified by the Trustless Computing Certification Body, launched last June by the NGO from which we spun off.

name: Codacy
about:
Codacy is an automated code review tool that helps identify issues through static code analysis. Integrating seamlessly into workflows, Codacy helps engineering teams save time in code reviews and tackle technical debt.  
Users receive notifications on security issues, code coverage, code duplication and code complexity in every commit and pull request along with advanced code metrics on the health of a project and team performance.
Codacy supports 40 coding languages and is available in free open-source, and enterprise versions (cloud and self-hosted).  For more see https://www.codacy.com/

name: Wevest Digital
about: Based in Berlin, BLOXXON AG offers institutional investors and financial service providers product solutions and API-services for digital assets in the core business areas of custody (safekeeping of digital assets), tokenization (issuance of digital securities) and asset servicing (trading, reporting, access to trading venues). Kapilendo Custodian AG (provisionally approved §32 KWG crypto custodian) and Kapilendo Invest AG remain as subsidiaries.

name: Cosuno
about:
Cosuno entwickelt Software für die Baubranche. Mit knapp 2 Millionen Beschäftigten und fast 400 Milliarden Euro Bauvolumen ist das Baugewerbe in Deutschland ein bedeutender Wirtschaftszweig. Die Digitalisierung treibt die Produktivität vieler Wirtschaftsbereiche bereits voran, allerdings gibt es im Baugewerbe Nachholbedarf.

Wir wollen die Digitalisierung in der Baubranche vorantreiben und beschäftigen uns täglich damit, wie Generalunternehmern, Bauträgern und Architekten die Herausforderungen im Ausschreibungsprozess durch Digitalisierung besser meistern können. 

Probleme wie mühsames Versenden vieler E-Mails, unkoordiniertes Sammeln von Angeboten und mangelhafte Übersicht bei deren Vergleich werden durch unsere intuitive Software gelöst. 

Unsere Kunden profitieren von 30% mehr Angeboten bei Ausschreibungen, gesteigerter Transparenz beim Einkauf von Nachunternehmern und Materialien und haben nachweislich geringere Prozesskosten. 
Ein übersichtlicher Ausschreibungsprozess und die Möglichkeit alle relevanten Baudokumente an einem Ort zu verwaltet sorgt für mehr Effizienz bei Bauvorhaben und eine bessere Rendite.

Und das ist erst unser Anfang. Ziel ist es den Wandel der Baubranche mit innovativen Verfahren und digitalen Prozessen stetig voranzutreiben und  weiterhin einfache und transparente Lösungen zu entwickeln und diese kontinuierlich zu verbessern.

name: Hotelbird
about:
Hotelbird has transformed the guest experience in hospitality. With over 70.000 hotels rooms is Hotelbird the leading check-in/out platform in Europe. 

Our mission is to provide the core technology for a seamless digital guest journey and empower hosts to increase their operational success. 

Our technology platform gives every hotel total flexibility at the reception and saves an enormous amount of time and money by automating the check-in/out processes. As Europe’s market leader, we work with hotel companies like Achat Hotels, Amano Hotels, Amaron Hotels, Arcotel Hotels, Azimut Hotels, Best Western Hotels, Deutsche Hospitality, Dorint Hotels & Resorts, Flemings Hotels, Gorgeous Smiling Hotels, InterContinal Hotels & Resorts, Intercity Hotels, Leonardo Hotels, Lindner Hotels, Meininger Hotels, Novum Hospitality, Super8 Hotels and other hotel groups.

name: HandEX
about:
HandEX is revolutionising the export finance market by using leading technology, to revamp processes and make it as easy as possible for exporters and importers alike to access the financing they need for international trade. 

The platform provides German SMEs with export credit up to EUR 5 M ("Small-Tickets") with a particular focus on exports to emerging markets.

HandEX facilitates and integrates the issuance of export loans and export insurance covers, including guarantees issued by the German government, for which the export credit agency Euler Hermes is mandated.

name: EMIL
about: EMIL hilft Versicherungen bestehende Portfolios günstiger zu verwalten und neue Produkte in kurzer Zeit auf den Markt zu bringen. Die EMIL Group ist ein Technologieunternehmen aus Berlin und bietet eine proprietäre "no-code" Bestandsverwaltung für Versicherer. Die Plattform  deckt die gesamte Wertschöpfungskette von Sachversicherungen ab und wird von europäischen Versicherungsunternehmen lizenziert, um bestehende Portfolios günstiger zu verwalten und innovative Produkte schneller zu launchen. Durch die Software profitieren Versicherern von mehr Flexibilität und einem schnelleren Go-to-Market, was zu einer deutlichen Reduktion der Gesamtbetriebskosten (Total Cost of Ownership) führt. Die Software unterscheidet sich von bestehenden Lösungen für Kernversicherungssoftware, indem es sich um eine "no-code"-Plattform handelt: Integration, Produktanpassungen, Underwriting, Pricing etc. können von der Fachabteilung der Versicherung eigenständig und ohne Hinzunahme von IT-Ressourcen konfiguriert und verändert werden.

name: Copytrack
about:
What we stand for:
Our service is designed for anyone who makes images available on the Internet. These images are stolen countless times every day, illegally copied, and often used commercially.

The authors suffer enormous financial damage as a result of a lack of income.

Currently, there is very little one can do as a copyright holder. Copyright infringements are difficult to trace and are considered a trivial offense. In addition to the time required to find and punish a copyright infringement, proceedings always involve a legal risk.

With Copytrack we want to reduce these unsettling circumstances and provide our customers with a tool that they can use to assert their claims easily and without risk.

We offer our service free of charge and bear all the costs of the proceedings. Only in case of success do we retain a commission. A fair agreement of all sides is our first priority.

name: Blockbonds
about:
In a world where 1.7 billion people are still unbanked, SPENN Technology has democratized access to financial markets by bridging the crypto sphere with traditional finance. By utilizing blockchain technology Blockbonds has created a robust real-time payment system in which everyone can manage their savings, payments, investments and loans in an honest, transparent and secure way through the SPENN App platform. Although SPENN Technology A/S is a purpose-driven company with our vision to empower people, we are also a commercial player that always strives to develop new services for our customers.

The SPENN app is an innovative and unique digital banking platform for the unbanked as well as the banked to be able to send and receive money completely cost-free, in markets where the cost of financial services is the highest in the world. SPENN is disrupting the existing mobile payment distribution channels. SPENN has recently launched new integrated services in the platform and expects to launch more crypto services going forward.

SPENN is a technology provider to banks and governments based on a Software as a Service (SaaS) solution and has grown to become a key partner for their bank partners to drive deposits and to stay in front of innovation. SPENN is helping governments regulate the unregulated utilizing new technology and visionary ideas which have ultimately solved the biggest issue within financial inclusion.

name: heyData
about:
heyData ist ein Team engagierter Datenschützer. Wir helfen Unternehmen, mit Datenschutzgesetzen compliant zu werden - und wissen, wie Unternehmer denken. Profitiert von unserem praxisnahen Wissen! Bei uns erhaltet ihr ganz sicher keine lebensfremden Datenschutztipps. Unser oberstes Ziel ist es, mit unserer Expertise unseren Kunden ihre Datenschutzsorgen abzunehmen. So können sich unsere Kunden voll auf die Bereiche ihrer eigenen Expertise konzentrieren, an ihren eigenen Produkten und Dienstleistungen arbeiten - und DSGVO-Bußgelder vermeiden. 

In unserer DSGVO-as-a-Service-Plattform haben unsere Kunden einfachen Zugriff auf ihre Datenschutzdokumente und können direkt mit uns in Kontakt treten. Zugleich fungieren wir als externe Datenschutzbeauftragte und stehen unseren Kunden in jeder Datenschutzfrage zur Seite. 

Wir freuen uns, von dir zu hören! Besuch einfach unsere Website www.heydata.eu, um mehr über das Thema Datenschutz oder unsere Leistungen zu erfahren.

name: QuoScient
about:
Built by operators for operators, QuoScient supports customers across all industries against digital threats of all kinds.

QuoScient has been founded in April 2016 in Frankfurt am Main (Germany), Fabien Dombard (co-founder and CEO) and Ioannis Bizimis (Co-founder and CFO). 

Since March 2020 QuoScient has officially spun off its three business lines into separate entities to give each more focus and increased operational flexibility. These new companies will carry forward the product (QuoLab Technologies), threat-intelligence service (QuoIntelligence) and services (QuoSec) lines. QuoScient GmbH will continue as a business enabler for these new entities in the future.

For further questions please contact us at: +49 69 33 99 79 38 or curious@quoscient.io.

name: Tenzir
about:
Tenzir is an ambitious startup with the vision to substantially improve the security of computer networks. Our primary focus lies on network forensics: the systematic investigation of cyber attacks with big data analytics. Right now, we are building the next-generation solution to empower cyber security teams: intelligent decision support and automated forensic capabilities to defend against the complex threat landscape of tomorrow.

Our current mission involves transforming a research prototype, developed by one of Tenzir’s co-founders during his PhD program at UC Berkeley, into a full-fledged product for commercial use. The goal is to enable security teams to quickly locate attacks, analyze them interactively, and then neutralize them in a targeted fashion. This is how we help reduce the billions of dollars in damages annually which result from industrial espionage, data exfiltration, and insider abuse.

Legal Notice: https://tenzir.com/legal-notice/
Privacy Statement: https://tenzir.com/privacy-statement/

Brokers and agents are not engaging with this new class of insurance yet. CyberDirekt offers digital sales solutions for brokers to support cyber insurance sales, including lead generation, risk assessment, advisory, application process, pricing and immediate underwriting.  

Moreover, SME customers have a limited awareness for their own vulnerability concerning cyber-attacks. CyberDirekt offers a broad range of security awareness training which are offered free of charge and without constraints to their insurance customers.

name: Acatus
about:
Acatus GmbH was founded in September 2016 by Dr. Marie Louise Seelig and Dr. Daniel Wigbers and is building the first digital pan-European Debt Capital Markets (DCM) platform. Through the innovative instrument of digital single asset securitization, Acatus converts loans and other illiquid assets into fungible securities eligible for safe custody. For banks and other originators, Acatus offers a fast and cost-efficient refinancing option via the capital markets. For institutional investors such as family offices or pension funds, Acatus offers attractive investment opportunities à la carte in previously illiquid debt products. Since October 2018, the digital DCM platform has been live and transactions are taking place.

Acatus is based in Berlin and currently has 15 employees. The company is supported by renowned investors such as Partech, Berliner Effektengesellschaft and Berliner Volksbank Ventures as well as numerous business angels from the capital markets, securities and tech sectors. These include former bank directors, partners in management consultancies and commercial law firms, university professors and successful fintech founders. Acatus won the startup pitch of EXECfintech in 2018 and came 3rd place in the KPMG Smart Start Award 2017. The company is a member of the Association of German Banks, the Federal Association of German Startups and the digital association Bitkom.

name: Network Insight
about:
Next Generation Social Intelligence - Creating Value From Insights

INNOVATIVE ANALYSE VON NETZWERKEN

Mit tagtäglich zahllosen neuen Beiträgen in Social Media wird es immer schwieriger, die Bedürfnisse und Vorlieben der Kunden zu verstehen. Wir helfen Ihnen, Ihre Zielgruppe online zu finden und Ihren Puls zu fühlen – Finden Sie heraus, worüber Ihre Zielgruppe spricht, was sie emotional bewegt, und passen Sie Ihre Marketingstrategie entsprechend an!
Zudem verliert das klassische Online-Marketing immer mehr an Boden gegenüber neuen Formen der Marken- und Produktwerbung. Traditionelles Influencer-Marketing übergibt die Marketingaktivitäten an einflussreiche Konsumenten. Allerdings ist es oft noch unausgereift. Wir berücksichtigen ganzheitliche Netzwerkstrukturinformationen bei der Bewertung wirklich einflussreicher Konsumenten. Wir glauben, dass gutes Influencer-Marketing auf Authentizität, wissenschaftlichem Denken und Vertrauen basiert.

Was wir machen:

Audience Insights and Social Listening
Finden Sie Ihre Zielgruppe auf Social Media und gewinnen Sie datengetriebene Einblicke darüber – welche Themen treiben die Diskussion? Was beschäftigt die Nutzer? Wie ist ihre Stimmung? Hören Sie in Social Media-Kanäle herein und erfahren Sie, wie Konsumenten Ihre Marke und Produkte wahrnehmen.

Influential Content Marketing
Nutzen Sie unsere Kooperationen mit exklusiven Plattformen, die sich durch äußerst homogene Audiences auszeichnen, um inhaltlich fokussierte Kampagnen mit hohem Engagement durchzuführen. Lassen Sie kraftvolle Stimmen die Botschaft Ihrer Marke verbreiten.

name: InstaFreight GmbH
about:
InstaFreight is a leading LogTech company that revolutionizes how overland transports are done today. The majority of the industry is still very much offline with email and telephone communication being a major channel for coordination. The result is ~30% empty runs and a lack of transparency on operational performance as well as cost. With digital innovation, InstaFreight creates efficiency and transparency along the transport chain and reduces empty runs. 
For shippers, InstaFreight offers two services: Freight Forwarding and Transport Management. InstaFreight’s self-developed platform enables shippers to save direct & indirect costs and to gain visibility on operational, financial and sustainability-related performance. Learn more: instafreight.com/shippers
For carriers, InstaFreight offers suitable long-term business as well as spot loads to optimize fleet utilization while paying fast and reliably at attractive freight rates. Learn more: carrier.instafreight.com

Join our team:
Ready to innovate a challenging market of 350 billion euros? Let's go!
We are looking for the brightest minds to shape the future of road freight. Experts from all fields and young talents are a great mix to get great things moving. Are you ready to change gears and take the next step in your career? Check out our open positions!
instafreight.de/talent

name: Rehago.eu
about:
Virtual Reality Training für halbseitig Gelähmte #eHealth #Training #Schlaganfall

Allein in Deutschland werden jährlich etwa 500.000 Menschen NEU mit einer halbseitigen Lähmung (Hemiparese) diagnostiziert. 

Das entspricht fast einem neuen Betroffenen pro Minute!

Weltweit sind das hochgerechnet um die 25 Millionen Menschen. 

Damit gehen erhebliche Einschränkungen im Alltag einher: 
die Betroffenen haben Probleme sich selbständig anzuziehen und zu versorgen. 
Sie können ihren Hobbys, Arbeit und Sozialleben nicht mehr wie gewohnt nachgehen.

Der wichtigste Faktor für einen erfolgreichen Wiedereinstieg in ein eigenständiges Leben ist ein konsequentes und intensives Training. 

Die begrenzten Ressourcen in unserem Gesundheitssystem reichen jedoch nicht für ein hochintensives Training zur optimalen Genesung aus. Die Möglichkeiten für das Heimtraining sind langweilig, demotivierend oder viel zu teuer.

Rehago ermöglicht weltweit Millionen halbseitig gelähmten Menschen den Wiedereinstieg in ein eigenständiges Leben zu beschleunigen. 

Mit modernen Virtual Reality Spielen bieten wir den Betroffenen ein unabhängiges, günstiges und motivierendes Training und ermutigen sie regelmäßig an ihre Leistungsgrenze zu gehen. 

Dank der Mobilität des Systems kann in der Klinik, im Pflegeheim oder zu Hause geübt werden, wobei die Betroffenen selbständig oder in Begleitung eines Therapeuten trainieren können. 

Rehago - Mit Spaß zum Erfolg!

name: Leadtributor
about:
Warum die meisten Geschäftsführer und Vertriebsleiter es nicht schaffen, Leads automatisiert und ohne Aufwand an Ihre Fachpartner oder Handelsvertreter weiterzugeben, während unsere Kunden eine strukturierte & messbare Leadbearbeitung mit Ihren Fachpartnern haben.

Sie haben keine Lust mehr für jedes Lead aufwändig den richtigen Fachpartner zu suchen, wenn Sie Leads bearbeitet haben wollen? Sie möchten Ihren Fachpartnern nicht aufwändig nachtelefonieren, um Feedback zum Status Quo Ihrer Leads zu erlangen? Sie haben die Nase voll von Streitigkeiten um Dubletten?

Sie hätten gerne ein strukturiertes System, mit dem Sie und Ihre Fachpartner gemeinsam an Kundenanfragen arbeiten können, mit dem Sie jederzeit den Status zu Leads sehen können und das Ihnen die aufwändige Leadverteilung automatisiert abnimmt, denken aber, dass eine Systemeinführung zu teuer und aufwändig ist?

leadtributor hilft Unternehmen dabei, Leads automatisiert an Fachpartner zu verteilen und jederzeit den Überblick zu behalten, um messbare Zahlen über den indirekten, externen Vertrieb zu erhalten - ohne eine aufwändige Systemeinführung.

Die Ergebnisse durch unsere Hilfe:

- Sie automatisieren die Leadverteilung an Ihre Fachpartner und beseitigen Dubletten sofort.

- Sie erhalten endlich einen Überblick über alle Kundenanfragen, die bei Ihren Vertriebspartnern schlummern.

- Sie wissen jederzeit, wie Ihre Marketingkampagnen performen und kennen den Marketing Return on Invest.

- Mit unserem Sales-Dashboard haben Sie jederzeit aussagekräftige Zahlen über Ihre Leads & die Fachpartner oder Handelsvertreter.

- Keine Black Box mehr und Schluss mit lästigem Nachtelefonieren bei Ihren Vertriebspartnern.

- Mit intelligenter Software den mehrstufigen Vertrieb digitalisieren ...

Wenn Sie mehr darüber erfahren möchten, bewerben Sie sich auf unserer Webseite https://leadtributor.com/demo für ein kostenloses Erstgespräch mit mir.

name: Usercentrics
about:
Usercentrics is a global market leader in the field of Consent Management Platforms (CMP). We enable businesses to collect, manage and document user consents on websites and apps in order to achieve full compliance with global privacy regulations while facilitating high consent rates and building trust with their customers.

Usercentrics believes in creating a healthy balance between data privacy and data-driven business, delivering solutions for every size of enterprise. Cookiebot CMP is our plug-and-play SaaS for smaller businesses and organizations, App CMP handles user consent on mobile apps, and Usercentrics CMP serves companies with enterprise-grade custom requirements for unifying consent and data from capture to processing.

Helping clients like Daimler, ING Diba and Santander achieve privacy compliance, Usercentrics is active in more than 100 countries, with 2000+ resellers and handles more than 61 million daily user consents.

Visit usercentrics.com and cookiebot.com to learn more.

name: Scalerion
about: With Scalerion, manufacturers and distributors integrate independent retailers on a commission basis into their direct-to-consumer business and diversify their presence in the market and their access to consumers. Retailers expand their business model with an innovative marketplace solution and sell products on behalf of their partners. Purchased goods are shipped from centralized stocks directly to the consumers and the intermediary retailers receive the commissions agreed in advance, which, unlike traditional sales, are immediately reflected as contribution margins. Scalerion provides comprehensive information and transaction management, complete payment processing and can be implemented and operated in parallel to existing business processes. We enable the industry to achieve higher contribution margins – with lower risks and lower costs. Sounds interesting? Get in touch!

name: Nauto

This unique approach can improve driver performance and help reduce collision loss, providing rapid ROI while mitigating risk factors of greatest impact. Founded in 2018 by Lawrence Leuschner, Matthias Laug and Julian Blessin, TIER is headquartered in Berlin and currently operates in 95+ cities across 12 countries in Europe and the Middle East. With a focus on providing the safest, most equitable and most sustainable mobility solution, TIER has been climate neutral since 2020.

TIER- change mobility for good.

name: Wechselpilot
about:
Ohne Aufwand immer im besten Strom- und Gasvertrag? Kein Problem mit Wechselpilot!

Im Gegensatz zu den klassischen Vergleichsportalen hilft Wechselpilot nicht nur beim ersten Vertragswechsel, sondern übernimmt die laufende Optimierung Ihrer Strom- und Gasverträge. Mit seiner innovativen Dienstleistung wurde Wechselpilot Anfang des Jahres von Stiftung Warentest mit der Bestnote „Sehr empfehlenswert“ ausgezeichnet.

Auf den individuell eingesparten Betrag erheben wir eine Gebühr in Höhe von 20%. Somit wahren wir unsere Unabhängigkeit von den Versorgern und profitieren nur, wenn wir tatsächlich eine Einsparung für unsere Kunden erzielen können. 

Schauen Sie auf unserer Website vorbei und lassen Sie sich kostenlos ein Angebot von unserem Stromrechner erstellen – wir freuen uns auf Ihren Besuch!

name: Bikmo
about:
Bikmo exists to enable you to ride more. 

We build awesome insurance products to protect our customers for unexpected events, use technology to make taking out and managing your policy ultra-simple, and provide exceptional customer experiences through our team of bike geeks.

As of May 2019, we are proud to be the official provider of British Cycling bike insurance. Through the years we have grown our business through strong and long-lasting partnerships with companies such as Brompton, Deliveroo and Cycle Surgery. 

We believe that local bike shops are the cornerstone of the bike community and we have set ourselves a target to bring £10m annually back to independent local retailers 2023. Apart from cycle insurance, we offer peace-of-mind in the form of travel insurance to wanderers in the UK, designed for adventure sports trips across the world.

Bikmo was founded in 2014. We’re headquartered in Chester, UK, and in 2018 we have expanded to Ireland, Germany and Austria with offices in Munich, Germany and Innsbruck, Austria. 

If you would like to learn more about Bikmo, our team or would like to become our partner please visit our website - bikmo.com or bikmo.de

name: UniqFEED AG
about:
Here at uniqFEED, we develop virtual advertising technology for live sports using software – a novel approach, but one we believe is the future.

The company was founded in 2015, when virtual advertising was still in its infancy and most available solutions were dependent on complex hardware and adaptations to in-stadium equipment which made it costly, intrusive and difficult to deploy at scale. uniqFEED founder Lukas Gysin had a vision to create something simpler, scalable, and most importantly – future proof. He met co-founder Dr.-Ing. Ralf Dragon and Prof. Luc Van Gool and the three set about bringing the concept to life, driven by their combined passions for technology and sport.

uniqFEED is now a team with expert scientists and developers, based in three locations around the world, our headquarters in Zurich, our US office in New York, and our research facility in Hanover, Germany. Our fantastic team works hard to develop the best solutions for our customers.

For further information, please contact us: 
info@uniqfeed.com
+41 44 500 43 32

name: Motor AI
about:
Motor Ai is the only German autonomous driving company specialized in addressing the safety and legal requirements set by the European Union. Motor Ai is building an Intelligence for level 4 and 5 autonomous vehicles. Our cognitive intelligence-based
system is capable of making decisions in complex, urban traffic. In contrast to trained-model approaches, the system can explainably reach a decision in a completely new situation. This offers two great advantages: it is certifiable under international safety standards and does not need to be trained on infinite scenarios.
Motor Ai was founded in 2017. It was initially bootstrapped and quickly gained support through competitive accelerator programs such as the Horizon 2020 initiative by the European Union and through investments from experienced investors. Motor Ai’s international team is composed of experts in computer vision and cognitive neuroscience.

DE
Motor Ai ist das einzige deutsche Unternehmen für AutonomesFahren und hat sich auf die Einhaltung der Sicherheits- und gesetzlichenAnforderungen der Europäischen Union spezialisiert. Motor Ai entwickelt die Intelligenz für autonome Fahrzeuge der Level 4 und 5. Das auf kognitiver Intelligenz basierende System
ist in der Lage, Entscheidungen im komplexen Stadtverkehr zu treffen. Im Gegensatz zu reinmaschinellen Lernsystemen, welche auf trainierten Situationen beruhen, kann das Motor AiSystem in einer völlig neuen Szenarien sicherere und nachvollziehbareEntscheidungen treffen. Daraus erweisen sich zwei große Vorteile: Es ist nach internationalen Sicherheitsstandards zertifizierbar und muss nicht in unendlichen Szenarien trainiert werden.
Motor Ai wurde im Jahr 2017 gegründet und gewann schnell Unterstützung durch umkämpfte Acceleratorprogramme wie die Horizon 2020-Initiative der Europäischen Union und von renommierten Investoren und Professoren. Das internationale Team von Motor Ai besteht aus Experten für Computer Vision
und kognitiven Neurowissenschaften.

You will see and feel noticeable changes within a short time. The workouts are tailored to your own personal fitness level to keep you motivated and make you fitter step-by-step.

The program contains different effective training methods that help to improve overall fitness and performance levels, to better manage your daily life, to reach sporting goals or to improve your body shape.

name: FRISS
about:
FRISS is 100% focused on automated fraud and risk detection for P&C insurance companies worldwide. The AI-powered detection solutions for underwriting, claims and SIU help 200+ insurers grow their business. FRISS detects fraud, mitigates risks and supports digital transformation. Insurers go live within 4 months, realize up to 10 times ROI and 80% increase in straight through processing of policy application and claims. FRISS solutions help lower loss ratios, enable profitable portfolio growth, and improve the customer experience. 

The real time FRISS Score is the core of our solutions and indicates the risk for each policy or claim. The AI-powered score combines Text Mining, Machine Learning, Predictive Models and Network Analysis with Expert Business Knowledge out of 15+ years of insurance experience, your specific business configuration, proprietary data and external data sources. It provides you a white box, holistic view on fraud and risks, which delivers you actionable insights so you stay in control.

Durch verschiedene Tarife ist vom Standardsortiment und Einheitspreis mit ROOBEO united bis zu kundenindividuellen Konditionen, Sortimente und Lieferanten mit ROOBEO direct alles möglich. 

Durch die gewerkeübergreifende Plattform erreichen Lieferanten eine Vielzahl unterschiedlicher Gewerke, um Absatzkanäle zu erweitern und Neukunden zu erschließen. 

Bestrebt den Baustoffsektor zu digitalisieren, werden gängige offline Prozesse digital bei ROOBEO berücksichtigt um, unabhängig vom Endgerät, Bestellungen von Materialien bei gewünschten Lieferanten zu unterschiedlichen Liefermethoden durchzuführen und dabei Budgetgrenzen und Einkaufsberechtigungen je Nutzer zu beachten.

Objektlisten zu Bauvorhaben können einfach erstellt, untereinander geteilt und in den Warenkorb überführt werden.

Der digitale Warenannahmeprozess ermöglicht eine anschließende und automatisierte Rechnungsprüfung welche den Zeitaufwand minimiert und regelmäßige Auswertungen erlaubt.

Damit auch die Industrie als Teilnehmer des angebotenen Ökosystem profitiert, bietet ROOBEO eigens entwickelte Services rund um die Themen Markendarstellung und Produktstammdaten an, wodurch maßgeblich Einfluss auf die angebotene Qualität und Ausprägung von Produktinformationen genommen wird.

name: Comma.ai
about:
Comma’s mission is to provide a solution to enhance people’s drives, on cars they already own. We believe that driver assistance features, like automated highway driving, in conjunction with a monitoring system that checks the driver’s attention, will be a significant step forward in reducing driving stress and road accidents.

In 2016, comma launched an open source software project called openpilot, which includes a comprehensive suite of driver assistance features. openpilot is compatible with almost every new Honda and Toyota sold in the US, plus other selected car models. Combined, this amounts to approximately 5 millions cars in the US alone. As older cars gets replaced by newer ones, we estimate this number to grow to tens of millions over the next 2–3 years.

We have over 20 million miles of video and car's data from thousands of users driving with our comma two devkit (https://comma.ai/shop), which also supports openpilot.

You can check out and contribute to openpilot (https://github.com/commaai/openpilot), follow us on Twitter (https://twitter.com/comma_ai) and/or join our community (slack.comma.ai). We're also hiring (https://comma.ai/jobs/).

name: DFV Deutsche Familienversicherung
about:
Die DFV Deutsche Familienversicherung AG (nachfolgend DFV genannt) ist das erste börsennotierte InsurTech Europas und ein Versicherungsunternehmen mit Sitz in Frankfurt. Die DFV bietet insbesondere Krankenzusatzversicherungen und ausgewählte Sachversicherungen an. Der Vertrieb erfolgt direkt, vorzugsweise über Onlinekanäle, aber auch Kooperationen und einige ausgewählte Makler. Die DFV wächst weit überdurchschnittlich schnell, was auch darauf zurückzuführen ist, dass die angebotenen Versicherungsprodukte regelmäßig Bestnoten bei Stiftung Warentest erhalten bzw. als Testsieger ausgezeichnet werden. Das Unternehmen selbst ist weitgehend digitalisiert. Noch bestehende analoge Prozesse werden zunehmend umgestellt.  

Das Unternehmen beschäftigt derzeit rund 115 Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter und wird im Laufe des Jahres auf ca. 175 Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter anwachsen. Letzteres ist unter anderem in der Tatsache begründet, dass die DFV Mitglied eines Versicherungskonsortiums geworden ist, das allen Beschäftigten der pharmazeutischen und chemischen Industrie Versicherungsschutz im Rahmen einer Arbeitgeber-finanzierten Pflegezusatzversicherung gewährt.

Die DFV legt großen Wert auf eine hohe Kundenzufriedenheit. Produktseitig wird diese erzielt durch die genannten Spitzenbewertungen bei Stiftung Warentest. Im Umgang mit den Kunden sollte die Zufriedenheit vorzugsweise über einfache und leicht verständliche Prozesse, schnelle Entscheidungen und ein kurzfristiges Bedienen von Kundenanliegen und Abhelfen etwaiger Beschwerden erfolgen.

Weitere Informationen unter: www.insurtech-germany.com

name: Roomer
about:
Roomer is the marketplace for travel, connecting travelers who are stuck with a nonrefundable hotel room with those looking for a last minute, discounted accommodation. Using an automated validation system to authenticate each and every reservation on its marketplace, Roomer works vigilantly to ensure safety and security for all of its users, buyers and sellers alike. Since its founding in 2011, Roomer has come to the rescue of distressed travelers all over the world who were stuck with nonrefundable hotel reservations and used Roomer's secure platform to sell these reservations to spontaneous, deal-seeking travelers. 

Roomer's unique marketplace serves more than just its individual users. Roomer also works with hotels and travel companies around the world to both expand their customer bases and to solve critical customer service problems relating to canceling guests with nonrefundable reservations. 

Roomer was founded by Ben Froumine and Gon Ben David, and is backed by the BRM Group, with directors Eran Barkat and Yael Reznick Cramer of BRM Hi-Tech and Uri Levine, co-founder of Waze.

name: Liva Healthcare
about:
Liva Healthcare is Europe’s leading provider of scalable digital health coaching. Through an app Liva is providing personal human coaching programmes to help people manage obesity, pre-diabetes, type 2 diabetes and cardiovascular diseases.

Liva is headquartered in Copenhagen with offices in London and Berlin, and the company's multi-award winning platform is now operational in nine countries across Europe and the South-Pacific. 

The company was founded in 2015 by the founders behind Europe’s leading independent health information portal, NetDoctor.com, Rune Bech and Carl Brandt, together with Kristoffer From.

In 2017, Liva was selected by NHS England among 84 providers as a digital provider to their world-leading National Diabetes Prevention Programme (NDPP).

Among Liva’s other major clients are insurance giants like AXA and Bupa, and pharmaceutical companies like Amgen and Novo Nordisk, and public and private healthcare providers across Europe. 

Through Liva’s app, users have access to a real human health coach, designing a personalised lifestyle change programme for them based on their individual needs. 

After a live video kick-off the participant then receives continuous professional guidance, support, motivation, and empathy via Liva's app. The goal is to help them prevent, manage or reverse chronic conditions through a new sustainable healthy lifestyle and behaviour changes. 

Participants can track their progress real-time via the app and engage with a support group of peers to keep them motivated. 

In several studies, Liva has been proven to drive substantial clinical outcomes, also in socio-economic backgrounds normally hard to reach.

Liva is funded by VerlInvest, MIG, Digital Health Ventures, Santo Venture Capital, and Maj Invest.

For more information visit livahealthcare.com

Soll das gute Verhältnis zu den etablierten Geschäftspartnern mit einer härteren Gangart bei Forderungen riskiert werden? name: Preventor
about:
Preventor was founded in 2017 in Delaware. Our headquarters are based in Miami, FL. Since then, we have expanded our business to Peru, Ecuador, Mexico, and France. With over 35 years of experience, our team continues to work towards an efficient, secure way to identify and prevent fraud, and to deliver a new way to comply with global KYC and AML regulations. Our mission, however, goes well beyond that.

Transparency in identity is essential to our economy and the attainment of freedom and safety around the world. This transparency, and how to achieve it, is foundational to Preventor's score beliefs and pursuits. Some argue that anonymity and transparency cannot exist together. At Preventor, we understand and are in lockstep with the evolutions of electronic currencies and their global impact. 

Why Preventor?
The power of fraud prevention with the intelligence of AI and biometrics integration. Offer your clients a seamless user experience without sacrificing thorough identification and monitoring.
Preventor integrates all the tools you need to digitally automate the onboarding of your client:

1. Verify: identity document, face recognition, liveness detection, and credentials
2. Onboard: any client from any location and device
3. Screen: against AML sanctions, PEP, and adverse media
4. Monitor: automate the KYC and continuous monitoring
5. Prevent: synthetic identity fraud and reduce false positives



Our Solutions:
• Identity verification: onboard clients with a superior experience and peace of mind. Ensure
that your customer is who they claim to be and prevent unwanted access to their accounts.
• AML risk screening: protect your business against fraud and comply with regulatory
mandates, including screening against sanctions lists and conducting customer due
diligence.
• Compliance platform: obtain a complete picture of who your client really is and establish a
clear communication flow in your organization with our client-centered platform.

AkinovA will provide valuable data and analytics to participants and regulators from the aggregated data that passes through the marketplace.
 
AkinovA will help to grow the overall size of the insurance marketplace by enabling new participants to enter and existing participants to transact more business. There is significant pressure from the Capital Markets wanting an appropriate mechanism to access insurance risks which are decorrelated from traditional bonds and equities. Creating an effective secondary market for (re)insurance risks, to enable these risks to be traded, will dramatically increase the volume of business that is transacted across the marketplace. AkinovA is working with a number of brokers, who act as key channel partners for the existing industry, to kickstart liquidity on the marketplace. AkinovA will provide them with a venue to service their clients’ needs in a more efficient and timely manner as well as giving them access to new clients entering the market who would benefit from their advice.
 
AkinovA’s goal is to remain an independent marketplace enabling it to attract and work with all parties without undue influence from industry participants.

name: Tractable
about:
Tractable develops artificial intelligence for accident and disaster recovery. We are on a journey to help the world recover faster from accidents and disasters that affect hundreds of millions of lives, from car accidents and burst piping, to full-scale floods and hurricanes. 

Accident and disaster recovery starts with visual damage appraisal: assess the damage, calculate the cost, unlock the funds and rebuild. However, the first stage of assessing the problem can take days to weeks. Our belief is that when accidents and disasters hit, the response could be 10 times faster, thanks to AI. 

We are starting with motor damage. Our AI assesses damage to any car, whether in Europe, North America or Asia, and we work with the world's leading insurers in over 10 countries across the world, including Tokio Marine in Japan, Ageas in the UK, Covéa in France, The Hartford in the US, and Talanx-Warta in Poland. 

Founded in 2014, Tractable has a world-class research and development team with over 30 years of combined research experience, and its solution is built on five years of dedicated research and development work undertaken by a team of Oxford/Cambridge-trained researchers. Tractable has raised $55m from Georgian Partners, Insight Partners and other top-tier investors, and the company is based in London, with offices in New York City and Tokyo.

name: Omnius
about:
De missie van Omnius is om juridische dienstverlening bereikbaar en betaalbaar te maken. Met een heldere toekomstvisie speelt Omnius in op dynamische marktontwikkelingen en de veranderende vraag van rechtzoekenden, zowel zakelijk als particulier. Innovatie zit in onze genen en wij maken het recht toegankelijk voor iedereen.

Omnius is marktleider met het grootste advocatennetwerk van Nederland en investeert continu in vernieuwingen en verbeteringen die inspelen op trends en ontwikkelingen die voldoen aan de verwachtingen rechtzoekenden in deze tijd. Persoonlijk contact, goede service en laagdrempelige bereikbaarheid zijn van het grootste belang.

Onze juristen zijn 7 dagen per week bereikbaar voor eerstelijns telefonisch juridisch advies. Juridische dienstverlening voor elke situatie. Om de rechtzoekende te voorzien van het beste advies, werkt Omnius volgens de formule van trapsgewijze juridische hulp. Eerst legt u de hulpvraag voor aan onze eigen intakebalie. De juristen bij deze laagdrempelige adviesdesk luisteren naar de vraag en geven kosteloos en vrijblijvend het eerste advies.

Omnius is in 2012 opgericht en inmiddels uitgegroeid tot een moderne juridische dienstverlener met een eigen landelijk dekkend kwaliteitsnetwerk. Het grootste advocatennetwerk van Nederland met meer dan 260 onafhankelijk advocaten. Het Omnius Keurmerk waarborgt de service en kwaliteit van de advocaten en gaat zelfs verder dan de gedragsregels en kwaliteitseisen die worden gesteld door de juridische beroepsorganisaties.

Met onze vooruitstrevende diensten en digitale oplossingen maken we het verschil in de - soms nog ouderwetse - juridische branche. De klantgerichte formule heeft ervoor gezorgd dat Omnius is uitgegroeid tot het grootste en meest succesvolle advocatennetwerk van Nederland. Juridische dienstverlening van de nieuwe generatie.

name: Radiant.Earth
about:
Radiant Earth Foundation empowers organizations and individuals globally with open AI and EO data, standards and tools to address the world’s most critical international development challenges.

Our goals are three-fold: First, it is to provide an open source “Hub” for data scientists and programmers to discover and access Earth observation training datasets and machine learning models, as well as to lead a sustained community-wide effort to capture image labels for various applications across the Global South. 

The second goal is to foster a community of practice to develop standards around machine learning on Earth observation and to expand the interoperability of these tools and datasets. 

The third goal is to educate and inform global development actors and geospatial professionals on progress and innovation in the Earth observation marketplace. 

Radiant Earth Foundation is a United States registered non-profit organization with offices in Washington D.C., and San Francisco, California.

Our OrbiWAN network solution success is built on the robustness and scalability of its platform, offering highest quality customer support & a wide range of features including real time device instant messaging & targeted device group profiling whether it be supporting a single or thousands of gateway access points in smart city, rural or industrial environments to enhance management of pollution controls, increasing agricultural & manufacturing efficiency, facilitating city parking or improving employee health & security amongst many other applications.

Having established ourselves globally & winning major projects on all five continents, we have deployed the largest LoraWAN® network in the world in India for one of our partners, Tata Communications, & also provide end-to-end noise pollution measurement solutions in several European cities through our network platform, gateways & measurement sensors.

We believe in the positive impact our expertise contributes to smart city, smart agriculture & industry 4.0 initiatives through supporting our customers and partners, and our active participating member of the Lora Alliance (www.lora-alliance.org) & the SynchroniCity initiative (www.synchronicity-iot.eu).

name: Pockit
about:
Over a million people in the UK still don't have a current account - they have often
been ignored by traditional financial services and miss out on what many consider an everyday norm, such as internet shopping. In this report we show that these people are having to pay up to an additional £485 per year through higher energy bills, phone contracts and more expensive loans - simply because they don't have a current account.

name: Outdooractive
about:

On the online platform, the data of our partners and community members will be connected. With numerous tools, Outdooractive supports its users in planning and accomplishing all activities in the open.

name: Vehiculum
about:

Unsere Plattform ermöglicht einen effizienten und einfachen deutschlandweiten Vergleich verschiedener Anbieter und Leasing-Angebote in Echtzeit. Neben dem Preisvergleich bietet VEHICULUM auch Zusatzfunktionen wie unser Vertragsmanagement, was vor allem für kleinere Flotten das Management der Flotte deutlich vereinfacht. 

VEHICULUM is the first digital solution for hassle-free car leasing. Our platform empowers our customers to compare multiple models and leasing offers in real-time. Beside the price comparison we also offer additional feautures such as our contract management, which mainly supports companies with small fleets to manage their carfleet.

name: Aggregion
about:
It is often said that data is the new oil, the most lucrative new commodity on the market today. Major customer-facing companies collect tremendous amounts of data — big data. It is a vast global repository of first party data. But this repository is highly fragmented — no company has the full Customer Portrait 360.

Here in Aggregion we have developed technology to securely match data from different companies without them losing control or transferring the data to any central repository. The data never leaves their servers and the process is fully transparent and auditable to participants. The result are vast opportunities for ecosystem cooperation and product building.

name: Health Rise
about:
Health Rise wurde als ganzheitliches Unternehmen gegründet. Wir stellen fundierte und verständliche Gesundheits-Informationen einem breiten Publikum zur Verfügung, führen Gesundheits-Experten und Patienten zusammen und arbeiten an einer elektronischen Gesundheitsakte. 
Unser Ziel ist, was Sie gesund macht.

Diese Vision leben wir – jeder Kollege, jeden Tag. Werden Sie Teil des Health Rise-Teams, egal ob als Mitarbeiter, Gesundheitsexperte oder als interessierter Nutzer.

Health Rise ist ein Gesundheitsportal, das informative Texte und spannende Podcasts mit Gesundheits-, Fitness- und Ernährungsexperten, sowie interessante Videos mit praktischen Hinweisen bereitstellt. ►https://www.health-rise.de/

Im Health Rise Shop finden sich Angebote von Gesundheitsexperten, die online oder ganz klassisch offline, Menschen dabei unterstützen, sich wohler, besser und gesünder zu fühlen. ►https://shop.health-rise.de

Abgerundet wird das Gesundheitsportal durch eine Reihe von nützlichen Gesundheits-Apps. Die beliebtesten sind der digitale Impfpass, der digitale Mutterpass und das digitale Kinderuntersuchungsheft. ►https://portal.health-rise.de

name: Mootral
about:
MOOTRAL is a British-Swiss AgriTech company that develops innovative solutions for companies and governments to reduce greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions as well as the usage of antibiotics in the agricultural sector. Our first technology is Mootral Ruminant, a natural feed supplement that significantly reduces methane emissions from ruminants. Mootral Ruminant is based on a proprietary combination of garlic and citrus extracts.

The Mootral business model sets out to prove “there is good business in the business of doing good”. Mootral unlocks new, innovative and profitable approaches to reducing GHG emissions, including the creation of a new climate-friendly food standard for beef and dairy products and a “cow credit” currency. Mootral is a “win-win” for all, but especially for farmers. Today, farmers are facing economic hardships and regulatory challenges unforeseen just a few decades ago. In order to support their future financial prosperity in a sustainable way, and one that meets the emerging needs of consumers, new thinking is needed. Mootral is the result of that thinking – bringing strong benefits to all stakeholders.

Cows, being the highest methane producers amongst ruminants, are a crucial factor in our environmental ecosystem and the economy, Mootral is setting the foundation for the future through a solution that makes an impact today. It enables a positive transition to climate-smart agriculture designed to help farmers earn more money and industry partners to reduce their impact on the environment. The future is climate-smart and the future is now.

For further information visit: www.mootral.com

name: Hausgold
about:
Das ist HAUSGOLD:
HAUSGOLD ist ein stark wachsendes PropTech mit dem Ziel, das Immobiliengeschäft für alle einfacher, transparenter und erfolgreicher zu machen. Dank unseres selbst entwickelten Algorithmus sowie der gesammelten Daten über den Immobilienmarkt und die Performance von Maklern sind wir eine der größten und stärksten digitalen Immobilienplattformen in Deutschland und erreichen so eine Marktabdeckung von 100 Prozent. In einem stark fragmentierten Umfeld bieten wir eine einfache Lösung und ermitteln die jeweils für das Verkaufsobjekt geeigneten Immobilienmakler. Darüber hinaus erleichtern wir mit unseren digitalen Maklermanagementtools die Immobiliengeschäfte für Makler und führen diesen wertvolle Kunden zu. Gegründet wurden wir 2014 von Sebastian Wagner

So arbeiten wir:
Unser Büro in der hippen Hamburger Schanze beherbergt mittlerweile rund 60 Mitarbeiter*innen. Teamwork, Transparenz und eine offene Unternehmenskultur sind für uns entscheidende Kriterien einer erfolgreichen Zusammenarbeit. Innovation und Problemlösung sind unsere Kernkompetenzen, deshalb sind wir stets offen für neue Anregungen und begrüßen es sehr, wenn du dich mit deinen Ideen und Fähigkeiten einbringst.

Das bieten wir:
- Flache Hierarchien und eine Zusammenarbeit auf Augenhöhe
- Flexible Arbeitszeiten und die Möglichkeit aus Homeoffice
- Einen top ausgestatteten Arbeitsplatz in der Hamburger Schanze
- Frisches Obst, aber auch Süßigkeiten dürfen bei uns nicht fehlen

name: Imburse
about:
In a world where consumers payment preferences and technologies are ever-evolving, the Imburse “Payments as a Service” enterprise platform offers integration-free access to the entire global payment ecosystem, from card collections, to debit orders, e-wallets, push to card transactions, and more.  Never again will a project related to any form of payment be delayed by financial or resource constraints.  Imburse offers the complete freedom to rapidly enhance and deploy any change to your payment offering in less than 5 mins at zero cost to deploy. 
Instead of having to integrate with single payment providers or payment technology providers, our solutions allow for companies to connect to us, once, and thereby gain access to multiple different payment providers and technologies around the globe.

name: Crosslend
about: CrossLend is a FinTech company, licensed & supervised by BaFin and CSSF, with a mission to transform private debt into a more efficient, transparent, and profitable space for both loan originators and investors by providing end-to-end digital solutions and standardisation for loan asset transactions. As a hub for loan data management and standardisation, as well as debt trading and securitisation as a service, CrossLend provides leading-edge technology for loan asset transactions on a pan-European scale. The heart of CrossLend’s business model is a private debt platform where originators and investors can interact with each other seamlessly and transparently, viewing loan data clearly in a standardised format. This makes it easy for institutional investors to identify and compare loans according to their criteria. CrossLend was founded in Berlin in 2014 and employs more than 70 people from over 30 countries. In addition to its headquarters in Berlin, CrossLend has offices in Frankfurt, Vienna, Luxembourg, and London.

Unsere Vision:
Wir ermöglichen allen Projektteilnehmern eine Qualitätskontrolle und bringen Transparenz in die Beschaffung. Dadurch ermöglichen wir nachvollziehbares, ESG konformes und kontrollierbares Bauen. name: Secure CloudLink
about: WINNER - Public Sector Cloud Project of 2016, Cloud Hosting Awards. Providing highly secure Single Sign On for the UK Governments innovation department, Innovate UK. Secure Cloudlink Ltd. is a UK based cloud security software company determined to make passwords obsolete. Secure Cloudlink uniquely eliminates the security risks, administration costs, license abuse or user frustrations associated with issuing and maintaining passwords. The patented token technology built into Secure Cloudlink does not transmit, store or replicate user credentials anywhere and includes third party multi-factor, biometric or single sign on (SSO) technology for roughly a third of the price of alternative identity management solutions. Our customers include government, SaaS providers, financial institutions and is applicable to any organisation needing to provide simple yet secure user access to cloud and on premise application or services.

name: Mitipi
about:
Kevin is a virtual roommate. He makes sure that your apartment, office or home looks inhabited, while you are gone. The risk of becoming a victim of burglary is dramatically reduced.
Thanks to the free Mitipi App you can control Kevin from wherever you are and you can personalise him.
Kevin is not only inspired by the film "Home alone". It is a multifunctional Swiss designed bluetooth speaker, lamp, audio-light- and shadow simulation machine. All-in-one, like a Swiss army knife for your home.

name: Plantura
about:
Plantura - the digital brand for gardening. 

As a vertically integrated direct-to-consumer brand we are thriving to make gardening more sustainable and ecological-friendly. To do so, we combine high-quality content on our website plantura.garden with sustainable products that make your garden blossom. 

Since our launch in 2017, we grew our Plantura fan base to more than 1m hobby gardeners and provide them educational and inspiring content. In summer 2018, we launched our first product line consisting of five organic and vegan fertilizers. Currently, we are expanding our product portfolio to biological plant protection and soils with a low CO2 footprint.

Our team consists of highly-motivated entrepreneurs, sharp branding & communication talents and passionate horticultural scientists with the mission of sustainable gardening for everyone. 

Feel like joining our team? Currently, we are hiring talented and like-minded people. Check https://plantura-jobs.personio.de/ for our job offers.

name: Attest

The Attest identity platform allows governments to offer a convenient and secure identity service to citizens; consumers to regain control of their digital footprint and unlock the value of their personal data; and businesses to extend “government-grade trust” to all transactions with consumers.

name: StudySmarter

The Startup is headquartered in Munich and employs more than 400 people. StudySmarter's vision is to leverage state-of-the-art technology to empower everyone to achieve their educational goals.

name: WeGift
about:

Operating in more than 30 countries, and dozens of languages and currencies, WeGift’s digital payouts platform and open API solution is directly integrated into every brand on its platform, offering corporate buyers the only true global network with direct access to more than 700 brands. Habito, Perkbox, Seated, Sodexo, Vodafone, and Vouchercodes all rely on WeGift to digitally engage their audiences.

We are committed to providing a hiring and working experience in which all people feel they are equally respected and valued regardless of race, religion, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status, or disability status.

name: VeeZoo

To learn more about Veezoo and why natural language is the key to democratizing data and creating data-driven organizations, visit:

name: DataWerks
about:
dataWerks GmbH is a German-owned software company in Frankfurt, specialising in real-time data virtualisation to provide organisations with the ability to make instant, well-informed decision. We believe the breadth and volume of data available today should be easily accessible to all.

dataWerks' patent pending solution in a nutshell:

- Data Virtualization and data mashups.
Mashup data from any number of sources in real-time with high performance. Data correlation, analytics and profiling help to identify patterns and links between sources.

- Unlimited Sources of any format.
Mashup any number and all types of sources including structured, unstructured, web and big data. Patent-pending technology accesses data without performance impacts.

- Real-Time.
Analyze information the moment they are being created and with response times that have never been seen before.

- No ETL. No Data Replication.
Virtually unify disparate data sources. No more ETL or data replication! Query all sources as though they belong to one big source.

- Half the time. Half the cost.
Quickly deliver integrated data and insights to meet changing business needs. Flexible data delivery options include web services, reports, triggers and alerts.

http://www.datawerks.com

name: Helpcheck

Dabei kooperieren wir eng mit ausgewählten Anwaltskanzleien aus ganz Deutschland, die auf Basis unserer eigens entwickelten Claim-Processing-Software mit intelligenten Algorithmen Fälle effizient bearbeiten.

name: Acurable
about:
Acurable is a fast growing MedTech company headquartered in London. We produce the first wearable medical device able to accurately diagnose and manage respiratory conditions at home. Our award-winning patented technology is a major engineering innovation and the product of over 10 years research at Imperial College London.

- Accurate : 5x more accurate readings than current solutions, enabling automated diagnosis and drastically reducing misdiagnosis.
- Easy to use : non-invasive and no training required, enabling home use without the assistance of a specialist or a visit to the hospital, which significantly lowers overall costs.

We aim to understand human biosignals so well that nobody dies of a treatable condition ever again. To achieve our objectives, we are building a team of exceptional people who are inspired by our vision, share our values, and who have the attitude and skills required to help Acurable succeed.

name: Campanda
about:
Campanda is the largest motorhome rental marketplace in the world with hundreds of professional motorhome lessors in over 30 countries. We connect camping enthusiasts with local experts providing vehicles for every demand.

What sets us apart?
Campanda is built on trust. We're committed to providing first-class customer service and ensuring peace of mind for everyone involved. So whether you're searching for the perfect motorhome for a family road trip or looking for extra money renting out your motorhome(s), we're here to help you do it right.

name: Vote2Work GmbH
about:
Wir glauben, dass im Zeitalter von Digitalisierung und Arbeit 4.0 starre Arbeitszeitmodelle aufbrechen und Arbeiten im operativen und wertschöpfenden Bereich genauso flexibel und selbstbestimmt wird wie in der Wissensarbeit. Vor allem Lösungen, die die Wünsche der Arbeitnehmer nach familienfreundlichen Arbeitszeiten und flexibler mitbestimmter Einsatzplanung in den Vordergrund stellen, werden das Berufsbild der nächsten Jahre prägen. 

Mit unserer SaaS-Lösung Vote2Work® schaffen wir ein Werkzeug, das bei der Flexibilisierung der Arbeitswelt unterstützt und die Mitarbeiterpartizipation fördert. Dabei setzen wir auf digitale Vernetzung mit interaktiven Workflows, die Mitarbeiter im Bedarfsfall orts-& zeitunabhängig erreichen und die Mitbestimmung bei der Gestaltung der Arbeitszeit ermöglichen.  Kollaboration und Selbstorganisation stehen im Fokus von Vote2Work®. Mitarbeiter informieren sich zudem stets online über ihre Einsatzzeiten und erhalten die Möglichkeit, Präferenz- und Ausschlusszeiten zu definieren. 

Wir möchten auch Ihr Unternehmen dabei unterstützen, die Transformation von starren Anwesenheitsmodellen hin zu einer flexiblen, hochoptimierten Einsatzplanung zu verwirklichen. Vor allem die Einsatzplanung der Blue Collar und Deskless workforce kann von Vote2Work® profitieren, durch den Mirarbeitereinbezug das Berufsbild attraktiver zu gestalten und ein Stück „New Work“ auch auf den „Hallenboden“ zu bringen.  

Wir helfen Ihnen, das Ungeplante in Ihren Arbeitsabläufen schneller in den Griff zu bekommen!

Ihre

Dipl.-Ing. Katrin Pape
CEO | Co-Founder

name: Solvemate
about:
Solvemate enables brands to deliver quality customer service through meaningful conversations. 

Our customer service automation platform is powered by smart conversational AI that allows companies to create highly personalized chatbot conversations at scale, guiding customers to find answers when they need them, so service teams can focus their expertise where it matters most. Solvemate’s unique contextual conversation engine approach means it learns more quickly, integrates more easily and resolves requests faster and more reliably than any other chatbot on the market. We have a dedicated team to help you every step of the way with industry-specific best practices to ensure you see value within weeks. Brands benefit from a highly personalized, real-time self-service experience that increases customer satisfaction, reduces costs, and offers actionable customer service insights. Solvemate has empowered innovative, growing companies to improve their customer experience and  is trusted by brands such as On Running, musicMagpie, egym, andJustPark. Learn more at solvemate.com.

name: Qunomedical
about: Qunomedical makes it easy for you to search for clinics which perform any treatment you’re looking for. We’ll give you an overview of how much you can expect to pay and the destinations you can travel to. If you find a clinic you like, you can request a free quote from the clinic and you’ll receive a personalized treatment plan along with the price. After you’ve booked your treatment, we’ll assist you with the formalities relating to your medical travel arrangements, in cooperation with the hospital. Rest assured we only select clinics which adhere to the highest standards in quality. All of our clinics have received accreditations from the Joint Commission International (JCI) or have the highest national accreditation. Consultants at JCI-accredited institutions are the most skilled and experienced in the industry. We work exclusively with hospitals that are highly experienced in dealing with international patients, and which have English-speaking staff, translators and high customer ratings. Many hospitals also feature international wings.

about:
ufirst è un’app che fornisce soluzioni di gestione delle code d’attesa in modalità in-cloud e paperless.

Attraverso un innovativo sistema di accodamento virtuale, ufirst risponde a un’esigenza sempre più diffusa nel mondo moderno, ottimizzare il tempo passato in fila, migliorando l’esperienza dei singoli utenti all’interno di strutture come ospedali, università, uffici pubblici e negozi. 

Sono tante le aziende pubbliche e private ad utilizzare questa tecnologia per efficientare la gestione dei flussi di persone in accesso alle strutture. Attivando ufirst è possibile offrire ai propri clienti/utenti la possibilità di mettersi in fila da remoto o di prenotare il proprio appuntamento, tutto tramite App, semplice da usare e molto intuitiva. 

Qualsiasi struttura voglia attivare ufirst deve sapere che il processo è immediato: si può attivare facilmente da remoto, senza investimenti in hardware e acquistando una licenza.

Attiva subito ufirst nella tua azienda!

name: Dotphoton
about: Dotphoton™ is an image compression solution for professional applications: it makes RAW images up to 10 times smaller with a strong guarantee that quality is preserved, saving a corresponding amount of time and money and enabling the next generation of high quality imaging solutions in photography, cinema, AI, biomedical and aerospace.

name: Imverse
about:
Real-time capture, editing and streaming of 3D Holograms for Live Telepresence and Volumetric Content.

We all know that the digital future is 3D. The digital future is streamed LIVE. The digital future is SOCIAL. Our vision is to make it happen NOW.

We are building the future of live 3D telepresence and real-time 3D graphics, powered by our proprietary voxel (volumetric pixel) rendering and simulation engine.

We firmly believe that voxels will become the new 3D graphics representation standard and we aim to pioneer this technological revolution.

The scope is vast with applications across multiple Telepresence verticals - from Remote Work, Training and Collaboration, Online Education to Telehealth, Art, Gaming and Live Entertainment.

Yet we do not build products or create content. We are technologists enabling others to augment existing products, services and applications and to build exciting new ones.

Contact: info@imverse.ch

name: Moka Studio
about: With more than 10-year experience in 3D animation research and development, the startup has created a unique technology in collaboration with the EPFL, called NumIK, that accurately gives life to any 3D characters (Virtual Humans, animals and more) in real-time. Based on NumIK, Moka Studio invented and released Mosketch Light, a 3D animation software that allows professionals and artists to animate any 3D characters by the stroke of a pen. The technology will further be applied to solve limitations faced by VR and AR companies that struggle to fully immerse the user in the digital world. Moka Studio offers software solutions to precisely and accurately animate and control Virtual Humans.

name: GymCraft
about: GymCraft is a software and game-development company, innovatively combining the mediums of gaming and fitness to build the sports virtual experience of the future. It interactively connects people all over the world and pushes the boundaries of virtual reality standards, providing users with a real-time interactive fitness experience, while performing their favourite sporting activities. The first product to the market will be FreeDriverVR (freedrivervr.com), a single and multi- user experience, designed for exercise bikes. GymCraft is introducing gamification to fitness equipment with ergometer treadmills, steppers, cross-trainers and rowing machines.

name: Hemanext Inc.
about: Hemanext is a medical technology company with headquarters and R&D Center of Excellence in Lexington MA, and manufacturing operations in Avon MA.  Hemanext is committing its resources to the continuing effort of the transfusion medicine community to save lives and improve patient outcomes. Our distinctive focus is on innovations in systems enabling blood collection, processing, storage and transfusion that will promote dramatic improvements in transfusion therapies. For more information, visit www.hemanext.com.

name: Maklaro GmbH
about:
**Maklaro - Digitale Services von Maklern für Makler**

Gegründet als erster Digitaler Immobilienmakler Deutschlands vereint das Maklaro-Team Immobilienexpertise und digitales Knowhow wie kein anderes. Mit seinen erfolgsgeprüften, digitalen Services bietet es anderen Immobilienmaklern unter www.maklaro.com die Möglichkeit, über Nacht mit den digitalen Herausforderern aufzuschließen. 

Mit den digitalen Services stellt Maklaro parallel seine eigenen Tools zur Effizienzsteigerung entlang der gesamten Wertschöpfung des Immobilienverkaufs anderen Maklerunternehmen zur Verfügung. Jahrelang erfolgserprobte Services werden auf Basis neuester Technologie mandantenfähig als SAAS-Lösung angeboten.

name: HeavenHR
about:
HeavenHR verändert die Welt des Personalmanagements. Unser Ziel ist es, die einzige Software zur Verfügung zu stellen, die Firmen benötigen um Ihr Personal zu verwalten. Unternehmen sollen Zeit sparen und sich auf das konzentrieren, was sie vom Wettbewerb absetzt. Vom Einstellen neuer Mitarbeiter bis zur Lohnabrechnung, wir verbinden alle separaten HR-Prozesse in einer einzigen und einfach zu bedienenden Plattform.

Besuchen Sie unsere Webseite um mehr zu erfahren: www.heavenhr.com

name: LendingCrowd
about:
LendingCrowd is an award-winning fintech lending platform that matches investors with SMEs throughout the UK seeking finance. 

As the only such platform headquartered in Scotland, we are pioneers in this space. SMEs are finding it increasingly difficult to gain financing from traditional outlets like the banks. In their place we offer a flexible, intuitive and efficient solution for these SMEs with our in-house team of credit specialists. 

We are keen to support businesses achieve keener loan rates with flexible terms, straightforward security arrangements, minimum ongoing administration and no exit fees. LendingCrowd also provides investors an opportunity to gain favourable risk-adjusted returns through a convenient, secure and easy-to-use website. Our app is available to download now: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/lendingcrowd-peer-to-peer/id1035268278

If you invest through LendingCrowd you should understand that as a lender you're lending to businesses so your capital is at risk and borrowers need to be mindful that defaulting will lead to the debt being passed to an agency for collection. LendingCrowd and its products are not covered by the Financial Services Compensation Scheme.

LendingCrowd is the trading name of Edinburgh Alternative Finance Ltd, Company Number SC468392, authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (Firm reference number 670991). LendingCrowd and its products are not covered by the Financial Services Compensation Scheme. The company's registered office is 23 Manor Place, Edinburgh, EH3 7DX.

Copyright © LendingCrowd 2018. All rights reserved.

name: safedrivepod international b.v.
about:
SafeDrivePod offers valuable driver behavior insights, minimizes distracted driving and greatly reduces emergency response times. An affordable, privacy-friendly and multifunctional telematics solution for fleet managers, insurance companies and lease agencies.

Our tiny device measures driving behavior without the need for always-on data connections, continuous use of GPS, or even an external power source. 

Another key feature of SafeDrivePod, is that it hugely improves traffic safety by limiting smartphone use while driving. Drivers can still use their favourite navigation app and all of the handsfree options available to them. Thanks to advanced technology and a combination of hardware and software that has been developed fully in-house, we are able to offer a much more economical alternative to traditional telematics solutions. It is easy to install, end user privacy is guaranteed and the benefits to road traffic safety are clear.

We want you to get home safely!

name: Leondrino, Inc.
about:
Leondrino, Inc., a FinTech startup with its roots in Berlin/Germany, established a Delaware corporation with its office in New York in November 2014.

Leondrino Inc. is a Currency Management-as-a-Service (CMaaS) provider and offers a blockchain-based platform-cum-marketplace for organizations to issue their own private, branded currencies.

The company will complement the monetary system by introducing Leondrino: a new category of private branded currency, which is backed by the current and future business of global brands. Using the potential of latest Technologies of its ecosystem partners, Leondrino Exchange creates added value for global brands.

Leondrino are issued for each eligible brand and will be named after the associated brand. The supply of each currency is managed by Leondrino Algorithm in combination with a dedicated monetary board and based on a brand-specific monetary policy. The branded Leondrino will be used as a medium for exchange of goods and services and will be interchangeable with fiat currencies.

The goal of Leondrino Inc. is to become the most trusted issuer of private branded currencies.

https://www.leondrino.com
Site Notice: https://www.leondrino.com/site-notice

name: Parlamind
about: parlamind ist eine Künstliche Intelligenz (KI) für den Kundenservice. Basierend auf neuesten Forschungsansätzen des Natural Language Processing und Machine Learning sowie State-of-the-Art Cloud-Software schafft das parlamind Team eine KI der nächsten Generation. parlamind wird eingehende Kundenkommunikation analysieren, vorverarbeiten und autonom beantworten und gliedert sich nahtlos als Teammitglied in den Kundenservice ein.

name: Freework
about: The next generation agency app. Freework helps teams to ship better projects from start to finish.

name: Bikoshu
about:
Bikoshu is an hyper local market place that enables its users to shop locally. Targets to expand rapidly throughout Turkey and abroad. Aims to offer its customers a practical and entertaining experience for local shopping and dining.

Bikoshu has been nomited finalist in BigBang 2017 for Istanbul Technical University Incubation programme among 10.000+ startup projects. Bikoshu has also won prizes from IngBank and EnergySa in BigBang 2017. Bikoshu was also among top 100 Startups 2017 held by Capital Businees Monthly Magazine.

name: Impak Finance
about:
Notre mission est d’aider le secteur financier à faire des choix plus durables grâce à des évaluations allant au-delà des critères ESG et comprenant à la fois les impacts négatifs et positifs de leurs actifs, cotés et non-cotés.

Agence leader de la notation d’impact basée sur une clientèle d’investisseurs, impak propose des données sociales et environnementales transparentes, comparables et mesurables, augmentées par l’intelligence humaine. Nous œuvrons pour que les gestionnaires de capitaux intègrent ces données dans leurs processus décisionnels afin de leur permettre de financer une économie véritablement capable de relever les défis sociaux et environnementaux actuels. Notre offre convient aux investisseurs institutionnels, aux services bancaires et d’investissement, aux gestionnaires d’actifs, de patrimoine et de capital-investissement, aux créateurs et gestionnaires de fonds indiciels cotés ainsi qu’aux services d’investissement responsable. 

Le Score impakMC et le bilan d’impact ont été développés par impak et sont issus de notre méthodologie basée sur les Objectifs de développement durable des Nations Unies et l’Impact Management Project. Au cœur de notre solution, ces deux éléments permettent une contextualisation de la donnée, une analyse suivant les principes de la double matérialité ainsi qu’une évaluation de son alignement aux nouvelles réglementations, grâce à nos modules personnalisés, tels que Taxonomie européenne, SFDR et Stratégie Climat.

Par exemple, nos bilans d’impact offrent à nos clients et partenaires de mieux gérer leurs risques internes et externes, et d’identifier les opportunités à impact positif, essentiels pour avoir une perspective à long terme sur les changements climatiques et l’impact alpha. 

Nous sommes la 2e génération d’agences de notation extra-financière, celle qui a appris des erreurs de la 1re génération de notation ESG pour réaliser un vrai changement de paradigme.

Visitez https://www.impakfinance.com/
