name: asgoodasnew
about:
asgoodasnew wurde 2008 gegründet und hat seinen Sitz in Deutschland. Das Unternehmen ist der europäische Pionier der Kreislaufwirtschaft für Hightech-Produkte im Bereich der Unterhaltungselektronik wie Smartphones, Tablets, MacBooks & iMacs, Kameras & Objektive, Smartwatches und andere hochwertige Geräte. Mit Büros in Berlin und Frankfurt (Oder) deckt das Unternehmen die gesamte Wertschöpfungskette des europäischen Re-Commerce-Marktes ab. Durch seine eigenen Plattformen für Beschaffung, Aufarbeitung und Verkauf hat asgoodasnew ein einzigartiges vertikales Geschäftsmodell mit umfassendem technischen Know-how und direktem Zugang zu Millionen von Endverbrauchern entwickelt. Mehr als 1.000.000 Kunden in ganz Europa haben bisher dank asgoodasnew bereits Geld beim Kauf eines umfassend geprüften und überholten Geräts gespart oder eine Weiterverwendung ihres bisherigen Geräts ermöglicht und somit erfolgreich ihren ökologischen Fußabdruck verbessert.


Founded in 2008 and based in Germany, asgoodasnew is a European circular economy pioneer for premium consumer electronics products, such as smartphones, tablets, MacBooks & iMacs, cameras & lenses, smartwatches and other valuable gadgets. Working from offices in Berlin and Frankfurt (Oder), the company covers the entire value chain of the European re-commerce market. Through its own sourcing, operations, and sales platforms, asgoodasnew has developed a unique vertical business model with extensive technical know-how and direct access to millions of end consumers. To date, asgoodasnew has helped over 1,000,000 customers throughout Europe to impact their ecological footprint by finding a new home for their preloved gadgets or helping them purchase a fully tested, refurbished device.

name: Qnips
about:
We at qnips help commercial food service operators to improve their consumer experiences at each operational location. We do this by enabling modern online and mobile communication channels.  

The qnips system combines features such as online pre-ordering, mobile payment, customer loyalty and content management into a modular solution for app, web and digital signage. As an interface to various merchandise management systems and POS systems, the qnips platform can be flexibly adapted to the needs of our customers. 

We believe that customised services and usability are the key for our clients to increase customer satisfaction, identify new revenue streams and to optimise resource allocation. 

We love what we do, and our passion is proven in the value we create for our global clients and their customers. 

Let’s get in touch!

name: bonusbox
about:
bonusbox is the leading loyalty platform used by over 3 000 partner merchants. Our technology helps merchants to grow their business and convert visitors into loyal customers.
 
The backbone of our technology displays our comprehensive data analysis algorithms allowing merchants to individually target and incentivize customers, thereby generating mutual benefits for merchants and customers alike.
 
Today, more than 4 million online shoppers are registered on bonusbox, making it the fastest growing loyalty program in its core markets.

bonusbox has offices in Berlin, New York and São Paulo and is backed by several venture capital investors and industry experts.

For more information, feel free to check-out our website at: http://bonusbox.me/

name: MyLorry
about:
Einer für alle: Food Express ist Deutschlands erster unabhängiger Lieferservice, der Gastronomen jeder Art einen einzigartigen Service anbietet. Anstatt eigene Fahrer für die Auslieferung ihrer Speisen anzustellen, können Restaurants einfach und flexibel einen Fahrer buchen – je nach Auftragslage. Die Food Express-Fahrer sind in der gesamten Stadt unterwegs und erhalten ihre Aufträge direkt aufs Smartphone. Durch die automatische Routenführung ist ein effizienter und zuverlässiger Service garantiert.

Mehr Infos unter www.food-express.com

name: Finanzen.net
about:
Unter dem Dach der finanzen.net GmbH findet sich heute ein breites Portfolio an Online Portalen und mobilen Angeboten wieder. Unser Kernprodukt www.finanzen.net ist Deutschlands größtes und am schnellsten wachsendes Börsenportal. Mehr als 4 Millionen Unique User (AGOF digital 05/19), 31,5 Millionen Visits und 202,8 Millionen Page Impressions (IVW 05/19) spiegeln unseren Erfolg.

finanzen.net vereint tagesaktuelle Daten zu den Entwicklungen am Finanzmarkt mit Realtime­Push­Kursen zu Indizes, Rohstoffen und Devisen sowie Informationen zu Aktien, Unternehmen, Zertifikaten, Fonds und zur Konjunktur. Interaktive Tools zur Chartanalyse, Musterdepots und persönliche Nachrichtenseiten machen das Angebot individualisierbar.

Neben der deutschen Plattform betreiben wir Finanz– und Börsenportale in der Schweiz, in Österreich, Russland, den Niederlanden, Frankreich sowie in den USA. Darüber hinaus stellen wir unseren Nutzern eine Vielzahl mobiler Angebote zur Verfügung.

Um den Erfolg unserer Finanzprodukte sicherzustellen, setzen wir nicht nur auf innovative Inhalte, sondern stellen darüber hinaus einen sehr hohen Anspruch an die bei uns zum Einsatz kommende Technologie. Diese erlaubt es uns beispielsweise, mehrere Zehntausend User gleichzeitig mit Realtime­Pushkursen zu versorgen.

Im Januar 2016 wurde das Produktspektrum von finanzen.net um ein Brokerage Angebot erweitert. Damit ist es den Usern von finanzen.net möglich, direkt aus der Informationswelt heraus Wertpapiere zu handeln.

name: Lottohelden
about: Bei Lottohelden.de haben wir neben Lotto nur eines im Kopf – Dich als Kunden. Daher ermöglichen wir Dir die Spielscheinabgabe für staatliche Lotterien: Lotto 6 aus 49, EuroJackpot und die GlücksSpirale nicht nur sehr einfach, sondern auch besonders preiswert. Egal, für welches Lotto-Produkt Du Dich entscheidest und wie lange Dein Lottoschein läuft: bei uns bekommst Du immer den besten Preis für Deinen Spieltipp. Günstiger kannst Du nirgendwo gewinnen!

name: Monoqi
about:
MONOQI is the online destination for hand-picked design. Founded in 2012 by Simon Fabich and Felix Schlegel and now led by Managing Director Niels Nüssler, the Berlin-based company curates collections of hard-to-find and limited edition design products, making them available on monoqi.com, monoqi.co.uk, and monoqi.ch. Now operating with a staff of more than 100 employees, MONOQI's international scouting team searches the globe for the best contemporary design, making strong selections for the company's growing customer base.

We are a multinational, enthusiastic, and creative team based in the heart of Berlin with a unified vision for changing the design industry.

name: Caseable
about:
caseable is an international company with offices in Berlin, Brooklyn and Lauterbach. We produce hand-crafted phone cases, laptop bags, e-reader and tablet cases. With our customized products, we not only make people in over 30 countries happy, but also work together with partners like QVC and Amazon. Our international team of 30 employees was able to make over one million customers happy in the last couple of years.

caseable stands for creative, urban lifestyle and tries to make the unique ideas and dreams of its customers come true. Our in-house artists have created over 1,000 different designs to give each case an original touch.

With our entertaining, simple and user-friendly design tool, we enable our customers to give their selected product a personal touch and upload pictures and text. With caseable, customers can turn their device into a unique piece of art. 

caseable works closely with partners and manufactures to constantly expand the product portfolio. The main channels are caseable.com, online and offline retail, marketplaces, (broadcast) vouchers and our checkout-integration system “caseable Interface”. Main partners include Amazon, Sony, QVC, T-Mobile, O2, preisboerse24.

name: Springlane
about:
Springlane fuels people‘s passion for cooking. Started as a shopping club for cooking enthusiasts, Springlane quickly became the leading online retailer in its vertical in Germany, offering more than 20 thousand products from third-party  brands. The combination of a state-of-the-art business intelligence technology and a unique content-driven marketing approach for customer acquisition and retention set the foundation to build integrated consumer brands, which became the company’s strategic focus in 2018. Today, Springlane ranks among the most influential food content websites in Europe and develops and markets products under its own brands Springlane and Burnhard (with sales in all major European countries)

www.springlane.de
www.burnhard.de

Visit our homepage to learn more about our job opportunities www.springlane.de/karriere

name: SymbioCellTech
about: SymbioCellTech (SCT) is an early stage, university spin out, that has developed stem cell-based technology that achieves euglycemia (glucose control) in Type-1 Diabetes, and will soon be adapted for Type-2 Diabetes. The SCT proprietary Neo-Iset therapy, comprising both pancreatic islet and mesenchymal stem cells, can be administered in a simple out-patient procedure resulting in glucose control identical to that of a normal healthy individual. Backed by rigorous NIH, VA and privately funded research and resultant data, SCT has completed pre-clinical trials and is preparing for FDA submission and approval to begin well-designed, controlled, clinical trials treating humans suffering from Type-1 Diabetes. FDA Investigational New Animal Drug (INAD) approval for diabetic companion animals has been approved and canine clinical trials are ongoing with outstanding results and outcomes.

name: Dailypresent
about:
Dailypresent is a mobile brand engagement platform where users discover and share new brands in an interactive gaming environment. Users are offered new daily exciting knowledge quizzes and content around brands and products, and are rewarded with gifts and vouchers.

Dailypresent is the marketing and advertising platform for brands with highest engagement and interaction rates:

- 7 min user interaction per user per day.
- 30 brand interactions per user per day.
- 50% open the app twice a week.
- 50% share brand and product offerings to their networks.

name: Bitplaces
about:
Bitplaces is the technology partner for highly efficient mobile marketing solutions based on relevance and targeted customer outreach.  We are re-thinking mobile marketing and re-inventing the market. We connect online marketing and offline world through relevant and pro-active customer targeting. 

Check www.bitplaces.com for more information

name: Ryzze
about:
RYZZE is a digital brand holding that aims to redefine online commerce for a new generation.

We merge technology with cutting edge creativity and precise financial practices to incubate and scale successful brands globally. Our passion is in to forge new markets and opportunities from innovative thought, accentuating the consumer experience. With 5 brands under our belt we experienced the entrepreneurial roller coaster first hand. Experiences that we want to pass onto the next generation of online-born brands, while committing to investing our creativity, passion and insights to create value.

We see enormous opportunity for a truly seamless retail experience at the nexus of online and offline. With over 15 years of experience, we introduced a vital new platform that provides an optimal blend of resources and support to emerging brands and designers, bringing their creative visions to vivid reality. 

We manage our brand portfolio out of Berlin and Los Angeles, two cities known for their creative energy and global impact.

name: MediNavi
about: MediNavi AG (MDQ) is an Internet company located in Uhdestrasse 2, Starnberg, 82319, Germany, Starnberg, Bavaria, Germany.

name: Vicampo
about:
WE'RE NOT A TYPICAL WINETRADER

We are an online marketplace at which more than 2.500 of the best German and international winemakers offer their products. 

The target audience of wine lovers buying on-site at the wineries is steadily declining. At the same time, online shopping enjoys a growing popularity. For small, traditional businesses, like most German wineries, this is a huge challenge. 

Our digital marketplace concept not only enables many of them – especially small winemakers abroad – to offer their wines nationwide in Germany for the first time. Vicampo.de also helps them to reach a younger, wine-loving target audience outside their region. 

TECHNICAL KNOW-HOW & WINE - AN UNBEATABLE TEAM

Not only does our development and technical operations department work daily on the improvement of our customers' shopping experience. Our five wine experts sample hundreds of wines every month, in order to present the most outstanding products. In short: we put in hard work so that our customers may have easier access to great wines. 

Award winning e-commerce with a heart: Vicampo.de is a team of 150 wine-loving people that wants to excite people in every aspect. Founded in 2012, we are a well-established wine trader that profits from solid funding as well as from the advantages of a young and dynamic startup.

Take your chance to work in an enthusiastic startup and take advantage of a great company culture! Don´t live for work, work to live.


Data policy: https://www.vicampo.de/datenschutzerklaerung

name: Valmano
about:
Since its launch in 2013, VALMANO has become the most popular German online store for Watches & Jewelry. Our target is to become the most successful, most trustworthy and most customer-oriented online jeweler in Europe. Our employees are enthusiastically following this vision by achieving extraordinary service, optimal selection and affordable prices for our clients, without neglecting our responsibility and the aspect of sustainability.

We love accessories and are crazy about opening our customers’ hearts with small and big treasures. That’s why we present them an incredible selection of both renowned and rare watches and jewelry brands, but also a unique collection of precious, yet affordable fine jewelry made from gold, silver and diamonds. Our outstanding service, the fast and reliable delivery and the fantastic prices have reserved us a place in our clients’ hearts.

name: Cuculus
about:
We provide software solutions since 2007 for the energy sector and beyond both as in-house installations or as cloud services. Our products combine cutting edge technology with in-depth market expertise and sector knowledge.

The ZONOS™ IoT Platform, our core solution, enables to control millions of devices and to process their incoming data. This industrial scale IoT Platform is the basis for tailored solutions that we develop in close cooperation with our customers.

Our cooperative working style is reflected in close and longstanding partnering with system integrators, device manufacturers, and software vendors.

Cuculus' origin and current head office in Ilmenau (Thuringia, Germany) is supplemented by a further office in Leipzig (Saxony, Germany) and in Erfurt (Thuringia, Germany) as well as by European sales offices.

Our Partner Network is completed by local and global partners serving a growing customer base worldwide. This network shares our commitment to provide high quality cutting edge solutions to our customers.

Cuculus is actively contributing to addressing the key challenges in the energy markets and has joined different associations to contribute to this.

name: Itembase
about:
Itembase is the leading eCommerce API integration platform that helps eCommerce Solution and Service Providers globally connect with Shopping Carts, Marketplaces and POS Systems to automate their integration and data automation processes, create strategic partnerships and enable their customers with value-added services from other companies in the network.

Itembase works with Solution and Service Providers from verticals like Shipping, Financial Services, Accounting and Tax to Marketing and Aftersales.

Itembase has offices across the US and Europe and host local eCommerce Events across 12 Cities from Bangkok to San Francisco.

name: Crealytics
about:
Crealytics helps retailers and brands activate customer data to master paid media performance and acquire new, loyal customers.  

Through performance advertising and site monetization, we service over 60 worldwide eCommerce brands including ASOS, Urban Outfitters, and Foot Locker. 

In 2020, Crealytics generated 1.7 billion in client revenues. A worldwide team of retail experts supports offices in New York, London and Berlin.

name: Milo Networks
about:
Milo Networks ist eine Plattform für Mobile Point-of-Sale Werbung. Unsere einzigartige Technologie ermöglicht es festzustellen wann sich Kunden im Geschäft befinden und ihnen gezielt Nachrichten auf ihr Smartphone zu senden.

Milo Networks rüstet Händlerfilialen mit einer eigenes entwickelten Präsenz-Technologie aus um festzustellen ob sich Kundem mit ihrem Smartphone im Geschäft befinden. Gleichzeitig liefert Milo Networks an seine Partner-Apps ein SDK aus, welches es ermöglicht die Kunden über Apps im Geschäft anzusprechen. Die somit geschaffene Plattform zum Mobile Point-of-Sale Marketing bietet Milo Networks Markenherstellern und Händlern an um Kunden mit ihren Werbebotschaften am Point-of-Sale zu erreichen.

Der Clou an der Technologie des Unternehmens ist, dass für die Ausrüstung der Händlerfilialen keinerlei neue Hardware benötigt wird. Die enormen Kosten die bei anderen Technologien für Installation und Wartung anfallen werden somit eliminiert. Darüber hinaus funktioniert die Technologie mit ALLEN Smartphones, so dass eine maximalen Kundenreichweite erzielt werden kann.

name: Sharemagazines
about: Die sharemagazines GmbH, ausgezeichnet mit dem Gründerpreis der Universität Oldenburg, wurde 2014 gegründet. Die selbst entwickelte App für iOS und Android bietet Kunden in ausgewählten Locations einen grenzenlosen Zugriff auf über 500 digitale Tageszeitungen und Magazine.

name: Solid Sound Labs
about:
Solid Sound is the music player for a superior audio quality at all volume levels optimized for Apple EarBuds / EarPods and many more headphones. 

Listen to your music as intended by the artists and get back the full richness of sound when listening on lower levels. 

Developed jointly with renowned artists, producers and sound engineers - the people in the know of good sound. 

GET THE SOLID SOUND BENEFITS 

• Balanced sound at all volume levels 
• Patented technology 
• Headphones sound like professional studio devices 
• Tuned by famous artists and sound engineers 
• Prevention of ear fatigue 
• Customized for the individual hearing ability

name: Biofrontera
about: Biofrontera AG is an international biopharmaceutical company specializing in the development and commercialization of a platform of pharmaceutical products for the treatment of dermatological conditions and diseases caused primarily by exposure to sunlight that results in sun damage to the skin. Biofrontera's approved products focus on the treatment in the U.S. and Europe of actinic keratoses, which are skin lesions that can sometimes lead to skin cancer, as well as the treatment of certain forms of basal cell carcinoma in the European Union. American Depositary Shares representing Biofrontera's ordinary shares are listed on the NASDAQ Capital Market under the symbol "BFRA", and Biofrontera's ordinary shares are listed in the Frankfurt Stock Exchange (B8F, ISIN: DE0006046113). Information is also available at www.biofrontera.com.

name: nu3
about:
Do you want to be part of one of Europe's most dynamic and innovative foodtech companies?

About us:
Founded in 2011, nu3 combines diet, taste and health with the target of bringing intelligence and transparency to your nutrition – all this through four product lines: performance line, fit line, smart & organic and health line. 
Thanks to our team of nutrition experts, we offer more than 200 products with high-quality ingredients, optimal nutrients and amazing taste – for your best health and fitness. You can order online via our web shops in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, France, Belgium, Luxembourg and Italy. nu3 products can also be purchased on 6 Amazon sites on over 26 countries and are available at @Coop in Switzerland, @BIPA in Austria and @Monoprix in France and Luxembourg. 

Career:
More than 70 employees from over 10 countries are working in our lovely office in the heart of Berlin. Since 2018 nu3 is part of the Shop Apotheke B.V. group. We all have great ambitions and want to improve nutrition together. 

Are you ready to join our story?

#EmpowerYourBody #BetterMeWithnu3 #FitnessFood #Superfoods #WeightManagement #HealthSupplements

name: crossvertise
about:
crossvertise kombiniert Media-Selbstbuchung und individuelle Mediaberatung auf Augenhöhe.

Die Buchungsplattform crossvertise.com ist die weltweit einzigartige und mehrfach ausgezeichnete Buchungslösung für alle Arten von Werbung, auf der Unternehmen Medien einfach finden, transparent vergleichen und direkt buchen können. Die Lösung richtet sich vor allem an kleine und mittelständische Unternehmen, die somit Werbung über alle Kanäle professionell und bequem buchen und damit ihr Marketing erfolgreicher machen können. crossvertise.com bündelt das komplette Angebot der in Deutschland verfügbaren Werbemedien - von Plakat über Radio, Print Kino und digitalen Medien bis zu TV.

Unter der Mediaagentur-Marke crossadvise (www.crossadvise.com) entwickelt ein Team erfahrener Mediaberater individuelle Media-Strategien und übersetzt diese in wirkungsvolle Werbekampagnen. Regionale und diversifizierte Kampagnen abseits der Standardmedien gehören dabei zum Alltag.
Zu den Kunden zählen auch bekannte Marken wie EASYFITNESS, SEIKO oder Haufe Lexware.

name: Blacklane
about:
Blacklane’s global chauffeur service brings peace of mind to travelers moving through a fast-paced world.

The crew’s dedication to safety, reliability, and smart technology places Blacklane at the forefront of a new era of stress-free travel. Since 2017, the company has been carbon-neutral, combining a five-star guest experience with care for the planet. 

Upgrade your travels on Blacklane’s mobile apps or website.

name: Orderbird AG
about: Über 12.000 Kunden vertrauen bereits auf unsere Kassensysteme. Das iPad-Kassensystem orderbird Pro mit Online-TSE bietet ein elektronisches Kassensystem für Restaurants, Cafés, Bars sowie Foodtrucks. Die iPad-Kasse kann jederzeit und spielend leicht an Deine Wünsche und Vorstellungen angepasst werden. Funkbonieren erlaubt es dem Servicepersonal, die Bestellung drahtlos an die Küche und Tresen zu schicken. Das iPad-Kassensystem liefert jederzeit und von überall mit der Datenzentrale MY orderbird übersichtliche Reports und ermöglicht individuelle detaillierte Analysen. Per W-LAN kommuniziert das Kassensystem mit vorkonfigurierten Bondruckern und Routern. orderbird hat den Vorteil geringer Anschaffungskosten in Verbindung mit einem einfach zu bedienenden Kassensystem. Unsere iPad-Kasse erhält kostenlose technische Updates. Zum Service zählen Telefonsupport, der 24/7 Notfall-Service und das detaillierte Live-Reporting. Du unterliegst keinen Vertragslaufzeiten, keinen versteckten Kosten und keiner Kündigungsfrist. Alles natürlich GoBD- und finanzamtkonform, garantiert auch KassenSichV-konform.

name: Pflege.de
about:
Wir sind pflege.de, Deutschlands führendes Portal für das Wohnen und Leben im Alter. Wir helfen dabei, Hilfs- und Pflegebedürftigen ein möglichst langes und selbstbestimmtes Leben zuhause zu ermöglichen.

pflege.de hat viele spannende Serviceleistungen im Repertoire. Unsere Mitarbeiter aus den Teams Operations & Inside Sales koordinieren z. B. Umbaumaßnahmen für ein barrierefreies Badezimmer oder den Einbau von passenden Treppenlifts. Sie sorgen auch dafür, dass unsere Kunden die für sie notwendigen Hilfsmittel erhalten. Kunden schätzen unser breites Angebot an Informationen, die kostenfreie telefonische Beratung sowie unsere Unterstützung bei der Suche nach konkreten Lösungen und Dienstleistern.

Neben dem für unsere Kunden stets hilfreichen Service-Angebot kann pflege.de als auch als Informations-Plattform im Internet punkten. In den Abteilungen Product & Engineering und Online Marketing arbeiten wir jeden Tag daran, pflege.de praktischer, informativer und attraktiver für den User zu gestalten. Dafür entwickeln wir u.a. nützliche Tools wie den Pflegegradrechner oder unseren Notruflotsen.

Wir sorgen dafür, das pflege.de jährlich von rund 12 Millionen Menschen besucht wird. Damit entwickeln wir uns zum digitalen Marktführer im Bereich Elder Care.

Du willst noch mehr über unser Team oder pflege.de als Arbeitgeber erfahren? Dann besucht gerne unsere Instagram Seite "pflege.de_jobs".
